(3375, '0004000e000edf00', 'CTR-U-AXCE', 'Super Smash Bros.™ Update Ver. 1.1.6', 'USA', 344718180, 'update', '50010000026015', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/263877b2c097eb8eb318b935c631294a37a95f8592a62ef8c58427e7040d0ddd.jpg', 'This is an update for the Super Smash Bros.™ for Nintendo 3DS game. This download does not contain the full version of the title. In order to use this update, you must have the full version of Super Smash Bros.™ for Nintendo 3DS.\n\nUpdate Details:\nUsers will be able to purchase newly added downloadable content.\nAdjustments have also been made to make for a more pleasant gaming experience.\n*Once version 1.1.6 has been installed, local wireless will not work with older versions of the software. Replays created with older versions of the software will not work either.\n*Version 1.1.6 is required for online play.\n', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4dd14200549e9beff84f14dacb0a5b35c4dc41ffb487562f7088ed7d23898410.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/Lk1wQ6X.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/nbSWgZj.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3376, '00040000000d7e00', 'CTR-N-JNUP', 'Steel Diver™: Sub Wars', 'EUR', 205773668, 'eshop', '50010000020194', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c37db79f8562e06af2a5a70c38492057428865195028d9f0ae61edd28bad6bf2.jpg', 'Dive, dive, dive for strategic\nsubaquatic combat! Amass a fleet of\nsubmarines and blow your opponents\nout of the water in Steel Diver: Sub\nWars. Pilot your sub in first-person\nview, with total control over its speed,\ndepth and direction, and use tactics\nand tenacity to win the day!\n<br/><br/>\nIn the purchasable Premium Version,\nunlock and command up to 18 unique\nsubmarines across seven varied\nmissions. Try the first two missions\nand two basic submarines for yourself\nin the Free Version!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1da8eb3ae0aedacca44734509d07753644068fd9f520f127bd1203d26c381d4b.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/agQxu3B.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/9oJW9LR.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3377, '00040000000ec400', 'CTR-P-BZLP', 'The Legend of Zelda™: A Link Between Worlds', 'EUR', 717814628, 'eshop', '50010000017393', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e391564b0a37952c448d711e0759afb6bc5953d770eb17cd6aff21991c703d75.jpg', 'The Legend of Zelda: A Link Between\nWorlds follows on from the story of\nthe 1991 Super NES instalment,\ntelling a new story in the kingdom of\nHyrule. The 3D visuals of\nNintendo 3DS bring a new layer of\ndepth to the game world, allowing\nyou to experience heights like never\nbefore. It might once have been\ndifficult to tell the difference between\nfloor levels, but they are now quite\nclear, lending more realism to the\nbattles and dungeon exploration!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/y6yQBcj.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3378, '00040000000f1e00', 'CTR-N-AGKP', 'Phoenix Wright™: Ace Attorney™ – Dual Destinies', 'EUR', 580561764, 'eshop', '50010000016433', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e18d1cac51dad94291ce01a70b341b1ff4a6f72afad0f74d906c133cdb903314.jpg', 'Phoenix Wright™: Ace Attorney™ -\nDual Destinies sees the return of\ncourtroom hero Phoenix Wright. The\nmuch loved gameplay and features\nfrom previous titles in the Ace\nAttorney™ series are back but for the\nfirst time in stunning 3D graphics,\nbringing the courtroom and characters\nto life and putting players directly in\nthe heart of the action.\n<br/><br/>\n1. More courtroom drama as Apollo\nJustice and new Associate Attorney\nand psychoanalysis expert Athena\nSykes join Phoenix at the Wright\nAnything Agency\n<br/><br/>\n2. Psychoanalyse witnesses to reveal\nthe truth with the brand new Mood\nMatrix feature\n<br/><br/>\n3. Hold it! Present your evidence,\nchallenge the witnesses and\nexperience life as a real Attorney\n<br/><br/>\n4. Stunning dynamic 3D graphics:\nbring the characters and courtroom to\nlife and investigate crime scenes from\nvarious angles to uncover hidden\nclues\n<br/><br/>\n5. Brand new interface and game\nprogression system for fans and\nnewcomers alike', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5c460a589e614a3e9e8dbb663c432be0da6aac862311e619e43a55b5eff4712a.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/n9GKw3s.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/TuzvN7l.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3379, '000400000016e800', 'CTR-N-KP6P', 'PICROSS e6', 'EUR', 24632164, 'eshop', '50010000035635', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e12fdeedcd5625caf2ff0fe2baf79fb2ffc073e80de08090e4b80b843e887b3b.jpg', 'The 6th game in the Picross e series,\nwith a Navigation Feature!\n<br/><br/>\nNew to this title, each puzzle can be\nplayed in either Picross or Mega\nPicross mode!\n<br/><br/>\nEnjoy over 300 puzzles, including\nspecial puzzles.\n<br/><br/>\nYou can also choose the fill\nanimation for the puzzle screen.\n<br/><br/>\nPicross is a "Picture Crossword\nPuzzle Game" where numbers act as\nhints to complete images.\n<br/><br/>\nThe rules are simple and easy to\ngrasp. Anyone can do it!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/DcyHvGY.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3380, '000400000009f100', 'CTR-P-AFEP', 'Fire Emblem™: Awakening', 'EUR', 1152424804, 'eshop', '50010000013215', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f4843691f1859a8f5a3358a6215ac71bd6dcc8350dd9c3f37a6c4d7d47592bdd.jpg', 'Turn-based combat comes alive like\nnever before on Nintendo 3DS! Fire\nEmblem: Awakening continues the\ntraditions of the classic series while\nenhancing the experience with 3D\nvisuals and making the strategic\ngameplay more accessible for\nnewcomers. Players lead forces\nacross maps, fighting enemies and\nachieving goals across a fantasy\nworld rich with character.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4913aa281d6195d5b10bb0be788846669a27ee92dc47be7d362b7ba97a86c15e.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/IHiAAtd.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ZYhF3EL.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3381, '0004000000086400', 'CTR-P-EGDP', 'Animal Crossing™: New Leaf', 'EUR', 819690340, 'eshop', '50010000014210', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b691596a4011778eda12e8c1c0b991a81e4eff12a867af0e36e8d63bdf80dca5.jpg', 'An exciting new life awaits you in\nAnimal Crossing: New Leaf!\n<br/><br/>\nHave you ever wanted a new home, a\nnew job, a new life? There''s one\nwaiting for you in Animal Crossing:\nNew Leaf! Move to a new town and\nbecome mayor, then live life at your\nown pace; make new friends, have all\nkinds of experiences and create the\ntown of your dreams!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/85e6b71d60465927769f437a515a350beea81b498c80276c7b24f8ea280dbed1.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/BHOKYJx.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ocwhID9.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3382, '00040000000ee000', 'CTR-P-AXCP', 'Super Smash Bros.™ for Nintendo 3DS', 'EUR', 1437735780, 'eshop', '50010000024975', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e4a8fdb5ea32aa57bb89252dd7f006982ad9f04b43010ad2a5cf1382fe2b166c.jpg', 'Famous names from favourite\nNintendo franchises and guest\ncharacters come together in a\nportable fighter filled with spectacular\naction. With unique modes, online\nmultiplayer, the ability to customise\nyour fighter and the series’ biggest\nroster of playable fighters ever, Super\nSmash Bros. for Nintendo 3DS is truly\na clash for the ages!\n<br/><br/>\nThe basics of Super Smash Bros. are\nsimple. Use your chosen character’s\nunique attacks and special moves to\ndamage your opponent, then hit ‘em\nwith a smash attack to send them\nflying off the stage! The higher your\nopponent’s damage – represented as a\npercentage – the farther they’ll fly\nwhen launched, so pummel away until\nyou see them steaming, then unleash\nyour strongest smash attack and\nwatch your target skyrocket off the\nstage! Take on nearby challengers in\nlocal multiplayer, or bring the battle\nto faraway friends and foes in online\nmatches.\n<br/><br/>\nVisit amiibo.nintendo.eu for\ncompatible amiibo™ and the latest\ninformation. To use amiibo on\nNintendo 3DS, Nintendo 3DS XL and\nNintendo 2DS systems a\nNintendo 3DS NFC Reader/Writer is\nrequired.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/81ff9df6c1460e872e9a7c1143c333f84518b2f39b2a407753b328399d1362cb.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/qL9yjSW.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/nNW7KLw.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3383, '0004000000126100', 'CTR-P-BFGP', 'Monster Hunter™ 4 Ultimate', 'EUR', 2734750564, 'eshop', '50010000028495', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/04e3e2132dc84b3f6a534f6e2482cf5382bd32ca717a78ac742c6366039c922c.jpg', 'A demo is available for this software!\nTo download it, touch the "Monster\nHunter 4 Ultimate Demo" link in the\n"related searches" section near the\nbottom of this page to be guided\ntowards the separate demo game\npage.\n<br/><br/>\nTake up your weapons, greet your\nfellow adventurers and head for the\nfield to battle huge, fearsome\ncreatures in Monster Hunter 4\nUltimate on Nintendo 3DS and 2DS!\nWith full online and local co-op play,\nthe fight for the land looms large in\nthis sprawling action RPG!\n<br/><br/>\nYour first steps in a deep,\nnarrative-led adventure see you join a\ntravelling caravan as its designated\nhunter, sworn to protect the people\nfrom wild monsters that roam the\nland. Choose your quarry, hunt it\ndown, and despatch it with a\ncombination of weapons and tactics.\nSetting out, you’ll discover a plethora\nof new content, including a wealth of\narms and armour to forge and\ncustomise, and scores of\nundiscovered beasts to hunt. Terrain is\nmuch more vertical than before –\nassault your enemy from above, and\ndeliver a flurry of blows while holding\non for dear life!\n<br/><br/>\nMake no mistake – Monster Hunter 4\nUltimate is a strategic, expansive and\nepic action RPG just waiting to be\ndiscovered. Glory awaits!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ac4fe889f8e953860ae57b57684760e37db02411e9d8e59f35a3fa56626130e1.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/KDYiNUN.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/GscnS6W.jpg', 1, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3384, '00040000000b0f00', 'CTR-N-JYTE', 'YouTube', 'USA', 8227636, 'eshop', '50010000017873', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d875936f1c9f4127b5b2d57fb5eb0df04dd65d7c3b30685c63108b394873fe94.jpg', 'Account or subscription may be required from provider.\n<BR><BR>\nDiscover and watch your favorite videos and channels on YouTube. From comedy to music to sports, find the channels you love. Watching a video is just the beginning when you can like, share, comment, and more. By signing in to YouTube, you can easily access your subscribed channels, playlists, and favorites.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d5eddba93ab6600dbcd28029c8d9582b71047de21d7fb848b0f5a8bbe35f202e.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/dsMJ4i1.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/7a8Iej9.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
