(3393, '0004000e0008c400', 'CTR-U-EC6P', 'Tomodachi Life™: Update', 'EUR', 45988708, 'update', '50010000023037', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5c34b911e95e3b4a9c692d4c8fc86befb72d8011b579c0aa319082d76b46fd27.jpg', 'An update for "Tomodachi Life™" is\nnow available from Nintendo eShop.\n<br/><br/>\nAll customers who own a copy of\n“Tomodachi Life™” should download\nthe update.\n<br/><br/>\nThis will update the software to\nVersion 2.0 with the following\namendments: \n<br/><br/>\n- Various bugs have been fixed in\norder to provide a smoother gaming\nexperience.\n- Dutch language is now available.\n<br/><br/>\n• Once the update has been\ndownloaded, it will be installed\nautomatically.\n<br/><br/>\nWe apologize for any inconvenience\ncaused, and recommend downloading\nthis update to ensure a smooth game\nexperience.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/483d073a3116857d8090d6aa5ef906cce0862613b3c93b35e8fe83a32937d429.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/cCtwbjW.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ksd9kt2.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
