(3426, '000400000014a300', 'CTR-N-NAHA', 'Pokémon Omega Ruby and Alpha Sapphire Special Demo', 'ALL', 251972452, 'eshop', '50010000026335', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/232a4d83080fe6d0878a02ad360436370db3f4a0682e7e75f862edc502461918.jpg', 'Become a Pokémon Trainer and catch, battle and trade amazing creatures called Pokémon! In this Special Demo Version, you''ll experience exclusive scenarios you won''t find anywhere else! You can get a head start on your adventure in the Hoenn region where you’ll encounter Pokémon with new Mega Evolutions! You’ll even be able to transfer the Pokémon Glalie, who now Mega Evolves, into your full version of Pokémon Omega Ruby or Pokémon Alpha Sapphire! In addition, certain items that you get while playing the Special Demo Version can be transferred to the full game version upon purchase!\nWhether this is your first time playing a Pokémon game, or you''re an experienced Pokémon Trainer, this Special Demo Version has something for you!\n<br><br>\nPlease note, this is the same Special Demo Version that was previously given out by download code. If you have already received the Special Demo Version by download code, you do not need to download this.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/806eff4b527903587e8b806891d72131dd4197572b3516aa229b3408ba3c1c5c.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/c8htWxW.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/T6zVr0X.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3427, '0004000e0011c400', 'CTR-U-ECRA', 'Pokémon™ Omega Ruby: Update', 'ALL', 35027764, 'update', '50010000025576', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bc335db9848247d0a24ede0e87f6a2893dadfc01d2929cf17b42dffe2bd228fc.jpg', 'An update is available for Pokémon Omega Ruby.  \n<br><br>\nUpdate Details:\nAdjustments have been made for an improved gaming experience.\n<br><br>\nUsers will need to download the software update prior to using the following online features:\nConnecting to the Internet using the Player Search System\nUsing Wonder Trade\nUsing Game Sync\nConnecting to the Global Trade Station\nRedeeming a Mystery Gift\n<br><br>\nThis update also includes all previous updates.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e7538010948e55a8148fb20c6e6f1ec547bf0facc3d48597b664d00a4344dc16.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/Om6AgJB.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/yLYGT5D.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3428, '0004000000164600', 'CTR-N-KCFA', 'Pokémon Rumble World', 'ALL', 108231524, 'eshop', '50010000032056', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c98a88ff15e8a7d272d57aff123554408185e7ec778f1f5dd5f4f52ed5a2448f.jpg', 'Download the latest version of Pokémon Rumble World for your Nintendo 3DS system today! Once you do, you’ll be able to visit a new area, get bonus items, and more! First, take a ride on the newly added Lucky Balloon. It will take you to a mysterious area called Changing Land, where you’re more likely to meet Pokémon you haven’t yet caught. The Lucky Balloon will be added to the hot-air balloons available in the shop. It’s free, but you’ll need to have reached Adventure Rank 40 to ride on it.\n<br><br>\nReceive 100 Poké Diamonds when you update your game! Enter the following password into your game to receive 100 Poké Diamonds. You have to reach Adventure Rank 4 before you can enter the password.\nPassword: 48213190\n<br><br>\nThe Pokémon™ Rumble World game is an action-packed adventure that’s free to download. Battle and collect over 700 Toy Pokémon, including some that Mega Evolve! You’ll travel on your hot-air balloon and battle in 18 different areas with more than 80 stages. The more Toy Pokémon you collect, the more ways you have to defeat Toy Pokémon you’re facing.\n<br><br>\nEach Toy Pokémon has a type, and each type has strengths and weaknesses—use them to your advantage to defeat your foes quickly. There are also rare Toy Pokémon to find and collect! Even Primal Groudon and Primal Kyogre appear as Toy Pokémon.\n<br><br>\nDress up your Mii™ character in cool outfits, and then share it with your friends! \nBy using Poké Diamonds, players can obtain items that help them progress through the game at their own pace.\n<br><br>\nPoké Diamonds can be purchased from an in-game shop with funds from your Nintendo eShop account. You also earn some Poké Diamonds in-game. Purchasing Poké Diamonds isn’t required to play or enjoy this title.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/qMUQCD3.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3429, '000400000015d800', 'CTR-N-KFLE', 'IRONFALL Invasion', 'USA', 505662308, 'eshop', '50010000031216', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1cbd2fbe71d8c0f2fcce9e8e33ec60ce9ebbb2dacfb1453c37281daf8dc18b6e.jpg', 'IronFall: Invasion is a thrilling third-person shooter. Equipped with an arsenal of destructive weapons, take cover and repel an invasion of Alien Robots.\n<br><br>\nIronFall: Invasion is divided into two separate modes, which can be tried for free and purchased separately!\n<br><br>\nThe "Campaign" mode is a single-player adventure, which will have you travel from various locations over 11 levels.\n<br><br>\nThe "Multiplayer" mode allows up to 6 players to join locally or online for competitive battles in 6 different arenas.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/HDuftEZ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3430, '0004000e00126300', 'CTR-U-BFGE', 'Monster Hunter™ 4 Ultimate Update Ver. 1.1', 'USA', 48122724, 'update', '50010000030695', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/074d0f1e9b7d18f5c1a55972b6579a2e30f818abe35fe61a640646e17f28c77b.jpg', 'This is update data required to access the "Gift Area" in "Monster Hunter 4 Ultimate", where you can download free items.\n<br><br>\nIn the event that update data (ver. 1.1) hasn''t been downloaded, the "Gift Area" in "Monster Hunter 4 Ultimate" cannot be accessed.\n<br><br>\nAfter the download, talk to the housekeeper character in your house, select "Downloadable Content", and then "Gift Area". We ask that you please download update data (ver. 1.1), and apologize for any inconvenience.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ff4ce677af94ac393cd4664517d0b1222d58c3c341e7a7e046828c2833f762da.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/rCsb08Y.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/0KF2IQW.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3431, '0004000e00167700', 'CTR-U-AYWE', 'YO-KAI WATCH™ Update Ver. 1.2', 'USA', 527854436, 'update', '50010000038335', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/13f452fe08f5cbdd940d7934f2aec11a85930bc8f782192afdff9e317798a309.jpg', 'This is an update for the YO-KAI WATCH™ game. This download does not contain the full version of the title. In order to use this update, you must have the full version of YO-KAI WATCH™.\n<br><br>\nYou can play your YO-KAI WATCH in Spanish or French if you download this patch from Nintendo eShop. Install the patch on your system, and set your system language to Spanish or French. It will change in-game text and character voices to your set language. *This patch is not compatible with YO-KAI WATCH eShop demo.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3eba02f659a6d3dfcc97d1afced618dbbe50f2afc8f620f6794e0ed35105a4eb.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/WSMZz56.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/jo4RwUW.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3432, '0004000e00176f00', 'CTR-U-EA3E', 'The Legend of Zelda™: Tri Force Heroes Update', 'USA', 143268708, 'update', '50010000038695', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f31cafeedd34d35d19b465b9a6241c9c0642efc1d4818a466f7e6d6776c2b8bb.jpg', 'This is an update for the The Legend of Zelda™: Tri Force Heroes game. This download does not contain the full version of the title. In order to use this update, you must have the full version of The Legend of Zelda™: Tri Force Heroes.\n<br><br>\nUpdate details:\nA new “Hero Points” feature has been added to enhance the game. Collect enough hero points and you can trade them for materials you need or even power up a certain outfit.\n', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7ef04f805115825c0f685ff6e4c9e279d52923a69549ea6324d235510f4c4702.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/MYJQdkK.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/rGP3t4Y.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3433, '0004000000167700', 'CTR-N-AYWE', 'YO-KAI WATCH™', 'USA', 869317476, 'eshop', '50010000036595', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ce523afe8daaf36bd0830d1028282d95671b52573f043dd3d32a3108f9a4e71f.jpg', 'YO-KAI WATCH was a cultural phenomenon in Japan, selling millions of games and capturing the hearts of a nation. Now you can experience the international sensation for yourself with the YO-KAI WATCH demo, available for download now.\n<br><br>\nHundreds of sometimes spooky, sometimes cute, and usually mischievous Yo-kai secretly inhabit our world. From flaming feline Yo-kai to three-headed bosses, they’re hiding everywhere! Discover these secret tricksters to battle and befriend them. Then turn them into a team on your Yo-kai Watch and take down troublemaking Yo-kai to help people in need.\n<br><br>\nWith your Yo-kai Watch, you can see Yo-kai that are normally invisible hiding everywhere in your town, flying around trees, and hiding under vending machines.  Many of them are causing trouble in the daily lives of residents of your town! Now you’ll need to assemble a team of six Yo-kai on your Yo-kai Watch and call upon them when you need their help.  Every Yo-kai has a unique personality and abilities, so it will take strategy to form the right team and gain the upper hand against troublesome Yo-kai.  Support your team in real-time battles by initiating Soultimate moves and purifying Yo-kai with quick touch-based movements.\n<br><br>\nGame Informer: “…great sense of humor, unique combat, and collection hooks that sink in quickly.”\n<br><br>\nGame Informer: “Yo-kai Watch is a big seller in Japan, and it’s easy to see why.” (Score: 8.5/10)\n<br><br>\nDestructoid: “…falling in love with it.”\n<br><br>\nDestructoid: “incredibly charming and worth playing…” (Score: 8.5/10)\n<br><br>\nGameZone: “…great visuals and voiceovers.”\n<br><br>\nGameZone: “It''s a fantastic game…” \n<br><br>\nNintendo World Report: “Level-5 has successfully created a large, complex world filled with so much unique material and style...” (Score: 9/10)\n<br><br>\nUSGamer: “There''s a ton of things to do packed inside the dense world…”\n<br><br>\nUSGamer: “…looks fantastic.” (Score: 4/5)\n<br><br>\nExaminer: “… hard to put down RPG…”\n<br><br>\nYou can play your YO-KAI WATCH in Spanish or French if you download the patch from Nintendo eShop. Install the patch on your system, and set your system language to Spanish or French. It will change in-game text and character voices to your set language. *The patch is not compatible with YO-KAI WATCH eShop demo.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/cOFYSNd.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3434, '0004000000125600', 'CTR-P-AJRP', 'The Legend of Zelda™: Majora''s Mask 3D', 'EUR', 676199268, 'eshop', '50010000027775', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/cbaa982811e625a6107d3ec9a81d55c5e12d727b9c6e74bcd30033f58aa000d9.jpg', 'Race against time and save a\ndoomed land in The Legend of Zelda:\nMajora’s Mask 3D. In this full\nremaster of the fan favourite\nNintendo 64 title, which includes\nrefreshed visuals and features while\nremaining true to the original title,\nembark on an engrossing, spooky\nquest through a mysterious world.\n<br/><br/>\nJoin Link as he seeks to save the\nland of Termina from a crushing fate –\nin three days, the moon will crash\ndown and destroy everything and\neveryone in its path. By using the\nmagical Ocarina of Time, Link must\ntravel through time, re-living the same\nthree days over and over again, to\nprevent calamity and save the world.\nExplore every corner of Termina and\ndelve into dangerous dungeons,\nacross treacherous mountains,\npoisonous swamps, an eerie desert\nand a vast ocean, on your mission to\nstop Skull Kid!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b5d64634430889ed66a3116279dbf092095fd373fa02046bc8d77e4afca8619f.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/FSTTLtQ.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/KbcrtsE.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3435, '0004000000054000', 'CTR-N-AREE', 'Super Mario™ 3D Land', 'USA', 303446884, 'eshop', '50010000007541', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9e6a7b1c499a17710074976e63f849dc33599face764e5fc96bafc3068f736be.jpg', 'Platforming with serious depth! With the 3D visuals of Super Mario 3D Land, players can see exactly where floating blocks and flying Paragoombas are, so that they can jump and stomp with the precision of the pros. Expert gamers will appreciate\nthe way 3D graphics reveal the true challenge of the levels, so that they can focus on nailing the perfect jump or shaving precious seconds off their speed runs, while new players will find that 3D makes platforming simple to grasp and satisfying to master.\n<br><br>\nTry on Mario''s Tanooki Suit, and put some spring in your step! While longtime gamers will delight in using Tanooki Mario''s tail-spin attack to sweep enemies off their feet and fluttering through the air to land super-long jumps, a new generation will learn\nwhat makes this classic suit a fan favorite. But even seasoned players will be in for a surprise—Mario''s enemies may be sporting the familiar Tanooki tail too!\n<br><br>\nMario at his very best! Mario™ returns to his roots in his first 3D platforming adventure designed exclusively for a handheld system. From the frantic\nrace-against-the-clock dash through the Mushroom Kingdom to that final leap to grab the top of the flagpole, this eye-popping addition to the Super Mario™ series combines everything that\nmakes Mario great from one generation\nto the next.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/KrUcl8E.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3436, '0004000000137f00', 'CTR-P-BMAP', 'New SUPER MARIO BROS. 2: Special Edition', 'EUR', 359533412, 'eshop', '50010000022256', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3437, '0004000000126300', 'CTR-N-BFGE', 'Monster Hunter™ 4 Ultimate', 'USA', 2726263652, 'eshop', '50010000028535', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/22c6794f065df4bf310b4a4758c1614f25a3bbda013bfd2931e4035d3622e337.jpg', 'Offers in-game purchases\n<br><br>\nCheck out the theme inspired by this game in the Theme Shop. Just tap the icon in the upper left corner of your Nintendo 3DS HOME Menu to get started.\n<br><br>\nIn Monster Hunter™ 4 Ultimate you''ll embark on an epic journey, traveling across a vast world hunting larger than life beasts as you search for the source of a mysterious virus. Travel with a caravan of fellow hunters and merchants as you make your way across multiple locales, each with its own unique look and feel in the largest Monster Hunter™ ever!\n<br><br>\nThis grand adventure will include hundreds of quests to take on a variety of extraordinary creatures that yield valuable resources used for weapons and equipment. Choose from 14 different weapon classes such as the Dual Blades or Gunlance, or try one of the new weapons classes, the agile Insect Glaive or the devastating Charge Blade. Craft hundreds of different armor sets, each with their own unique skills and stats as you become the ultimate hunter.\n<br><br>\nBut don''t hunt alone! Form a party with up to three other friends locally or via the Nintendo Network to take on the fiercest foes together.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/MwTFkj7.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3438, '0004000000030800', 'CTR-N-AMKE', 'Mario Kart™ 7', 'USA', 665119636, 'eshop', '50010000007703', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7b08b94ea2d841adb536d708f8104d152d8e354af0604e5d41ccabc54e7491ae.jpg', 'A New Dimension of Kart Racing!\n<br><br>\nThe newest installment of the fan-favorite Mario Kart™ franchise brings Mushroom Kingdom racing fun into glorious 3D. For the first time, drivers explore new competitive kart possibilities, such as soaring through the skies or plunging into the depths of the sea. New courses, strategic new\nabilities and customizable karts bring the racing excitement to new heights.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Sqqe5jk.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3439, '0004000000030700', 'CTR-N-AMKP', 'Mario Kart™ 7', 'EUR', 669473684, 'eshop', '50010000007914', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/329d0b6d457e6024e69ac208d0a61718c1a44ce1bad8bc994935743963358782.jpg', 'Mario Kart 7 brings Mushroom\nKingdom racing fun into glorious 3D -\nand that''s just the beginning, as new\ncourses, strategic new abilities and\ncustomisable karts bring the racing\nexcitement to new heights.<br>\n<br>\nUp to 8 players can enjoy local\nwireless races or race together online.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/397c565cffd5e8b2d7d5fa78e1a1b88158965cd44ef09e140da4be27f7f173b5.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Mqw3sid.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/lEjKSgd.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47');
