(3445, '0004000000051800', 'CTR-N-JFRP', 'Nintendo Letter Box', 'EUR', 13015908, 'eshop', '50010000008422', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ea9436998e843aadda6de04a069d6437f28433dc906f60a00546c816717c107a.jpg', 'Share messages and more with your\nfriends in a fun, new way with\nNintendo Letter Box.\n<br/><br/>\nThis free software allows you to send\nand receive messages via StreetPass.\nWrite a greeting or make a drawing, in\n2D or 3D, and your friends will see\nthe message animate as if it is being\nre-created before their eyes!\n<br/><br/>\nYou can also share photos and sound\neffects from your Nintendo 3DS, and\nyou can even use Play Coins to\nunlock new stationery designs.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b365e9cc5f40011b434132c439794335c2a221cd3ae371769f5566559cccafdf.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/HuHbTYv.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/LQtImtK.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3446, '0004000000076800', 'CTR-N-PAHP', 'Mario vs. Donkey Kong™', 'EUR', 18512740, 'eshop', '50010000008261', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/dbc03396aea4a278bf1ce19ea9bf4372be919b37831657b66875dcbfcb33b592.jpg', 'Mario vs. Donkey Kong pits the\nNintendo mascot against his old\nadversary in a unique twist on the\nplatform genre that made them\nfamous.<br>\n<br>\nThe mischievous ape has swiped all\nthe Mini-Mario toys from Mario’s toy\nfactory, so it’s up to you to rescue\nthem from across six inventive worlds.\nYou’ll be scratching your head at\npuzzles in some stages, before leading\nMini-Marios to safety in the next; each\nworld ending with a showdown against\nDonkey Kong himself!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f691d1882b6466583cf10cbbb0a4c0fd271474e0fe11c3638a2756f51fa76bc3.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/zulyv5Z.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/jXIKgOL.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3447, '000400000006ef00', 'CTR-N-TADP', 'Metroid™', 'EUR', 5172068, 'eshop', '50010000007308', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/155c215500a1bbdca6482dc193991f680bcf16a94e0248e0b3534e16d27d0ed2.jpg', 'Metroids – the most dangerous\ncreatures in the galaxy – have fallen\ninto the hands of Space Pirates! As\nbounty hunter Samus Aran, battle\nthrough the depths of planet Zebes to\ntake out the pirates’ leader Mother\nBrain and restore peace to the galaxy.\n\nThe original NES classic Metroid\nintroduced gamers to a unique mix of\naction and exploration that has\nbecome the series’ trademark. Use\nSamus’s Morph Ball ability to search\nevery nook and cranny, and uncover\npower-ups like the Ice Beam, Varia\nSuit and Screw Attack.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4f9422266ad04605c876a02726b7ed0e9e391cfb0d1c41575d61b17db0776786.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/h8NdQWr.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/pPrmnaa.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3448, '0004000000072700', 'CTR-N-JMFP', 'Mighty Switch Force!', 'EUR', 235682660, 'eshop', '50010000008101', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c63fa04b1b6eb6004799db3dc8d89f73e4d25622ea2e33dd8b5ccd3ccfd8737a.jpg', 'Meet Patricia Wagon, cybernetic\npolice officer on a mission to put the\nHooligan Sisters back behind bars. By\nactivating her Siren Helmet, Patricia\ncan shift the machine matrix of Planet\nLand, altering the world around her.\nUse your wits and trusty Pellet Gun to\nblow crime away!\n\nUpdate includes: \n- 5 bonus levels\n- enhanced 3D graphics\n- quick-retry feature', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/O1iemGV.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3449, '0004000000063000', 'CTR-N-JE5Z', 'Luigi''s Mansion 2 E3 Video', 'EUR', 26874164, 'eshop', '50010000007015', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4d4ea7b85d92aa236c3b89de8139c24a1e9319c411a6f1d95fd74d7cc4b142cd.jpg', 'Luigi™ is back and on a mission to remove a bunch of stubborn ghosts from some spooky mansions. Armed with his trusty Poltergust ghost-sucking vacuum cleaner, he will try to act brave as he bumbles his way through the darkness while trying to capture these pesky phantoms.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2c89fe55f6b73b0588419c6b2b04cabecadd409e324588650c319f5861e8a95f.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/4P4ROFF.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/3zYQSOO.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3450, '000400000006f800', 'CTR-N-TAGP', 'Wrecking Crew', 'EUR', 7371620, 'eshop', '50010000007279', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e21dd79225d60ce352ad761af92f48451078038ec233062db4eddf9d1be368f9.jpg', 'In NES™ classic Wrecking Crew,\nMario and Luigi swap their plumber’s\ncaps for hard hats as they take on the\nrole of demolition engineers!\n<br/><br/>\nOne or two players must demolish\nevery obstacle in each enemy-infested\nlevel, while working out the most\ndestructive route through the\nnetworks of ladders and scaffolds.\n<br/><br/>\nWrecking Crew also includes a mode\nfor designing your own levels. This\nVirtual Console™ version also features\nthe ability to save your creations,\nwhich was not possible in the NES\noriginal.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d1bdd0d6d077b18dbc3e6911f37c987ed959f783a99f360337e17917c251c32e.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/AyAddKG.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/BjYqHZc.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3451, '000400000009f400', 'CTR-N-JKFP', 'Johnny Kung Fu™', 'EUR', 41130852, 'eshop', '50010000011306', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d286fd67d783a77e32d52e915bbc32eac01dc052d1fce3928baf0c2892dca52c.jpg', 'Johnny Kung Fu is an old school\naction game that mixes the old with\nthe new! Johnny Kung Fu puts you\ninto the Kung Fu garb of a seemingly\neveryday man, Johnny. The local\norganised crime group, The Mr Wang\nGang, led by the mysterious man\nknown as Mr Wang, seems to have a\nbone to pick with Johnny and has\ncaptured his girlfriend Paula. Knowing\nthat an ambush awaits him, Johnny\nchases the kidnappers into one of Mr\nWang’s hideout towers regardless.\nWill Johnny be able to save Paula or\nwill the Mr Wang Gang prevail?', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/bfhcdGw.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3452, '0004000000068f00', 'CTR-N-JCAP', 'Pullblox™', 'EUR', 21076836, 'eshop', '50010000008021', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ac6fce2909227dabdd551f3c3d9fbcb3c6b2dc41cbdcb70cad45a166d2920541.jpg', 'Pullblox is a unique part-puzzle,\npart-platform game that will tax your\nbrain and creativity!<br>\n<br>\nChildren in Pullblox Park have been\ntrapped inside giant block puzzles –\n‘pullblox’ – that are as big as houses.\nSo it''s tiny hero Mallo to the rescue!<br>\n<br>\nClimb the structures, pushing and\npulling blocks to use as steps, and\nrescue the children. If you make a\nmistake, simply rewind time and try\nagain!<br>\n<br>\nThere are more than 200 pullblox to\nenjoy, and you can also create your\nown in Pullblox Studio and exchange\nthem with friends via QR Code™.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0cb2aab4d5489e38fc71121d9d767750ece19f8ed2dabce284f4897141cdba49.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/X6OlyuU.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/jAphQ6l.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3453, '000400020005ed01', 'CTR-T-ACQP', 'cooking mama 4 DEMO', 'EUR', 24891392, 'demo', '50030000000141', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3454, '0004000000063c00', 'CTR-N-JE9Z', 'Resident Evil Revelations E3 gameplay trailer', 'EUR', 32918836, 'eshop', '50010000006972', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8ec1417adb7958e81376cacc3d4190c2aa0a6ba1b3c9961c08b1c6a8d1465df8.jpg', 'Adding a new unique horror setting to the series, Resident Evil: Revelations gives players the chance to venture underwater as they try to escape the terrifying creatures that are roaming a supposedly abandoned cruise ship on the Mediterranean. New storyline featuring series favourites Jill Valentine, Chris Redfield and introducing BSAA member Parker Luciani. Explore the dark, sinister areas of the cruise ship; there''s nowhere to run and hide with evil creeping out of the shadows. Touch Screen control scheme adds depth to puzzle solving and provides easy access to switching weapons on the fly. Use the Genesis scanning equipment to analyse enemy weaknesses and hidden items that will prove crucial for the player’s survival. Players can choose the shooting style that suits them with the ability to alternate between first and third person views to best pinpoint enemies.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a6e5b295b5c7eb68eb02222c83f403ea9686c55e9ec7e567a81e4d1b08c066a6.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/Isq05yP.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/sjHdu2d.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3455, '0004000000075400', 'CTR-N-PADP', 'Mario Advance 3', 'EUR', 10058596, 'eshop', '50010000008322', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/84b45bacafe72f1ac681728a5ca2d6f46c1b3f1847a2da5cb59d5c5aedb18b79.jpg', 'When the evil Kamek tries to kidnap\nthe baby Mario brothers, Yoshi must\nsave the day. Carrying Baby Mario on\nyour back, traverse a gorgeous\ncrayon-coloured world – stomping on\nenemies and throwing eggs – to\ndefeat Kamek and his master Baby\nBowser!<br>\n<br>\nYoshi''s Island: Super Mario Advance\n3 is acclaimed for its captivating\nvisuals and gameplay that keeps you\non your toes, as you protect Baby\nMario through fiendishly designed\nlevels.<br>\n<br>\nAlso included is the original Mario\nBros. to round off a perfect nostalgic\npackage!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0a4915662f845214288b53e6ba3e5089aba9aa08244d682b8c3d2846ca4cf437.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/mfd6uWg.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/JZJACuC.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3456, '000400000006e600', 'CTR-N-TAAP', 'Super Mario Bros.™', 'EUR', 5090148, 'eshop', '50010000007301', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/dcf3717328b45edfa1293e0641c367f713c149a92ea6c82b6eb0c6297e249eda.jpg', 'For more than 25 years, the Super\nMario series has conquered the\ncharts, and won the hearts of fans the\nworld over.\n\nNow you can discover - or\nrediscover - the original game that\nmade Mario a household name.\n\nRun and jump with Mario or Luigi\nthrough caves and castles, down\npipes and across platforms, and face\noff against Bowser to rescue your\nbeloved Princess Peach.\n\nIt may be more than a quarter of a\ncentury old, but Super Mario Bros. is\nstill as enchanting as ever!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/58a5de343f246e9fc40856006f15353029ac09dcc980246080f54cbf3226c5f6.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/tqNvZUC.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/IOFFaNP.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3457, '0004000000063900', 'CTR-N-JE8Z', 'METAL GEAR E3 Video', 'EUR', 28830516, 'eshop', '50010000007016', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4633e70e23640dc8596b157f952426556d850af744d2ef10727d5faa7964beab.jpg', 'From the critically acclaimed director, Hideo Kojima, a new 3D experience re-imagined from one of the most popular Metal Gear Solid titles from the past, comes Metal Gear Solid 3D Snake Eater. Experience an all-new re-interpretation of Metal Gear Solid 3: Snake Eater, in 3D for the first time ever. "Photo Camo" system utilising the built-in camera technology of the hardware bringing customised stealth and camouflage options to the player. By snapping a photo in the real world, players will be able to use the same image as a camouflage pattern applied to Snake''s uniform within the game. Utilising the Gyro Sensor, players will become one with Snake through specialised tilt mechanics throughout the game design. As Snake climbs trees, or traverses bridges and other environmental obstacles, players will be in danger of falling based on the balancing of the system. An intuitive menu utilises the touch screen for quick and easy equipping of items and weapons.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/89ccb0b813686f1ad874d8f18cb8ba28b9d9343ffd17b6e9a103c4e42581bded.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/ZCBLnyi.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/XKRsN1N.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3458, '0004000200040401', 'CTR-T-ACRP', 'CRUSH™3D (Demo Version)', 'EUR', 81899520, 'demo', '50030000000244', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3459, '000400000006a200', 'CTR-N-JENP', 'Zen Pinball 3D', 'EUR', 69938020, 'eshop', '50010000007967', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d3940cd50c18c19a1304612543d122ddbbf5fbae0c2b523159a687e61cf22750.jpg', 'Zen Pinball 3D for Nintendo 3DS\nbrings an incredible stereoscopic 3D\nexperience to the acclaimed video\ngame pinball series for the first time\never. Featuring four beautifully crafted\noriginal tables, Zen Pinball 3D\nfeatures the most advanced ball\nphysics in a video pinball game to\ndate, online leader boards ranking\nyou against other players, in-game\nfriend challenges, interactive 3D\nmodels, and more!<br>\n<br>\nZen Pinball 3D for Nintendo 3DS is\nthe definitive pinball experience on\nportable game consoles.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a90c2cc1e25fb9ded67e20acebb70b5c71b678695081ee74e35d93ddceb4001a.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/YQtIj2v.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/wYWHMqM.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3460, '0004000000063f00', 'CTR-N-JEZZ', 'Starfox 64 3D E3 Video', 'EUR', 50658612, 'eshop', '50010000006980', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a4ff88ee94d9a569691fc7f8a9ed6d25d4618fc0b22560e9dafbf1a9b43842f9.jpg', 'Fox McCloud is back in a re-mastered Nintendo classic. Play as legendary Fox McCloud and lead your fearless squadron of wing-men into fierce laser blasting aerial combat against the evil forces of Andross. Rich 3D visuals provide a remarkable sense of depth, distance, and position while dodging meteors and blasting enemy fighters out of the sky. New features such as motion controls and new multiplayer options allow long-time fans and newcomers alike to discover the excitement of the Starfox universe.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/47d2b00c7c64d336472dabac4357b983a71bf523bba96aee5bf0a836f66a3bf2.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/WV4zhbE.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/gpkonzZ.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
