(3468, '0004000000075a00', 'CTR-N-PAFP', 'WarioWare, Inc™: Minigame Mania', 'EUR', 9739108, 'eshop', '50010000008341', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8c7e9b30f1b776b9d6af24839bfdf13646cc7ad71e5439515d29b4478b0cd937.jpg', 'Before he branched out his business\nto Wii and Nintendo DS, Wario first\nset up shop on Game Boy Advance in\nthe original WarioWare, Inc.: Minigame\nMania!<br>\n<br>\nWarioWare is packed with more than\n200 wacky microgames, each very\nsimple but played at lightning-fast\nspeed; from hitting a baseball to\npicking a disembodied nose. Complete\nmultiple microgames in succession,\nand beat the boss, to clear each\nstage.<br>\n<br>\nThere are even bonus games which\ncan be played by two people sharing\none Nintendo 3DS system!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/15249feaf37cd961619ca345a8d12dd60b199eb42ea60d2055837d11b5ef07fe.jpg', 1, 'http://i.imgur.com/rNWg5Ec.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/eUgF1bp.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3469, '0004000000070700', 'CTR-N-TAMP', 'Ice Climber™', 'EUR', 13433748, 'eshop', '50010000007312', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7c15ddca0d54e572114e149ca7b4717873aef7b4865cb19a8d028ec15bcb7973.jpg', 'Conquer treacherous peaks, leap\nacross icy chasms and swat\nsnow-dwelling beasts – solo or with a\nfriend – in this NES™ classic.\n<br/><br/>\nUse your hammer to bash blocks and\nto defend yourself from the wildlife as\nyou head towards the summit. Make it\nthrough all eight floors to reach the\nbonus stage and grab as many\nvegetables as you can before hitching\na lift on a friendly condor.\n<br/><br/>\nIn two player mode, either work\ntogether to reach the mountaintop or\ncompete to see who can get the glory\nfirst!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/03a23bb0b89856f845824d392e46e23bbfc6fda7942a4f0e21ce460da7367c53.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/FIyC2Kb.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/YTrWHVK.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3470, '0004000000063300', 'CTR-N-JE6Z', 'Zelda: Ocarina of Time 3D E3 Video', 'EUR', 24452404, 'eshop', '50010000006964', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1bc79682e264de8c3102444b7a11cbc3273517248db527cf51e1625037f31aa9.jpg', 'The Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time 3D brings a completely re-mastered version of this epic entry in the beloved The Legend of Zelda series to the Nintendo 3DS system. The game couples phenomenally enhanced graphics with stunning glasses-free 3D visuals to bring to life the daring adventures of its hero, Link™, in the epic tale of the creation of Hyrule and the struggle for control of its all-powerful ancient relic.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c0c061655958925d156a1798eda368969a7d6a100ae600220fde7864555910a0.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/I6EQwOM.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/iZjMuly.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3471, '0004000000075000', 'CTR-N-PACP', 'Wario Land™ 4', 'EUR', 9907044, 'eshop', '50010000008321', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e665f8dd705bfa4b8884dc15eeca65bf47d27bf8d70246fe94a911d279de94e8.jpg', 'Loot-loony Wario has discovered his\nbiggest score yet: a fabulous golden\npyramid filled with riches. Trouble is,\nits denizens don’t want to give up the\ntreasure easily, but that hasn’t\nstopped Wario before!<br>\n<br>\nIn Wario Land 4, the greedy hero\nfinds himself no longer invincible, as in\nhis previous platform adventures.\nHowever he can undergo amazing\ntransformations that aid him in his\nquest: like becoming Bat Wario,\nBouncy Wario and even Zombie Wario!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fde2797bfa96200efab1ebec0db937c0da27199bfa5716c33f7ef8436cfdeba6.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/PhgDCBL.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/MuNz9w6.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3472, '0004000000063600', 'CTR-N-JE7Z', 'Super Mario E3 Video', 'EUR', 27561268, 'eshop', '50010000006968', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5c497401214de12dcc184dc14b7d795dde611e1dbe44e7a1d1ab524d0ecf75ed.jpg', 'Super Mario for Nintendo 3DS is an all new game that combines classic Mario game play and 3D visuals in a truly amazing way. It’s the return of the Tanooki Mario! Tanooki Mario has a tail that allows him to hover jump easily from platform to platform or even take out enemies with a quick whip of the tail. Players of all skill levels will enjoy playing the game.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ba8e97c2463f7ad4c5729c0068b9932a7baaf6d191291b169455bb750bb67dda.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/9qkYSc2.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/Xk1c2qL.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3473, '0004000000055200', 'CTR-N-SAAP', '3D Classics Kid Icarus™', 'EUR', 42744676, 'eshop', '50010000008381', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e18e5e12252f4fee0bd2fd83ba87ded0eee9967aabcbdbbcf3580ee7635c9ce3.jpg', 'Enjoy classic games in a new\ndimension with the 3D Classics range,\nremastered with immersive 3D visuals!<br>\n<br>\nKid Icarus™ is an action-platformer\nfrom the creators of Metroid™;\nstarring angelic warrior Pit, who must\nrescue the goddess Palutena and save\nAngel Land from the evil Medusa.<br>\n<br>\nArmed with his trusty bow and arrow,\nPit must battle from the underworld to\nthe sky, to seek out the Three Sacred\nTreasures. Only then will Pit have the\npower to take on Medusa.<br>\n<br>\nLook out for Pit''s return in\nKid Icarus™: Uprising for\nNintendo 3DS!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Qs3gCqn.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
