(3491, '0004000000076b00', 'CTR-N-PAJP', 'Fire Emblem™: The Sacred Stones', 'EUR', 36191076, 'eshop', '50010000008241', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6940181b05336117bb8af57ceca0509fc7a608bb2a68cc61eaa5cb00fad534d6.jpg', 'In Fire Emblem: The Sacred Stones,\nthe peaceful kingdom of Renais is\nattacked by its ally the Grado Empire.\nThe heirs to the throne of Renais must\nfree their homeland and uncover the\nsecret behind the Grado treachery.<br>\n<br>\nThis acclaimed chapter of the tactical\nrole-playing series brings a gripping\nnew storyline and many new features.<br>\n<br>\nCommand your army of soldiers –\nfrom familiar Pegasus Knights to brand\nnew units like the Mage Knights – and\nbattle across more than 20 levels of\nepic sword and sorcery action.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/987226b17e1ca8c93ac97d6411d36b29771d8f027d56fe1e9bde294ad476f80b.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/7qoKRwr.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/0irLWSF.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
