(3493, '0004000000070400', 'CTR-N-TALP', 'Balloon Fight™', 'EUR', 13335444, 'eshop', '50010000007311', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d3dec60f43d1e667d8770db5b095df1da8075e33dfcfae0d578eb9cd4927eb70.jpg', 'Go up, up and away with this NES™\nclassic from the 1980s. In Balloon\nFight you have one simple mission:\npop or be popped!\n<br/><br/>\nBurst enemies'' balloons from above,\nand hit them again before they have\ntime to re-inflate. Danger comes from\nthe sky or sea, too; watch out for\nlightning strikes and a very hungry\nfish.\n<br/><br/>\nBalloon Fight also features a\ntwo-player mode with cooperative and\ncompetitive play, plus a survival mode\ncalled Balloon Trip - which may be\nfamiliar to fans of Nintendo Land™!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/34ea469a823f091bd0f6845bd6099ad98e77b178b84d17830c9ac4903ad844b6.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/azfXn0M.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/Ri7deH9.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3494, '0004000000070100', 'CTR-N-TAKP', 'Donkey Kong Jr.™', 'EUR', 6826852, 'eshop', '50010000007310', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b42466ef767b8fdb010149fe7ada44603188f1a90492043f83fe8a81e1baecc8.jpg', 'Donkey Kong has finally been\ncaptured by Mario! In this unique\nrole-reversal platformer, you play as\nDK''s son, Junior, and must save dad\nfrom Mario''s clutches.\n\nSwing and climb your way across\nvines and chains to grab the keys that\nunlock Donkey Kong''s cage, avoiding\nnasty critters like Snapjaws and\nNitpickers.\n\nIt''s a game all about speed and high\nscores - so get swinging and rack up\nthose points - but don''t forget to\nrescue DK!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ecb1958be708aba797ed49b63337bbdebe897654636c2d8f0aba2126cd8cd576.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/1IrgV5b.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/UVvLhS2.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3495, '0004000000097000', 'CTR-N-JT9P', 'Bird Mania 3D', 'EUR', 29739876, 'eshop', '50010000009909', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2c2486f39740239ef1c7dcceca902bf1ddeccb845d0b2acf711395c9b2ef00f4.jpg', 'When Mojo realises his friends from\nthe flock set out to Africa he begins a\nfrantic chase after them because he\nwants to go on a vacation too! Fly\nfaster and faster, dash, soar, glide,\nand collect all bonuses. How far can\nyou get in pursuit of a delightful\nvacation? Bird Mania 3D is a\nskill-based action game where you\nsteer a little birdie on his way to\nAfrica. Keep him out of trouble as\nlong as possible and beat your best\nscore! You will be hypnotised for long\nhours while trying to collect all\nbonuses and avoid obstacles. And if\nyou really want to perfect the art of\nflying, try to get all achievements.\nBeware, it’s totally addictive!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/PN4fM5O.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3496, '0004000000076e00', 'CTR-N-PAKP', 'The Legend of Zelda™: The Minish Cap', 'EUR', 18893668, 'eshop', '50010000008301', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d4cac41f1b44524abd2dc799e2f19cf6d3a9c1ecacc2a4cd0071b61580eed2bb.jpg', 'This classic Legend of Zelda\nadventure sees the heroic Link embark\non a journey into a massively tiny\nworld with the help of his wondrous\nnew headwear: the Minish Cap!<br>\n<br>\nLink can shrink down to microscopic\ndimensions, which will prove essential\nin saving the miniature Picori people\nfrom disaster.<br>\n<br>\nOf course, it just wouldn’t be The\nLegend of Zelda without ingenious\nnew items to master, captivating\nside-quests to conquer, and a\nplethora of dungeons to explore.\nSmall really is beautiful!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/39ec751f4d535dfd8975e64a45c84498e6822531efb3e706a26e833987cc15f2.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/K4mDZMQ.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/PATs8FY.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
