(3514, '00040000000c6300', 'CTR-N-JGCP', 'Gunman Clive', 'EUR', 32373604, 'eshop', '50010000012836', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6a668caad6c18a99224cca7fe796a34b6d777d5446bdf759df312a23977a8642.jpg', 'In the year of 18XX, the west is\noverrun by thugs and outlaws. A\ngroup of bandits have kidnapped\nMayor Johnson''s daughter and are\nspreading havoc across the land. Only\nGunman Clive can bring order to the\nwest and save the girl!\n<br/><br/>\nJump and shoot your way across\ndiverse and challenging levels and\nfight massive bosses. Gunman Clive is\nan old-school sidescrolling platform\ngame set in the old west with full 3D\ngraphics and a unique art style.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3bea5db7c925313f0b318b469877a403133035b584b1c0ad631e7159a9cdd47c.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Ba9qE7d.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ZVaU7pN.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3515, '00040000000d9a00', 'CTR-N-SN7P', 'Donkey Kong Country™ Returns 3D: Trailer', 'EUR', 19905332, 'eshop', '50010000013301', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/623c163c6130e6237a985ebc7541b2239b30c087ea7fc5db24759505e8e1cc72.jpg', 'This is a downloadable 3D trailer of\nDonkey Kong Country™ Returns 3D.\n<br/><br/>\nIt also enables you to receive further\nnotifications about Donkey Kong\nCountry™ Returns 3D via SpotPass.\n<br/><br/>\nNote that the video was taken from\nthe Japanese language version and\nmay contain Japanese text or voice\novers.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b0413b91c13b5c27148f21b30eea032f4dba393b7def50bd187ccf28a78badff.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/Nh2FaOw.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/abVQZjc.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3516, '00040000000cbc00', 'CTR-N-JP2P', 'PICROSS e2', 'EUR', 21179236, 'eshop', '50010000013091', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d740c75071dba0d86de83627227dc577701199f247d093c4e10d873755ab8771.jpg', 'This is the sequel to "Picross e" with\na navigation feature to make gameplay\neven smoother. Like the previous\ngame, this game has 150 new\npuzzles, plus an all new gameplay\nelement known as "Micross."\n<br/><br/>\n"Picross" is a "Picture Crossword\nPuzzle Game" in which you use\nnumbers as hints to complete\nillustrations. The rules are simple and\neasy to understand. Anyone can do it!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/W6gr2xa.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
