(3649, '0004000e00119a00', 'CTR-U-JK8E', 'Shovel Knight Update Ver. 1.1', 'USA', 4614964, 'update', '50010000026255', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2dfa2ca4fd0ae8d3c6e1fd1c02109a9fdf46c85e43e4d75b64e4a6a7b4a6e504.jpg', 'An update is available for Shovel Knight.\n<br><br>\nFixes a bug which caused Shovel Knight to celebrate endlessly after defeating Tinker Knight.\n<br><br>\nFixes for multiple Feats and Boss encounters across the game. Feat progress is now immediately saved upon unlocking. Previously, Feats could be obtained but lost by the regular saving mechanisms if a game exited or turned off before reaching the next autosave.\n<br><br>\nRemoves a Song Scroll from the Clockwork Tower stage which could never be collected or turned in.\n<br><br>\nAdds an Update option to the Title Screen to allow even more convenient Updates in the future!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/dfdee87a42d21a84a68fb393cdc322fcd546276c729acfd237b1fb3b20d0226f.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/bB9MoPZ.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ueyJfnV.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
