(3652, '0004000e000d7d00', 'CTR-U-JNUE', 'Steel Diver™: Sub Wars Update Ver. 4.1', 'USA', 41261924, 'update', '50010000021233', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c28581f4d68ac31d4ea287ca07a46f213fe05b5dfacb36ae708c61c076cb47aa.jpg', 'This is an update for the Steel Diver: Sub Wars game. This download does not contain the full version of the title. In order to use this update, you must have the full version of Steel Diver: Sub Wars.\n<br><br>\nThe update includes:\n<br><br>\nYou now have the option to remodel your sub on the Submarine Selection screen.\nFor $0.99 (MX$11.99, R$ 1,99, plus tax) you can remodel a sub to expand the crew carrying capacity. Before this update, the number of crew each sub could carry varied, but now you can remodel any sub to carry up to six crew members.\n<br><br>\nSubmarine diving and surfacing angles\nThe angle of a sub when it dives or submerges will not be as steep, which makes it easier to evade frontal attacks.\n<br><br>\nMatched-Skills Battles\nPlayers between level 30 and level 49 can now match-up in Matched-Skills Battles.*\n<br><br>\nPlay Coin requirement\nWe have removed the Play Coin requirement for players of the free version to play Internet Mode. *\n<br><br>\nOther adjustments have also been made to balance the game and make for a more fun gaming experience.\n<br><br>\nThis update also includes adjustments that were made in updates previous to Ver. 4.1.\n<br><br>\n*Broadband Internet access required for online features. For more info, go to support.nintendo.com.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e56acfc99a06561a6e1444ffc701474b70f2854938b5ce8db42261a34eb5a422.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/oQbn8QT.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/hfk5ygq.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
