(3687, '0004000000162700', 'CTR-N-KSNJ', '3D ソニック･ザ･ヘッジホッグ2', 'JPN', 35429220, 'eshop', '50010000035495', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6a673140c268e95009d83c149afebf69cd5d8eca2faca7fbcd9130a0e05e1273.jpg', 'スピード感、爽快感ともにパワーアップしたソニックシリーズ第2弾が登場。立体視対応はもちろん、新要素「リングキープモード」やゲーム途中のセーブ機能、ステージセレクトなど、クリアに便利な機能が満載です。またローカルプレイにも対応しているので、テイルスとの2人同時プレイもばっちり対応しています。\n※ローカルプレイによる2人同時プレイには、それぞれの本体にソフトが必要です。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6f5cf2a25b471fe9fabc93db03087ff836f8064342e5a00bbc661498feb0c0c2.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/VmvDU95.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/z9RBQ3y.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3688, '0004000000042a00', 'CTR-N-QAAP', 'The Legend of Zelda™: Link''s Awakening DX™', 'EUR', 5577572, 'eshop', '50010000006772', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/073ed0657fd971113acb576d0acff1c1fb550e7da64a19aeb47d2b6c7a306850.jpg', 'In the Legend of Zelda series’ first\nGame Boy adventure, Link is\nshipwrecked on the mysterious\nKoholint Island. To return home, he\nmust face a nightmarish new enemy\nand solve the riddle of the Wind Fish.<br>\n<br>\nThis definitive Game Boy Color\nversion improves on the original Game\nBoy release with an exclusive new\ndungeon and colour graphics.<br>\n<br>\nHelp Link search for the eight\nInstruments of the Sirens, collecting\nitems like the Pegasus Boots and\nHook Shot, traversing challenging\ndungeons, and battling deadly\nbosses.<br>\n<br>\nThe Legend of Zelda: Link’s\nAwakening DX is as rich and\nengrossing an adventure as any you\nwill find on the big screen.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/zmnmkV2.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3689, '000400000008aa00', 'CTR-N-JSLP', '3D Solitaire', 'EUR', 40045412, 'eshop', '50010000010417', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/db7552ca9654416cde088cdbaf5c660b276620dffeb78905a0b7a60c549a01fa.jpg', '3D Solitaire for the Nintendo 3DS™\nbrings the classic game to beautiful\nstereoscopic 3D environments.\nFeaturing multiple modes of play,\nplayer rewards and fun environments,\n3D Solitaire provides classic\ngameplay for the Nintendo 3DS™.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/hbG051O.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3690, '00040000000ffb00', 'CTR-N-QA5P', 'Super Mario Bros.™ Deluxe', 'EUR', 5340004, 'eshop', '50010000019993', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f426b827892705f00ac5bcb5995e77951458e2cafc4ce007340e376aef5d78c6.jpg', 'This souped-up version of the all-time\nclassic was a big hit on Game Boy™\nColor. Super Mario Bros. Deluxe\nfeatures all 32 original levels from the\n1985 classic, plus a whole lot more!\n<br/><br/>\nIn Challenge mode, revisit classic\nlevels and collect special red coins\nand Yoshi eggs to beat the high\nscore. Or race against a familiar foe\nthrough eight special courses in You\nVs Boo mode! There are even\nchallenging secret levels to be\ndiscovered, for a true test of your\nSuper Mario Bros. skills!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bc655b894ca3b325294262cae9d7a04377c425d701add8d69269973f36edebbd.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/LK6pvcd.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/1VMbTka.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3691, '0004000000041c00', 'CTR-N-RAGP', 'Super Mario Land™ 2: 6 Golden Coins™', 'EUR', 5020516, 'eshop', '50010000007501', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6bf34f3b50d02690c755f9b9b107d5361d46d373fb5ff3b4dbb3cc0a94ac2efe.jpg', 'In his greatest Game Boy™\nadventure, Mario faces off against his\nevil rival Wario, who has captured\nMario Land and turned it into his\nprivate playground.<br>\n<br>\nTo force Wario off his ill-gotten\nthrone, Mario must search all-new\nworlds for the six golden coins that\nunlock the gate to Mario''s castle. A\nmob of monsters, old and new, seek\nto stop him. Along the way, through 6\nzones, Mario can nab Power\nMushrooms, Super Stars and Fire\nFlowers for extra power. And if he\neats the Magic Carrot, he''ll turn into\na high-flying bunny.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4f678d0e3f10ca2ead5db0cc0c0d1d666d1ee3fa0003083b261cf7677efac351.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/4aL12H0.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/J8WjbP2.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3692, '0004000000041f00', 'CTR-N-RAHP', 'Donkey Kong™', 'EUR', 5176164, 'eshop', '50010000006891', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/cc5a9fcd940edde8f3ae5c305cc9dca9b76417dad2b15070b67e0c8504b5468d.jpg', 'Think you know Donkey Kong? Think again! This Game Boy version takes the arcade classic to a new level, with 101 unique stages of platforming perfection.\n\nLike the original, Mario must rescue Pauline from DK’s clutches; but beyond the initial arcade-style stages lies a whole new experience. In each new action-puzzle themed level, Mario must dodge traps, avoid enemies and hit switches, to bring the key to the exit.\n\nLuckily Mario has learned some new moves, too, like the handstand and backflip; and he’ll need all his skills to contend with Donkey Kong in the numerous boss battles. Go teach that ape some manners, Mario!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7c1a454bf5dcfb48d0e72471d7d0859d9c3f274f152e2d2ac715d1fa631c8c57.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/cGFs6mz.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/Obk3BHX.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3693, '00040000000ed400', 'CTR-N-JSTP', 'SteamWorld Dig', 'EUR', 44297060, 'eshop', '50010000015534', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0b0d8695140429cf404d6629e689501f6f1894690abbb1172e887245de2002f6.jpg', '10/10 - "...an utterly phenomenal\nvideo game." - PocketGamer.co.uk\n \n9/10 - "A totally unexpected love\nletter to bold concepts." -\nNintendoWorldReport.com\n \n9/10 - "...super-fun, addictive and\ninspired gameified manual labour..." -\nGamesBlip.com\n\nSteamWorld Dig is a platform mining\nadventure. Take the role as Rusty, a\nlone mining steambot, as he arrives to\nan old mining town in great need. Dig\nyour way through the old earth,\ngaining riches while uncovering the\nancient threat that lurks below...\n<br/><br/>\n* Explore an underground world full\nof secrets, treasure and terrors.\n<br/><br/>\n* Uncover the remnants of Human\ncivilization, a degenerate race of\ndynamite-wielding troglodytes.\n<br/><br/>\n* High-res graphics with dynamic\nlights and parallaxed background\nlayers.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/jVkXK2U.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3694, '00040000000c6700', 'CTR-N-JKZP', 'Flipnote Studio™ 3D', 'EUR', 9812836, 'eshop', '50010000015295', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e3a0f8285fb463fb077567f265c36571e1d09a288c4322327b3d666a22b3e99a.jpg', 'Flipnote Studio 3D is an exclusive\nfree download for members of My\nNintendo to celebrate the launch of\nthe service.\n<br/><br/>\nIn order to become a member and\ndownload it, you first need to create\na Nintendo Account at\nhttps://accounts.nintendo.com. You\nhave to do this either by signing in\nthere with the Nintendo Network ID\nyou use on your Nintendo 3DS\nsystem, or by linking that Nintendo\nNetwork ID in your Nintendo Account\nsettings after the registration.\n<br/><br/>\nThen just visit the Flipnote Studio 3D\nproduct page on the official Nintendo\nwebsite while being signed in with\nyour Nintendo Account, and you''ll\nfind the software ready to download\nto your Nintendo 3DS system.\n<br/><br/>\nThis offer is valid only until 30 April\n2016, after which the software will\nbecome unavailable for download. You\nmust be 13 years of age or older in\norder to register a Nintendo Account.\n<br/><br/>\nFlipnote Studio 3D is a free drawing\napplication that allows you to create\nyour very own animated masterpieces.\nWhether you want to scribble quick\nnotes or draw sketches, you’ll never\nrun out of pages with Flipnote Studio\n3D. There are a whole host of tools\nthat will let you bring your creations\nto life and create high-quality\nanimations. You can then share these\ncreations with friends and users from\naround the world so everyone can be\nwowed by your talents.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9fbafef018ae6387c6b2106972fca42ca0741469bfb7c67d28d228a65fd71e0d.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/lUvHtPM.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/tYRiwvk.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3695, '0004000000126b00', 'CTR-N-NC6P', 'Tomodachi Life™ Welcome Version', 'EUR', 130956132, 'eshop', '50010000023035', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d55d2f84aaadf243cf3dbd2b4986fae83e0915db8ed16f964dd43b2b2f2c2c1a.jpg', 'This Tomodachi Life: Welcome\nVersion* gives you a taste of\nTomodachi Life by creating up to three\nMii characters with individual voice\nsettings and personality traits. You\ncan sample the gameplay, such as\nfeeding Mii characters, giving them\nitems such as new interiors and\nclothing, and watching them perform.\n<br/><br/>\nIf you like Tomodachi Life after\ncompleting the Tomodachi Life:\nWelcome Version, you can even keep\nyour progress and move the islanders\nyou created to the full version of\nTomodachi Life (purchasable in\nNintendo eShop and retail).**\nFurthermore, players who complete\nthe Tomodachi Life: Welcome Version\ncan unlock a rare panda suit*** in\none of eight colours to put on their\nMii characters, and also use in the full\nversion.\n<br/><br/>\n* Features and locations are limited\nin this Tomodachi Life: Welcome\nVersion compared to the full version\nof the game, but any Mii™ characters\ncreated can be transferred to the full\nversion.\n<br/><br/>\n** The Tomodachi Life: Welcome\nVersion can be completed multiple\ntimes, however each time it will\noverwrite the previous save file. Only\nthe last completed save file can be\ntransferred to the full version.\n<br/><br/>\n*** Users of the Tomodachi Life:\nWelcome Version must own the full\ngame (purchasable at retail and in\nNintendo eShop) to exchange the\npanda suit with other players. The\nplayer that gifted the download code\nfor Tomodachi Life: Welcome Version\nto another player does not receive the\npanda suit automatically. The panda\nsuit can also be unlocked through\nnormal gameplay in the full version.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b4db2a3f7740e8d25c90c523f1a5730575554a9c1e7807041a6ad70ab21e133c.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/n3PZKuF.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/RY21VS1.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3696, '00040000000ed100', 'CTR-N-AVHE', 'SENRAN KAGURA Burst', 'USA', 1825332068, 'eshop', '50010000017953', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b198161fe0dd94640df7a8141c7c0aa1945f18478926cea4470f39aeda8f4726.jpg', 'Enter a world filled with beautiful ninja destined to break down the barriers between good and evil.\n<br><br>\nPlay two different storylines, each with its own perspective. The girls of Hanzo believe they fight on the side of righteousness, but are their methods always right? The girls of Hebijo are mercenaries to the highest bidders, but what if their motives aren''t as clear as they seem?\n<br><br>\nCrush your enemies with your favorite buxom ninja girl using fast punches, mid-air flight sequences, combos, super attacks, revealing cut-scenes and sexy Ninja Arts. \n<br><br>\nDozens of costumes expose endless combinations!<br>\nChoose from 72 different costume sets such as school uniforms, swimsuits and ninja gear, along with hairstyles that can be changed, mixed and matched to provide an endless array of looks.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/nKl6G4n.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3697, '00040000000bd300', 'CTR-N-ASJE', 'Etrian Odyssey™ IV: Legends of the Titan', 'USA', 748333924, 'eshop', '50010000013116', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e0482bdbbc075313273ae8e23758235fe3dfb195b32719270194dd2352b0b5ef.jpg', 'For centuries, the tree Yggdrasil has been a constant presence in the lives of the people of Tharsis. It looms on the horizon, visible from everywhere in the city. But its roots are in a far-off land where no one has ventured until the Outland Count of Tharsis sponsors an Explorers Guild to reach Yggdrasil and discover its secrets.\n<br><br>\nYou are the latest explorer arriving in Tharsis to seek your fame and fortune. Board your skyship and set out into the clouds in search of treasure, glory, and the answer to Tharsis’ oldest mystery.\n<br><br>\nEtrian Odyssey IV brings an enhanced graphics engine boasting polygonal enemies and new 3D special effects; upgradable, customizable skyships that let players travel and battle amid the clouds. An exceedingly atmospheric and fully orchestrated musical score from Yuzo Koshiro in addition to expanded, more immersive 3D dungeons with analog camera control rounds up the features of the newest addition to this beloved franchise. ', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/iQWwgmZ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3698, '0004000000154600', 'CTR-N-JCPP', 'BOXBOY!™', 'EUR', 84474772, 'eshop', '50010000032455', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/afc8b4db5a8a0d65e841bba3c05f770d9a2f90945beda9ebe8035ca179644581.jpg', 'BOXBOY!™ is a 2D puzzle-platformer\navailable exclusively on\nNintendo 3DS™.\n<br/><br/>\nThe game features a minimalist style\nwith black-and-white graphics. The\ngameplay revolves around the main\ncharacter Qbby’s ability to create\nboxes he can use to protect himself,\nclimb on to, or activate switches.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/QDmJMK3.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3699, '0004000000116900', 'CTR-N-AUFP', 'Sayonara UmiharaKawase', 'EUR', 134572900, 'eshop', '50010000021822', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/92e4d8bdf54db6d2577941ddc7a97eccb9bdaa7b7acc5be855a512f49979e021.jpg', 'Use your elastic fishing hook to play!\n<br/><br/>\nFeaturing a girl armed with only with\nher backpack and trusty fishing hook,\nthis travelling sushi chef departs on a\njourney in a dream-like world filled\nwith fish and other wildlife gone awry.\n<br/><br/>\nYou will need to think how to get out\nof the stages like a puzzle game, and\nlearn to use the hook to get out\nASAP, action game-style. You will\nalso be able to `restart` from the\ncheckpoints, and `slow` to move\ncarefully and avoid failing. On top, if\nyou connect to the internet, you will\nsee your ranking among players in\nyour territory!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/30bb29e966382aa410aef3d1525f953283034b4ee4aaf00cbaa1fc6332113375.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/P0aZala.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/aWhG3I3.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3700, '0004000000133300', 'CTR-N-BHDP', 'Phoenix Wright: Ace Attorney Trilogy', 'EUR', 385186660, 'eshop', '50010000028355', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6308424b5da050b7c65bfa4813562ec9e0e29c679431b221b51061d1ee05e4d8.jpg', 'Defend the innocent and save the\nday! Experience the original trilogy\nlike never before in clear,\nhigh-resolution re-drawn graphics and\nimmersive 3D visuals optimized for the\nNintendo 3DS™ system. Join rookie\nlawyer Phoenix Wright through the\nearly years of his career in his quest\nto find the truth behind all of the\nclassic cases! Prepare for intense\ncourtroom showdowns by investigating\ncrime scenes, collecting evidence,\nand questioning witnesses. Use\nevidence and the testimonies of\nwitnesses to your advantage as you\nbattle for the innocence of your client.\nNothing less than a full acquittal will\ndo in this court of law. Find the\ncontradictions in witnesses''\ntestimonies to expose the truth!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/03aHAQj.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3701, '0004008c000ee000', 'CTR-M-AXCP-00', 'Super Smash Bros. for Nintendo 3DS', 'EUR', 3391488, 'dlc', 'none', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3702, '0004000000137800', 'CTR-P-AZGP', 'Puzzle & Dragons Z', 'EUR', 958184292, 'eshop', '50010000032637', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b7e12b9f936e5e66b597d70e0a38c0ef56303529b848288556e740a158928139.jpg', 'In this colourful puzzle game, the\nplayer is a Dragon Tamer who\nexplores dungeons, battling enemies\nby matching three or more Orbs of the\nsame type within a grid. RPG-type\nelements add a strategic layer, while\nthe player can recruit defeated\nmonsters, then improve their attributes\nusing experience points and Chips.\nThis pack also includes a Super Mario\nBros. Edition, featuring a streamlined\nversion of the game starring Mario and\nLuigi!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/12fbf60a6985e21eb2ec4f7d0392014eb9b0aa1cf15df765fd2b91a67a840b82.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/IQGkGif.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/BvxM4Rh.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3703, '0004000000055d00', 'CTR-N-EKJA', 'Pokémon™ X', 'ALL', 1807289188, 'eshop', '50010000014807', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f4fe4829ef40ce208128c6f91982acec1216dab65136890b539831150bcae90f.jpg', 'Skate, bike, and even ride a Pokémon as you set out for all-new adventures in the Kalos region. The new Fairy-type shakes up battle strategies and brings the number of Pokémon types up to a total of 18. Some Pokémon can even Mega Evolve while in battle, throwing standard battles out the window in favor of all-out brawls. With Mega Evolutions, Fairy-type Pokémon, Super Training and more, an undiscovered world of new battle strategies awaits. And with the new Player Search System, you can also connect and communicate with players nearby and around the world at the press of a button!*\n*Broadband Internet access required for online features. For more info, go to support.nintendo.com.\n<br><br>\nCheck out the theme inspired by this game in the Theme Shop. Just tap the icon in the upper left corner of your Nintendo 3DS HOME Menu to get started.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ju6FWkA.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3704, '00040000000c9c00', 'CTR-N-NLMA', 'Poké Transporter', 'ALL', 28011364, 'eshop', '50010000018434', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3873f25dcb8d83686d8a3d7b20a63ad50f9c567649e2ce963732073eaebd7ec4.jpg', 'Poké Transporter is an application which can be downloaded from Pokémon Bank for free. You can transfer Pokémon from your Pokémon Black Version, Pokémon White Version, Pokémon Black Version 2, or Pokémon White Version 2 to your Pokémon Bank by using Poké Transporter. In order to transfer your Pokémon, you need to insert Pokémon Black, Pokémon White, Pokémon Black 2, or Pokémon White 2 in all the systems in Nintendo 3DS family''s Game Card slot. Once you use Poké Transporter to transfer Pokémon, the Pokémon will disappear from that game and cannot be transferred back.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3debbdf98dbfe4fbaa225a9a0c280be3d71cf5dba484063c99cf9bea75c5cb03.jpg', 1, 'http://i.imgur.com/bgUHIxT.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/NSKxrzM.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3705, '0004000000055000', 'CTR-N-SAFP', '3D Classics Kirby''s Adventure™', 'EUR', 60042084, 'eshop', '50010000007966', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c0abbfd21834ec33e115429b172e483f67bd4bc8339a07cc14c36fe6c2e814c5.jpg', 'Enjoy classic games in a new\ndimension with the 3D Classics range,\nremastered with immersive 3D visuals!\n<br/><br/>\nIn 3D Classics Kirby''s Adventure,\nKirby must reassemble the pieces of\nthe Star Rod so that the people of\nDream Land can dream once again.\n<br/><br/>\nOriginally on NES, Kirby''s Adventure\nintroduced Kirby''s copy ability;\nallowing the innocent pink blob to fire\nlasers, burst into flames, become a\ngiant mallet, and more.\n<br/><br/>\nWith lots of minigames and secrets to\ndiscover, too, Kirby’s Adventure – like\nKirby – is full of surprises!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f54c4440bc0d2a9b86184ff85e820fab7e489e18a5d91d80d300bdf9bf6f00c6.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/scLBWBl.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/I30U14M.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3706, '0004008c000ba900', 'CTR-M-APDP-00', 'Pokémon™ Mystery Dungeon: Gates to Infinity', 'EUR', 252043264, 'dlc', 'none', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3707, '0004000000174600', 'CTR-N-BPXE', 'Pokémon™ Super Mystery Dungeon', 'USA', 1847815012, 'eshop', '50010000037195', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6330925a9a15772777ea30fbe09cce97295fc300387872d96147144e5a884cb2.jpg', 'The definitive Pokémon Mystery Dungeon! Prepare yourself for a grand adventure where you become a Pokémon and battle alongside Legendary and Mythical Pokémon to help save the world! Befriend Pokémon and explore ever-changing mystery dungeons with them!\n<br><br>\nPlayers are suddenly transformed into a Pokémon and sent out to a world inhabited only by Pokémon. From a group of 20 Pokémon, including the starters from core RPG Pokémon games plus Pikachu and Riolu, you can choose your Pokémon and your partner Pokémon! Battle alongside your partner Pokémon, who will become your best friend as you investigate ever-changing dungeons.\nBefriend and interact with all 720 known Pokémon as you attempt to save the world from a crisis in a tale of unprecedented scale! The possibilities are limitless!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ipvJ6Wa.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3708, '0004000000030100', 'CTR-N-AKDE', 'Kid Icarus™: Uprising', 'USA', 1690520420, 'eshop', '50010000009081', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/16e5d4cdf79ce259e3fbb7699c5030c1733a186c0b0a5aa602dd3774fe438d56.jpg', 'Take Aim at a Timeless Adventure\n<br><br>\nSome 25 years after the original Kid Icarus™ game for NES™ captured the hearts and imaginations of gamers worldwide, Kid Icarus: Uprising brings the action and adventure of this beloved series to new heights—and new visual dimensions—on the Nintendo 3DS™ system. The dark goddess Medusa and her Underworld Army have returned, and they’ve got their sights set on the heroic angel Pit.\n<br><br>\nWith the aid of Palutena, goddess of light and guardian of the human race, Pit must fend off this malevolent threat. The richly immersive graphics of the Nintendo 3DS system offer incredible depth as Pit battles enemies by air and by land.\n<br><br>\nTo order AR cards, tap the “Buy AR cards” button in the Website section below.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/q1KG3Dh.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3709, '00040000000a5e00', 'CTR-N-AG5E', 'Paper Mario™: Sticker Star', 'USA', 549927780, 'eshop', '50010000012007', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3075462dc6d4b24c83c1d9d1413ea855670245a444768b5c8a8ffdeb404969d3.jpg', 'When an accident scatters stickers across the land, Mario™ sets off on an adventure to repair a torn world. Searching Forests, Deserts and Mountains, Mario collects stickers to solve puzzles and battle monsters. In a first for the series, there are no experience points, so finding power-ups to improve Mario’s abilities is more important than ever. Mixing sticker-based gameplay elements with the traditional action-battle system of the Paper Mario™ series delivers a new twist on a classic franchise. Flatten-out characters, roll out towns, and walk through living, breathing dioramas in a brand-new Paper Mario adventure on the Nintendo 3DS™ system!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/G3GVtTq.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3710, '00040000000c2d00', 'CTR-N-AQ7E', 'HarmoKnight™', 'USA', 244964196, 'eshop', '50010000013391', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1652d843f6f643eb2f1def29e92e509e340e5f17cad661586c1c46b56932531f.jpg', 'GAME FREAK inc. brings all of the polish players have come to expect from their Pokémon franchise to a brand-new action-packed rhythm game! Use Tempo’s Music Note Staff to beat drums, crash cymbals, and smack enemies through more than 50 levels with unique boss fights.\n<br><br>\nOn your journey, you’ll team up with multiple characters like Lyra, who can slide under obstacles and shoot musical arrows, and Tyko, who can pound out powerful beats with his drums! More challenging speeds and unlockable stages await those locked onto the beat. Feel the music and find your rhythm to save Melodia!\n<br><br>\nA new rhythm-based action game from the makers of Pokémon!<br>\nJump, Hit, and Groove your way through 8 huge worlds<br>\nMore than 50 replayable levels in a digital package<br>\nBob your head to original music', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/LsNJjCY.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3711, '0004000000083800', 'CTR-N-JELE', 'Ketzal''s Corridors™', 'USA', 35281764, 'eshop', '50010000009846', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/080f06af4c7e82b9983411bb52c3de8fee1de6905a3832ce7588592e1e820e4e.jpg', 'Use speed, skill, and lightning-fast reflexes to save the spirit world from destruction in this engaging, action-packed puzzle game in which a variety of compelling spatial challenges await! Rotate and maneuver block-shaped Guardians to explore sacred shrines and climb towers that reach high above the clouds. Face adrenaline-fueled races against the clock, cerebral shape-matching missions, and mazes that you’ll need a sharp memory to escape. The evil god Koruptal has brought chaos and destruction to the spirit world, and it’s up to you to put things right!\n<br><br>\nThree player-vs.-player modes and 96 replayable, fast-paced, 3D single-player stages offer a wealth of puzzle-packed excitement, only available on the Nintendo 3DS system!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/WvZCE4c.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3712, '0004000000049000', 'CTR-N-ANRE', 'Star Fox 64™ 3D', 'USA', 604658580, 'eshop', '50010000007116', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/01b3c9e14034f3a8308b97da8487fe4003a3d188f274ba9f51744ca1fc063438.jpg', 'Fox McCloud is back in the remastered\nNintendo classic, Star Fox 64 3D!<br><br>\n\nThe single-player space-blasting adventure at the heart of Star Fox 64 3D, fondly remembered by many fans and often thought of as the best game in the Star Fox series, offers a cinematic adventure unlike any other. As Fox, it’s your duty to lead the Star Fox team into battle against the mad scientist Andross and his evil forces. Each mission takes place on a different\nplanet of the Lylat system, culminating in a final showdown with Andross at his\nhome planet Venom. Play Nintendo 64\nmode to recreate the original challenge of Star Fox 64, or take off in\nNintendo 3DS mode to battle using the new gyro controls and the Circle Pad.\n<br><br>\nThe new Score Attack mode allows you to replay any mission you’ve cleared in the main game and shoot for\nthe high score. Each mission has three\npossible medals—gold, silver, and bronze—that can be earned by scoring enough hits.\n<br><br>\nBattle mode, also new to Star Fox 64 3D, is a robust local-wireless multiplayer mode that brings a whole new level of competition to the Star Fox experience. Challenge up to three of your friends and square off in aerial combat via Download Play, which requires only one Game Card. Opt to use the Nintendo 3DS system’s inner camera to display a live video feed of everyone''s faces during the battle, enhancing the fun and personalizing the multiplayer experience. Featuring four unique battle levels, several all-new power-ups, and three battle types,\nStar Fox 64 3D lets you face off against your friends to prove once and\nfor all who is the ultimate pilot.\n<br><br>\nWith three game modes, new gyro controls that allow you to steer the Arwing by moving the Nintendo 3DS system, and fully voiced dialogue,\nyou''ll find that the Star Fox team is back in top form. Good luck...', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/0UtAZOO.jpg', 'none', 1, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3713, '000400000007c400', 'CTR-N-JAME', 'Dillon''s Rolling Western™', 'USA', 48651108, 'eshop', '50010000009261', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6e6c017b08bc7cef8839d37de827eb5f2f8388511ebe09dab8e6d7c7f0b20439.jpg', 'Can you protect the innocent and live to tell the tale? Try out your luck, partner, in the Dillon’s Rolling Western game—a unique combination of tower-defense strategy and character-driven action!\n<br><br>\nMeet Dillon, the armadillo ranger, and his trusty sidekick Russ as they travel the Wild West to aid ten frontier villages that are in need of some home improvements. By day, Dillon will scour the plains for resources in order to build up the villages’ defenses. By night, the unrelenting forces of the Grocks attack and it is up to our stoic hero to save the day! Plan out your tactical defenses, and use Dillon’s fighting skills with the stylus to roll and claw down the oncoming enemies.\n<br><br>\nAt each village, you will spend three days and nights to assess the situation and prepare a plan of attack. Use your time well to meet with the villagers, upgrade abilities and learn more about Dillon’s past. Replay villages to test out new strategies and obtain a higher star rating to unlock new villages!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/X0r8LN9.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3714, '00040000000cc500', 'CTR-N-JGWE', 'Dillon''s Rolling Western™ The Last Ranger', 'USA', 300112740, 'eshop', '50010000013427', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a1be684eaaa61cc3b18b668310fa30052709cb6c5f63232c7c2e13a8e6998244.jpg', 'Armadillo ranger Dillon is back, and this time he’s brought the cavalry. Join Dillon on new missions to protect each town. Gather supplies, fortify each town, and equip gun towers during the day. Recruit new allies by battling and defeating them throughout the game. As night falls, voracious grocks rise up from the underground.\n<br><br>\nThe only things standing between the decimation of the town and livestock are you, your hired gun, and the gun towers manned by locals. In addition to keeping villages safe from the waves of approaching enemies, Dillon must now also protect a train that moves throughout each of the game’s main stages. Get ready to roll!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/UrSLZwS.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3715, '00040000000c8700', 'CTR-N-JHSE', 'Kersploosh!™', 'USA', 25344868, 'eshop', '50010000013392', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2d26d82a43666c349b88c69076e3333e186244ba1a1e7bb0bf04bf06c6c54af7.jpg', 'Be one with the stone from the toss to the splash. With a sharp mind and a deft touch on the Circle Pad, master the journey to the bottom of wells filled with obstacles. As you learn to maneuver each stone in free fall and complete each level, you’ll unlock more stones and wells. Embrace the challenges that lie ahead…for the flight is at hand. \n<br><br>\nEach well is designed differently, with various hazards to impede your journey. Some wells have pizzas that break apart; others contain floating cookies that will sacrifice their delicious lives to stop you from getting to the bottom.   With a selection of stones, such as the beefy iron ball and the fragile gem, race as fast as possible to the bottom of each well. Then turn on the StreetPass feature and share your speedy conquests with others!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/qKnrFS2.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3716, '00040000000c9d00', 'CTR-N-JB7E', 'Mario and Donkey Kong™: Minis on the Move', 'USA', 54762340, 'eshop', '50010000014078', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/31b9e4dee1052169790c8e62ca0979dc3d4d122e7a2c381e707983ef349ac937.jpg', 'Test your puzzle solving skills in this spin-off of the Mario vs. Donkey\nKong™ series. Use tiles to create the best path through each level. The main game contains over 180 levels, across four different puzzle modes. Although each mode has a slightly different style of play, they all share the same goal: get the Minis to the star!\n<br><br>\nTake a break from the main game to challenge high scores in four unlockable minigames. Feeling creative? Try your hand at building your own puzzles with an easy-to-use level builder. Once you’re done you can play your puzzles and even share them with other players around the world. Access new levels created by fellow users, and save up to an additional 100 puzzles! Plenty of surprises await you in this rich action-puzzle game.\n<br><br>\nA discount for this title is currently available to My Nintendo™ members as a reward. Go to my.nintendo.com/rewards to learn more.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/a8J5ve5.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3717, '000400000007cd00', 'CTR-N-JLLE', 'Sakura Samurai: Art of the Sword™', 'USA', 59571044, 'eshop', '50010000008943', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5f03569ca62acd8a95825b107f3ade4e9023ed3b3f9aaedb9b3201e7ffd524a1.jpg', 'Leave button mashing behind. Sakura Samurai: Art of the Sword is about precision swordplay, battlefield finesse, and martial-arts style.\n<br><br>\nAs the heroic title character, you’ll travel a world rife with cherry-blossom beauty—and deadly danger—to rescue the legendary Princess Cherry Blossom. Her kidnapper has set dozens of blade-wielding henchmen in your path, and you’ll have to exercise your best battle senses to defeat them and save her. Learn to predict your foes’ moves, deftly dodge their attacks, and create opportunities for devastating counterattacks.\n<br><br>\nStart with the Sakura Sword, a little health, and some basic training from your water-spirit guide. Make your way from battleground to battleground fighting wave after wave of increasingly cunning enemies. Fight through huge castles to duel epic bosses. And don’t forget to stop at small villages along the way to get help, gear, encouragement (and distraction) from the quirky townsfolk. Prove that you truly are the Sakura Samurai!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/1vK2kNR.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3718, '00040000000ae000', 'CTR-N-JA2E', 'Fluidity: Spin Cycle ', 'USA', 191724388, 'eshop', '50010000012044', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/37021d4ab4fa198335ac647e119eee99fb6d7934ee3aca6169c709edbea1e02f.jpg', 'Tilt, turn, and even completely rotate your \nNintendo 3DS™ system  360 degrees to maneuver a puddle of water named Eddy through a mazelike magical world filled with tricky tunnels and crazy contraptions. Change from liquid to a block of ice or a steam cloud to solve fun, gravity-defying puzzles and defeat Goop monsters as you try to rescue the Rainbow Spirits trapped in the pages of a magical book. Each state of water provides the player with different abilities that must be mastered. Levels are designed to be enjoyed over and over while racing the clock to collect all the hidden water pickups and puzzle pieces and maximize your star rating. Each chapter of the book covers a different era, from the lost age of dinosaurs to the modern world—and beyond!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/IL2f81o.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3719, '0004000000107c00', 'CTR-N-JPME', 'Chibi-Robo!™: Photo Finder', 'USA', 484305764, 'eshop', '50010000019533', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1ebd24616aa3df075935c13a8eeffc98294772503ef8523ad2a3f4bad3370bd4.jpg', 'Become one of the world’s best tiny robot helpers by doing your part to open a new museum. Collect Happy Points by vaccuming, picking up trash, and helping a cast of colorful characters, and then use those Happy Points to purchase special film that lets you photograph real-world objects and transport them into the game for the museum’s displays!\n<br><br>\nMr. Curator wants to immortalize objects from your day-to-day life, and it’s Chibi-Robo’s job to collect them! Lead Chibi-Robo on a scavenger hunt, taking photos of real-world objects with the Nintendo 3DS Camera so that he can transport them into his world for the museum’s collection.\n<br><br>\nAlong the way, you’ll meet eclectic characters who need Chibi Robo’s help, like a sushi-slinging squid, a high-flying super hero, and an eccentric pair of chefs. The more happiness you spread, the faster your quest for exhibits can progress. Just make sure Chibi-Robo doesn’t run out of watts. He’s a tiny robot, after all.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/awzaBaa.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3720, '000400000005c800', 'CTR-N-AQ8E', 'Crosswords Plus', 'USA', 15686500, 'eshop', '50010000011489', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7c76fc8cad1adbfa2c2e13a39841e75689acdcbd1881d3ea2a3fa19c63622d1b.jpg', 'The Crosswords Plus game offers over 1,000 professionally designed crossword puzzles at multiple skill levels to challenge all types of players. It is all controlled with the stylus and touch screen to input your answers. Within the crossword puzzles, players will discover 4 different skill levels (Easy, Medium, Hard, and Expert) and an accessible Hint system.  \n<br><br>\nPlayers can work through puzzles at their own pace as they improve their skills. Additionally, new crossword puzzles will be available for download through the SpotPass™ feature at no additional charge (wireless Internet access required). You can also unlock new puzzles by connecting with others through the StreetPass™ feature.  And with the new giant-sized puzzles, players will feel like they are working through multiple crossword puzzles at one time.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/fIMN0mC.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47');
INSERT INTO `3dsgames` (`id`, `titleID`, `serial`, `name`, `region`, `size`, `type`, `contentID`, `iconURL`, `gdesc`, `thumb`, `scrcount`, `imgur_iconURL`, `imgur_thumb`, `count`, `time`) VALUES
(3721, '00040000000b3c00', 'CTR-N-ASRE', 'Brain Age™: Concentration Training', 'USA', 439077732, 'eshop', '50010000012990', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/04e2cd91dc1c3d6b87ca7149e5ced242bcd5725b76f47c0b6747840cc8751e02.jpg', 'Brain Age is back with all-new devilishly difficult brain-training exercises designed by world-famous brain researcher Ryuta Kawashima, MD to refocus the modern mind.\n<br><br>\nPeople today have numerous devices to stay connected (e.g. laptops, smart phones, tablets), and these distractions have led to an information overload making it difficult to stay focused on specific tasks.\n<br><br>\nBrain Age™: Concentration Training brings newly designed training exercises that will challenge players with activities to help improve their concentration skills and the ability to access their short term memory. Spend at least 5 minutes a day to try and better your focus and attention skills.\n<br><br>\nThe new Devilish Training exercises dynamically increase or decrease in difficulty based on your real-time results to help consistently train players at the limit of their abilities.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/HWV9upo.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3722, '000400000013ee00', 'CTR-N-KWDE', 'Woah Dave!', 'USA', 10664804, 'eshop', '50010000026575', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/304a54fc27649c95a8dc2f18dd4cf72f4fc510a1825d641a5142fd8ef392e021.jpg', 'Purchase this game at full price through Nintendo eShop and get a free digital version of Woah Dave! for Wii U. The same Nintendo Network ID must be linked to your Wii U and Nintendo 3DS systems as well as your eShop account prior to purchase in order to be eligible for the offer.\n<br><br>\nOffer applies to US, Canada, and Mexico only.\n<br><br>\nIn Woah Dave!, players gun for digital glory by slaughtering aliens, stealing their loose change, and racking up the highest score possible. Easier said than done, however, as everything on the map—including your own ammo—is trying to kill you. No one ever said being a Dave was easy.\n<br><br>\nThe brave players who manage to survive the alien onslaught and collect the most coins will be rewarded with top placement on the leaderboards. Do you have what it takes to be the best Dave? Or will you end up playing second fiddle to another, more powerful Dave? <BR>\n<BR>\nIf that isn’t enough Dave for you, there’s also Bonkers Mode with more aliens, more lava, and more chances to get killed. Those who brave the storm will be rewarded with a splendor of precious coinage; those who fail will be revoked of their License to Dave.<BR>\n<BR>\nGood luck, and may the best Dave win.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/PphlPJZ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3723, '0004000000066300', 'CTR-N-JMFE', 'Mighty Switch Force!', 'USA', 235473764, 'eshop', '50010000008481', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/90da559f358c58d596cb05a2a8acc05411be18c3106d9945af052ca73181bc31.jpg', 'Space Hooligans have escaped custody and are wreaking havoc all over Planet Land! HQ calls on cybernetic peace-keeper Patricia Wagon to bring these renegades to justice! With the help of Corporal Gendarmor and her trusty Pellet Gun, there''s nothing she can''t handle. When the going gets tough, Wagon activates her Helmet Siren, altering the world around her in 3D space! Even the third dimension can’t hide criminal ne’er-do-wells from the long arm of the law! Enter the mechanical shape-shifting, dimension switching world of Mighty Switch Force and blow crime away!\n<br><br>\nFeatures:<br>\nThe next game in WayForward’s “Mighty” series<br>\nRun and gun action meets brain teasing navigation<br>\nNever before seen three dimensional puzzles<br>\nBring the background to you -- Smash foes against the screen<br>\nWayForward’s signature pixel animation reaches new heights; more colors and higher resolutions than ever before<br>\nPuzzles can be solved in 2D or 3D\n<br><br>\nCheck out the theme inspired by this game in the Theme Shop. Just tap the icon in the upper left corner of your Nintendo 3DS HOME Menu to get started.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/JKkbDmm.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3724, '000400000007d800', 'CTR-N-QAJE', 'Wario Land™ II', 'USA', 5581668, 'eshop', '50010000012814', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4c795025e930b3acef7f7b07e181d8f9ff8f7e5b533d23c87a500cf5df412cce.jpg', 'Original Release Date: March 1999<br><br>\nWhat kind of no-good ruffians would break into my castle and steal my treasures?! It''s that rotten Captain Syrup and the Black Sugar Gang! I''m looking out for bad guys and scavenging for coins as I track down my treasures. If I don''t get them all the first time, that''s OK. I can go back again and again until I find them all. Captain Syrup doesn''t stand a chance against me!<br><br>\nWith lots of hidden treasures, bonus games, and multiple endings, we''re in for our own voyage of discovery!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/dOaJFag.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3725, '0004000000041a00', 'CTR-N-RAGE', 'Super Mario Land™ 2: 6 Golden Coins™', 'USA', 4098916, 'eshop', '50010000007499', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d9f11b61ace450c452983a2f57a48d071a3e910b7f7aaf03f6e0dfb854290ec9.jpg', 'In his greatest Game Boy adventure, Mario faces off against his evil rival Wario, who has captured Mario Land and turned it into his private playground. To toss Wario off his ill-gotten throne, Mario must search all-new worlds for the six golden coins that unlock the gate to Mario''s castle. A mob of monsters, old and new, seek to stop him. Along the way, through six zones, Mario can nab Power Mushrooms, Super Stars and Fire Flowers for extra power. And if he eats the Magic Carrot, he''ll turn into a high-flying hare!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/UMub8ks.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
