(3742, '0004000000182800', 'CTR-N-KHTE', 'Petit Novel series - Harvest December', 'USA', 459180900, 'eshop', '50010000038779', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5f85ad84d292fb317c1862833369efc54bc54135faf39bbb4105b29ae85d4629.jpg', '"Petit Novel series - Harvest December" is a collection of 13 stories set in the small, snowy town of Tagami.<BR>\nFollow Masaki Konno, a teenager prone to falling into sticky situations through his last year of high school.<BR>\nEach month is a new story that connects and leads up to the final installment, "Perfect December".<BR>\nSometimes heartwarming, sometimes violent, sometimes comical, often mystical - for Tagami is known to be a land where a god resides...', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/vVOL6n6.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
