(3779, '0004000000141200', 'CTR-N-KLTP', 'Nintendo Anime Channel', 'EUR', 25492324, 'eshop', '50010000030735', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9c0a5382271404d1c7447e829bf72aba399cf7780c0ceded43dd27129da3babc.jpg', 'The Nintendo Anime Channel is a\nfree, streaming video on-demand\nservice presented by Nintendo. This\nservice allows you to directly stream\nepisodes from anime series to any\nsystem in the Nintendo 3DS family.\n<br/><br/>\nAll content is carefully selected by\nNintendo. New content will be added\nto the catalogue on a regular basis,\nso you can watch the complete series\nof your favourite shows!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/091c6bdaacb8c1fa57c3dc354084f72530ac04683a417a66de560b2275d2039a.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/e5xOT4d.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/OYOrgK7.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3780, '000400000015b100', 'CTR-N-KFLP', 'IronFall: Invasion', 'EUR', 506207076, 'eshop', '50010000030596', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/eaba2f31bb2ac68cad3bdb3d31a9615e397037cf832ecce92671ba9caa676b14.jpg', 'IronFall: Invasion is a thrilling\nthird-person shooter. Equipped with\nan arsenal of destructive weapons,\ntake cover and repel an invasion of\nAlien Robots.\n<br/><br/>\nIronFall: Invasion is divided into two\nseparate modes, which can be tried\nfor free and purchased separately!\n<br/><br/>\nThe "Campaign" mode is a\nsingle-player adventure, which will\nhave you travel from various locations\nover 11 levels.\n<br/><br/>\nThe "Multiplayer" mode allows up to\n6 players to join locally or online for\ncompetitive battles in 6 different\narenas.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Cz9kUL3.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3781, '0004000000141000', 'CTR-N-KRXA', 'Pokémon™ Shuffle', 'ALL', 90962788, 'eshop', '50010000029615', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1a052601b48e09d31afa59abe6409ca3169d01235b33b6858270228c428baae4.jpg', 'Get ready for the latest Pokémon puzzle game! Match three or more Pokémon to clear them from the screen and damage the opponent Pokémon. But watch out—your moves are limited, so use them wisely! With no time limit, you can create the best matches to deal out maximum damage. With many popular Pokémon, including some Mega-Evolved Pokémon, this is the perfect puzzle game for fans and for new players who want to get in on the Pokémon fun.\n<br><br>\nYou can download this game from Nintendo eShop for free and start playing right away! You begin the game with five Hearts. Each stage takes one Heart to play. A Heart takes 30 minutes to recharge, and the game will recharge up to five Hearts only. Jewels, which can be exchanged for more Hearts, can be purchased from an in-game shop with funds from your Nintendo eShop account. You also earn some Jewels in-game. Purchasing Jewels isn’t required to play or enjoy this title.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/vg0iPwa.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
