(3936, '0004000000182300', 'CTR-N-KALP', 'The Legend of Zelda™: Tri Force Heroes Demo', 'EUR', 146160484, 'eshop', '50010000037775', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0547c6df1e4d6cc8c3454594a59d96c9326019a4cd48285d34e3e30ebed97ccd.jpg', 'Connect! Co-operate! Conquer!\n\nBuddy up with two other heroes locally or online (when available) to triumph over enemies and puzzles as a dynamic trio in this exclusive multiplayer demo for The Legend of Zelda™: Tri Force Heroes!\n\nYou need to team up with two other friends in local co-op multiplayer to enjoy this demo.\nEach player needs a copy of the demo, then you can play together using Local Play.\n\nAt the moment, there are no online multiplayer sessions available. We apologise for the inconvenience.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/089053b75af1c121c5b6f6dfc7ff5ffb4a471152a3378dac8886bbee09cef29c.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/FdaKjMV.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/2PjSfPA.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
