(3974, '0004000000121000', 'CTR-P-AHXP', 'Hometown Story', 'EUR', 578009956, 'eshop', '50010000021293', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4c0e534eb9586392acecd590b9e64898ebcef2e8efa7d63e9fbacff98c220a1c.jpg', 'From Yasuhiro Wada, the father of\nthe Harvest Moon series, comes a\nnew heart-warming experience\nfull of fun, laughter and excitement.\nPrepare yourself for a whole new\nlife as you create your own \nHometown Story!\n<br><br>\nHaving inherited a run-down shop,\nit’s up to you to return to your\nhometown and turn the place into\nsomething your late grandmother\nwould have been proud of. Join\nforces with a magical sprite named\nPochica and make new friends as\nthe town grows along with your\nsuccess. Expand the shop, discover\nfantastic new wares to sell, go on\nexciting adventures and even meet\nthe partner of your dreams! Now\nwith enhanced gameplay and new\nfeatures, Hometown Story is the\ndefinitive version of Yasuhiro Wada’s\nvision.\n<br><br>\nGame Features\n<br><br>\n• The definitive version of a new\nadventure from Harvest Moon\ncreator Yasuhiro Wada, Final Fantasy\ncomposer Nobuo Uematsu and\ncharacter designer Atsuko Nishida.\n<br><br>\n• Inherit a run-down store and help\nPochica the magical sprite turn it\ninto the best shop for miles around!\n<br><br>\n• Pick out the right products to\nsell, making sure they’re what\nthe local townsfolk want so they’ll\ncome back for more!\n<br><br>\n• Venture outside and meet new\npeople, collecting materials and\nother items that can be used to\nmeet people’s needs.\n<br><br>\n• The more your shop sells, the\nbigger it’ll get... and so will the town\ntoo! Attract new townsfolk and\nmake both a success!\n<br><br>\n• Relationships made around town\ndevelop over time and people will\nchange; strangers become friends,\nand friends become something more!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/292b59dcde157d650225a3cdbc0d92376e9a05386ba1c5b7e909557f44d79786.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/gpNyMgc.jpg', 'http: