(3992, '0004000000086e00', 'CTR-N-JF2E', 'Fun! Fun! Minigolf TOUCH!', 'USA', 38411108, 'eshop', '50010000009661', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4358b89e2515900462b595fce97d4e8014dd1698952e043a0aca55cbc3fc29c7.jpg', 'Play minigolf with your Mii and master new cups and trick shot challenges in beautiful environments.\n<br><br>\nThe perfect touch controls make for a fun and rewarding putting experience. Customize your Mii to add a personal touch to your game. Play 81 holes spread across America, Asia and Europe. Enjoy exotic locations all over the world. Earn coins and spend them on flight tickets, trick shot qualifications, luxury equipment, and much more.\n<br><br>\nFUN! FUN! Minigolf TOUCH! is the ultimate minigolf game for everyone.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Pnm2ODe.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3993, '00040000000a9700', 'CTR-N-SNNE', 'Paper Mario™: Sticker Star Trailer', 'USA', 31423284, 'eshop', '50010000010436', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6028872d8e56e094f8b13e97b436340957e666a10e2b7f89e28ba71249c8d1eb.jpg', 'Launching this holiday, this classic action role-playing franchise gets a fresh 3D look in its hand-held debut as Mario uses stickers found in the game to win battles and solve puzzles.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/df5042f245e3de6b48fe7828c92824ea486decc3dba1f2fb3fef804b5cd66ec8.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/S5jxO5f.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/7vekQV9.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3994, '00040000000a9500', 'CTR-N-SNLE', 'Luigi’s Mansion™: Dark Moon Trailer', 'USA', 25037620, 'eshop', '50010000010435', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1f280e6c20cebec3d5b0965272005390578d6ed864c7354e9cc05b7dbb7261cb.jpg', 'This action-filled follow-up to the original Luigi’s Mansion for Nintendo GameCube launches for Nintendo 3DS this holiday. Players can expect more haunted mansions to explore and new ways for Luigi to take on a wild assortment of ghosts in this new adventure. In addition to using the strobe function of his flashlight to stun ghosts, Luigi must solve various puzzles and reveal hidden details in the environment to unlock new areas in the mansions.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ae0004b3f9ecbff9736262ed825ec87e321e5066be7b423673db5569b008e0b4.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/Y2NjG3L.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/4OIYQNh.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3995, '000400000008ff00', 'CTR-N-JABE', 'Art of Balance TOUCH!', 'USA', 49650532, 'eshop', '50010000010374', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4fb6149822a4d98aa5b965caf5a66eda254918b8e4bc2e9d64458cf899003643.jpg', 'Grab your stylus and build a balanced stack in this physics-based puzzler!\n<br><br>\nPuzzle games must be addictive. This was our top priority during the development of the game. That''s why we designed 200 levels that not only challenge your skills but also your imagination. With its perfect touch controls Art of Balance TOUCH! is easy to pick up and hard to put away.\n<br><br>\nSeeking a real challenge? Then try out the new endurance mode and drive your score ever higher.\n<br><br>\nArt of Balance TOUCH! brings the ultimate “just one more puzzle” experience to your Nintendo 3DS™.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/feJ7a5n.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(3996, '00040000000c6f00', 'CTR-N-JMUE', 'MH3U Data Transfer Program', 'USA', 12618596, 'eshop', '50010000013695', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/81d959d4ddbfcda4b58b17f380e00859ea553dcd833c4de612268032403ae803.jpg', 'Hunt anytime anywhere! The Monster Hunter 3 Ultimate Data Transfer Program allows players to transfer their Monster Hunter 3 Ultimate saved data from their Wii U system to their Nintendo 3DS. Now gamers can take their hunting from their living room to the streets.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/AElelxk.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
