(4030, '000400000011a000', 'CTR-N-QBBE', 'Pokémon™ Trading Card Game', 'USA', 4750180, 'eshop', '50010000027715', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b662f8082ebee3d5a09a2b7051c71128f56326ad993af3ab199da2748eaca021.jpg', 'The greatest Pokémon™ Trading Card Game players of all time – The Grand Masters – are looking for one player worthy of inheriting the four rare Legendary Pokémon™ Cards!\n<br><br>\nBuild new decks with the Auto Deck Machine, hone your skills on the Challenge Machine, and test your ability in the Challenge Hall. Expand your card collection, duel your way through eight Club Masters, and earn the right to challenge the Grand Master in the Pokémon Dome! Shadowy figures, wise instructors and powerful opponents await you in the ultimate trading card game adventure!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/QPh7kUJ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
