(4117, '0004000000049800', 'CTR-N-RARE', 'Avenging Spirit', 'USA', 3631972, 'eshop', '50010000007183', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/56de2f060e170e132a218d7e886ab74e1d73a98acb38a0e50830fcdcca7c06a2.jpg', 'A classic action game that provided a unique gameplay system of possessing\nand controlling other characters is now\navailable on the Nintendo eShop!\n<br><br>\nWhile out on a walk with his girlfriend, the daughter of a prestigious scientist, our poor hero is gunned down by an evil syndicate that wants to harness ghost energy, and plans on ransoming the poor girl to force her father into helping them. But our hero''s adventure\nisn''t over. In fact, it''s just beginning! He''s come back as a ghost so that he can rescue his girlfriend from her kidnappers and finally rest in peace!\n<br><br>\nWhoever said love was easy? With six fun and exciting stages, help reunite the protagonist with his beloved. Watch the moving ending as this\nhero''s quest for revenge is finally put to rest!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/X450m6J.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
