(4122, '00040000000fd400', 'CTR-N-ABZZ', 'Boulder Dash-XL 3D', 'USA', 39697252, 'eshop', '50010000016293', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2d6d66f7e9a4936ee7a1137048bd4537748f303a812e13d43e2674093a3d284c.jpg', 'Boulder Dash-XL 3D is a classic action puzzler shining on Nintendo 3DS.<br>\nIn this sequel to the 1984 classic, players set forth as Rockford™ or Crystal™ and mine their way through a variety of hazardous, yet stunning, three dimensional Caves. Explore the 100 caves and collect the right number of diamonds, while avoiding Boulders and Enemies to unlock the exit. But hurry… the clock is ticking! The difficulty increases with each new cave and more enemies and challenges will emerge as you progress. After completing a cave successfully, a green checkmark will appear next to it in the cave list. If you complete a level perfectly, a gold checkmark will appear.\n<br><br>\nFeatures Include:<br>\n 4 Varied Gaming Worlds<br>\n 5 Game Modes (Arcade, Puzzle, Zen, Score Attack and Retro)<br>\n Over 100 All New and Exciting Caves\n<br><br>\nCan you master the power ups, transform boulders into jewels, squash enemies, and get to the exit before time runs out and without becoming trapped?', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/mGMX9De.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4123, '0004000000126e00', 'CTR-N-JYHE', 'Pyramids 2', 'USA', 24243044, 'eshop', '50010000026755', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9c559162cbecf0affe96cfa9e8f36f03025fd40ccbecb9d58d665b93875d3bcf.jpg', 'The Pyramid master is back! Enjoy Gaming gives you 54 new levels and 3 new pyramid worlds. New improved and varied gameplay, new features and a built in Editor to create your own levels to play and share with other players. Masses of gameplay, masses of fun!\n<br><br>\nThe creation of new styles of levels with more varied contents has made Pyramids 2 a far more testing game that has more variety than the original very successful Pyramids\n<br><br>\nNEW GAME TYPE\nDarkness levels with Lamps.\n<br><br>\nNEW BONUSES\nEnd level time & Elixir to drink.\n<br><br>\nNEW ENEMIES\nApes, Pygmies & Ghosts.\n<br><br>\nNEW MECHANISMS\nTraps, Heavy blocks, Peak switches, Trap switches, Blocks that can only be destroyed by Flames, Lamps & Black Holes!\n<br><br>\nEDITOR\nCreate and fine tune your own levels,\nExport your levels trough QR Code images,\nImport new levels trough QR Code images,\nSave up to 27 custom levels', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/GNBnrCg.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4124, '000400000007d000', 'CTR-N-JQTE', 'Thriller', 'USA', 40692532, 'eshop', '50010000007764', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fb02f590f0124abafcdbd62f9fd7cf6e9d6b8033200a63daf2fd419b429990d1.jpg', 'Shrek, Fiona and Donkey are in for the\nscariest Halloween of their lives when they attend a midnight musical based on Michael Jackson’s classic video...\nit’s bound to be a Thriller!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/565dfcef76e6944306a213ecd1bf37793be9f1aace362db36c8bd75e82a62cd8.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/bbqsrUc.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/S5Hr0V5.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4125, '0004000000068200', 'CTR-N-JA9E', 'Pyramids', 'USA', 19762020, 'eshop', '50010000007906', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/125aed041981bbd61733e739727415e0377ff158e86c3cc481b5c7f2f909b325.jpg', 'Pyramids is a platform/puzzle game where an explorer tries to get out the pyramids with his loot.\nThe task will not be easy. Many traps, monsters and dangers will put your dexterity and ingenuity to\nthe test. The player will have to use TNT and a gun but his best friend remains his shovel which allows him to create and destroy bricks. These bricks will be used as stairs, bridges, protections...\nThe explorer will venture through 54 challenging 3D levels divided in 6 worlds. At the end of each level, the player will obtain a star rating which will be used to unlock levels:\n<br><br>\n- 1 star for finishing the level<br>\n- 2 stars for finishing the level and stealing all the loot<br>\n- 3 stars for finishing the level and stealing all the loot in a given time<br><br>\n\nThe game will let the player use QR Code to unlock free news levels put on the Pyramids web page.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/R4Wd13M.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4126, '00040000000c1400', 'CTR-N-JAQE', '10-in-1: Arcade Collection', 'USA', 36653924, 'eshop', '50010000015793', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4b054bc98c5a3222e84030c2fbb362be4d60b70dd2fd004c4acb072f49a9ab31.jpg', 'Ten minigames filled with retro arts, music, sound effects and fun. One hundred levels filled with a host of enemies to destroy. Dozens of collectable items and power-ups are waiting to help you achieve victory. \n<br><br>\nBattle against time and enemies to achieve the highest score in each challenge in this 10 in 1: Arcade Collection. \n<br><br>\nEvery minigame has a new 3D approach to the famous classics. Enjoy hours of fun reliving fond memories of your youth and, if you''re too young to remember, see what computer games looked like in the old days!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/isbL6ea.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4127, '000400000013c900', 'CTR-N-SRBE', 'Kirby: Right Back At Ya!', 'USA', 119196468, 'eshop', '50010000023635', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/36bc21acb6d4900f5c5aa4a55ab9d401a880b10d5a21805532846bb71b50d8f9.jpg', 'Congratulations! You’re a Winner!\n<br><br>\nYou’ve won a download of Kirby: Right Back At Ya! from Nintendo Video. Now you can watch both parts of this 3D classic whenever you like. Download it, enjoy it, and show off to your friends because you’re a winner!\n<br><br>\nThanks for entering and tune-in to Nintendo Video for more opportunities to win!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a00ac31be19a1637965a3f55da096fca6e663fb08d2a0ee331444c66f2bbf528.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/hMs3HPz.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/0QqEHMF.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4128, '0004000000093c00', 'CTR-N-QAQE', 'Mario Golf™', 'USA', 5815140, 'eshop', '50010000012169', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b8bb9364fec99ebc666a84731b4a3dc73272995206e0cb266b696b7309cf43d4.jpg', 'Original Release Date:  October, 1999\n\nThe stakes are high in the race to become the Grand Champion of golf. Four Club Champs stand in your way, and you''ll have to defeat them all to get a shot at playing the most famous golfer in the land! Create up to three of your very own characters, and power them up as you play. To improve your game, pick up tips from the other golfers you meet. With four courses, tweleve practice ranges, five play modes, and a variety of minigames, hours of fun is par for the course!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Uvoe3iG.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
