(4130, '0004000000041100', 'CTR-N-RADE', 'Tennis', 'USA', 3447652, 'eshop', '50010000006912', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0c81052967d13db3bffcc34157aab321e84ac8f97b5c6d3c6349b795d6f06768.jpg', 'For fans of the classics and of the sport, this is one to add to your collection.  As seen in the 1989 Game\nBoy™ release, this game allows for realistic match-play action. Choose your opponent''s skill level. Against them, you can practice your power serves, skillfully placed shots, lofty lobs, and killer cross courts. You may even recognize a friendly face on the court--Mario™! He will serve as umpire and call the close ones.\n<br><br>\nGet ready to game, set, and match in Tennis!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/hWwzhau.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
