(4138, '000400000015aa00', 'CTR-N-KPBE', 'PUZZLEBOX setup', 'USA', 57879396, 'eshop', '50010000029175', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a00e708486103d584b13a88291cefbcc642c119590056911456af6398a09f63a.jpg', 'In PUZZLEBOX setup you hold the Nintendo 3DS™ system upside-down. Use the stylus to select a colored tile on the Touch Screen which is then on the upper side. If you release the color the tile falls down in the selected column.<BR>\n<BR>\nLet the matching tiles fall down into the glass bottle on the 3D Screen to copy a painting or to complete a setup.<BR>\n<BR>\nShare High Scores in Miiverse™', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/CbutJQ9.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4139, '00040000000fc000', 'CTR-N-JCXE', 'Bike Rider DX', 'USA', 78642020, 'eshop', '50010000015515', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/133f87542379ff97e74af56e510156af3155902820a221c666158c90d9fb30b2.jpg', 'Enjoy a new kind of jump ''n run action, riding your bike on bumpy roads, crossing deep valleys and dodging all kinds of obstacles. Travel the globe to be the champion of the WORLD TOUR mode, or break the highscore in the endless GRAND PRIX mode and see how far you can go.\n<br><br>\nYou can use a variety of power-up items like the "Air Ride" and make use of fun gimmicks such as giant whirlwinds on your way through the stages! Will you be able to collect all gold coins and unlock the special bonus stages?\n<br><br>\nJust jump! - Everyone can quickly become familiar with the controls, while a large variety of stages and modes provide fun for both newcomers and experienced gamers!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/OShz5g1.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4140, '0004000000051e00', 'CTR-N-AQ9A', 'Pokédex™ 3D Pro', 'ALL', 438315876, 'eshop', '50010000010264', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d2765e982f7b1a9815b0c112914b86a9de86befa3f5f14ae33fcde4c797de49a.jpg', 'The Perfect Companion Application to Pokémon Black Version 2 and Pokémon White Version 2\n<br><br>\nThe Pokédex 3D Pro application is a fully enhanced and upgraded version of the original Pokédex 3D application. It includes detailed information about more than 640 Pokémon from the Pokémon video game series. The Pokédex 3D Pro application also includes in-depth sorting, comparison and ranking tools, as well as comprehensive details about the moves each Pokémon can learn, and how and when each Pokémon evolves. Additionally, the application features augmented-reality capabilities, including the ability to take photos of Pokémon in the real world.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/317cb303b99e0bbad6453782d838839d9df10961c4b3cc03a181a25baec05649.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ToT7Goa.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/DemMu8B.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
