(4204, '0004000000171700', 'CTR-P-RCVA', 'Pokémon™ Version Bleue', 'ALL', 10267492, 'eshop', '50010000038521', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e2efa6b30e0eaa27efbae9b3f33158fbd75a9deb4b6ebeb3d029cfff5b5497b2.jpg', 'With classic graphics and music, Pokémon Red and Pokémon Blue Version stay true to the originals released nearly 20 years ago. You’ll feel like you’re playing them just as they were, but now you can trade and battle Pokémon using local wireless on the Nintendo 3DS family of systems! Revisit these timeless games, or play them for the first time!\n<br><br>\nExperience the original journey that started the Pokémon phenomenon nearly 20 years ago, but now on the Nintendo 3DS family of systems as a digital download! Relive the feeling of catching your very first Pokémon from the original 150, complete with monochromatic pixel art and 4-bit background music. You’ll take on the role of a Pokémon Trainer and travel across the land searching for amazing creatures called Pokémon. Catch, battle, and trade as you face Gym Leaders and try to stop Team Rocket! If you want to catch the original 150 Pokémon, you’ll need to trade wirelessly with your friends.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/zN5XFQd.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4205, '00040000000d3e00', 'CTR-N-QAWP', 'Mario Tennis™', 'EUR', 6888292, 'eshop', '50010000018953', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/875bb70631ebb6c1ff3992e7f82dfff8907d707005a6a20ba1680c896b6b9b45.jpg', 'The Game Boy™ Color version of\nMario Tennis is a winning mix of court\naction and RPG. Train your character\nfrom novice to pro as you rise through\nthe ranks of the Royal Tennis\nAcademy, before taking on the\nchampion himself: Mario!\n<br/><br/>\nBuild up your skills in Mario Tour\ncareer mode, jump right into the\naction with exhibition matches and\nrelax with minigames while playing as\nLuigi, Donkey Kong and more. There\nis even a dictionary to help you brush\nup on your tennis terminology!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/26e261e8c4e34aae2699b01c05a8b9c832920e572e8b33f9d89bedc0c76c761a.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/NZaoR3U.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/LoGWAoi.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4206, '0004000000171800', 'CTR-P-QBHA', 'Pokémon™ Version Jaune', 'ALL', 10263396, 'eshop', '50010000038519', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/cbaad17d2b8ec4cfa57f0727f603184a7531438178c1b852e44d5f24004b4034.jpg', 'With enhanced color graphics and Pikachu by your side, Pokémon Yellow Version stays true to the original game released nearly 20 years ago. You’ll feel like you’re playing it just as it was, but you can trade and battle Pokémon using local wireless on the Nintendo 3DS family of systems! Revisit Pokémon Yellow Version or play it for the first time!\n<br><br>\nExperience one of the original adventures that began the Pokémon phenomenon, but now on the Nintendo 3DS family of systems! Set out on your adventure together with your friend Pikachu, complete with monochromatic pixel art, 4-bit background music and, for the first time in the series, enhanced color elements. You’ll take on the role of a Pokémon Trainer and travel across the land searching for Pokémon with Pikachu. Catch, battle, and trade as you work to become the best Pokémon Trainer! If you want to catch all of the Pokémon, you’ll need to trade wirelessly with your friends who have Pokémon Red or Pokémon Blue Version.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/RkGTxbE.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4207, '00040000000bba00', 'CTR-N-GATP', 'Sonic the Hedgehog™', 'EUR', 5700452, 'eshop', '50010000013413', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/94df56d320dc2cf9ec3e38ffeaf66f90563760edb049c627b46916681538bfd6.jpg', 'Get into gear with Sonic the\nHedgehog! Originally released for the\nGame Gear, play as Sonic as he\nspeeds through zones and frees\nanimals from their mechanical prisons\nwith his devastating spin attacks!\nBlaze through five super challenging\nzones and defeat all of Dr. Eggman’s\n(AKA Dr. Robotnik) machines in order\nto put an end to his evil schemes!\n<br/><br/>\nFeatures:\n<br/><br/>\n- Dash through five super\nchallenging zones with three acts in\neach zone.\n<br/><br/>\n- Soar through bonus levels\nbrimming with springs, bumpers,\nflippers and more.\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/pCiPOQG.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4208, '0004000000041600', 'CTR-N-RAEP', 'QIX', 'EUR', 4008804, 'eshop', '50010000007040', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1ccf89e2c98272c845e1d681fe31f922da1986f2ca025f121dcac9d75a2d05bf.jpg', 'Released on Game Boy in 1990, this\nversion of QIX has not lost its appeal!<br>\n<br>\nQIX is an acclaimed arcade classic in\nwhich your goal is to capture areas of\nthe playing field by drawing Stix\n(lines) with your marker. Capture the\nplaying field step by step by drawing\nmore and more closed shapes, but\navoid the unpredictably moving,\nsticklike Qix and the Sparx traversing\nthe edges.<br>\n<br>\nPerform well enough and you might\neven see Mario, Luigi and Princess\nPeach make an appearance!<br>\n<br>\nThis version of the game does not\nhave multiplayer functionality.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b1e0e803db1b23d58777aee0a224f549a3e7b63e858eb855a384249a3bd353f7.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/VEzq3Yl.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/OdLxI1h.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4209, '00040000000be600', 'CTR-N-QAVP', 'Shantae™', 'EUR', 8760164, 'eshop', '50010000015174', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/34859f3ef71613aa757e10d626f3b6940033aff9aa24f70cd200faeca342b404.jpg', 'Take control of Shantae, the\nhair-whipping belly dancing Guardian\nGenie of Scuttle Town. In the\nadventure that started it all, Shantae\npursues the nefarious lady pirate Risky\nBoots through burning deserts,\ntwisting labyrinths and haunted forests\nin search of magical components that\ncould mark the end of Sequin Land.\nMake friends, battle monsters and\ntake down steam-powered pirates –\nit’s all in a day’s work for Shantae!\n<br/><br/>\n- A platform/quest game of epic\nproportions!\n<br/><br/>\n- Whip monsters using Shantae’s\nmagical ponytail.\n<br/><br/>\n- Belly dance to transform into a\nmonkey, elephant, spider and more!\n<br/><br/>\n- Over 50 enemy packed locations\nthat change from day to night.\n<br/><br/>\n- Power up with magical items, relics\nand fighter’s gear.\n<br/><br/>\n- Dance Parlor, Gecko Match and\nfootrace mini games!\n<br/><br/>\n- Multistage boss battles and a killer\nsoundtrack!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/183c10f9cd1e3fa20b359de68313b1ab916a0eeb3877586d9faa5507b16570bd.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/uCpsk7M.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/oAuhdvd.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4210, '000400000008b100', 'CTR-N-RBZP', 'Kirby''s Pinball Land', 'EUR', 4893540, 'eshop', '50010000010427', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7080d09228f697896543306ff683ec287d200ac21ecf916d9569b20adebc024c.jpg', 'Take a spin with Kirby in this\nGame Boy™ classic, to defeat King\nDedede and his minions through the\npower of pinball!<br>\n<br>\nBounce Kirby around three\naction-packed tables filled with\nenemies, bonuses and secrets galore.\nKick back with wacky minigames and\nbattle the bosses at the end of each\nstage.<br>\n<br>\nKirby''s Pinball Land is filled with fun\ntouches that Kirby fans will love and\nplenty of action for pinball wizards to\nflip over!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5a8a7784072b3493c93d9c971d402f2efbf7c1ea995e2d5dfd5b1fac4e78bfdd.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/2XO3mMP.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/kO68GFP.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4211, '0004000000050500', 'CTR-N-RA4P', 'Metroid™ II - Return of Samus', 'EUR', 5192548, 'eshop', '50010000007948', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ab2a7eae7cb90415e0d81e5bc138a5ed220a6cb701729fabff373fd33b10e72a.jpg', 'The Game Boy''s exclusive chapter in\nthe Metroid series sees Samus Aran\non a mission to rid planet SR388 of\nthe Metroid menace.\n\nBattle through a sprawling\nunderworld, seeking out every last\nMetroid, and build up your arsenal by\ndiscovering mysterious artifacts.\n\nEnjoy new abilities like the Spider\nBall, and powerful new weapons like\nthe Plasma Beam, as you eradicate\nthe Metroids once and for all.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6041602763869ec7dda8f123214050152f4ddb6bf9212cbbafa148547ea4105c.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/yXNfBbu.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/SiduQYu.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4212, '0004000000058200', 'CTR-N-RBCP', 'Trip World™', 'EUR', 4111204, 'eshop', '50010000008403', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a63e390c75f2f4614a7128a9cfd6ea46359a79fb01648ab258fed24a469ad7b7.jpg', 'Trip World is a cute platform game\nstarring the innocent-looking yet\nheroic Yakopoo, who can transform\ninto various different forms.<br>\n<br>\nWhen their symbol of peace, the\nFlower of Maita, is stolen, the people\nof Shabubu began fighting each other.\nEven the grass and plants are in a\nfrenzy! Only Yakopoo can save the\nday.<br>\n<br>\nAdvance through each world by using\nYakopoo''s transformations. Fly, swim,\nbecome a bouncing ball and more,\nand retrieve the flower.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ba557c24ecdc55f0494c28b39df4d8387be3ad5241d94ec4d97abfb2089ab0bc.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/eQH325A.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/vlo6TDK.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4213, '00040000000ff400', 'CTR-N-TDWP', 'Street Fighter 2010: The Final Fight', 'EUR', 7109476, 'eshop', '50010000026116', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e83629a02a29be24f8e3cc47f660b588f5b299494183b23d030ea9b8d8348698.jpg', 'Ken from the Street Fighter™ series\nbecomes a bionic warrior, out to\navenge the death of his friend, in this\nspin-off side-scrolling shooter. Aliens\nhave stolen a superhuman serum so,\nwith his newly enhanced abilities, Ken\nmust battle across the planets to stop\nthem.\n<br/><br/>\nUse your weaponry and athletic skills\nto liberate each planet, and seek out\nspecific target enemies to clear the\nstage. Ken can backflip to evade\ndamage, which can be upgraded to\nperform a powerful kick. It''s time to\ntake the fight from the streets and\ninto space!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0c897870459cc259a3269f0f6bc9ef497a264c5aec37eaa1c8094d6916649ce9.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/0yV7nOj.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/iQwtBdN.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4214, '0004000000094100', 'CTR-N-TAUP', 'MIGHTY BOMB JACK™', 'EUR', 6990692, 'eshop', '50010000012266', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/16f88d8ae2c6e41b183a003a5290296554d4e7794098da883ff863e189fb43bd.jpg', 'When the royal family is imprisoned\ninside the Great Pyramid of Evil by the\ndemon Belzebut, it''s up to Jack, the\nonly remaining heir, to rescue them.<br>\n<br>\nAs Mighty Bomb Jack you must jump\nand glide through treacherous\ncorridors and enemy-infested rooms,\ncollecting bombs and treasures as you\ngo.<br>\n<br>\nJack can increase his abilities by\ncollecting Mighty Coins - but don''t be\ngreedy or you''ll be sent to the\nTorture Room!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/73aa37e22e753c341bc3bea753dd90b2489dfab4f29b13e3c32c52dc4134e608.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/EGnfj1X.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/2XYQjKo.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4215, '000400000004ff00', 'CTR-N-RA2P', 'ADVENTURE ISLAND', 'EUR', 4299620, 'eshop', '50010000007910', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ed7d6ade65538c91969ac1d486278fd853f22e9fda0e75642fc984427529ffa3.jpg', 'Master Higgins is back! Help him\nsearch through uncharted islands for\nthe missing princess Tina! Grab a\nskateboard and dash across savage\nlands filled with spiders, cobras,\nskeletons and more! Crack open\nmonster eggs to free your dinosaur\nbuddies - they''ll give you a wild ride!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ab61df46ebda914111a1c4c2ccfde6d1cbcf409c6dcd511d6f5f4a0dc9ed4ab2.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/3DKTbNh.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/IpUSVU5.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4216, '000400000004f900', 'CTR-N-RAYP', 'CATRAP', 'EUR', 4316004, 'eshop', '50010000007612', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/66697e7ad0f0eb0f1be49e3619ace25b638881e426ad0d8095723ebff182ebbc.jpg', 'One day a boy and a girl going out\nfor a picnic mistakenly stumble into a\nforbidden haunted house and are\nturned into cats. In order to return to\nnormal, Catboy and Catgirl have to\nmake their way through 100 rooms of\nan underground labyrinth!<br>\n<br>\nHelp Catgirl and Catboy push around\nblocks to bridge a path to defeat the\nmonsters. If you make a mistake,\nsimply use the rewind function and\ntravel back in time to correct it.<br>\n<br>\nCATRAP is more than just a game of\nmindbending intrigue and action. Be\nthe architect of the underground\nlabyrinth and make your own levels of\nintricate mazes.<br>\n<br>\nWhether you choose to be a maze\nbuilder or a maze solver, we know you\ncan help Catboy and Catgirl land on\ntheir feet.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ca2c37b32eb36509739c7aa49be4aaaf4dec9381e0943b2ec76b1b28e68992ec.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/2i4HZ1l.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/DYZ51Tk.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4217, '000400000004f500', 'CTR-N-RAXP', 'GARGOYLE''S QUEST', 'EUR', 4369252, 'eshop', '50010000007232', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a7108aa94de118196bf88266cb869a6cd2b7c842d62eaa248e69e0ba41f64e0f.jpg', 'The fascinating epic adventure from\nthe Game Boy era makes a comeback\non the Nintendo 3DS!<br>\n<br>\nYou are the Gargoyle Firebrand, the\nproud guardian of the Ghoul Realm.\nThe Destroyers have returned to wipe\nour your planet… and they take no \nprisoners!<br>\n<br>\nUse your breath of fire and your flying\nability to combat the enemy. Fight\nheroically, and you''ll recover stolen\nmagic items that will strengthen you\nfor your many battles.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/cccfc70cda32d9e5652a9eaf37a8c527bc22ca8193627137c257fc285d646dc8.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/vMUGRwh.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/3OQMVnr.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4218, '0004000000069500', 'CTR-N-RBLP', 'Kid Icarus™ Of Myths And Monsters', 'EUR', 5081956, 'eshop', '50010000009575', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/20cd93b17eedf7d21a65fd552cabb39177f3478b44a3e67e4090411ad895b17b.jpg', 'First there was Kid Icarus for NES\n(and now 3D Classics for Nintendo\n3DS) in which angelic warrior Pit\nfought against the forces of Medusa.<br>\n<br>\nFive years later, Pit returned in Kid\nIcarus: Of Myths and Monsters for\nGame Boy; expanding on the original\nvertical-scrolling action game with a\nside-scrolling action-adventure, as Pit\nfaces off against the forces of the\nmysterious demon Orcos.<br>\n<br>\nIt would take 20 years for Pit to take\nflight again, in Kid Icarus: Uprising for\nNintendo 3DS!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/728182714d51aed3c6cee312620e4c03ceddf7498a28017573e1969240966595.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/vL4SlzF.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/UDIshpz.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4219, '0004008c00169600', 'CTR-M-BDVP-00', 'Dragon Ball Z: Extreme Butoden Update', 'EUR', 57344, 'dlc', 'none', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4220, '0004000200169601', 'CTR-T-BDVP', 'DRAGON BALL Z: Extreme Butoden Demo', 'EUR', 92090368, 'demo', '50030000006766', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4221, '0004000000088400', 'CTR-N-GAEP', 'Columns™ ', 'EUR', 5696356, 'eshop', '50010000012903', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/748bff735400c62570724d703f74c72e7a05c18babb9c6e1b97c7aaf191f69bc.jpg', 'Drift back in time to a bygone\ncivilisation, the ancient world of\nPhoenicia. Play a game that\noriginated among the Phoenician\nmerchants. It''s incredibly captivating,\nyet easy to pick up. You''ll find\nyourself losing track of time!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/i8ba1N3.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4222, '0004000e00166f00', 'CTR-U-KW2P', 'Comic Workshop 2: Update', 'EUR', 2393444, 'update', '50010000035735', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f98e560c3e20b8565f6b671efc398b8703be10fe38cb24a58edb763b1c97f80b.jpg', '- An auto-correction for curves has\nbeen added. Making quick curves will\nnot result in straight line segments\nanymore.\n<br/><br/>\n- Preview icons displaying the size of\nvarious tools like the Pencil, Text or\nBlur tools have been revised to look\nmuch sharper.\n<br/><br/>\n- Fixed a critical error occurring\nwhen making small selections when\nthe zoom level is higher than 100%.\n<br/><br/>\n- Density level for the Pencil, Eraser\nand Straight Lines has been improved.\n<br/><br/>\n- A display bug when making small\nand thin panels has been fixed.\n<br/><br/>\n- The size of texts appearing in\npop-up windows has been adapted for\nbetter readability purposes.\n<br/><br/>\n- Other small bugs have been fixed.\n<br/><br/>\nThis is an update for the Comic\nWorkshop 2 application.\n<br/>\nThis download does not contain the\nfull version of the title.\n<br/>\nIn order to use this update, you must\nhave the full version of Comic\nWorkshop 2.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e8495c5658d198e08067641f446543b259f29da59450efa5721bcf877921e3a8.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/3iHRTSH.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/gV5nXnA.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4223, '000400000009b600', 'CTR-N-GANP', 'Crystal Warriors', 'EUR', 6343524, 'eshop', '50010000014578', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a27b16536fe53f4b7823993c97966630cb0c48f5982e44b425149165d7a8a31f.jpg', 'In the Kingdom of Ariel, four\nelemental crystals have long\nprotected the land and its inhabitants,\nbut an evil force has appeared to\ndestroy this peace by stealing them!\nWith the kingdom in turmoil, guide\nPrincess Iris in her quest to recover\nthe lost crystals from the evil Jyn.\n<br/><br/>\nIn this classic strategy game, arm\nyour warriors and tame monsters to\nfight alongside you against Jyn’s\narmies!\n<br/><br/>\nDo reconnaissance and arm your\nwarriors in town. Fight and tame\nbeasts to fight against your enemies!\n<br/><br/>\nOver five unique classes to use\nagainst Jyn’s forces!\n<br/><br/>\nChallenge a friend via local\ntwo-player multiplayer!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/DI5mQuT.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4224, '000400000009b700', 'CTR-N-GAJP', 'Defenders of Oasis™', 'EUR', 6490980, 'eshop', '50010000013135', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/12cf52d716e99a29ad0a1739081773695d80ccf89af52cc4e42bf8a296d6ab38.jpg', 'Once captured by heroes of a bygone\nera, the foul wizard Ahriman has been\nsummoned by dark forces and his\narmies now threaten to ravage the\npeaceful land of Shanadar. As the\nprince of the kingdom, rally powerful\nallies to your side and lead them\nonward to repel Ahriman’s forces\nthroughout the kingdom in this classic\nJapanese role playing adventure.\n<br/><br/>\nRecruit unique allies such as a\nprincess, genie and thief!\n<br/><br/>\nFight enemies to gain strength and\nupgrade your heroes’ weapons and\narmour in order to fight Ahriman.\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/18x54X7.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4225, '000400000009b800', 'CTR-N-GARP', 'Dr. Robotnik''s Mean Bean Machine™', 'EUR', 5970788, 'eshop', '50010000014094', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/085ce5702bef587380276d5d75ebcb94eaf3cb5da8c36b177ea0221381e7ba87.jpg', 'The evil Dr. Eggman (AKA Dr.\nRobotnik) has built a machine that will\nturn the poor people of Beanville into\nmachines, but there’s safety in\nnumbers! In this colourful puzzle\ngame, help them out by pairing them\ninto groups of four matching colours\nso they can stick together and escape\ncertain doom!\n<br/><br/>\nFeatures:\n<br/><br/>\n- A challenging puzzle game! Pile up\nfour bean folk of the same colour so\nthey can stick together and escape!\n<br/><br/>\n- Defeat Dr. Eggman’s henchmen in\norder to reach the evil doctor and\nsave Beanville once and for all!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/xBrVaMK.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4226, '0004000000088800', 'CTR-N-GABP', 'Dragon Crystal™', 'EUR', 6019940, 'eshop', '50010000009806', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/414fdbc12d0290b663a33629bb584574266b6994ac91cbf4b5a65d8cd2a108e1.jpg', 'Imagine a glowing magic crystal. As\nyou gaze into it, an intense force pulls\nyou in and causes a blackout. You\npinch yourself. But you don''t wake\nup. You''re caught in a fantastic world\nof unearthly beauty and deadly\ndemons. Here, countless evil forces\nconfront you. Your only ally is your\nloyal pet dragon.<br>\n<br>\nBlaze a trail through the treacherous\nlabyrinths of four magic kingdoms -\ncollecting weapons, armour, magic\nbooks, potions, rods and rings as you\ngo. Fend off enormous insects,\nmonstrous centipedes and sneaky\nsand sharks.<br>\n<br>\nPass through 30 worlds in search of\nthe Magic Goblet. There''s no way out\nof this musical nightmare...until you\nfind it.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/PCASD5v.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4227, '000400000009b900', 'CTR-N-GAPP', 'G-LOC™: Air Battle', 'EUR', 5708644, 'eshop', '50010000013494', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/471b21149e2f8a3bb9cffb9e3b8ffc4a427d51a926fcca17f84ee5bc70a12cae.jpg', 'Strap yourself in and take to the\nskies in G-LOC Air Battle. Dive, climb\nand bank as you outmanoeuvre enemy\npilots and blow them out of the sky\nwith your impressive arsenal. Gain\nexperience with every mission and\nequip yourself with more powerful\nweapons and armour in order to\ndestroy the Future World Army and\nbring peace back to the skies.\n<br/><br/>\nChallenge a friend via local\ntwo-player multiplayer!\n<br/><br/>\nTrade points earned for more\npowerful missiles, high calibre guns\nand armour upgrades.\n<br/><br/>\nNine different air, land and sea\nmissions.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Ae6kzOp.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4228, '000400000009bb00', 'CTR-N-GASP', 'Shining Force™: The Sword of Hajya', 'EUR', 6138724, 'eshop', '50010000014433', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b6c93e9c6ddae82a422cbf3364f5dfd33009ee37fb0836184c60a35dcdc77679.jpg', 'The peaceful Kingdom of Cypress has\nbeen disrupted by the corrupt ambition\nof the evil King Iom. Terror rampages\nacross the land as the Castle of\nCypress is invaded and the magical\nSword of Hajya is taken! It will take\nstrength, courage, agility and your\nkeen sense of strategy to defy this\nominous power and bring peace back\nto the land.\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ZrCuW3B.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4229, '0004000000088600', 'CTR-N-GACP', 'Shinobi™', 'EUR', 6036324, 'eshop', '50010000009807', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/63632d75759bbfbad0862d188d6217f322700ac1678fab4ad806876269716bd9.jpg', 'Only you can save them.<br>\n<br>\nAs Joe Musashi, Red leader of the\nOboro School of Shinobi, your destiny\nawaits. An evil force emanating from\nNeo City has captured your fellow\nstudents. Attack with your powerful\nkatana as you battle for their freedom.\nEach ninja you rescue adds their\nformidable weaponry, training and\nNinjutsu magic to yours.<br>\n<br>\nDestroy the enemies with bombs,\nshurikens, a crescent blade and more.\nUse the magic of the ninja to wreak\nhavoc with the force of a tornado or\nthe blinding glow of lightning. When\nall else fails, turn your body into a\nliving bomb and explode with\nconcussive damage. Do not stop until\nthe City of Fear is annihilated! Are you\nready for the challenge of Ninja\nwarfare?<br>\n<br>\n-Special abilities include running on\nwater, swinging from a crescent blade\nand walking on ceilings<br>\n<br>\n-Ninjutsu magic includes tornadoes,\nearthquakes and energy fields', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/AmHak97.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4230, '0004000000096b00', 'CTR-N-GAGP', 'Sonic Blast™', 'EUR', 5917540, 'eshop', '50010000010377', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/49a60e3b39f636d01e6b731cea739a8b1f76146230f76f1b70da838c13429a10.jpg', 'Sonic the Hedgehog, Knuckles the\nEchidna and their world blast off in\nthis fully rendered Game Gear classic.<br>\n<br>\nThe evil genius Robotnik has stolen\nthe Chaos Emeralds and it''s up to\nSonic and Knuckles to stop him.\nLuckily, Sonic has new moves and\nother special power-ups to defeat the\nevil genius. Travel with Sonic and\nKnuckles through a maze of traps, evil\nrobots and fearsome scenery to prove\nto Dr. Robotnik that there''s no trap\nmade that a determined Hedgehog or\nEchidna can''t overcome.<br>\n<br>\n- Play as Sonic or Knuckles as you\nrace through 14 levels in search of\nhidden power-ups.<br>\n<br>\n- Use Sonic''s new Boost Blast to\njump up to hard to reach areas. Take\nadvantage of Knuckles'' climbing skills\nto gain extra points.<br>\n<br>\n- Look out for Big Rings to enter\nbonus stages where there are extra\nlives and Chaos Emeralds to be found.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/XJ1moDp.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4231, '0004000000088500', 'CTR-N-GADP', 'Sonic Drift 2', 'EUR', 6253412, 'eshop', '50010000013495', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f86e45d66448ff0069cfdf24b98b487ec33e7166f1c2167348e2fb92c34c38f3.jpg', 'Start your engines and prepare for\nthe race of your life!Choose from\nseven of your favourite Sonic\ncharacters including Sonic, Knuckles\nand Dr. Eggman (AKA Dr. Robotnik)\nand race your way to the finish line.\nUse each racer’s special ability to\ngain an edge over the competition and\nwin the fabled Chaos Emeralds!\n<br/><br/>\nRace across 17 courses in the\nultimate Chaos Grand Prix!\n<br/><br/>\nChallenge a friend via local\ntwo-player multiplayer!\n<br/><br/>\nChoose between seven classic Sonic\ncharacters including Sonic, Tails,\nKnuckles, Amy Rose and the\nnefarious Dr. Eggman!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/gPTmTRb.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4232, '0004000000096900', 'CTR-N-GAFP', 'Sonic Labyrinth™', 'EUR', 5725028, 'eshop', '50010000010295', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c62a3a50d2d072c7f6a73953640aa7fc55d07301eecc5492c2fddf6eeaa9299d.jpg', 'Dr. Robotnik has tricked Sonic into\nwearing a pair of magical sneakers\nthat prevent Sonic from running at\nsuper-sonic speeds. Sonic thought\nquickly though: "These sneakers keep\nmy feet from moving fast, but they\nwon''t slow down my Super Spin\nDash!" The only thing that can restore\nSonic''s speed are the Chaos Emeralds\nhidden in Dr. Robotnik''s super\nlabyrinth. Help Sonic find the Chaos\nEmeralds before his time runs out as\nhe spins through four Labyrinth zones,\neach containing three regular stages\nand a Boss stage.<br>\n<br>\n-Step into special sneakers to make\nyou run faster. But hurry, the power\nonly lasts a short time<br>\n<br>\n-Use square warp gates to help you\nfind special items<br>\n<br>\n-Grab 100 rings in the bonus stage\nto win an extra try', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ODMZLT2.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4233, '0004000000088700', 'CTR-N-GAAP', 'Sonic the Hedgehog™: Triple Trouble', 'EUR', 6372196, 'eshop', '50010000009808', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9dd03defa2e3086f4e329b8aea86195252bc9a7d04f888527a1731d62e75557f.jpg', 'While the evil genius Dr. Robotnik is\ntesting the ultimate destructive\nweapon, one of his assistants makes a\nmistake, causing his lab to explode\nand scattering five Chaos Emeralds\nacross the planet Mobius. Sonic and\nTails spin-dash to rescue them. Tricky\nKnuckles streaks right behind, with\nsticky-fingered Nack the Weasel\njoining the hunt. It''s a triple-threat\nrace to see who will get the Emeralds\nfirst!<br>\n<br>\n-Three times the action and Triple the\nTrouble! Loop, blast and super\nspin-dash through six zones, five\nbonus rounds and a wild 3-D stage.<br>\n<br>\n-Check out Sonic''s moves as he jams\nwith his awesome Strike Dash,\nJet-Boards on snow and ice, rolls in\nhis Spin-Coaster and swims deep\nunderwater with Propeller Shoes.<br>\n<br>\n-Help Tails as he submarines through\nwater with his Sea Fox and Heli-Tails\nto explore parts of the zone beyond\nSonic''s reach.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/uiL7Enp.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4234, '00040000000dcb00', 'CTR-N-GAVP', 'Tails Adventure™', 'EUR', 6105956, 'eshop', '50010000014452', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5789f5f1c51d7ff679056b6e8a1c17b32c127abc35235f049fad0a434e4f8e39.jpg', 'Sonic’s trusty sidekick flies solo in\nhis very own adventure! When Tails\nstumbles upon a small part of what\nlooks to be a very large machine, he\ndecides to embark on a journey to\nfind its source!\n<br/><br/>\nAs Tails, fly through 12\naction-packed stages on a quest to\ngather all the mechanical parts and\ndiscover the secret of their origin.\n<br/><br/>\nGather items to augment Tails’s\nvarious abilities!\n<br/><br/>\nUse your wits to defeat enemies\nacross 12 stages, in order to discover\nthe origin of the mysterious machines!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/PCtxiNC.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4235, '000400000009ba00', 'CTR-N-GAQP', 'Vampire: Master of Darkness', 'EUR', 5823332, 'eshop', '50010000012612', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/14229c8314c54751fac6cfefd6f491d58bc74ac71d98ebfe5d1486379c248cad.jpg', 'The shadow of Dracula has spread\nover Victorian England. Make your\nway through strange and forbidding\nstreets and cavernous warehouses\nwhile fighting his army of monsters.\nFind Dracula, the Master of Darkness,\nand rescue England from his terrifying\ngrasp.\n<br/><br/>\nArm yourself with powerful weapons\nranging from swords to bombs and\npistols!\n<br/><br/>\nDefeat terrifying monsters across five\nrounds in order to put an end Dracula.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/MDKTVH2.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4236, '000400000011a900', 'CTR-N-QBDP', 'Bionic Commando™: Elite Forces', 'EUR', 6441828, 'eshop', '50010000027555', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/df5880ba163ad0f1af75e2f4573fe905e4d54dd1b34a08c8a979ba16a88da4c9.jpg', 'You are the perfect soldier; a\nsynthesis of human and machine. You\nare the Bionic Commando! This\nfast-paced Game Boy Color exclusive\nblends elements from previous\nversions of the classic platform shoot\n‘em up and adds new features of its\nown.\n<br/><br/>\nChoose from a stealthy female or\npowerful male commando, and battle\nthrough more than 20 diverse levels.\nEnjoy favourites like communication\nscreens to contact your HQ or to tap\ninto enemy transmissions, plus all-new\nelements like a first-person sniper\nmode to take out enemies at a\ndistance.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fa7e80d6b003dc47cf7383752480328c581893ee4108836e6161723f4d1fdc74.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/OQPuONB.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/eKLwTzD.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4237, '0004000000061d00', 'CTR-N-QAEP', 'Blaster Master Enemy Below', 'EUR', 5565284, 'eshop', '50010000007999', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/89592094af8e827409fd49f32d09b06ef1bc08ad8158b700a5e4fafddef69136.jpg', 'An old enemy has returned, and the\nworld is once again in danger. Only\nJason, hero of the original Blaster\nMaster, and his all-terrain tank Sophia\nthe 3rd can save the day.<br>\n<br>\nBlaster Master Enemy Below brings\nthe series’ trademark mix of action\nand exploration to the small screen.\nShoot through enemy-infested\nenvironments in your tank, and then\njump out to continue the fight on foot.<br>\n<br>\nExplore eight sprawling catacombs,\nbattle bosses to win upgrades for\nSophia the 3rd and delve deeper into\nthe enemies’ lair.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e1e02bd0d00f1a014269ab6a7fe30c0904fed0bb0313a2119ec99330d8a1e10f.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/866Z9fY.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/Pbrn7mQ.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4238, '0004000000082c00', 'CTR-N-QAKP', 'Game & Watch™ Gallery 2', 'EUR', 5409636, 'eshop', '50010000010294', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d4416bc67d09b4b67b02500caa61b101d55e18d56ed7a3ddbb5471416a48edfe.jpg', 'Game & Watch Gallery 2 is a\ncollection of five classic handheld\ngames; playable in their original 80s\nversion and a remastered version with\nenhanced graphics, sound, and new\ngameplay.<br>\n<br>\nParachute - catch the parachutists\nbefore they fall into the sea.<br>\n<br>\nHelmet - dodge the falling tools and\nhead for the shed.<br>\n<br>\nChef - juggle ingredients with your\nfrying pan as long as you can.<br>\n<br>\nVermin - use your mallets to keep the\nmoles and other critters at bay.<br>\n<br>\nDonkey Kong - destroy the platform\nbelow DK while avoiding the barrels.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8850e82241ead4a0c86b9d0abcb252fec41e27fb11bc9968f17ed85c91e516b0.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/XjhKEb7.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/6jEJtHx.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4239, '000400000010ff00', 'CTR-N-QA6P', 'Game & Watch™ Gallery 3', 'EUR', 5466980, 'eshop', '50010000025995', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b61081d5107729d5f1c5e6140d260d7f3910fd05ae99bc07dce669084f5339d2.jpg', 'Flash back to the ''80s with Game &\nWatch Gallery 3, featuring original\nand updated versions of five handheld\nclassics. Experience the original\nLCD-style versions plus modern\nremakes with enhanced graphics,\nsound and gameplay.\n<br/><br/>\nEgg: catch them before they hatch.\n<br/><br/>\nTurtle Bridge: carry the packages\nacross the turtles'' backs.\n<br/><br/>\nGreenhouse: protect plants from\npesky pests.\n<br/><br/>\nDonkey Kong Jr.™: grab the key and\nfree DK.\n<br/><br/>\nMario Bros.™: help Mario™ and\nLuigi™ keep the factory flowing.\n<br/><br/>\nPlus, play well and you can unlock\nnew features and even hidden classic\ngames!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/93c3e85fb64af3c9939e80a0a2ab9351991656a594da6f34e76109218523526c.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Z5bktXw.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ZjNjs6A.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4240, '0004000000099e00', 'CTR-N-QATP', 'Legend of the River King™', 'EUR', 5909348, 'eshop', '50010000013430', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/74ead0f8f205eb25259193aaf781cea5848b052541da3c124f2e1a521766a9fc.jpg', 'Cast off on a unique role-playing\nadventure! Legend of the River King\ntasks you as a young fisherman\nseeking a mystical fish to cure his sick\nsister.\n<br/><br/>\nEndure a perilous quest; angling\nthrough streams, rivers and raging\nrapids. Sell your fish at local markets\nto buy supplies, and do battle with\nlocal predators trying to steal your\ncatch.\n<br/><br/>\nYou can also raise a virtual pet fish\nand watch it grow, and even evolve\ninto another species.\n<br/><br/>\nIt’s an aquatic quest that will test\nyour bravery, skill, heart and -\nindeed - sole!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1c3d6ce6c806da535157041cb15b07ad938fd3ab77adb41ef2716af60e1687be.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/SYA3jHS.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/A5cVeij.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4241, '0004000000110600', 'CTR-N-QA9P', 'Legend of the River King™ 2', 'EUR', 5503844, 'eshop', '50010000026536', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6c6102804efce99a24b6ba278aaef9b58a2e4814c81e5db280ca1c49cab7aac0.jpg', 'When a mystical jewel to control\nnature is stolen, it’s up to you and\nyour brother to retrieve it by searching\nthe vast waters of your land, putting\nyour fishing skills to the ultimate test.\nFirst you’ll need to fish for small fry\nto feed yourself and to sell for better\ntackle and rods, before you take on\nthe big catches.\n<br/><br/>\nLegend of the River King 2 is a\nmassive role-playing adventure\nfeaturing all types of angling from\nfresh water fly-fishing to deep-sea\ntrawling. Plus, try your hand at bug\nhunting and flower picking, too.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9ff51e07f577a2bafc8929640b4fa2e6f7674db26cfc73d18faeccbe8729b754.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/EaYq866.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/pIhxcmz.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4242, '000400000011ab00', 'CTR-N-QBEP', 'Lufia®: The Legend Returns', 'EUR', 6355812, 'eshop', '50010000027618', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9303b7cc2f995d912f3b2213cde6c1f07e151da7d037aca22b89c752262a2e40.jpg', 'Wain always wanted to see the\nworld, but he never expected he\nwould end up fighting to save it!\nFollow the young warrior and his\ncompanions on an epic adventure that\nspans vast continents, as you try to\nstop an ancient evil.\n<br/><br/>\nThe third in the series, and the first\nfor a handheld system, Lufia: The\nLegend Returns features 12 playable\ncharacters, each with their own unique\npersonality and special attacks, plus a\ncompelling storyline and in-depth\nbattle and magic systems, including\nthe return of Infuriating Point special\nattacks.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/feea8481e2cc45c943c616dbf258540415406d31bb888ce2848fe6fd589fc61e.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/79B69Po.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/YEW7IUC.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4243, '00040000000f0400', 'CTR-N-QAZP', 'Mega Man™ Xtreme', 'EUR', 5331812, 'eshop', '50010000025475', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/397e58efb9b84b875349af4b546c852c228fcd072f51faa3fe3f5477f27ceeee.jpg', 'Many years ago, Mega Man X—a blue\nrobot possessing high intelligence, a\nkind personality and formidable\npower—was found and studied by Dr.\nCain. The scientist attempted to\ncreate more in the likeness of the\nrobot, calling them ''Reploids''.\nHowever, some of the Reploids began\nto malfunction, and these were called\n''Mavericks''. The ''Maverick Hunters'', a\ngroup of capable Reploids like Mega\nMan X, Zero and Sigma, was\nassembled to fix the situation.\nHowever, one day, Sigma revolts and\nhacks into the Mother Computer,\ncausing the Mavericks to grow in\npower.\n<br/><br/>\nWith chaos brewing on the horizon,\nMega Man X must join forces with\nMiddy, a genius hacker, and his\npartner Zero to restore peace. Blast\nthrough the past, defeat strong\nrobotic enemies and obtain new\nabilities as you clean up crime in this\naction-packed platformer!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/FmvAFzt.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4244, '00040000000f0100', 'CTR-N-QA2P', 'Mega Man™ Xtreme 2', 'EUR', 5679972, 'eshop', '50010000025615', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3487d890f8ea60de9a4b7e6b3c07c5c5929747c385a8bce53d3fb0df547bed53.jpg', 'In MEGA MAN Xtreme 2, return to\nthe worlds previously seen in the\nMega Man™ X series, and play as\neither X or Zero, facing a new danger\nthat threatens all Reploids.\n<br/><br/>\nReploids are being turned into lifeless\nshells as if their souls have been\nerased, so X and Zero must hunt\ndown the culprits. Switch between X\nor Zero as you battle enemies and\ndefeat deadly bosses.\n<br/><br/>\nGather power-up parts to increase\nyour abilities, equip special weapons\nunique to X or Zero, and solve the\nmystery to restore the Reploids''\nmissing souls!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e0e7a966ec3b92a0312fdbec7ed0327dd5fb006d10a921bab753e7998bb4455e.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/J2BSXYd.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/lZwCr1n.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4245, '0004000000119e00', 'CTR-N-QBAP', 'Pokémon™ Puzzle Challenge', 'EUR', 6683492, 'eshop', '50010000027620', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/152ef14bde932b6ffb1f0a3db738f06200de08ad889a4fe6b692b344d513686a.jpg', 'Journey to Johto for a different kind\nof Pokémon challenge, as you put\nyour puzzling skills to the test against\nthe toughest gym leaders! Classic\nPokémon like Pikachu, Chikorita,\nTotodile and Pichu will help you take\non challengers and rival Pokémon.\nUse your lightning-fast reflexes to\nclear blocks and form chains and\ncombos to rack up huge scores.\n<br/><br/>\nChoose from six thrilling modes\nincluding Marathon, Challenge, Time\nZone, Line Clear, Puzzle and the\ngripping Garbage! mode as you try to\nhang on for big points while blocks\nrain down.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3a6a1f000c726372e71162ffa2f9d9a3cfc2fc59f116fa8fa0020f7ca6524b4e.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/FP767gT.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/pI26W0b.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4246, '0004000000069b00', 'CTR-N-QAGP', 'Prince of Persia', 'EUR', 5028708, 'eshop', '50010000008942', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e60528b76e1025d799a2b91b94d564adf78c34cd7d0ea006b65be414d8a298b0.jpg', 'The classic Prince of Persia is now\navailable for download! Relive this\nclassic platforming game that is often\nheralded as a pioneer of the\nplatforming genre. This re-release is\nfaithful to the original game, complete\nwith the dashing acrobatics of the\nPrince that made the original famous.<br>\n<br>\nTraverse sprawling levels, dodge\ndeadly traps like spikes and\nguillotines, clash swords with palace\nguards, before facing the evil Grand\nVizier and rescuing the princess. But\nbe quick: you only have one hour! The\nsands of time are flowing...', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b94551f4dcfa2d4cc5060767843bda45f93d778aa821a517fdb2cfdbe56e0faa.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ZNCY75X.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/zcf9WXM.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4247, '0004000000083700', 'CTR-N-QALP', 'Rayman®', 'EUR', 8043364, 'eshop', '50010000009729', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/50662e3c8c22c984fc8dac1825abffa8192d1691784ddd41ec1b17ef12267317.jpg', 'Rayman, the critically-acclaimed\nclassic platforming adventure, is now\navailable! Known for its\ngroundbreaking animations and music,\nRayman is a game that stands the test\nof time. One fateful day in the Glade\nof Dreams, the evil Mr. Dark threatens\nthe world and traps the Electoons.\nIt is up to Rayman to free them and\ndefeat evil forces.<br>\n<br>\n- Over 25 levels of platforming\nmadness.<br>\n<br>\n- Explore seven unique worlds.<br>\n<br>\n- Menacing enemies and an epic boss\nbattle.<br>\n<br>\n- Fun for all, but difficult to defeat...', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4f9731c396d39e6c759bf43cbc47e22802adbbb87c5f72ef8fa7ab3a4c219a23.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/AmVWuyx.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/BRyZUhu.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4248, '0004000000094d00', 'CTR-N-QARP', 'Toki Tori', 'EUR', 5253988, 'eshop', '50010000011446', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/aa686905f667ce2b32961e9a0c064aa6fc24e37aa4b63c37fb6866c3938cad13.jpg', 'He may be a small, yellow chicken,\nbut Toki Tori is no coward! He''s the\nhero of this egg-cellent puzzle\nplatformer in which he must rescue all\nhis kidnapped brothers and sisters,\nstill in their fragile eggs.<br>\n<br>\nIn this Game Boy™ Color classic, you\nmust keep Toki Tori safe, avoiding\nmonsters and traps, while working out\nhow to collect all the eggs in each\nlevel before the timer runs out.<br>\n<br>\nLuckily, there are lots of items to aid\nToki Tori''s mission; so what are you\nwaiting for? Time to get cracking!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c8e67d6e1ab266fcaca2ff0f36b235d4a7549724aa631b805a1e9c8e952e7882.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/JHArUQ8.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/OFsBk2C.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4249, '00040000000f0300', 'CTR-N-QA4P', 'Xtreme Sports', 'EUR', 8694628, 'eshop', '50010000024715', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/75a0d217c6aee63bacb0788382cc0b4aa95cd92eba7f5cb43166046f53cd75a8.jpg', 'The Xtreme Cola Company has invited\nall-comers to Xtreme Island to\nbecome the Xtreme Sports champion!\nGuppi and her boyfriend Fin take up\nthe challenge, with your help!\n<br/><br/>\nFrom the makers of cult classic\nShantae comes this colourful spin on\nhigh-adrenaline sports. Try your hand\nat surfing, street luge, in-line skating,\nskateboarding and even skyboarding!\n<br/><br/>\nExplore the island to find friends,\nfoes and even a few hidden treats.\nPractise hard and then compete in\nevents to win medals; there are more\nthan 400 to collect!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c3683e0c455793cc3e8baf00d23fd2ed90bc6e07dd81f94d9116f97ac53824ce.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/l3947Z5.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/Cs18bXe.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4250, '00040000000b5b00', 'CTR-N-TBZP', 'Life Force', 'EUR', 13265812, 'eshop', '50010000018738', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/99c77e4b7f2c4cf70aee30a0f0e638f3fdf15545b16faba6c14348889557123f.jpg', 'Pilot the Vic Viper on a mission to\ndestroy an enormous alien that\nthreatens to devour the galaxy!\n<br/><br/>\nClassic shoot ‘em up Life Force is a\nspin-off of the seminal Gradius series,\nfeaturing six stages that take place\ninside the gigantic creature,\nalternating between horizontally and\nvertically scrolling environments.\n<br/><br/>\nCollect capsules to gain new\nweapons and power-ups, and defeat\nthe bosses at the end of each stage.\nGo it alone or team up with a friend in\nthe cooperative two player mode via\nDownload Play.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9bdf73e2b32f54be46565fbf622f9f4b32cd8548df40dafb508934314cac10e4.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/kZsbG53.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/AuR67AA.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4251, '0004000e00169600', 'CTR-U-BDVP', 'Dragon Ball Z: Extreme Butoden Update', 'EUR', 35019620, 'update', '50010000040037', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a338428025d382b291f93a8da7a16a4222dda53672ec811cd053c0eb4437d951.jpg', 'This update brings new content\nto the game:\n-More than 10 new Z-Assists\ncharacters including Goku (Farmer),\nMira, Towa, Broly SS4…\n-Training Mode\n-Extreme Survival mode\n-Online Battle Mode to fight friends\naround the world', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/95f430e7278127f5736c9549ca71bedaa6ea1e975eefc9a02bb663781df9f296.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/vZNvC4N.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/sIdSGis.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4252, '0004000000180200', 'CTR-N-KGVE', 'Gunslugs 2', 'USA', 22645604, 'eshop', '50010000037875', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/cc537d22fc62361a631806cead38164baa25a5ae78641a4da3bbf10cbf2dcd8f.jpg', 'The black duck army is back! They are sending signals into space, which can''t be good... In fact, the army has teamed up with aliens! You and the gunslug squad have to defeat the risen army with all their might again before its too late. And of course the slugs have enough equipment to do that. Flamethrowers, tanks, guns and many more are at your disposal and ready to kick some alien butt! ', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/4NIyfu6.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4253, '0004000000041000', 'CTR-N-RACP', 'Alleyway™', 'EUR', 3971940, 'eshop', '50010000006767', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4146a7280a4fef921812e035c72d3dd38381a4d9cbb310ead1cb927b988db78a.jpg', 'Originally released at the launch of\nthe Game Boy, Alleyway is a fondly\nremembered update to the classic ‘bat\nand ball’ style of games.<br>\n<br>\nThe aim is simple: survive and rack up\na huge high score! Take control of the\npaddle and deflect the ball to break\nthe blocks, but don’t let it drop.\nBreak all the blocks to move onto the\nnext of 32 challenging stages.<br>\n<br>\nIt starts out simple but later levels\nintroduce walls of blocks that move\nhorizontally or vertically. You can also\nenjoy bonus stages where the aim is\nto break as many blocks as possible\nwithin the time limit.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/spYeFnX.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4254, '0004000000049700', 'CTR-N-RARP', 'Avenging Spirit', 'EUR', 4344676, 'eshop', '50010000007153', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8eb806a9c9ed3685c6e3b7bb46d2b9b144cb1c713046607bc65e48ea6a53e173.jpg', 'You have been deep sixed by\ngangsters and turned into a ghost.\nTo make matters worse, the mob has\nkidnapped your girlfriend and held\nher for ransom, they want the secret\nof ghost energy.<br>\n<br>\nTo rescue her and get even with the\nmob, you must inhabit any one of 20\ndifferent creatures and search for\nyour girlfriend on 6 dangerous levels.<br>\n<br>\nSo grab a body, any body, make a\nbeeline to the big rescue, and rescue\nyour doll face.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a10152c4d917399442a560c8db826a0334abe0352f3bb2000d9fe9e901b86aa4.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/gusWq48.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/kcgPdad.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4255, '0004000000067300', 'CTR-N-RBEP', 'Balloon Kid™', 'EUR', 3902308, 'eshop', '50010000008841', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/34eaa63db509aa3f87d16cee9de61b67898e414f421ad3019257e7af0ff891cb.jpg', 'Take to the skies on a trip through a\nland filled with danger, with nothing\nbut balloons to keep you afloat!<br>\n<br>\nWhen her brother is swept away on\nthe wind, Alice must save him by\nfloating through eight perilous stages.\nNavigate your way through enemies\nand obstacles, collect balloons to\nearn bonuses, or let go of your\nballoons to face enemies on the\nground.<br>\n<br>\nAlso, in Balloon Trip mode, negotiate\nincreasingly tricky levels to earn a\nhigh score and move up the ranks.\nWill you rise to the challenge?', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/50d2fcfd40959785610b4d78001b10eca490cc9fe1f38f99441e893242d15565.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/31OU7zl.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/samsyDP.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47');
INSERT INTO `3dsgames` (`id`, `titleID`, `serial`, `name`, `region`, `size`, `type`, `contentID`, `iconURL`, `gdesc`, `thumb`, `scrcount`, `imgur_iconURL`, `imgur_thumb`, `count`, `time`) VALUES
(4256, '0004000000040d00', 'CTR-N-RABP', 'Baseball', 'EUR', 4897636, 'eshop', '50010000007052', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0156141e77c7707e79ada5e0dc8db8e8b89c9f4e26298dd1d16a22344169eba4.jpg', 'Strategy, skill and determination.\nIt takes all three to win in Baseball!<br>\n<br>\nChoose a starting pitcher from your \nbullpen (Mario is an old favourite). \nHurl fastballs past the batter. If he \nconnects, your outfield backs up to\nsnag a fly. A sturdy infield backs you\nup on grounders and pop-ups. \nThree outs later and your team is up. \nTake a strike to feel out the pitcher. \nThen drive a long one. \nIt''s a home run! <br>\n<br>\nYou can even choose between \nAmerican or Japanese-style modes.<br>\n<br>\nThis version of the game does not\nhave multiplayer functionality.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/26ef325e19a0dbff89ad7099f7cca8b4c08a102965030de48b2f30198d9653ce.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/XFkA0na.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/g3eXKCL.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4257, '0004000000058500', 'CTR-N-RBDP', 'BIONIC COMMANDO™', 'EUR', 4885348, 'eshop', '50010000008004', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f0dda5212ce71ce3b20b76bfefd71bcbbc4ac53d76c1d65bf0845db7e6b6d90b.jpg', 'A ruthless army stands ready for war,\nbut the one man who can stop it has\nbeen captured. As Rad Spencer, the\nBionic Commando, use your high-tech\ngrapple hook and assault rifle to\ninfiltrate the enemy’s stronghold in a\ndaring mission to rescue Super Joe.<br>\n<br>\nThis Game Boy™ version of the NES™\nclassic brings you all the\nplatform-swinging, gun-toting action\nof the original plus a brand new\ngraphical style. Reunite with your ally,\ntake out the evil Director Wiseman,\nand bring peace to the world.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0a237dbebc0f2cd50ad432bbe3faa559e56632f9b9a2f1961fd434595f187ca4.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/zHrufqV.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/5nh0k0i.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4258, '0004000000050b00', 'CTR-N-RA6P', 'Burger Time DELUXE', 'EUR', 4074340, 'eshop', '50010000007841', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b766e6407834c0431f6f6b4dcd71e85e3b3536bfd4d6e041ea37fdd652867bb6.jpg', 'Chef Peter Pepper has a problem. A\nrival is out to stop him from creating\nthe ultimate burger, by sending his\nevil food minions to take over his\nkitchen.<br>\n<br>\nYou must dodge deadly hot dogs,\npesky pickles and evil eggs, as you\ntraverse the platforms to assemble the\ningredients for your burgers.<br>\n<br>\nFortunately, Peter has one weapon\nthat instils fear in any food foe: his\ntrusty pepper grinder. Burger Time\nDeluxe is a classic that never goes\nstale!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9eaf820d4b165b15f3f94d702c5246b22e54c098c60d35e13225250f447a8041.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/9FOG53T.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/VBIN721.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4259, '000400000007df00', 'CTR-N-RBPP', 'Castlevania The Adventure', 'EUR', 3955556, 'eshop', '50010000010420', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1b377ed5fbc9cd0f67929e4a15b5d3819404c5aebddee0866fb3c88a1278cf5b.jpg', 'Count Dracula has risen from his\ngrave to threaten Transylvania, and\nonly the chosen one - who wields the\nmystic whip - can stand in his way.<br>\n<br>\nCastlevania The Adventure was the\nfirst of the series to appear on\nGame Boy™. Taking place before\nthe original Castlevania™ for NES™,\nit stars Christopher Belmont, ancestor\nof the original game''s hero Simon.<br>\n<br>\nWield your trusty whip, seek out\nupgrades to increase its power, and\nbattle Dracula and his minions to save\nthe day.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/33988a6c69d1c01fac5487d937bacf3cd3b993a649bf007c606ac94776d38d36.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/3MgMFVG.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/PJkIewZ.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4260, '0004000000050200', 'CTR-N-RA3P', 'Donkey Kong™ Land', 'EUR', 5225316, 'eshop', '50010000026295', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0d80e6c5fbd59c492ddfb5e38dd13f208fe3c277026d40abd0ebbe4ca0932629.jpg', 'Donkey Kong teams up with his\nsidekick, Diddy Kong, on a new\nadventure in this platformer inspired\nby the classic Donkey Kong Country™.\n<br/><br/>\nFace flying pigs, deadly Zingers and\nreptilian Kremlings, as you journey\nthrough a mysterious pirate ship,\nperilous snow, an unbelievable\nunderwater temple and crazy capers in\nthe sky.\n<br/><br/>\nFun fact: the original Game Boy\nversion was released with a special\nbanana-yellow Game Pak!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7dc16adcb6b2b204c49dc7c0a9b2485ddbec9c23a7d78303ebc6764a97e01f22.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/R7k5IDG.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/zCwQ2cj.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4261, '000400000011a400', 'CTR-N-RCJP', 'Donkey Kong Land™ 2', 'EUR', 4758372, 'eshop', '50010000026555', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/035d2782bb53e3486dac0bbd5b2e3b5bc3ba8dbb4a9ad1ae6e7e6f03cab59e8c.jpg', 'Donkey Kong has been kidnapped by\nthe evil King K. Rool who is\ndemanding his entire banana hoard as\na ransom! Rather than give up the\nprecious stash, Diddy Kong teams up\nwith Dixie Kong to rescue their pal.\n<br/><br/>\nWhile the story may be familiar to\nfans of Donkey Kong™ Country 2, the\nlevels are all new. Jump in with Diddy\nor Dixie and enlist the help of friendly\nanimal buddies like Rambi the Rhino,\nSquitter the Spider, Enguarde the\nSwordfish and Squawks the Parrot to\nbring DK back to safety!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4c9566602269a5370d2e4c470e65c40ea7cfe5377e252b2508dd9497b3eda0ae.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/8GeS2Lh.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/SGrUmr3.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4262, '000400000011a700', 'CTR-N-RCKP', 'Donkey Kong Land™ III', 'EUR', 4729700, 'eshop', '50010000026539', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0affd02613643067fcece67eae6b82d3e9f9e2797ba5e8b4cea613b682c3ce08.jpg', 'Donkey Kong™ and Diddy Kong™\nhave gone to seek their fortune by\nfinding the fabled Lost World, leaving\nDixie Kong™ literally holding the\nbaby. However, Dixie decides to find\nthe Lost World before anyone else,\nbringing cousin Kiddy Kong™ along\nfor the ride.\n<br/><br/>\nPlay as Dixie or Kiddy across 36\nKong-sized levels of platforming\naction and adventure. Get a little help\nfrom your animal friends Squitter the\nspider, Squawks the parrot, Ellie the\nelephant and Enguarde the swordfish,\nas you seek out secrets to uncover\nthe truth behind the Lost World!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/695992289e1839000746c2ac2a242e189fddf6add22b9a0928e2ccf7a682f2c4.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/9VjbxSD.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/Gqc80Gt.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4263, '0004000000049d00', 'CTR-N-RAUP', 'Double Dragon', 'EUR', 4062052, 'eshop', '50010000006909', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9efb8aa4aa0d9aa51c3fafd5335772c6b77261b88c9bf7a8c5f606e5e7471369.jpg', 'Re-experience the first handheld\nappearance of the acclaimed Double\nDragon series!<br>\n<br>\nIn this side-scrolling beat ''em up you\nfight your way through rival gangs''\nturfs using jumps, punches, kicks and\nmore to save the kidnapped girl\nMarian.<br>\n<br>\nThis version of the game does not\nhave multiplayer functionality.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/23c436152dd1433ab07631b02e67f86f60053975c1dd8ece89216d2ffc420ffe.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/8EJ2ooQ.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/AjLrUrz.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4264, '0004000000050800', 'CTR-N-RA5P', 'Dr. Mario™', 'EUR', 4078436, 'eshop', '50010000007949', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2a1d84307bdab953ad45022dd3fdb0e559ba548466b1161ed5d4fc255b88112a.jpg', 'At Mushroom Kingdom Hospital,\nnasty viruses are on the loose. It''s\ntime to give them a dose of Mario''s\nmedicine!\n\nIn this classic puzzle game you must\neradicate all the viruses in the bottle,\nby spinning and lining up the coloured\nvitamin capsules as they fall.\n\nThe more lines of viruses you clear,\nthe more points you rack up, scoring\nhuge combos. But beware of\nside-effects: this game may be\naddictive!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/064bf23f314b9efee741ccf73f1059fb87beb46104e9f573625cf45388cbdd2e.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/Bm7tnU0.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/S8KGqMz.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4265, '0004000000046d00', 'CTR-N-RAQP', 'Fortified Zone', 'EUR', 4221796, 'eshop', '50010000007039', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7b581d16d4110706a50b0dc170ca5abedede1bb6e8786207834a3b65d6ae8ec9.jpg', 'Two special operatives on a\nseemingly impossible mission: To\ndestroy a gigantic enemy fortress from\nwithin and stop the development of a\nsecret weapon.<br>\n<br>\nMasato Kanzaki and Mizuki Makimura\nare forming a team that complements\neach other perfectly: Masato is a true\none-man army who once destroyed a\nwhole tank battalion single-handed!\nAdd the certified genius Mizuki whose\nagile moves have earned her the\nnickname "The Leopard" and there''s\nfinally hope to take down the fortress.<br>\n<br>\nThis version of the game does not\nhave multiplayer functionality.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4eb21957158a8dad5047b597a912adf5b6acd533abe02b2d5343e1c7c4b64455.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/T6yreQ7.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/3ftZIZ5.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4266, '0004000000042500', 'CTR-N-RAKP', 'Game & Watch™ Gallery', 'EUR', 4852580, 'eshop', '50010000007042', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1fa355a405c17b4871fb3c84441984f403f7ce1da7fa943f49ec8a29ee2e0f63.jpg', 'Game & Watch Gallery is a revival\nof the classics: four masterpieces\nfrom the Game & Watch series!<br>\n<br>\nManhole:\nKeep up with the moving pedestrians\nand do not allow them to fall into\nuncovered manholes.<br>\n<br>\nFire:\nThe building is on fire! Can you safely\nbounce the escapees to the\nambulance?<br>\n<br>\nOctopus:\nAvoid the tentacles and dive\ndown to the treasure stowed in the\nchest.<br>\n<br>\nOil Panic:\nThe pipes are leaking! Catch the\ndripping oil and find a way to get\nrid of it.<br>\n<br>\nBesides the Classic Mode, all games\ncan be played in the exciting Modern\nMode that combines the simple\nmovements of the original games with\nnew graphics featuring your favourite\nNintendo characters!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0ebcea0a5a8ab59e086808fc30210eaef067df4bb7fb7ea9cf3b1b5539a7d25d.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/KLObWNY.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/Lsi91UZ.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4267, '0004000000042d00', 'CTR-N-RALP', 'Golf', 'EUR', 4864868, 'eshop', '50010000007662', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8855765ece8ca4cea4de45177d84902aa1808362f25a13349421b41c56479965.jpg', 'Bogey, par, birdie, or eagle.<br>\n<br>\nThe score is up to you.<br>\n<br>\nGolf is 18 holes of realistic links\naction. Each hole has tricky hazards,\nso strategy is a must.<br>\n<br>\nRead the wind direction, check the\ndistance, select a club, adjust your\nswing and keep your eye on the ball.\nNow drive it home.<br>\n<br>\nFrom twisting fairways and hungry\nsand traps to big water hazards and\ndeceptive greens, Golf is packed with\nchallenges.<br>\n<br>\nThis version of the game does not\nhave multiplayer functionality.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/293ba9975238d026be7944a7ce3ddf01d0aed23fc4c5d67a01dadd6fc3c402ce.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/V1ua5mj.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/NZyskfh.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4268, '0004000000042200', 'CTR-N-RAJP', 'Mario''s Picross™', 'EUR', 4746084, 'eshop', '50010000007041', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/adc79d046ab3bc774d57d6f89b3f06f170c3c4b9bc330ccf2662a59709a118fd.jpg', 'In the 1995 puzzle classic Mario’s\nPicross, over 200 challenging picture\npuzzles await to be mastered.<br>\n<br>\nReveal the hidden pictures in each\npuzzle by filling in the correct squares\nin the grid. Hint numbers at the edges\nwill tell you how many squares in\neach row or column should be filled.<br>\n<br>\nAfter completing the regular picross\nmodes, a Time Trial mode will put\nyour picross skills to a true test.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/63ed02c090493a8ca29379aa7d03f99ca80b5672a497f42b6e676f58ec3fd2db.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/cxwk6aR.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/YU9VEZp.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4269, '00040000000ef300', 'CTR-N-RCDP', 'Mega Man™ 2', 'EUR', 4303716, 'eshop', '50010000024555', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a4cfcb2e3bde4003cefc59dc55f7eecf991192749bb5a8b9828976f32d4860b2.jpg', 'Dr. Wily is up to no good, once\nagain. This time he’s stolen an\nexperimental time travel device and\nzipped off to the future! Meanwhile,\nMega Man and his trusty sidekick,\nRush, are sent on a mysterious\nmission to investigate an underground\nlair.\n<br/><br/>\nJump and blast your way through a\nbarrage of maniacal enemies while\ncollecting a variety of weapons and\nitems to help fight more Robot\nMasters! Who is this stranger from the\nfuture called Quint? Can Mega Man\nreach Dr. Wily before time''s up? So\nsuit up and let''s go!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5c9cfbcfd1b1efacd8ac10c35c1597a9a58646c46064243be2187bebaa555de7.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/d8TBTV6.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/SqQw23n.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4270, '0004000e00160c00', 'CTR-U-BX2E', 'Project X Zone 2 Update Ver. 1.2', 'USA', 10861412, 'update', '50010000039505', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b5bc348cf324f70b116cee9eff1c510551a5a9e98b754b8f29be53260b4db303.jpg', 'This is an update for the Project X Zone 2 game. This download does not contain the full version of the title. In order to use this update, you must have the full version of Project X Zone 2.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/189fec8c4f0aaa3ca7df947b895a9a0a3d4e52098e2447eb544d691f17b9433c.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/KP5DMEP.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/gT8JgMT.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4271, '0004000000183700', 'CTR-N-KHSE', 'BRAVELY SECOND™: END LAYER DEMO', 'USA', 338062180, 'eshop', '50010000039636', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d818d4e95b1cbbacb7662bfda8378a5999b90dbdfbd025f9b8a5e30146a9b85f.jpg', 'Square Enix’s critically acclaimed Bravely Default game is all set to enjoy a much-lauded sequel and you can try a portion of it out right now, for free! In the Bravely Second™: End Layer demo: The Ballad of the Three Cavaliers, you’ll return to the land of Luxendarc and embark on a bonus adventure not found in the main game.\n<br><br>\nJoin the Three Cavaliers on a mission from Her Holiness Agnès Oblige to investigate strange happenings in the desert of Harena. Make sure to try out different jobs during your adventure—mix and match abilities and secondary job commands to take down tough enemies and bosses. Whether they’re formidable fighters and mages looking to test their skills, giant trolls with a chip on their shoulder, or alien entities with a bent for drama, all of them pose a risky challenge…along with the irresistible promise of great rewards.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/NJmoBE3.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4272, '0004000000096100', 'CTR-N-JVVP', 'VVVVVV', 'EUR', 63605604, 'eshop', '50010000010296', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8a6f2ccbf56cd5fc5307e3737875d1d234a52859f78b290562c80436b6d56e7f.jpg', 'There''s something terribly wrong in\nan alternate dimension! Help Captain\nViridian flip to find five crew members,\n20 hard-to-reach Trinkets and save a\ndimension on the brink of destruction.\nIt''s a space opera in the most unique\nscale with a style that only VVVVVV\ncan bring to you. Instead of jumping,\ncontrol the direction of gravity by\ninverting your gravity and allowing\nCaptain Viridian to flip between the\nfloors and ceilings of the\nenvironments.<br>\n<br>\nFor adventurers who save the\ndimension, there''s still hours and\nhours of new gameplay with all-new\nPlayer Levels. Test your mettle and\nsee if you have what it takes to beat a\ncollection of levels created by other\nfamous game developers. Inspired by\nclassic 8-bit days gone-by and now\nwith experience-heightening 3D,\nVVVVVV will challenge even the most\nbattle-hardened old-school gamers.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/IminHwH.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4273, '0004000000079100', 'CTR-N-JJZP', 'Luigi''s Mansion™ 2: 3D Trailer', 'EUR', 19723572, 'eshop', '50010000007493', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d41b2bdf4224644792521eb77ac153fed1edfb4ce0303b38b5ac727051ab1c8c.jpg', 'This is a downloadable 3D trailer\nof Luigi''s Mansion™ 2, released\nto coincide with the Nintendo\n3DS Conference 2011 that took\nplace in Tokyo.<br>\n<br>\nIt also enables you to receive\nfurther notifications about Luigi''s\nMansion™ 2 via SpotPass.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c7d1f6176715f48706c765c3a3a079f97f029d3cba5adbfc7ce0cfd0b6c8718a.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/EVCIwgu.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/Erhi3Ex.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4274, '00040000000ad000', 'CTR-N-SNLP', 'Luigi''s Mansion™: Dark Moon E3 2012 Video', 'EUR', 29915956, 'eshop', '50010000010527', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2e834ccdb0c102f9cb9193c221a06676753af43c830e7a221e8458638382ea5a.jpg', 'Luigi™ is back and on a mission to\nremove a bunch of stubborn ghosts\nfrom some spooky mansions. Armed\nwith his trusty Poltergust\nghost-sucking vacuum cleaner, he will\ntry to act brave as he bumbles his way\nthrough the darkness while trying to\ncapture these pesky phantoms.<br>\n<br>\nThis trailer was made for E3 2012.\nThe title name displayed in this trailer\nis intended for the North American\nmarket, and may vary with the title for\nthe European market.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b17a9c908fe13c28d6a7408fecc90c6cf9540610f3fe1365cb8bfb819c11b6ed.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/wRVJlgf.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/hIz3STN.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4275, '000400020016e901', 'CTR-T-BM9P', 'Etrian Odyssey 2 Untold: The Fafnir Knight (Demo)', 'EUR', 152387584, 'demo', '50030000007766', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4276, '0004000000106200', 'CTR-P-AHBP', 'Nintendo Pocket Football Club™', 'EUR', 401480548, 'eshop', '50010000021258', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c16bdde0219006c748fcdc43b8daa1cbe39e17ef289ef836d3edbd09af37cc1b.jpg', 'Head up your own football team and\nshoot for the top! Nintendo Pocket\nFootball Club puts you in the\nmanager’s seat at your very own\nfootball club, only on Nintendo eShop\non Nintendo 3DS. Can you keep the\ncrowds chanting and guide your\npint-sized players from the lower\nleagues to the wonders of the world\nstage?\n<br/><br/>\nAs manager, train up your players\nand choose your tactics wisely to\nmake the most of their abilities. Once\nyou’re satisfied, send your team forth\nand watch your decisions play out in\nmatches packed with action – but\ndon’t be afraid to alter your approach\nif it all starts to unravel before your\neyes. Delve deep and show plenty of\nskill on the sidelines and you could\nlead them all the way to the glorious\ntreble of the Pro League 1, the\nFederation Cup and the European\nChallenge Cup. With enough work,\nyou could even bring the World Club\nClassic back home!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/17ba373087443068158194f1affdd8f8a7cc71e82dc5babe736e2b36fa516bab.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/d6SEqDj.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/yqUclZa.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4277, '0004000000032d00', 'CTR-N-ASSE', 'SUPER STREET FIGHTER® IV 3D EDITION', 'USA', 1767623572, 'eshop', '50010000000259', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c1981702cc9e3026d00a0fc36b2b9020fb9da13e1225770c04b9b36ac74fc4fe.jpg', 'The ultimate version of Street Fighter® makes its seamless transition to the Nintendo 3DS with Super Street Fighter IV: 3D Edition. The console experience is now in the palm of your hand with rich new features that utilize the capabilities of the Nintendo 3DS to its fullest.  \n<br><br>\nPacked with 35 playable characters, bonus stages and cinematic Ultra combos, Super Street Fighter IV: 3D Edition expands the action by allowing you to fight your friends around the world using Wi-Fi.\n<br><br>\nNew to the franchise are the figurine mode, which utilizes the StreetPass feature to add a collectible meta-game, and the 3D over-the-shoulder camera option that takes fighting to new depths. For those new to the franchise, a simple mode has been added allowing players to pull off challenging moves with a single touch of the screen.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/fgnPkeJ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4278, '000400000005b800', 'CTR-N-JE6E', 'The Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time 3D E3 Video', 'USA', 18971956, 'eshop', '50010000006867', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1bc79682e264de8c3102444b7a11cbc3273517248db527cf51e1625037f31aa9.jpg', 'The Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time 3D brings a completely re-mastered version of this epic entry in the beloved The Legend of Zelda series to the Nintendo 3DS system. The game couples phenomenally enhanced graphics with stunning glasses-free 3D visuals to bring to life the daring adventures of its hero, Link™, in the epic tale of the creation of Hyrule and the struggle for control of its all-powerful ancient relic.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c0c061655958925d156a1798eda368969a7d6a100ae600220fde7864555910a0.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/SJCe4ZV.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/sHZFk8U.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4279, '000400000005b200', 'CTR-N-JECE', 'Mario Kart E3 Video', 'USA', 26738996, 'eshop', '50010000006868', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3dcc60ad94482e6233d9b36de894b4d7100bae106da2a1793f1a475d5148a8a7.jpg', 'A New Dimension of Kart Racing.\nThe newest installment of the fan-favorite Mario Kart™ franchise brings Mushroom Kingdom racing fun to new heights, in glorious 3D. There are new customizable Karts with new abilities that will have players soaring through the skies on wings and propelling through the seas on their quest to become a Mario Kart Champion.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/cf0acc9810e009f0e805cefabf64026c93c273bdbc66b6e1919f8dab357c68ec.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/BtcY5o5.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/f2n57H2.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4280, '000400000005b600', 'CTR-N-JE5E', 'Luigi''s Mansion 2 E3 Video', 'USA', 17760564, 'eshop', '50010000006869', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4d4ea7b85d92aa236c3b89de8139c24a1e9319c411a6f1d95fd74d7cc4b142cd.jpg', 'Luigi™ is back and on a mission to remove a bunch of stubborn ghosts from some spooky mansions. Armed with his trusty Poltergust ghost-sucking vacuum cleaner, he will try to act brave as he bumbles his way through the darkness while trying to capture these pesky phantoms.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2c89fe55f6b73b0588419c6b2b04cabecadd409e324588650c319f5861e8a95f.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/OGdCurb.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/xGOKOoq.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4281, '000400000005ba00', 'CTR-N-JE7E', 'Super Mario E3 Video', 'USA', 19930420, 'eshop', '50010000006870', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5c497401214de12dcc184dc14b7d795dde611e1dbe44e7a1d1ab524d0ecf75ed.jpg', 'Super Mario for Nintendo 3DS is an all new game that combines classic Mario game play and 3D visuals in a  truly amazing way.  It’s the return of the Tanooki Mario! Tanooki Mario has a tail that allows him to hover jump easily from platform to platform or even take out enemies with a quick whip of the tail. Players of all skill levels will enjoy playing the game.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ba8e97c2463f7ad4c5729c0068b9932a7baaf6d191291b169455bb750bb67dda.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/IL1VZCl.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/3t9Ma7L.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4282, '000400000005ae00', 'CTR-N-JE3E', 'Kid Icarus: Uprising E3 Video', 'USA', 27669300, 'eshop', '50010000006871', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/76500889975232490f78833f667cd82e04b3608df72b61cb5ff71ad161ec0297.jpg', 'The dark goddess Medusa and her Underworld Army have returned, and they’ve got their sights set on the heroic angel Pit. With the aid of Palutena, goddess of light and guardian of the human race, Pit must fend off this malevolent threat. The richly immersive graphics of the Nintendo 3DS system offer incredible depth as Pit battles enemies by air and by land.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7a0895f1a1861b3f6a7db3ffda06b4a74b7c4e3df9b06e64905b9e230f320db2.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/BIAsyoX.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/zOdA9YV.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4283, '000400000005c000', 'CTR-N-JEZE', 'Starfox 64 3D E3 Video', 'USA', 33844532, 'eshop', '50010000006872', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a4ff88ee94d9a569691fc7f8a9ed6d25d4618fc0b22560e9dafbf1a9b43842f9.jpg', 'Fox McCloud is back in a re-mastered Nintendo classic. Play as legendary Fox McCloud and lead your fearless squadron of wing-men into fierce laser blasting aerial combat against the evil forces of Andross.  Rich 3D visuals provide a remarkable sense of depth, distance, and position while dodging meteors and blasting enemy fighters out of the sky. New features such as motion controls and new multiplayer options allow longtime fans and newcomers alike to discover the excitement of the Starfox universe.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/47d2b00c7c64d336472dabac4357b983a71bf523bba96aee5bf0a836f66a3bf2.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/LKBnlYd.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/YWeUxt1.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4284, '000400000005b000', 'CTR-N-JE2E', 'Paper Mario™ E3 Video', 'USA', 23612212, 'eshop', '50010000006873', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0543a5b1a84a5fce05b548cbe1138728607c81dc2ce518be2e46ea0d946a9d2f.jpg', 'Coming soon to Nintendo 3DS!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/93e05e131b2b60da65a8ef25c284b9de177b131eb60a6ebbad4f1271d878e476.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/POsJZFA.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/3AZonya.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4285, '000400000005b400', 'CTR-N-JE4E', 'Animal Crossing™ E3 Video', 'USA', 24373556, 'eshop', '50010000006874', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/946a1586f29621fc720d7e0187026df98ccddf912978bf7db40c8bc5e03970d4.jpg', 'Coming soon to Nintendo 3DS!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/66eb60837bbdb898c92a1b809d1cea7747444260e51dfd401e4eceac9790557b.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/eaZmNCo.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/6by2c06.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4286, '000400000005bc00', 'CTR-N-JE8E', 'METAL GEAR SOLID 3D SNAKE EATER E3 Video', 'USA', 29227828, 'eshop', '50010000006875', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4633e70e23640dc8596b157f952426556d850af744d2ef10727d5faa7964beab.jpg', 'From the critically acclaimed director,Hideo Kojima,a new 3D experience re-imaged from one of the most popular Metal Gear Solid titles from the past, comes Metal Gear Solid 3D Snake Eater. Experience an all-new re-interpretation of Metal Gear Solid 3: Snake Eater, in 3D for the first time ever. "Photo Camo" system utilizing the built-in camera technology of the hardware bringing customized stealth and camouflage options to the player. By snapping a photo in the real world, players will be able to use the same image as a camouflage pattern applied to Snake''s uniform within the game. Utilizing the Gyro Sensor,players will become one with Snake through specialized tilt mechanics throughout the game design. As Snake climbs trees, or traverses bridges and other environmental obstacles, players will be in danger of falling based on the balancing of the system. An intuitive menu utilizes the touch screen for quick and easy equipping of items and weapons.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/89ccb0b813686f1ad874d8f18cb8ba28b9d9343ffd17b6e9a103c4e42581bded.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/lzSfsve.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/hJLF0gz.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4287, '000400000005be00', 'CTR-N-JE9E', 'RESIDENT EVIL®: Revelations E3 Video', 'USA', 18824500, 'eshop', '50010000006876', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8ec1417adb7958e81376cacc3d4190c2aa0a6ba1b3c9961c08b1c6a8d1465df8.jpg', 'Adding a new unique horror setting to the series, Resident Evil: Revelations gives players the chance to venture underwater as they try to escape the terrifying creatures that are roaming a supposedly abandoned cruise ship on the Mediterranean.  New storyline featuring series favorites Jill Valentine, Chris Redfield and introducing BSAA member Parker Luciani. Explore the dark, sinister areas of the cruise ship; there''s nowhere to run and hide with evil creeping out of the shadows. Touch Screen control scheme adds depth to puzzle solving and provides easy access to switching weapons on the fly. Use the Genesis scanning equipment to analyze enemy weaknesses and hidden items that will prove crucial for the player’s survival. Players can choose the shooting style that suits them with the ability to alternate between first and third person views to best pin point enemies.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a6e5b295b5c7eb68eb02222c83f403ea9686c55e9ec7e567a81e4d1b08c066a6.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/LRB5Vnj.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/uLz6h1s.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4288, '000400000005f000', 'CTR-N-JG5E', 'GREEN LANTERN TRAILER', 'USA', 24001332, 'eshop', '50010000006887', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3989eb96323bbaa83e5fc3f19e41d6005705d17daa560fe5eef739e617a61620.jpg', 'In a universe as vast as it is mysterious, a small but powerful force has existed for centuries.  Protectors of peace and justice, they are called the Green Lantern Corps.  A brotherhood of warriors sworn to keep intergalactic order, each Green Lantern\nwears a ring that grants him superpowers.  But when a new enemy called Parallax threatens to destroy the\nbalance of power in the Universe, their fate and the fate of Earth lie in the hands of their newest recruit, the first human ever selected: Hal Jordan.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bcf60f2b148d20b289ae7f871d4f930a6a1cba35592b461627edd545d5d3b579.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/dFInFh2.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/dWGPlff.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4289, '0004000000040e00', 'CTR-N-RACE', 'Alleyway™', 'USA', 3349348, 'eshop', '50010000006803', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d14e86b8e403c9b7929d29cc1151b72f0669f13ef9dc254ebf644551ea354f15.jpg', 'Your spaceship is at the gate of the Alleyway™.\n<br><br>\nAs Mario™, you will need to use your vessel to deflect the energy ball towards oncoming space grids. Hitting the grids will either weaken or destroy them, and you''ll need to keep returning shots until the entire field is cleared! \n<br><br>\nAs you progress through each level, you will confront new challenges of alternating stages, bonus rounds, and more. Speed and agile reflexes will quickly become your strongest allies as you reach to beat the top score!\n<br><br>\nYou''re in command in the Alleyway!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/NdU072q.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4290, '0004000e000a0b00', 'CTR-U-ANEJ', '更新データ Ver. 2.1 大合奏!バンドブラザーズP', 'JPN', 124078996, 'update', '50010000018613', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f3f573335c9a71d083ffdc7fe22e81484f9038a77dd058e8495996c2677efcea.jpg', 'ニンテンドー3DSソフト『大合奏!バンドブラザーズP』の更新データです。\n\n更新データの配信以降は、更新データ（Ver. 2.1）をダウンロードしていないニンテンドー3DS LL/3DS本体では、更新データ（Ver. 2.1）をダウンロードした本体とのローカル通信ができなくなるほか、インターネットを利用した機能もご利用いただけなくなります。お客様におかれましてはお手数をおかけいたしますが、更新データのダウンロードをお願いいたします。\n\n■Ver. 2.1 [2014.12.19配信]\n\n●「プレイヤー」モードを追加しました。\n・曲と順番を選んでプレイリストを作ったり、アレンジして再生したりできます。\n\n●「レコーディング」に以下の機能を追加しました。\n・複数の曲を選んで一括でレコーディング可能になりました。\n・生声アーチストについてパート別にレコーディングができるようになりました。\n\n●ゲーム起動時に最新情報が表示されるようにしました。\n\n●ギター演奏時に十字ボタンのかわりにABXYボタンでも演奏できるようにしました。\n\n●マイアーチストの髪型を増やしました。\n\n●そのほか、ゲームを快適に遊んでいただけるよういくつかの機能の改善や問題の修正を行いました。\n\n※以前の更新内容もVer. 2.1に含まれています。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f1a427cae10a265d69c545e5974c3aa44af4b09ef5fa6f572cd47e34f7dbfc97.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/yX771UK.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/Txozjwg.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4291, '0004000000067600', 'CTR-N-ARTE', 'Rhythm Thief & the Emperor''s Treasure™', 'USA', 1585834900, 'eshop', '50010000008006', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/391e8817830d8c7435c41e674f2f699f20592ebc262e9cf523a560d67b39655e.jpg', 'Pump up the tempo in the most mysterious rhythm adventure ever to hit the Nintendo 3DS. \n<br><br>\nRaphael has a secret life as a heroic thief who is famous among Parisians for stealing counterfeit paintings only to return them a few days later. \n<br><br>\nThis time he has his sights set on the Wristlet of Tiamat on display at the Louvre.\n<br><br>\nFeel the beat and conquer the rhythmic riddles in pursuit of the hidden truth about the city and his father’s disappearance. \n<br><br>\nMaster the beat and conquer the variety of rhythm challenges.<br>\nDive into the colourful 3D adventure in Paris.<br>\nUnmask the truth hidden behind treasures. <br>\nChallenge your friends and collect fans on your 3D map through Streetpass™.   ', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/fN3X83W.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4292, '000400000008c300', 'CTR-N-EC6E', 'Tomodachi Life™', 'USA', 407837540, 'eshop', '50010000021073', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/360361ca4e5756586c1f29e85bb10732ce24116e1d712d8738d7ef80b2b6d6bc.jpg', 'What happens when friends, family, and celebrities become Mii™ characters and live on an island? Tomodachi\nLife—that’s what—and it’s exactly the type of crazy that memories are made of! Give Mii characters items, voices, and personalities, then watch as they rap, rock, eat donuts, fall in love, get denied, and have little Mii babies.\nWait…WHAT?!\n<br><br>\nCreate Mii characters, customize their voice and personality, dress them up, and decorate their apartments. Then watch as they come to life! They hang out, play concerts, engage in rap battles, hook up matchmaker-style, and even partake in cool games like Tomodachi Quest, a mini-RPG adventure. And when something really epic happens, take a picture and share it over Nintendo Image Share. Or, send a baby Mii on a journey into your friend’s game with the StreetPass™ feature. Expect the unexpected because your Tomodachi Life is about to begin!\n<br><br>\nTry before you buy!<br>\nDownload the free demo version on Nintendo eShop to experience a bit of Tomodachi Life for yourself.<br>\n<br>\nCheck out the theme inspired by this game in the Theme Shop. Just tap the icon in the upper left corner of your Nintendo 3DS HOME Menu to get started.\n<br><br>\nA discount for this title is currently available to My Nintendo™ members as a reward. Go to my.nintendo.com/rewards to learn more.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/IwQDiJT.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4293, '0004000000049c00', 'CTR-N-RAUE', 'Double Dragon®', 'USA', 3439460, 'eshop', '50010000007760', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5f8e94c83881f77a455ebf65e4251f1318885887d5a1e35ec2b229049192f63e.jpg', 'Join Billy as he fights through his enemies via various attacks such as punches, kicks and throws, as well as a myriad of different weapons to attack\nwith in order to save his girlfriend, Marian. Many enemies will try and stop\nyou from reaching the end of each stage, some with powerful weapons to defeat you with. But if you can knock them down, you can make those weapons your own. Various bosses will\nblock your way at the end of each stage, but if you''re strong enough and\npossess the skills to defeat them, the path to Marian will lay open to you.\n\nCan you defeat your enemies and save\nyour girl!? Only you can make it happen!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ifMYtr2.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4294, '000400020012bf01', 'CTR-T-JYSE', '(Demo) AiRace Xeno', 'USA', 70217728, 'demo', '50030000005126', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4295, '00040000000d2800', 'CTR-N-AR4E', 'Rune Factory 4', 'USA', 1435941732, 'eshop', '50010000016693', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a112a1f8455b239c2cba6ecc4420c7475bfd017d7e8049c4b8b64bd11a6bb1c8.jpg', 'Dive deep into a brand new adventure in the Rune Factory series!\n<br><Br>\nEstablish a new life in a new country, developing relationships, cultivating the land and adventuring with comrades on an epic quest that begins with a humble tumble. Designed for beginners and series veterans alike!\n<br><Br>\nPlan your battle strategies with a wide selection of weapons and items!\n<br><Br>\nUse various weapons, skills and magic to personalize your battle tactics against formidable monsters in trap-laden dungeons. Recruit the local townsfolk, befriend wild monsters and grow stronger together!\n<br><Br>\nPursue a passionate romance as a male or female character!\n<br><Br>\nChoose either a male or female hero and seek in-depth relationships with the other townsfolk. Develop true bonds with a select candidate by socializing and giving gifts, then spend time together as a couple to deepen your romantic ties, ultimately leading to marriage and even the birth of an adorable child!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Kllf1Jl.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4296, '000400000f700100', 'KTR-N-CAFE', 'Xenoblade Chronicles™ 3D', 'USA', 3778214756, 'eshop', '50010000030935', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e04b6c6d5dc900b32a7301fa957285e0dd973872a72b29ed3153ff82c906c565.jpg', 'Take up arms against an invading army in this remake of an acclaimed RPG, only on the New Nintendo 3DS™ XL system. Explore landscapes and beat down foes in battles that blend real-time action with RPG strategy. Exclusive features make the Xenoblade Chronicles™ 3D game the ultimate way to learn the truth behind the mythical sword, the Monado.\n<br><br>\nDue to the processing power and additional buttons of the New Nintendo 3DS XL, you can experience this epic RPG portably. Command your party or quickly jump between locations by pressing the new ZL & ZR buttons and look all around the game’s beautiful environments using the C-Stick.\n<br><br>\nThese features perfectly round out an already outstanding adventure comprised of intense combat and intriguing storytelling. British voice actors and gorgeous art direction lend the story an authentic fantasy feel, while the customizable moves of your characters and chainable combos keep you on the edge of your seat.\n<br><br>\nCheck out the theme inspired by this game in the Theme Shop. Just tap the icon in the upper left corner of your Nintendo 3DS HOME Menu to get started.\n<br><br>\nEarn in game tokens in Xenoblade Chronicles 3D by tapping a Shulk amiibo figure to the New Nintendo 3DS XL. Tokens can be used to unlock music and animated 3D models of various characters.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/DmnSVyZ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4297, '000400000015b200', 'CTR-N-BFDE', 'Etrian Mystery Dungeon', 'USA', 565222244, 'eshop', '50010000030455', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f6e76915be102a5512a8b75fd3515ef1a7fa398a47669aef15e5ae8512e6a3f1.jpg', 'Offers in-game purchases\n<br><br>\nFar off in the mountains, the small village Aslarga becomes a hub for adventurers looking for fame and fortune from the Mystery Dungeons. But dire challenges await even the most stalwart adventurers in Etrian Mystery Dungeon, a turn-based action RPG roguelike developed by ATLUS and Spike Chunsoft.\n<br><br>\nThe Nintendo 3DS™ exclusive mixes Etrian Odyssey’s vast RPG party and skill customization aspects, and Mystery Dungeon’s infinitely random dungeon adventures. The action/turn based combat means that battling monsters is not just about using the right skills, but becomes an elegant Pas de Quatre of strategic positioning. Players form their parties with familiar Etrian Odyssey classes, customize individuals using Etrian-style skill trees, and then take up to four members into the dungeons. Always randomized with various levels and paths, the dungeons require plenty of exploration, not to mention the incredible loot rewards -- just be wary of what waits among the deepest depths.\n<br><br>\nCheck out the theme inspired by this game in the Theme Shop. Just tap the icon in the upper left corner of your Nintendo 3DS HOME Menu to get started.\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/TXvkNBW.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4298, '0004000000146a00', 'CTR-N-KCXE', 'Castle Conqueror EX', 'USA', 39234404, 'eshop', '50010000027056', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/02280358b8fca6d39fdd516ca3601e6b9d34753e6129b232d697994c360217a5.jpg', 'Commander! Are you ready to lead your people against The Empire!?\n<br><br>\nCastle Conqueror EX is a real-time strategy game for casual gamers. Players can play as 1 of 4 heroes in the EX version of the DSiWare hit Castle Conqueror. Your mission is to lead your soldiers into battle, seize the enemy’s castle, and gain victories until The Empire is banished from your land.\n<br><br>\nOther features:<br>\nPlay through 50 levels with 4 unique heroes that have their own advantages in battle.<br>\nThe EX version features AI and levels that have been redone.<br>\nEnemies are more intelligent and the levels are more challenging.<br>\nAll items and hero abilities have been redesigned.<br>\nA play coins feature that can be used to boost battle effects in-game.<br>\nIntended for both casual gamers and hardcore gamers.\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/djSYu4t.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4299, '0004000000147100', 'CTR-N-ADNE', 'Little Battlers eXperience™', 'USA', 1894697828, 'eshop', '50010000035075', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2631aef27173443dc7edcf47423d0a858060ab247fdadc81531af503dd627f2d.jpg', 'In 2050, customizable palm-sized robots known as LBX are pitted against each other in battle, and now you can get in on the action! Customize your LBX with parts from over 130 sets to create one of more than 30,000 possible designs. Then wage robot war in real-time battles! Team up with characters from the TV series, or take on friends in local 3-on-3 battles.\n<br><br>\nObliterate your enemies across 20 different battlescapes, from deserts to open plains. There''s even an erupting volcano. You can equip your LBX with nine different weapon types that unlock powerful special attacks used to pulverize enemies. To continue the excitement of LBX, additional models, quests, and LBX cards will be distributed online for even more content.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/kkahX72.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4300, '0004000200146a01', 'CTR-T-KCXE', 'Castle Conqueror EX DEMO', 'USA', 35758080, 'demo', '50030000006586', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4301, '0004000000125500', 'CTR-N-AJRE', 'The Legend of Zelda™: Majora’s Mask 3D', 'USA', 661384036, 'eshop', '50010000027796', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4baa81fa9b8e74b108a40de7ba7cd9f85626bce29ae360afd5a2234c94550137.jpg', 'Check out the theme inspired by this game in the Theme Shop. Just tap the icon in the upper left corner of your Nintendo 3DS HOME Menu to get started.\n<br><br>\nIn three days, the moon will fall and the land of Termina will meet with a terrible fate. Can you save it in time? Relive the world’s final 72 hours, solve elaborate puzzles, conquer dungeons, battle giant bosses, and befriend the doomed people of Termina in one of Nintendo’s most suspenseful apocalyptic adventures ever. \n<br><br>\nThe Legend of Zelda™: Majora’s Mask 3D is a remastered and enhanced version of the Nintendo classic that’s unlike any other Legend of Zelda adventure. In this shadowy tale, a masked Skull Kid drags Link™ into the world of Termina, where the moon is falling from the sky. Lucky for Termina, Link can reverse time and relive his last 72 hours in limitless ways. Each time, he’ll don any of his 20+ masks, help different citizens, battle different bosses, and ultimately change the fate of a world. This is the definitive version of a dark classic.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/wBG42be.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4302, '00040000000d6800', 'CTR-N-JLHE', 'League of Heroes', 'USA', 90631012, 'eshop', '50010000028855', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/016ac8269d75e7574199d14cf26330e1b59f1487700deec40bf180fb0566c8ae.jpg', 'Become a true hero and save the villagers of Frognest!\n<br><br>\nA NEVER-ENDING STORY\nHack, slash and pummel your way through the endless Frognest Forest!\n<br><br>\nGEAR UP AND CUSTOMIZE YOUR CHARACTER\nKit out your character with numerous armor and weaponry options – then design the best strategy to defeat your enemies!\n<br><br>\nEVOLVE AS YOUR ADVENTURE UNFOLDS\nEarn experience, discover treasure and unlock a slew of cool items, including magic!\n<br><br>\nCOMPLETE QUESTS\nComplete 60+ daunting quests and earn valuable silver coins!\n<br><br>\nBEAUTIFUL HAND-DRAWN GRAPHICS AND ANIMATIONS\nImmerse yourself in spectacular 2D visuals and awesome animations!\n<br><br>\nPERSONALIZED, WEATHER EFFECTS\nIn League of Heroes, you can enjoy changing weather and time-of-day effects! You’ll experience thunderstorms, cloudy skies, fog, nighttime and much more!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/SEMeHYg.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
