(4322, '0004000000038b00', 'CTR-P-ABMP', 'Resident Evil™ The Mercenaries 3D', 'EUR', 617634660, 'eshop', '50010000000565', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7872d310248bee0ee0bd2c95a86249e5b3edc22ca7568eefd79b52b1b0b28106.jpg', 'It’s a race against time as players\ncompete to defeat as many enemies\nas possible before the countdown\nreaches zero.\n<br/><br/>\nResident Evil: The Mercenaries 3D\noffers players a variety of gameplay\nformats with a solo mission option or\nthe ability to team up with others\nacross the world in two-player co-op\nvia Internet Play. The game also\nincludes the addition of an all new\nSkill Slot feature. Players will be able\nto fill three skill slots from a selection\nof 30 skills including improvements to\nweapon performance, reload speed or\nmelee abilities and customise\ncharacters to best suit their style of\nplay.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/HUtXvpl.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4323, '00040000000ef600', 'CTR-N-RCEP', 'Mega Man™ 3', 'EUR', 4324196, 'eshop', '50010000024415', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b190fa701c450706ba9b38b223e2fddc31b3f74a013f8cbd8b5c415b67c9044a.jpg', 'The dastardly Dr. Wily has taken\ncontrol of an off-shore oil rig, aiming\nto drill to the centre of the Earth to\ncollect energy for his latest invention.\nSounds like a recipe for disaster and\nonly Mega Man can stop it!\n<br/><br/>\nAssisted by cyber-canine Rush and\nrobotic helper Eddie, you must\nprogress through Dr. Wily''s fiendish\nfortress, battling various Robot\nMasters and collecting their weapons\nbefore facing the mad scientist and his\nultimate creation!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a28a12e992c9755ebc052d8122f863d8cc6b743e647fa829e3e1af81a5393f31.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/DXdHFKD.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/agw8BSK.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4324, '00040000000ef900', 'CTR-N-RCFP', 'Mega Man™ 4', 'EUR', 4832100, 'eshop', '50010000024684', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6cb510b177eacc8ce759d4f5ed428261cefc569cc7835d1aca8501e0ac1eeb55.jpg', 'At a gathering of the World Robot\nExposition, chaos suddenly ensues.\nDr. Wily, with his mind-controlling\ndevice, sets all of the robots to\nattack! The only one not under his\ncontrol is Mega Man, who sets off to\nstop Dr. Wily.\n<br/><br/>\nJoining Mega Man are Rush and Beat,\nand together they battle fortresses of\nlaser turrets, waves of armed androids\nand fiendish Robot Masters. Blast\nyour way through while adding new\nweapons to your inventory and\nface-off with Dr. Wily once more!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/291bef470c7ad8d4955091e972aaa67d48db8fc29a388908deb79f5bc2f2c2c8.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/vkEZ5dt.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ixvZU4w.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4325, '00040000000efc00', 'CTR-N-RCGP', 'Mega Man™ 5', 'EUR', 4819812, 'eshop', '50010000024416', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d37eac55edd4e25589eaa541b60535225b65a573d297d78e7334ef6aea76a440.jpg', 'The last of the Game Boy™ Mega\nMan™ series begins with the hero\nbeing defeated at the hands of new\nfoe, Terra! Mega Man returns to the\nfight upgraded with the new Mega\nArm, vowing to defeat Terra and repel\nhis army of Stardroids – evil robots\nfrom space!\n<br/><br/>\nMega Man has robots of his own to\nsupport him, though. Rush the robot\ndog returns and is joined by\nnewcomer Tango the cybernetic cat.\nPlus, collect power chips to unlock\nnew upgrades in Dr. Light’s lab. You’ll\nneed all your skills to defeat the alien\ninvaders!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2ffcfa00da723882bfa48f919cb4a3690faa30a91d6a948af68509e45f3c7cca.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/4QMuoGD.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/xvIlN4A.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4326, '000400000004f200', 'CTR-N-RAWP', 'Mega Man™: Dr. Wily''s Revenge', 'EUR', 4770660, 'eshop', '50010000007436', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f234fb901e383d68b223b961b348f0f16cf341dbcc4f631ee066d69200d405ad.jpg', 'They''re alive, and ripping up the\ntown!<br>\n<br>\nInsane industrial wizard Dr. Wily has\nrevived 8 of his Robot Masters in\nanother try at taking over the world.<br>\n<br>\nDr. Wily''s really raving this time. As\nyou blaze and blast your way closer,\nhe runs further into even nastier\nmazes, and hides behind terrifying\ntons of mechanized maniacs, including\nthe all-new, Mega Man Hunter!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/66c6d5b2723ba5a3920c73334646aa2c3a7cc291b453d8b92b3331555e1d8182.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/UI2pAkI.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ktfTUv5.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4327, '0004000000093900', 'CTR-N-RB7P', 'Mole Mania', 'EUR', 4746084, 'eshop', '50010000011502', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/06187de6db7c3c3a33c973889a3fc82e91ecedeae83e88b6b24d39d35a48dafe.jpg', 'Produced by the legendary Shigeru\nMiyamoto, this classic action-puzzle\ngame stars Muddy Mole who must\nrescue his family from evil farmer\nJinbe.<br>\n<br>\nYour goal is to guide Muddy through\neach stage to the exit which is easier\nsaid than done! Enemies, obstacles\nand devious level designs bar your\nway.<br>\n<br>\nFortunately, Muddy can also dig\nbeneath the surface and uncover new\npaths. Also, look out for bonus stages\nwhere you can get your own back on\nJinbe.<br>\n<br>\nIf you like action games with a brain,\nyou''ll dig Mole Mania!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9953e58126a0316dd046a0c22ad42ad29233d28372f483f9de4b44ee37fa0f68.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/b41XkHB.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/GvybfUd.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4328, '000400000007e500', 'CTR-N-RBRP', 'MYSTICAL NINJA starring GOEMON', 'EUR', 4496228, 'eshop', '50010000010425', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9b55200d144db2c93902ae61747a1f4b4f079659fab37989acafca27c264e542.jpg', 'Join Goemon and his friends\nEbisumaru and Sasuke as they battle\nto save ancient Japan from the\nclutches of the evil Black Ship Gang,\nand rescue their fellow ninja Yae from\nthe gang''s clutches!<br>\n<br>\nMYSTICAL NINJA starring GOEMON is\nan action role-playing game featuring\nthree different characters to control,\neach with unique skills. Visit towns\nand question the inhabitants for clues,\nbuy items to aid your quest, and solve\nbrain-teasing puzzles to seek out Yae\nand defeat the pirates.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e464e6e84587b16f227833b39fd67a342425afae10f46bc464a85f0a8b3f92b2.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/bMrp1v3.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/Hd9qbqt.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4329, '000400000004fc00', 'CTR-N-RAZP', 'PAC-MAN™', 'EUR', 3849060, 'eshop', '50010000007146', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/56f75f55884edae2daa38a0855be9c74a480ebb7e26df800e2732d379e565fed.jpg', 'Someone''s got the munchies again!<br>\n<br>\nGobble, gobble, gulp! Who''s\nmunching Power Pellets? Who''s\nzipping around the maze at top speed,\nchomping up ghosts and scoring big\npoints? It''s Pac-Man, the world''s\nhungriest character! Devour a fruit\ntreat and get a big bonus score. But if\nyou''re caught by the little haunters,\nyou''re ghostflakes! Use the warp\ntunnel for a quick escape.<br>\n<br>\nHours of ghost-chomping action!<br>\n<br>\nThis version of the game does not\nhave multiplayer functionality.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3c3c2823525a9a3336a84a8d5d6091c3ab53dffef1327d12f8b73eb1ad217912.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/SU3Klkn.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/DjG247m.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4330, '00040000000b2800', 'CTR-N-RCCP', 'Pinball: Revenge of the Gator', 'EUR', 4012900, 'eshop', '50010000016214', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a67581803d8606301d7ad81b4babf49b7634dd6a4b4c0a76527bcbc099fbacd0.jpg', 'Revenge of the Gator is a snappy\npinball simulation that packs a table\nfull of tricks and traps into a perfect\npocket size.\n<br/><br/>\nThere are four scrolling screens and\nthree bonus stages to get your teeth\ninto. Direct the ball into certain spots\nto trigger extra balls and score\nmultipliers. But don’t let the ball fall,\nor the hungry gator below will\nswallow it up.\n<br/><br/>\nYou can also grab a friend and\nengage in the two player mode by\ntaking turns to see who can score the\nhighest.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/118570adf040ecadba30ee2f4d66b3e4ab617d721c352274d7257a153abea016.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/DiuowJp.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/biH71VX.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4331, '0004000000043000', 'CTR-N-RAMP', 'Radar Mission™', 'EUR', 4766564, 'eshop', '50010000006908', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a9aee90fd5234ca1a1feb1c6f9ff43fd00948b83f119ebb06a95522578b4c94e.jpg', 'The screen flickers to life in the dead\nof night... An intermittent\nbeep-beep-beep pulses out of the\nspeaker... Words on the screen spell\nout an urgent message from across\nthe waves:<br>\n<br>\n"ENEMY FLEET APPROACHING STOP\nDEPLOY IN ATTACK FORMATION\nSTOP"<br>\n<br>\nThere''s no time to lose. Steel your\nnerves and take command of a fleet of\nwarships and engage an enemy fleet in\nbattle, trying to sink their ships.\nBattles can be either fought using\nradar in Game A or controlling a\nsubmarine in Game B.<br>\n<br>\nThis version of the game does not\nhave multiplayer functionality.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/13554e0c5bbfd6c4063808423a97e139a99f0f0b6a5b30e9f15dac9c06142205.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/FpKcnC8.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/Ez3dlet.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4332, '0004000000050e00', 'CTR-N-RA7P', 'Side Pocket', 'EUR', 4459364, 'eshop', '50010000007924', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/289e235a2c3ff44eefb0c1de30027b2d1003883eca2bdf254a596507d077a518.jpg', 'Chalk up your cue and prepare to hit\nthe baize, in this deep yet\npocket-sized pool simulation.<br>\n<br>\nIn 9-Ball mode, simply try to knock\nthe numbered balls into the holes.\nWith no limit on the number of shots,\nit''s perfect for beginners.<br>\n<br>\nWhen you want a challenge, try\nPocket mode. Work your way up from\nrookie to world class champ. You''ll\nalso need to prove yourself with trick\nshots too!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7ae3b0db1f7c18c4e23485493d01b08fb6090663f7296c4dc84ce6d441a4dd55.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/fDtxcxZ.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/vWDthWA.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4333, '0004000000041300', 'CTR-N-RADP', 'Tennis', 'EUR', 4234084, 'eshop', '50010000006769', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/15f92e7ef73aa43b699cdc651f508e2d0ffa137617c31942301ceba04d237f23.jpg', 'Serve, volley, lob, smash… all the\nmoves of the real sport are faithfully\nrecreated, yet simple enough for\nanyone to perform, in the Game Boy\nclassic Tennis.<br>\n<br>\nFour levels of increasingly tricky CPU\nopponents are ready to take you on;\nso you’ll need fast reactions and\ncareful timing to become the champ.<br>\n<br>\nPerform power serves, skilful shots,\nlofty lobs and killer cross-courts, as\nyou rise up the ranks. Close calls will\nbe up to the umpire to decide; who\nmay look strangely familiar…<br>\n<br>\nThis version of the game does not\nhave multiplayer functionality.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/KBAgexV.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4334, '0004000000083200', 'CTR-N-RBVP', 'The Sword of Hope II', 'EUR', 4701028, 'eshop', '50010000011107', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e6c834bd12a02ea6d066d69074d478ef9280b34e93ea76d714a5a4eb1fbce640.jpg', 'When the ancient demon Zakdos was\nfinally sealed away, it ended the war\nagainst evil. But now Zakdos is free\nagain, and to make matters worse, the\nSword of Hope has been stolen!<br>\n<br>\nIn this classic adventure game, take\non the role of young Prince Theo and\nembark on a journey to retrieve the\nSword of Hope.<br>\n<br>\nExplore the land and recruit allies to\njoin your band of warriors and\nmagicians, and take control of three\ndifferent characters. The fate of the\nkingdom is in your hands!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7e8ac0194985c138ad7daab57936bbcc07bf0c2219b50314e229151fecd8abea.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/e0YnjxQ.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/LDVX6ox.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4335, '0004000000082f00', 'CTR-N-RBUP', 'Tumble Pop', 'EUR', 4442980, 'eshop', '50010000010415', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/cbc73deaaf995d0bc4b5ec99e1f7aead70e000a89b699046ba1d4f172c4a5a94.jpg', 'In the future, the world is infested\nwith strange beasties and weird\nmutations. So grab your trusty\nVacuulator and suck up those critters,\nand make the world fit for humans\nagain!<br>\n<br>\nThis classic action-platformer tasks\nyou with vacuuming up all the evil\nmutants, robots and aliens, and\nblasting them back at each other.<br>\n<br>\nTumble and pop your way through\neight worlds in the single player\ngame, and you can also get creative\nin Construction Mode and make your\nown levels!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ba7e304f7c9481b6a576acf1559289da22bb6090346d346f1ca4de7e47d93507.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/JRico2V.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/i38tiI9.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
