(4372, '0004000000124300', 'CTR-N-JQ7P', 'Cubit The Hardcore Platformer Robot', 'EUR', 23120740, 'eshop', '50010000020873', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/cfa3736b37f1f06a4a3099b8ff02f80b411b2ebf1e3d9a53e0befea41726be6e.jpg', 'Cubit The Hardcore Platformer Robot\nis an action-packed platform game,\nwhere music plays a very important\nrole.\n<br/><br/>\nWith only one button to jump, you\nmust help Cubit to go from platform to\nplatform, while you avoid obstacles\nand enemies through the different\nscenes of the game.\n<br/><br/>\nPerhaps you think this makes this\ngame not difficult, right? Well, you\nare right; this game is not difficult...\nthis game is Hardcore!\n<br/><br/>\nChoose the path you want to do in\neach game and reach each of the 3\nendings available!!\n<br/><br/>\nFeatures:\n<br/><br/>\n- Beware: This videogame has guest\ncharacters from other videogames.\n<br/>\n- 3 different endings!\n<br/>\n- 2 game modes: for all types of\ngamers, as well as Hardcore gamers.\n<br/>\n- A soundtrack that will send you\nback to the dance floor.\n<br/>\n- 24 challenges to enrol.\n<br/>\n- A videogame fully created by just\none person!\n<br/><br/>\nAnd now, new remastered version\nwhich includes:\n<br/><br/>\n- NEW! The new Hardcore+ game\nmode!\n<br/><br/>\n- NEW! Online rankings!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/WdVTftu.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4373, '00040000000a5b00', 'CTR-P-ASLP', 'Scribblenauts™ Unlimited', 'EUR', 488467300, 'eshop', '50010000013415', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e5731d59ee4f073fd84f09f51fd3a1e12c9da977dc152b8e6fe17f068f854284.jpg', 'In this Nintendo 3DS game, players\nsolve puzzles using anything they can\nthink of. Players simply tap in a word\non the Touch Screen and it appears in\nthe game – from anvils to zombies, the\npossibilities are nearly endless!\nPlayers can see how others nearby\ncreatively solved the puzzles via\nStreetPass too!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a11678021c44545a4b22656ca2e13c45d13ae7f5496cadbe35e5402f48f3fbfc.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/9C9BvS7.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/mqJLoRG.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4374, '0004000000124a00', 'CTR-N-JCYJ', 'リアル脱出ゲーム×ニンテンドー 3DS 超破壊計画からの脱出', 'JPN', 132909924, 'eshop', '50010000034635', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bc70540883e0a86075b992268c480d175aeb06ef360df56b77e01f7919f91cc0.jpg', '本作は、ニンテンドー3DSをインターネットにつないで、オンラインで参加者全員と同時に行う、謎解きゲームです。\n<br>制限時間60分のなかでほかの参加者と最大6人のチームを組み、協力しながら謎解きを進めていきます。ゲームは全5話構成となっており、どの回からも参加できます。\n<br>\n<br>■ストーリー\n<br>何者かが3DS内部に侵入して、「プログラムボム」と呼ばれる爆弾を仕掛けた。このままでは世界中の3DSが爆発してしまう。\n<br>爆発を止めるには謎を解くしか術はない。いったい誰が、なぜ、プログラムボムを仕掛けたのか。\n<br>全ての謎を解き明かし、あなたはニンテンドー3DSを爆発から守れるだろうか？', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4f198a5c0b06152643437f3ff53c3e31e49050ec4514e33b3ecb45c843476580.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/oBEPxf1.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/YfAdFhf.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
