(4481, '000400000014f100', 'CTR-N-EDHE', 'Animal Crossing™: Happy Home Designer', 'USA', 496257892, 'eshop', '50010000036675', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/76731c4e3a8f732a9b62b9949c39c1acc1b9d3f18c5060eeb392a9956f0c0595.jpg', 'Bonus: Get a download code for a free Animal Crossing: Happy Home Designer: Your Office theme when you buy the Animal Crossing: Happy Home Designer game for Nintendo 3DS in the Nintendo eShop*. You’ll find the download code for the free theme on your Nintendo eShop receipt.\n<br><br>\nAll of your favorite Animal Crossing™ villagers are looking for new homes, and you’re the designer! Use your creativity to design the perfect houses—inside and out—for old friends (and new ones too). Purchasing this digital version will give you a download code for a special theme to use on your Nintendo 3DS HOME Menu!\n<br><br>\nJoin the team at Nook’s Homes, alongside Lyle, Digby, and newcomer Lottie, and interact with over 300 villagers from the Animal Crossing series in a whole new way by designing their yards and homes! The more you help, the more your item catalog will grow. You can touch an amiibo™ card (sold separately in six-card packs) to the NFC area to call a specific character into your game! Isabelle will also bring you jobs for public facilities (like a school and a hospital), so you can help build up Main Street as the town grows.\n<br><br>\nTap amiibo cards to your New Nintendo 3DS XL to invite those characters into your game. You can also use the Nintendo 3DS NFC Reader/Writer accessory (sold separately) to use amiibo with your Nintendo 3DS XL, Nintendo 3DS, or Nintendo 2DS system.  Use amiibo cards to invite up to four characters into a room to hang out.  Tap the Special Character amiibo cards to call in animals that would otherwise not appear in your game with requests.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/7mBdz6L.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4482, '0004000000186600', 'CTR-N-KMJE', 'The Legend of Dark Witch 2', 'USA', 464837476, 'eshop', '50010000038815', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/aa7d0fc2a30bd2b701dad997a2b5d4f29b7814ebe50947adcc6506b85e52c01a.jpg', 'Created by indie games company INSIDE SYSTEM in 2014, The Legend of Dark Witch 2 is a 2D action story sequel to The Legend of Dark Witch.\n<br><br>\nTrue to its predecessor, Legend of the Dark Witch 2 retains its simple controls and enough challenges to satisfy the completist.\n<br><br>\nPlayers have 8 stages to choose from and must use SHOTs to make their way through a variety of obstacles to reach the boss enemy.\nWithin each stage there are hidden "Pura Syega" which are helpful to power up player characters.\n<br><br>\nNew Features\nIncreased number of stages to choose from\nAllows finer customization for player stats using "Tres" \n"Technical skills" can be customized not only to increase power, but add abilities as well\nNew "Forbidden" items added for a wider variety of game play', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/cAZdUYE.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4483, '0004000e0010e200', 'CTR-U-BCEJ', '更新データ Ver. 1.2 FINAL FANTASY EXPLORERS', 'JPN', 5327716, 'update', '50010000028755', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5356f022f99a669160f3d46cd849afc4b18e2a6fb9c623a139004bc21df00e45.jpg', 'ニンテンドー3DSソフト『FINAL FANTASY EXPLORERS』のインターネット通信プレイ時に必要な更新データです。\nゲームを快適に遊んでいただけるよう、いくつかの問題を修正しました。\n『FINAL FANTASY EXPLORERS』をお持ちのお客様は、必ずダウンロードしてください。\n\n※更新データ（Ver. 1.2）をダウンロードすると、更新データをお使いでない方とはローカル通信プレイができなくなります。\n※インターネット通信プレイを行うためには、更新データ（Ver. 1.2）が必須となります。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f1a427cae10a265d69c545e5974c3aa44af4b09ef5fa6f572cd47e34f7dbfc97.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/bmaukY3.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/kY2BdqP.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
