(4488, '000400000007dc00', 'CTR-N-RBNP', 'Kirby''s Dream Land™ 2', 'EUR', 4930404, 'eshop', '50010000009747', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/51d24371ad3b23d97f429e664a80e2986ec91a8e389fce845b5f3ef866370549.jpg', 'In his second Game Boy™\nadventure, Kirby must solve the\nmystery behind the disappearance of\nrainbow bridges that link the islands\nof Dream Land. Travel through all\nseven isles while battling the minions\nof King Dedede, and team up with\nKirby''s friends Rick the Hamster, Kine\nthe Fish and Coo the Owl.\n<br/><br/>\nKirby''s animal pals have their own\nunique abilities and can also magnify\nKirby''s powers, too! And you''ll need\nall the help you can get, to face a\nnew enemy: the malevolent Dark\nMatter!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8ff92af34b6b8c40084f73ff742a9a78dced93b1b374ee6a4a8deda6cd382a7b.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/2EbX4Xx.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ATIjXMk.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4489, '0004000000094500', 'CTR-N-TAWP', 'MEGA MAN™', 'EUR', 6945636, 'eshop', '50010000012200', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8c5ffdb14f45a4abfcabf68b6fa2d44f4d822f8b79113e70334cda6477b0d270.jpg', 'Mega Man''s original adventure blasts\nonto Nintendo eShop! The series\nbecame famous for its challenging mix\nof platforming and shoot ''em up\naction; and here you can see how it\nall began.<br>\n<br>\nAs a super-robot created by the\ngenius Dr. Light, it''s up to Mega Man\nto traverse ten unique stages and beat\nthe devious Robot Masters designed\nby evil Dr. Wily.<br>\n<br>\nBeating each boss allows Mega Man\nto use its trademark weapon, giving\nyou an advantage in other stages - a\ntechnique still used in the series\ntoday.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/66de8501da5ac4b35e881fafc627270b7c9a6d15fe787489fe607b573cafaaa0.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/0COc2B9.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/uGVIywQ.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4490, '0004000000041900', 'CTR-N-RAFP', 'Kirby''s Dream Land™', 'EUR', 4479844, 'eshop', '50010000006922', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/65883eac3aeceef380337d4a5c2936651d7295e79a1bdbf9a828ae26acefe42a.jpg', 'On a tiny star somewhere far, far\naway from Earth, there is a very happy\nplace known as Dream Land.\n<br/><br/>\nThat is, until one night the gluttonous\nKing Dedede and his band came to\nsteal all the food and the Dream\nLander’s treasured Sparkling Stars.\n<br/><br/>\nSuddenly, a spry little boy named\nKirby happened along and said "Don''t\nworry, I''ll get your food and your\nSparkling Stars back!".\n<br/><br/>\nIn Kirby''s Dream Land, you guide\nKirby through a series of\nside-scrolling action stages. Kirby can\nwalk, fly, inhale and defeat enemies -\neverything he needs to make it\nthrough Mt. Dedede!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2eb6008594c54880a10ae27e33a4e48f7042a9bdda38dd67bca263607dfd88b5.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Zh5mRzZ.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/qwqUwky.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4491, '000400000006ec00', 'CTR-N-TACP', 'Punch-Out!!™', 'EUR', 5159780, 'eshop', '50010000009321', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/940340d688bc68c8608db4a0837dfa3ee973b12ddb2d5f7510ce5cd46245817c.jpg', 'What rookie boxer Little Mac lacks in\nsize, he more than makes up for in\ndetermination. And with trainer Doc\nLouis by his side, Little Mac is ready\nto make a big impact.<br>\n<br>\nPunch-Out!! pits your pint-sized\npugilist against such diverse rivals as\nthe fragile-jawed Frenchman Glass\nJoe, sucker-punching Russian Soda\nPopinski and the Hollywood\nheavyweight Super Macho Man.<br>\n<br>\nUse jabs, body blows, hooks and\nuppercuts to discover your opponent''s\nweak spot and make the winning blow.\nAlso, look out for an appearance by\nMario as the referee!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/72d04072d4889bc55a43c62de75c0d4001e436314334c08c81e137fe9a3bb1e8.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/gwAb6eu.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/jrO0cmo.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4492, '0004000000055100', 'CTR-N-SABP', '3D Classics Xevious™', 'EUR', 22244196, 'eshop', '50010000007030', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9df879d8d931ed82d021aecb45640dd197ef9ec6f26762397adc1252ee434aee.jpg', 'Strike deep behind enemy lines in the\nintense classic shooter, now revamped\nin 3D!<br>\n<br>\n3D Classics Xevious puts you in the\ncockpit of a state-of-the-art Solvalou\nstrike fighter on a daring mission to\ninfiltrate hostile airspace. You are\nhumanity''s last hope of eradicating\nthe sinister XEVIOUS collective -\nshoot down wave after wave of enemy\nfighters, drop your deadly payload of\nguided bombs and take out the\ncolossal flying fortress to bring the\nXEVIOUS war machine to its knees!<br>\n<br>\nConsidered one of the forefathers of\nthe overhead vertical shooter, Xevious\ncan yet still dazzle with new 3D\nfeatures!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6f7782bcd291bdede18d4e9302a0777d0e700582b80eaf6fe8cac47e4f093957.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/PeEW6X4.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ljlwMgs.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
