(4572, '0004000000171a00', 'CTR-P-RCXA', 'Pokémon™ Edición Azul', 'ALL', 10263396, 'eshop', '50010000038518', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e2efa6b30e0eaa27efbae9b3f33158fbd75a9deb4b6ebeb3d029cfff5b5497b2.jpg', 'With classic graphics and music, Pokémon Red and Pokémon Blue Version stay true to the originals released nearly 20 years ago. You’ll feel like you’re playing them just as they were, but now you can trade and battle Pokémon using local wireless on the Nintendo 3DS family of systems! Revisit these timeless games, or play them for the first time!\n<br><br>\nExperience the original journey that started the Pokémon phenomenon nearly 20 years ago, but now on the Nintendo 3DS family of systems as a digital download! Relive the feeling of catching your very first Pokémon from the original 150, complete with monochromatic pixel art and 4-bit background music. You’ll take on the role of a Pokémon Trainer and travel across the land searching for amazing creatures called Pokémon. Catch, battle, and trade as you face Gym Leaders and try to stop Team Rocket! If you want to catch the original 150 Pokémon, you’ll need to trade wirelessly with your friends.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/xvMKZzu.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4573, '0004000000171900', 'CTR-P-RCWA', 'Pokémon™ Edición Roja', 'ALL', 10267492, 'eshop', '50010000038530', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7e3546f423cef3bc5301ebf8dd33590a8a50527db77d801b0cf4045f7bae4154.jpg', 'With classic graphics and music, Pokémon Red and Pokémon Blue Version stay true to the originals released nearly 20 years ago. You’ll feel like you’re playing them just as they were, but now you can trade and battle Pokémon using local wireless on the Nintendo 3DS family of systems! Revisit these timeless games, or play them for the first time!\n<br><br>\nExperience the original journey that started the Pokémon phenomenon nearly 20 years ago, but now on the Nintendo 3DS family of systems as a digital download! Relive the feeling of catching your very first Pokémon from the original 150, complete with monochromatic pixel art and 4-bit background music. You’ll take on the role of a Pokémon Trainer and travel across the land searching for amazing creatures called Pokémon. Catch, battle, and trade as you face Gym Leaders and try to stop Team Rocket! If you want to catch the original 150 Pokémon, you’ll need to trade wirelessly with your friends.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/OsRYwHw.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4574, '000400000012db00', 'CTR-N-AHRE', 'Fossil Fighters™: Frontier', 'USA', 1406126948, 'eshop', '50010000029575', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/690709e366fd1b7ac2a49c1c351ba51ac15cb7c398e7165ea6b89a7a9e071b3a.jpg', 'Buckle up for a wild ride across a fully-3D world in your own custom vehicle! While exploring the unknown, you’ll discover fossils of dinosaurs to dig up, bring to life, and pit against other vivosaurs in massive reptile rumbles. Deck out your ride with digging and battle tools, then set out for adventure and combat of prehistoric proportions!\n<br><br>\nUpgrade your vehicle to race over giant ramps or plow through rock in the search for your ultimate team. You can gather rare and hard-to-find fossils by taking on fast, puzzling challenges alone or with nearby friends in dig sessions! Team up against wild rogue vivosaurs, or battle it out in huge 3-on-3 brawls! In battle, vivosaurs can be given Support Shots that boost speed, increase defence, or make them stronger—it’s your strategy, no bones about it!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/AdhoawJ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4575, '0004000000040c00', 'CTR-N-RABE', 'Baseball', 'USA', 3648356, 'eshop', '50010000007056', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4d233baa9c48711e749f7ea401122b5b6f8107b80503e4ddb9403901c77e4883.jpg', 'Re-live the glory of this 1989 Game Boy™ classic!\n<br><br>\nAs the pitching team, deliver a series of fastballs while adjusting curve and speed. But be careful of wearing out your pitcher! If the batter connects, your outfield or infield will back you up. Three outs by the opposing team, and it''s your turn at offense! As the batting team, shift your batter on the home plate and time their swing at the incoming ball. Try to safely reach the next base, or score for a home run! Strategize your team''s moves, and score for the winning team! It''s time to play ball!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/oYkcTVQ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4576, '0004000000034700', 'CTR-N-JERJ', 'いつの間にテレビ', 'JPN', 5118820, 'eshop', '50010000006906', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c74e4f96115d0bb31fc71efb4f0e76d583c37fedc9c320ba36aacd66592500f3.jpg', '『いつの間にテレビ』は、テレビ放送でたくさんの人気番組をもつ日本テレビとフジテレビが制作する3D映像を観ることができるソフトです。\n<br>\n<br>ニンテンドー3DS本体の電源が入っている状態でインターネット通信ができる場所に置いておけば、『いつの間にテレビ』を終了しても映像をいつの間にか受信しますので、夜、おやすみの間などにスリープモード(電源をONにしたまま本体を閉じた状態)にしておくのがおすすめです。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fd8571f11dc184bdaad3c1c7215af34e0e62a4f9b623d7240ec3831540ee424f.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/NuEauWF.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/rTI0GYD.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
