(4796, '0004000000132000', 'CTR-N-BFRE', 'Ultimate NES™ Remix', 'USA', 118463332, 'eshop', '50010000027575', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2ef6182602385dbeea55cf774f81d9442e7111546de81a69dd9d67315d134564.jpg', 'Take on a rapid-fire onslaught of challenges and mash-ups from 16 of Nintendo’s finest 8-bit games! Test your skills on a gauntlet of quick, tricky challenges and remix stages that combine parts of different games. The best mix of titles from the NES™ Remix and NES™ Remix 2 games is on Nintendo 3DS. Now you’re playing with PORTABLE power!\n<br><br>\nLink™ vs. Donkey Kong™! Kirby™ vs. Boo™! It’s mash-up mania in this celebration of all things NES™! Race through to earn stars on increasingly tough tasks, like beating Ridley from Metroid™ or making Princess Peach™ save herself! Compete in Championship Mode’s blitz of challenges from the Super Mario Bros., Super Mario Bros.™ 3, and Dr. Mario™ games, then compare scores with others in your region via online leaderboards.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/uVMvOUk.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4797, '00040000000d0a00', 'CTR-N-BPCE', 'Pokémon™ Art Academy™', 'USA', 336198500, 'eshop', '50010000025495', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/050e982e15c050d168aedc9f842c2ab9a2cc53f1a73346521127b1733eedab36.jpg', 'Players take on the role of a young aspiring artist who enrolls in the Pokémon Art Academy to learn how to draw Pokémon under the tutelage of Professor Andy. Through novice lessons they are taught the basics of art, from simple shapes to coloring, and introduced to various tools and techniques they will use to create art.\n<br><br>\nThe basic gameplay allows the player to create illustrations of Pokémon and draw their way through the various lessons at the academy using the Nintendo 3DS Touch Screen. Once they graduate, all of the options within the game are unlocked, including a set of special lessons that include Mega Evolution Pokémon.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/2IBVYG1.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
