(4801, '0004000000081e00', 'CTR-N-AMGE', 'METAL GEAR SOLID SNAKE EATER 3D', 'USA', 3230456676, 'eshop', '50010000008864', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1c57401ed22e68166eef18639ac61eb7817355f88e9fd04c6942779160558497.jpg', 'Bonus: Get a free Metal Gear Solid Snake Eater 3D theme when you buy the Metal Gear Solid Snake Eater 3D game for Nintendo 3DS in the Nintendo eShop. You’ll find the download code for the free theme on your Nintendo eShop receipt.\nDownload codes available while supplies last.\n<br><br>\nExperience an all-new re-interpretation of Metal Gear Solid 3: Snake Eater, previously released and with over 4 million copies sold, in 3D for the first time ever.\n<br><br>\nAuto-stereoscopic 3D viewing capability that endeavors to create a rich jungle world with depth in settings of trees, rock/stone, water, and more.<br>\n‘Photo Camo’ system utilizing the built-in camera technology of the Nintendo 3DS system, bringing customized stealth and camouflage options to the player. By snapping a photo in the real world, players can use the same image as a camouflage pattern applied to Snake’s uniform within the game.<br>\nUtilizing the Gyro Sensor, players will become one with Snake, using specialized tilt mechanics throughout the game design. As Snake climbs trees, or traverses bridges and other environmental obstacles, players will be in danger of falling based on the balancing of the system.<br>\nAn intuitive menu utilizes the touch screen for quick and easy equipping of items and weapons.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/24tZXrf.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
