(4810, '0004000000127c00', 'CTR-N-BSBJ', 'ワールドサッカーウイニング イレブン2014 蒼き侍の挑戦', 'JPN', 881474404, 'eshop', '50010000021954', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b2beda1993fd72fa1255622f4987583d63de1407bb1185d9cdbb47e17b7f9016.jpg', '2014年12月25日(木)23時59分に、本ソフトの配信を終了いたしました。\n<br>\n<br>2014年ならではのスペシャルなウイイレ、『ワールドサッカーウイニングイレブン 2014 蒼き侍の挑戦』が登場!\n<br>\n<br>『ウイイレ 2014 蒼き侍の挑戦』は「ジャパンチャレンジモード」、「Jリーグモード」、「アジアチャンピオンズリーグ（2013シーズン）」 が新たに収録されたスペシャルなパッケージ。\n<br>その中でも最大の魅力は「ジャパンチャレンジモード」。「Jリーグモード」が収録されていることにより、Jリーグに所属するすべての日本人選手からサッカー日本代表のメンバーを選出することができるので、伝説のベテラン選手から期待の新戦力まで、メンバー選びを思う存分楽しむことができる。 さらには、自分の作ったオリジナル選手をゲームに登場させて、SAMURAI BLUEと競演させることもできる。\n<br>\n<br>また、ニンテンドー3DS版ならではのタッチ操作も魅力で、下画面をタッチするだけで繰り出される鋭いシュートや華麗なドリブルは直感的で、爽快感バツグン。\n<br>\n<br>キミが選んだサッカー日本代表で、世界の頂点を目指そう!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/291c6f08b95b59d1fb5ba08493f957ad1a3401221ae078237983d0725027b217.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/jvqjSZD.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/npR3fHI.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4811, '0004000000158300', 'CTR-N-KSRE', '3D Streets of Rage 2', 'USA', 38800228, 'eshop', '50010000035135', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/29b1b898067a38ba101b884f3505053f4ca90d3a1b9bd53e5272d5877b936895.jpg', 'The sequel to the original rumbler is back and re-mastered in 3D. Slam the asphalt with bigger, better and totally devastating attacks. Skull crushing ex-wrestler Max Thunder joins up with Axel and Blaze to throw earth shattering body slams and fist attacks. New thrasher Skate slices punks with high speed inline attacks and spinning jump kicks. Use secret weapons to bash your way through gangs of bikers to rescue your friend and defeat Mr. X.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/jg9n2pd.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4812, '0004000000094c00', 'CTR-N-QARE', 'Toki Tori', 'USA', 4438884, 'eshop', '50010000011686', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/76dd00f3a5232285af55c3a6235829b3f1e12754c5b0ba732824a164afde2be2.jpg', 'Original Release Date:  September 2001\nHe may be a small, yellow chicken, but Toki Tori is no coward!  He''s the hero of this egg-cellent puzzle platformer in which he must rescue all of his kidnapped brothers and sisters, who are still in their fragile eggs.\nIn this Game Boy™ Color classic, you must keep Toki Tori safe by avoiding monsters and traps while working out how to collect all the eggs in each level before the timer runs out.\nLuckily, there are lots of items to aid Toki Tori''s mission.  So what are you waiting for?  Time to get cracking!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/IDJos2c.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4813, '00040000000bb200', 'CTR-N-JDPP', 'Dress To Play: Cute Witches!', 'EUR', 29277028, 'eshop', '50010000012586', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ceaa6f17bc5a782cb83cda270b943c7bab6ee2ef225381a305735014df19ad4a.jpg', 'In Dress To Play: Cute Witches! dress\nto play and play to dress!\n<br /><br/>\nMake a little witch and design her\noutfit in the dressing room. When you\nfinish, get ready to set off on an\nadventure as your character flies away\non her broomstick to a peaceful world\ninhabited by fantasy characters.\n<br /><br/>\nThe more you play, the more rewards\nand gifts you''ll receive. You’ll also\nearn more items of clothing to dress\nyour little witches in!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ogLdY8m.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4814, '00040000000dae00', 'CTR-N-JL8P', 'Super Little Acorns 3D Turbo', 'EUR', 25299812, 'eshop', '50010000014011', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c074bd75c914aacbf278ef5ca8c03a26b964acab7f3da4ff273b82ceb16e6469.jpg', 'The press is nutty about Super Little Acorns 3D Turbo!\n<br/><br/>\n“we’re privy to a platformer that excels in every area of gaming” \nNintendo Fuse – 9.5/10\n<br/><br/>\n“If you pass on this one you must be nuts”\nNintendo Life – 8/10\n<br/><br/>\n“a fantastic freshman effort” \nDarkain Arts – 9/10\n<br/><br/>\n“a polished, amusing title from start to finish.” \nNintendo World Report – 8/10\n<br/><br/>\n“I hope Super Little Acorns 3D Turbo is the start of a trend.”\nFamily Friendly Gaming – 88%\n<br/><br/>Lead Mr. Nibbles on a 3D mission to\nrecover his acorn stash. Use his\ntrusty grapple rope to navigate the\ntreacherous woodland environments\nand defeat pesky critters!\n<br/><br/>\n• 90 levels of pixel perfect\nplatforming in beautiful crisp graphics\n<br/><br/>\n• 50% new exclusive levels, new\nbonuses, turbo mode and a whole\nbunch of zany outfits\n<br/><br/>\n• Smash and swing through 30\nexclusive challenges to test your skill\nat bronze, silver and gold level\n<br/><br/>\n• 60 main stages spread over four\nseasons with epic bosses\n<br/><br/>\n• Collect power-ups to supercharge\nyour adventure\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/XFXI9Ez.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4815, '00040000000d9000', 'CTR-P-AYMP', 'Mario & Luigi™: Dream Team Bros.', 'EUR', 889117540, 'eshop', '50010000014853', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/86a6d26eb5f333dff65b9fa0fc8ee045e58b8d317d7a903df263c2a5be7913c7.jpg', 'Uncover the power of Dreamy Luigi in\nMario & Luigi: Dream Team Bros. on\nNintendo 3DS!\n<br/><br/>\nIn this fourth instalment of the\npopular RPG series Mario & Luigi, the\nstory opens with Princess Peach and\nher staff, plus brothers Mario and\nLuigi in tow, being invited for a\nsightseeing trip to the mysterious\nPi’illo Island by its equally mysterious\nproprietor, Dr Snoozemore. But after\nan initially hospitable welcoming to\nthe island – albeit with Dr Snoozemore\nnoticeably absent – things take a turn\nfor the worse when Princess Peach is\nkidnapped and pulled into a Dream\nWorld by a new enemy in the series,\nthe ghostly bat king Antasma.\n<br/><br/>\nSolve puzzles, battle enemies, and\neven interact with creations of Luigi’s\nown imagination in order to succeed!\n<br/><br/>\nNew moves and attacks that use the\nNintendo 3DS system''s capabilities in\noriginal ways.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a45f0201dc5a9c980d3ded5adac447be4132c0211ca8a2c592c612044c8b410f.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/NX7EhxB.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/rQlK7UJ.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4816, '0004000000038900', 'CTR-P-ASMP', 'Super Monkey Ball™ 3D', 'EUR', 228039572, 'eshop', '50010000000214', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9f4d75248cf45d60053277a4534826cf05e9c4284142ab3a6010cfa33aeafb03.jpg', 'Super Monkey Ball as you''ve never\nexperienced before! Join AiAi and\nfriends as you tilt and roll your way in\nto the world of 3D! Lose yourself in\neach vibrant world as you twist, turn\nand aim to collect every banana in the\nfastest time possible. Then play\ntogether with friends and be the first\nto cross the finish line in Monkey\nRace or get ready for a manic melee\nin Monkey Fight. Everyone''s favorite\nmonkeys are jumping out of the\nscreen with excitement. Let yourself\nbe completely immersed in the world\nof Super Monkey Ball like never\nbefore. Watch as your favorite\nmonkeys truly come alive in front of\nyour eyes. Are you ready to join the\nfun!?', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f13e2c5e5c581cdf1f2b234adbfdf7b4ea526aead5f546373114593cdf153f56.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/xyDl6KH.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/BE1HmhO.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4817, '0004000000111a00', 'CTR-N-JKVP', 'Kung Fu Rabbit', 'EUR', 51751780, 'eshop', '50010000020453', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fb0e3be0aaa6686db67e69ed042c67194aa7e0174ecfe3bec82ce9d484f1fdb9.jpg', 'Life in the temple of rabbits hangs by\na thread. Universal Evil has struck\nagain and kidnapped all of your\ndisciples. Only you managed to\nescape. They let you live... They''ll\nsoon regret it!\n<br/><br/>\nUse your agility and combat skills to\nsave your disciples! Jump from roof to\nroof, slide gracefully along walls,\nsneak up on your enemies, and rip\nthem them to shreds!\n<br/><br/>\nDetailed graphics, humour, hours of\ngameplay and intuitive controls. Each\nof the 80 levels requires logic,\nprecision, agility and lots of sabre\nrattling. The game also has lots of\ntrophies to win, babies to save,\ncarrots to eat, and a Universal Evil to\nexpunge.\n<br/><br/>\n- 80 levels in normal and hard mode\n(dozen hours of play!)\n<br/><br/>\n- 15 unlockable items to customize\nyour rabbit.\n<br/><br/>\n- Text in English', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/1Dp3rgA.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4818, '00040000000b4800', 'CTR-P-ANLP', 'Girls'' Fashion Shoot', 'EUR', 225532772, 'eshop', '50010000018553', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d6280f3628db5a371aee15c19215ceeab8cee4fa27bee632f01f73028cfe0e63.jpg', 'Girls’ Fashion Shoot lets you enter\nthe world of fashion and become the\nnewest star on the scene! Become a\ntop fashion model AND the editor of\nyour own successful style magazine,\nusing thousands of customisation\noptions to propel yourself to the top\nof the fashion world. Choose your\nlook with make-up, hair and nail art,\nthen create outfits from hundreds of\nclothing items and go on photo\nshoots choreographed entirely by you!\n<br/><br/>\n• Become a successful magazine\neditor AND a top fashion model!\n<br/>\n• Thousands of customisation options\nto discover\n<br/>\n• Choose your own make-up, hair and\nnail art to get the right look\n<br/>\n• Mix and match hundreds of clothes\nto create the perfect outfit\n<br/>\n• Design photo shoots to show off\nyour style in your own magazine!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/nVFVwMX.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47');
