(4937, '0004000000158400', 'CTR-N-KGHE', '3D Gunstar Heroes', 'USA', 37690212, 'eshop', '50010000036515', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/02e540a88b459e4be8b30fa55695e9256488a45c75053c7aa804d985479b0da2.jpg', 'Treasure’s visually stunning side scrolling shooter, Gunstar Heroes is now re-mastered in 3D! Take advantage of Gunslinger Mode by choosing between FREE and FIXED shot modes on the fly and cycling through all your weapons. However, firepower can only take you so far! Go the distance and make it to the long-awaited boss battles with double life with the new Mega Life Mode. Take on the enemies alone or with a friend using two-player co-op via Local Play and prevent the world from destruction. ', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/lkLynzX.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4938, '00040000000b1c00', 'CTR-N-MATE', 'Dinosaur Office Remix', 'USA', 10836788, 'eshop', '50010000011488', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9dc3a7d656753c456374dfede75b603c64aa1fd772aa5e0e1cc7a1f5315cc762.jpg', 'Having problems with your CPU? Reboot it with this catchy remix of Dinosaur Office: Computer Problems. RAWR!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4a5850e7962f501a6b174cf12029532903c10c4a6e96231b9516113e045b8465.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/LT7TfIx.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/PuX1txd.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4939, '00040000000aa800', 'CTR-N-JFDE', 'Fractured Soul', 'USA', 390404964, 'eshop', '50010000011647', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6cf53a0d4c1622a6c745018cee60eab52a0b75f9a8fe3e8d4549b613f0083bd5.jpg', 'Old-school platforming on two screens!\n<br><br>\nFractured Soul is a classic side-scrolling platform game with a twist: it is played across both screens at once! Created by platform gamers for platform gamers and exclusively for the Nintendo 3DS system, Fractured soul literally adds a new dimension to this much-loved genre.\n<br><br>\nFeatures<br>\nDouble the action: Fractured Soul takes the classic, instantly familiar platform game and brings it to the next level with dual-screen gameplay!<br>\nOnline rankings for speed running: Compete against your friends and the world via Nintendo leaderboards.<br>\nGameplay variety: 5 major zones, each bringing a unique challenge to the second screen. Your dimension-shifting journey will take you underwater, through fierce winds, scorching heat and even inverse gravity!<br>\nHours of content: 30 levels across 5 zones, including both platforming and shoot-em-up game styles, as well as epic, dual-screen boss battles!<br>\nHardcore challenges: Unlock challenge levels, and test your skills to the limit!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/msfilr3.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(4940, '00040000000d0700', 'CTR-N-JWHE', 'Witch & Hero', 'USA', 39840612, 'eshop', '50010000013952', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5612c655ddc2fdd438f44ccad781e489d810501c05b9ab86649511daefd618cf.jpg', 'Witch & Hero is an 8-bit style action game. You play as a hero accompanied by a witch taking on the evil Medusa, whom has destroyed many villages and towns with the monsters that stand before her.\n<br><br>\nMedusa turned the witch into stone, so she is no longer able to move. So it’s up to the hero to defeat the monsters and collect their blood in order to recover the witch for a limited duration.\n<br><br>\nThe witch’s destructive magic easily destroys monsters, but you will have to rely on the hero’s will power primarily. He is able to try and try again, but the witch cannot, thus the hero must protect her.\n<br><br>\nFeatures:<br>\nRetro 8-bit pixel graphics and sound, along with simple controls<br><br>\nWipe out huge waves of monsters through 20 stages with 2 difficulties<br><br>\nChoose between trial mode and infinite mode for an in-depth challenge', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/2scLDDs.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
