(5089, '000480044b454e4a', 'TWL-N-KENJ', 'ほぼ日の健康手帳™', 'JPN', 5296948, 'dsiw', '50010000005133', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5fa054ec49de8a3365e34b14541c8944df68807653ad9f6613f215316bd65b98.jpg', '『ほぼ日の健康手帳』は、自分のからだに関する情報や、病気の症状などを記録することができるソフトです。\n\n■このソフトには身長・体重をはじめ、喫煙や飲酒の程度、アレルギーや病歴など、自分のからだに関する情報を記録することができます。これらの情報を定期的に更新し、自分のからだの変化を知っておくことは、日ごろの健康管理に役立ちます。\n\n■また、病院で診察を受ける際に、お医者さんに伝えておきたい情報をメモ形式で記録できます。\n\n■入力した情報は「お医者さんへ」というメニューで、手軽に確認することができます。このメニューを選んで表示される画面をお医者さんに見てもらうことで、自分の症状などの情報をすばやく伝えることができます。\n\n■他にも、健康を守るために役立つコラムが９本収録されています。\n', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8cf2c177652e2606173089818558b00125f6e77df2d8cc113bf4ade77427de3f.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/rb9uqws.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/nQjOwyB.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5090, '000480044b465a45', 'TWL-N-KFZE', 'Faceez', 'USA', 4877108, 'dsiw', '50010000002201', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a831c8092aaf68586e0aec748017ee0bfe722dd32aa170652f1df4dfedd5968f.jpg', 'Make your friends laugh with Faceez! Take pictures of their faces with the Nintendo DSi Camera and then mix them and animate them! Dress them up with lots of funny accessories! Place them in your own favorite settings! Give free reign to your imagination with millions of possible combinations! Thanks to the Nintendo DSi system’s connectivity with Facebook you can share your creations with your friends, who’ll be rolling on the floor laughing! Photograph, disguise, decorate, animate, and send... FACEEZ!\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/LES3l3I.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5091, '000480044b47334a', 'TWL-N-KG3J', 'じぶんでつくる ニンテンドーDS ガイド', 'JPN', 2814772, 'dsiw', '50010000005222', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/03035653db2b036261f796f4961a60a606358115245767a5bc647cabdba4dc91.jpg', '『じぶんでつくる ニンテンドーDS ガイド』は、ニンテンドーDSi/DSi LLでとった写真と音声を使ってオリジナルのガイドを手軽につくれるソフトです。\n\n■『ニンテンドーDSiカメラ』の「アルバム」に保存した写真と、DSi本体のマイクで録音した音声を組み合わせて、ガイドのデータをつくり、他のニンテンドーDSシリーズ本体へ配信することができます。\n・ガイドを他のDSシリーズ本体で聞くためには、このソフトを保存した複数台のDSi本体を使って、ガイドの再生ソフトと、写真と音声で構成されるガイドのデータとを、それぞれ配信します。\n・再生ソフトはDSダウンロードプレイで、すべてのDSシリーズ本体で受け取ることができます。\n■つくったガイドは「プレビュー」で再生して楽しむこともできます。\nまた、自動で連続再生する「スライドショー」機能もありますので、しゃべるフォトフレームのような使い方もできるなど、工夫次第で遊びが広がります。\n■初心者でもガイドを簡単につくれる「カンタン」と、慣れてきた人向けの「高度な編集」の2つのモードが用意されていますので、どなたでも手軽にガイドを作成いただけます。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e87628933eec60ddffadb9f15a06b68c0381992f681bf0263766bf0c144ac2ae.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/mNqMFIi.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/aM6rgs4.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5092, '000480044b47464f', 'TWL-N-KGFO', 'Game & Watch™ Mario''s Cement Factory', 'ALL', 1752884, 'dsiw', '50010000003581', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/61442eef2afbac7aabc0042fd4075c038b494aa3fed443a156b808f69af0f500.jpg', 'Nintendo first began releasing the Game & Watch series in 1980. This collection of games was available on portable LCD devices, and each title featured a game and a clock. Each Game & Watch title features two modes of play: GAME A (normal difficulty) and GAME B (more advanced play). While some controls have been changed in the DSiWare version to better suit the Nintendo DSi system, the appearance of the game itself has not been altered.\n\nConveyor belts carry tubs of cement to the mixers below. Use the elevators to move Mario to different levels of the factory, dumping cement from the top mixers to the mixers below and into the trucks. Earn points for every load of cement you drop from the mixers to the cement truck. Receive mistake icons by letting a mixer overflow with cement, trying to get on an elevator when you are not level with it, or hitting the floor or ceiling while riding an elevator; receive three mistake icons, and it’s game over!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/pSqHGin.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5093, '000480044b494645', 'TWL-N-KIFE', 'Drift Street International', 'USA', 9575220, 'dsiw', '50010000002424', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2f731fa364f5120feeb084e064340a64d9a6c443b530097b871cc9a484f330b7.jpg', 'Drift Street International is the ultimate high-speed, white-knuckle street racing experience, exclusively for Nintendo DSiWare. Slide and boost your tuned performance car around challenging city streets, in high-intensity midnight races across the US, UK and Japan. Precise, responsive controls give you total control of your car – push yourself to the edge and own your opponents! Drift sideways through corners, building your nitrous meter to let you boost past your opponents on the next straightaway. Test your skills against challenging, aggressive AI drivers, or take on your friends in four-player head-to-head wireless races. Additionally, each track plays host to arcade-style checkpoint races and challenging speed trials in which you have to keep the speed close to the max or risk getting eliminated! Unmatched speed, smoothness and draw distance are only possible by taking full advantage of the expanded Nintendo DSi hardware.\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/AtizEDF.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5094, '000480044b4b3745', 'TWL-N-KK7E', 'Music on: Electronic Keyboard', 'USA', 3404596, 'dsiw', '50010000003001', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bd1191e25793c4c920135b31846ef2f57815162ecaa08da6a1679db3b6b009b4.jpg', 'Music On is an electronic keyboard to take with you everywhere! Get creative and spend relaxing moments transforming your Nintendo DSi system into a complete electronic keyboard with a great variety of instruments and rhythms. This is the perfect way to have fun and impress your friends with your musical creations! If you are already an expert or if you are taking your first steps, Electronic Keyboard will help you capture your inspiration wherever you are.\n\nCharacteristics:\n*Automatic accompaniment function with chord recognition\n*Up to 8 user definable chords\n*5 different styles, each one with 4 variations\n*Independent drum, bass and chorus parts\n*6 octave keyboard (2 visible)\n*Pitch bend function\n*16 instruments\n*Integrated sequencer\n*Metronome\n*Recording and replay option', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/zNWHiiC.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5095, '000480044b503645', 'TWL-N-KP6E', 'Bird & Beans™', 'USA', 1290036, 'dsiw', '50010000003295', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/da27232b706226badc1e52fd5f13829d7646d88032caff62805c1e2d2dfe9ec9.jpg', 'In Bird & Beans, control Pyoro, a small bird with an elastic tongue and an insatiable appetite for beans. Scramble to catch beans that fall from the sky, racking up points as you go. The farther away the bean, the more points it’s worth. Beware any beans that are missed, though—they will leave a hole in the ground that can’t be crossed, potentially trapping Pyoro. Bird & Beans also features a second version that enables Pyoro to spit seeds at high speed, bringing down more beans than ever before. This fun and fast-paced game requires skill and strategy to master and always leaves you wanting to play just one more time...\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/KAVyldW.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5096, '000480044b504245', 'TWL-N-KPBE', 'Photo Dojo™', 'USA', 2579252, 'dsiw', '50010000003162', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e39950566a12dddb563e5ae9e95c911f5cc236fc86f4921125f2149c8e67b745.jpg', 'Welcome to Photo Dojo, where you create a dojo filled with ruthless (or humorous) fighting machines—using images of you and your friends!\n\nUse the Nintendo DSi Camera application to take pictures of yourself and your friends in various poses, then use the microphone to record sound effects and dialogue to give your warrior a voice. Choose one of the four available fighting styles, name your character, and you’re done! Better yet, repeat the simple, step-by-step process and create a lineup of up to eight fighters. Complete the setup of your game with the ability to make customized backgrounds and your choice of three awesome soundtracks...then prepare for battle!\n\nTwo players can share one Nintendo DSi system and face off against each other in a one-on-one grudge match, while single-player mode offers the chance to pick your favorite fighter and take on a relentless wave of opponents of your own creation.\n\nIf you’re ready for some seriously off-beat Kung Fu action—literally starring you—Photo Dojo’s unique twist on the side-scrolling beat’em up genre lets you use your imagination to set the stage for a fun-filled fight to the finish. May the best warrior win!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/r3qblE0.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5097, '000480044b513956', 'TWL-N-KQ9V', 'The Legend of Zelda™: Four Swords Anniversary Edition', 'EUR', 14850868, 'dsiw', '50010000007462', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ab129aef5e6d2a294fd148642ab165e2529f017e741beafa33268f6faffbb88a.jpg', 'Celebrate The Legend of Zelda''s\n25th anniversary with this new version\nof the multiplayer classic – available\nfor a limited time only* – for free!<br>\n<br>\nAs in the original, two to four players\ncan team up through puzzle-rich\ndungeons – while competing for\nRupees – to rescue Princess Zelda.<br>\n<br>\nAnd now, solo players can also enjoy\nthe full experience – controlling two\ncharacters by themselves. This version\nalso features new, exclusive areas that\nunlock some familiar favourites: the\nHurricane Spin and the Master Sword!<br>\n<br>\n*Until 20th February 2012.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ZCc7sQX.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5098, '000480044b534945', 'TWL-N-KSIE', 'Scrabble™ Classic', 'USA', 12446516, 'dsiw', '50010000003681', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e1d8f309707c3b3d5d4f08006934706527c931683841c229adada7634403ba88.jpg', 'Scrabble, long one of the world''s most popular board games, is enjoying a tremendous surge in popularity, both online and in the real world. Scrabble Classic for Nintendo DSiWare allows you to play this exciting game in both Single Player and Multi-Player modes! ', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/XyEAaa3.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5099, '000480044b555745', 'TWL-N-KUWE', 'WarioWare™: Snapped!', 'USA', 7834420, 'dsiw', '50010000004162', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fbd7d0ebed61f16d7acd91d96e8ea116fd153ed802625287911c52d757e9daf3.jpg', 'Wario returns with more manic action made especially for the Nintendo DSi system! WarioWare: Snapped! uses the built-in Nintendo DSi camera to make players the star of the show by placing them right into fast-paced minigames. Take part in wacky challenges simply by moving your face and body as you travel along four wild roller coasters, hosted by Wario and his pals. Beat the minigames using motions ranging from large to small or play with a friend for even more fun. Wario even has a few tricks up his sleeve for after you’ve finished moving...', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/QrPjDUc.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5100, '000480044b574245', 'TWL-N-KWBE', 'Mario™ Clock', 'USA', 2798388, 'dsiw', '50010000003576', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e58069c1754a1a116e944e7eaf0bce1328f96166ea5b4110055214783772e3a2.jpg', 'Turn back time and enjoy a bit of classic gameplay, based on the original Super Mario Bros., with Mario Clock. Help Mario and Luigi collect more coins than ever (POW block anyone?) while they run through a variety of stages. Gather enough coins and you’ll be treated to another scene bound to bring back fond memories for many. Mario Clock includes both analog or digital clocks which utilize the system’s internal clock or allow you to offset the time however you like. Program up to three alarms (with snooze functionality for those that need it) and assign them a Mario-related sound or use one created in the Nintendo DSi Sound application. You’ll find yourself thinking “Just a few more coins...” in no time!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/9l9Dk4g.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5101, '000480044b574645', 'TWL-N-KWFE', 'Mario™ Calculator', 'USA', 1727284, 'dsiw', '50010000004201', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5c7d1bad20f7e8bb01f60e8febea618029a664667ff878d3544abe07a8967e0c.jpg', 'Mario and Luigi take a break from their normal adventures to dedicate their heroic talents to working with numbers. Mario Calculator features the full functionality of a traditional calculator, including a Memory key and the ability to display up to 13 digits, and adds a layer of atmosphere reminiscent of the original Super Mario Bros. Use the Unit Converter to turn one unit of measure into another (such as length, weight, volume, age, and others), or track the history of calculations you’ve performed with ease. Listen to the Mario-related sounds and watch the coins fly as calculations are performed. Now to get back to adding up those high scores...', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/2JR66KK.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5102, '000480044b5a5045', 'TWL-N-KZPE', 'Pinball Pulse: The Ancients Beckon™', 'USA', 10263348, 'dsiw', '50010000008621', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/914c3ade1e2769e63619f4df03ab9b8973a1e33272da0bed59f88efe3144c714.jpg', 'Pinball takes on mythological proportions in the exclusive Nintendo DSiWare game Pinball Pulse: The Ancients Beckon. Choose from two modes of play (Regular Game or Daily Game) and begin your journey to becoming a pinball champion. Conquer mythic quests, collect gifts from the 12 Olympians, and push your skills to the limit by facing Medusa, the Sirens, and more. Your portable pinball table will give you a quick adrenaline rush, as you watch the steel ball fly through ramps and carom off bumpers all over the playfield. Rack up combo points, open specific game modes, and even enlist the Oracle for some help. Will you accept Zeus’s challenge?', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/t4e1bbd.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5103, '000480044b513945', 'TWL-N-KQ9E', 'The Legend of Zelda™: Four Swords Anniversary Edition', 'USA', 14499636, 'dsiw', '50010000007496', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a86f95012eaa1b79538d582ab209fa814cf0a197791caa9fb48805ffcbaafe81.jpg', 'When the evil Wind Mage Vaati escapes from confinement, Link must draw upon the power of the legendary Four Sword and save the kidnapped Princess Zelda! But there’s a catch—whoever touches the sword will divide into multiples! Play in 1-player mode and control two heroes, or play via DS Wireless Play with up to four friends! Hurdle through challenges by using teamwork as you scramble to collect the most Rupees! The Great Fairies are\nalways watching your efforts, and will reward your bravery based on how many Rupees you collect.\n<br><br>\nAll-new for this edition—new stages and modes! Upon completing the main\nquest, relive memorable moments from\nthe past with levels based on previous\nZelda games in the “The Realm of Memories”. For the bold and daring, test your adventuring skills in “The Hero’s Trial”!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/01nIgUe.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5104, '000480044b4d4745', 'TWL-N-KMGE', 'Mighty Flip Champs!™', 'USA', 6192948, 'dsiw', '50010000002843', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/16b5a043e2205fc79b002c8358f8cb2c61ddbbd66f4ca6081c92f6c19224fa59.jpg', 'Are you ready to become a Mighty Flip Champ? Take control of Alta, and Page Flip through a series of action packed mazes! The Touch Screen reflects a preview of the next chamber, and shows Alta''s projected destination within it. When it''s time to flip, use Alta''s Magical Warp Wand to replace her world with the next one. Will she land safely on solid ground, or be crushed under it? By cycling endlessly through room after brain busting room, you''ll match wits with some of the most devious traps in puzzle/platforming history!', 'none', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/XolMUyW.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5105, '000480044b533345', 'TWL-N-KS3E', 'Shantae: Risky''s Revenge', 'USA', 16730932, 'dsiw', '50010000003644', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1e859aae135da39e9b268e93cc561b87b1c656d508cf1b20625ac220c70ccef2.jpg', 'This is it! The sequel to the critically acclaimed Shantae! Fans asked, and WayForward answers with a powder keg of high octane, hair-whipping, hip shaking action available only on the Nintendo DSiWare service. Shantae: Risky''s Revenge sets the bar even higher with thousands of frames of animation, huge multi-sprite bosses, and a quest so big it’s bursting at the seams.\n\nGuide “half-genie” Shantae through haunted wastes, burning deserts, enchanted forests, dripping caverns and deadly labyrinths. Discover magical attacks, brew zombie coffee, save golden babies, and master the art of belly-dancing to transform Shantae into more powerful creatures. Use your powers to foil the lady pirate Risky Boots and save Sequin Land from certain doom!\n\nWith its infectious characters, flirtatious humor and deliciously outlandish action, Shantae: Risky’s Revenge offers up all the hair-whipping, belly-dancing action you can handle!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ERAJ4EX.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5106, '000480044b575945', 'TWL-N-KWYE', 'Mighty Milky Way', 'USA', 11383604, 'dsiw', '50010000004785', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e683070384da5a6b8fc036a16fddd406dfabcd04a8d62cfb9d250830b62b7151.jpg', 'Are you ready to pulse some planets and soar through space? With a pocket full of planet candy and a heart full of ennui, green-skinned cutie-pie Luna needs your help to accomplish her secret mission! Prepare for fever-pitched puzzles in another mighty game from WayForward!\n\nLuna uses her magical staff to create and destroy planets on a whim. Explode vicious space monsters, avoid sizzling electric barriers, and grab all the delicious planet candy you can. But watch out for the T-Rex, Luna’s arch-nemesis! His laser eyes are matched only by the awkwardness of his and Luna’s sketchy past. But enough incessant blathering! Let’s stare into the sun with stoic tears and embrace the rolling chaos that is life!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/1Cx6aYZ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5107, '000480044b443945', 'TWL-N-KD9E', 'Dr. Mario™ Express', 'USA', 3903284, 'dsiw', '50010000000592', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/631f627ff6b2fe866263af8f5b330c579d7e41bdf0744f3ed2e4b4f36cb5d924.jpg', 'Mario once again dons his stethoscope to battle the forces of illness in this downloadable version of the classic puzzle game. Use vitamins to eliminate viruses in Classic mode, or play against a computer opponent in Vs. CPU mode. Make an appointment with Dr. Mario today!\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/TVKGWNz.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5108, '000480044b544545', 'TWL-N-KTEE', 'Tetris® Party Live', 'USA', 11763508, 'dsiw', '50010000003881', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/48114fbd0e56f097c56edc60767773d174c7f1eddfd3d689d246bacf112c8a08.jpg', 'Now you can party with Tetris® whenever and wherever you want! Tetris Party Live features several exciting game modes from the popular Tetris Party series, including Marathon (a favorite single-player mode), Computer Battle (challenge the computer), VS Battle (challenge a friend), and Duel Space (strategize to claim the most space against a friend). But the party doesn’t stop there! Take the Tetris fun online via Nintendo Wi-Fi\nConnection, where you can play multiplayer Tetris against up to three opponents at a time. You can also see how your Tetris Party Live skills stack up against the rest of the world using the global ranking system.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/030VNKF.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5109, '000480044b4f4745', 'TWL-N-KOGE', 'G.G Series SUPER HERO OGRE', 'USA', 4203316, 'dsiw', '50010000003287', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/329fc50373db48a31c589c59f327c7f83e3aab09900268b4aa5577726fd18ca7.jpg', 'Charge up your Superhero Attacks and be a super cool superhero!\n\nAn evil army is on the march! Confront them and save the day in this superhero fighting action game. Each time you defeat an enemy with a Hero Attack, your Hero Gauge goes up. Then, with simple button commands, you can use the charged-up Hero Gauge to unleash powerful Superhero Attacks on your foes. Continue to land Hero Attacks to keep the Hero Gauge charged and perform a devastating chain of Superhero Attacks. After you destroy the lesser enemies, a boss will appear. Defeat it to clear the level.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/q1t2v1o.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5110, '000480044b454245', 'TWL-N-KEBE', 'Electroplankton™ Hanenbow', 'USA', 2770740, 'dsiw', '50010000001709', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3a246afac945ac0ed828d9efd93fb1ae68c7f15414b9d0095fdbf466e355203f.jpg', 'A strange electronic sea awaits you. In this sea, you’ll encounter unique species of tiny Electroplankton that respond to your touch and voice to create unforgettable sounds and melodies. Enjoy getting to know these fascinating plankton as you relax to their sights and sounds!\n\nNormally an aquatic creature, Hanenbow sometimes use floating leaves to launch themselves out of the water, creating strange sounds and melodies as they bounce off of leaves. Entire schools of Hanenbow have been known to launch out of the water, one after another! As a leaf is repeatedly hit by flying Hanenbow, it gradually changes color. This also alters the sound made by bouncing Hanenbow. When all of the leaves turn red, a flower will bloom. It is still unclear why the Hanenbow display this curious behavior.\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/cASRK0o.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5111, '000480044b454945', 'TWL-N-KEIE', 'Electroplankton™ Beatnes', 'USA', 3040052, 'dsiw', '50010000001903', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/54825f6fdd9aa08d0b5a50eb71cc978b912e35693be6b6af38ad497a8ccd5e92.jpg', 'A strange electronic sea awaits you. In this sea, you’ll encounter unique species of tiny Electroplankton that respond to your touch and voice to create unforgettable sounds and melodies. Enjoy getting to know these fascinating plankton as you relax to their sights and sounds!\n\nBeatnes are curious plankton with geometrically shaped heads that form vertical strands like seaweed. Their bodies are made up of eight sections, each featuring a distinctive diamond-shaped tail. The sound of a Beatnes can vary wildly depending on which segment of the body is tapped. However, all of the sounds closely resemble the short-wave and triangular-wave sound effects from a Nintendo Entertainment System sound chip. When Beatnes are tapped in time with a rhythm, they continue to repeat the sounds in perfect time for a short period.\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/a55M7wk.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5112, '000480044b4e4245', 'TWL-N-KNBE', 'myNotebook: Blue™', 'USA', 2257716, 'dsiw', '50010000003262', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/75fa934e9c26f914411b39f552a2dab6defda0b98ce0e8e039cfc5ad10217190.jpg', 'myNotebook allows you to take notes wherever you are. Just pop open your Nintendo DSi system and jot down your thoughts! Make a list and cross it off, or even play your favorite pen and paper games (games not included). You can even personalize your notebook by drawing on the cover and changing the paper type with 18 different unlockable squared and lined paper styles. Use the pen or pencil to make your notes or doodles and then erase the bits you don''t like. With five ink colors, you''ll always be able to make your notes and doodles look stylish.', 'none', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/z5MKjHh.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5113, '000480044b414945', 'TWL-N-KAIE', 'Art Academy™: First Semester', 'USA', 13966132, 'dsiw', '50010000006865', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c1771d95718e5775401c4bc938fdbf54f19a2c6e4b47e2f161410af6306c98db.jpg', 'Art Academy is a portable art course that anyone can join to replace the lecture-like structure of art school, or the trial and error on canvas, with a Nintendo DSi system.\n\nArt Academy: First Semester will guide you through the basics of using pencil and paints, which draw like the real things. With your own paintbrush set and color palette, you will learn texturing and blending techniques, along with how to depict light and shade. There is also Free Paint mode where you can select photos from your Nintendo DSi Camera Album to draw from. In just a few lessons, you will be discovering your inner artist and creating your own masterpieces, with art skills that you can apply with real-life materials.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/8g7RW2P.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5114, '000480044b4a494a', 'TWL-N-KJIJ', '最凶横スクアクション vol.1 ノロイ ノ ゲエム 血', 'JPN', 7565108, 'dsiw', '50010000005303', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/accf238f5d48a2eb7995ec321579ecb46cde38b94d5e793fdd7e793755dad68b.jpg', '最凶横スクロールアクション第１弾。\nニンテンドーＤＳ用ソフト「ナナシ ノ ゲエム 目」に搭載され好評を博した呪の横スクロールアクションゲームが、ＤＳｉウェアに登場。ジャンプを駆使して数々のデストラップをくぐり抜け、ゴールを目指す横スクロールアクションゲームです。\nコンパクトなステージにピリリと辛いアクションが詰まっていて、遊びごたえは十分。更に、誰でも遊べるノオマル、やりごたえ十分なアナザア、悶絶必至のジゴクと３つの難易度をご用意。順に解いていくことで、誰でもシンプルかつ深いアクションを楽しむことができるようになっています。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1278b87cb5d7c7429a161db5c8473d5414acf9ff4dacd70016c297017b110362.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/4lm4Lai.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ULuam6X.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5115, '000480044b424256', 'TWL-N-KBBV', 'BOMBERMAN™ BLITZ', 'EUR', 8572724, 'dsiw', '50010000002303', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b633d62ee1c321e4dcb0db83247e775435b7baa4968cc5d478ad0212844d536e.jpg', 'With 10 million copies sold, the\n"Bomberman" series is the definitive\nparty game, great for a quick battle\nanywhere, anytime.<br>\n<br>\nSingle Player: Hone your skills\nagainst CPU players.<br>\n<br>\nMultiplayer: Play wirelessly with\nother players who have the game. (Up\nto 8 players.)<br>\n<br>\nThis game includes 10 Battle Game\nstages from "BOMBERMAN 2".', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/95ae208f85134d6869cdb95804262690ca27df91b41743b2d1ae9adfe9d216af.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/C6tQRbE.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/kW1pI99.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5116, '000480044b4e4445', 'TWL-N-KNDE', 'Brain Age™ Express: Arts & Letters', 'USA', 8889140, 'dsiw', '50010000003263', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9b4d5d5ae7a618cfd384ec2b0fd39488d461ac4158b88429302d56872329efa3.jpg', 'This edition of the popular Brain Age series offers players a mix of new and familiar exercises, all with an artistic focus. Test your spelling in Word Attack, enjoy literary classics in Reading Aloud, and tune your musical skills in Piano Player. A new Themes mode challenges you in drawing, photography, and voice acting and lets you share your creativity with your friends and family. And if you need a break from things, the always-enjoyable Virus Buster makes its return. Prepare for another round of training your brain in minutes a day!\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/imZ9GHB.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5117, '000480044b565345', 'TWL-N-KVSE', 'Aahh! Spot The Difference', 'USA', 4695860, 'dsiw', '50010000009501', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b74090d3e69e3fbec483917c4a41f02ed59babe92c60904bd26bde5ac85eed4c.jpg', 'Demonstrate your skills of observation in this engaging "Spot The Difference" game! Complete 40 challenging levels in four unique scenarios by spotting the differences between the upper and lower screens. But you must be quick, as most of the objects and the camera are constantly moving. You can also test your skills in three additional modes: Survival, Speed Attack and Time Attack. You will earn one star for finding the required number of differences, two stars will be awarded if you find more, and if you find all the differences in the level you will receive three stars. Good luck!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/sZpF1r4.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5118, '000480044b334a45', 'TWL-N-K3JE', 'iSpot Japan', 'USA', 6288180, 'dsiw', '50010000009221', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/eb69f8feb5e01ca9abf64cbb1146759e8b12a63ad699bcde17a3c78f864a9204.jpg', 'iSpot Japan takes you on a journey across the land of the rising sun, explaining facts and curiosities about Japanese culture, while you play the classic “Spot the Difference” game in the country''s most beautiful locations. Find three, four, or five differences in each picture, depending on the selected difficulty level, and unlock them in the gallery to learn about local cuisine, historical characters or important monuments, together with their location in the map. Ranging from southern Kyushu to northern Hokkaido, you''ll get to know all of Japan through exclusive beautiful pictures carefully tricked to create visually challenging differences.\n\nFeatures:\n*Exclusive beautiful pictures of Japan.\n*Detailed explanation and map location of every picture.\n*Competitive VS multiplayer and gallery mode.\n*Three difficulty levels with three, four, or five differences per location.\n*A total of 150 pictures illustrating the 4 main islands of Japan.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/SHK1EAm.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5119, '000480044b585550', 'TWL-N-KXUP', 'Publisher Dream', 'EUR', 5378868, 'dsiw', '50010000014252', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/067a893b3a876d75484e04ce506a1afd99ded0e0fbfc9f9c57fe7e28709a131b.jpg', 'Ever dream about making and\npublishing your own digital games?\n<br/><br/>\nPublisher Dream is a simulation game\nthat places you in the owner''s seat of\na company called "Triangle". Triangle\nfocuses on a digital platform called\n"cShop" for development and\npublishing endeavours.\n<br/><br/>\nYou can hire people to develop\nvarious game genres, and control the\ngame budgets and quality to\nsafeguard limited resources. Do you\nwant to be one of the biggest\npublishers on cShop? This may be a\ngreat way to test your skills before\nactually starting your own game\ncompany.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Eg71gdJ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5120, '000480044b325856', 'TWL-N-K2XV', 'AlphaBounce', 'EUR', 8055604, 'dsiw', '50010000001321', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f05d8b8087ba1c9ce5717667eba14daee68edfae42e4c6ad0be016569bfe6fbc.jpg', 'AlphaBounce combines the classical\nbrick-breaking concept with RPG\nfeatures, offering you the chance to\nexplore an endless universe with\nmillions of levels!<br>\n<br>\nYou have been taken prisoner by an\nevil intergalactic mining corporation\nwhich exploits the galaxy''s mineral\nresources. Take your only chance to\nescape and blast your way through\nthe bricks back to Earth!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ba892f09b1197c3aae6611d60ed14bef49a5da5694c0a4e45cdac3dba8d14ba7.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/lbKsXLA.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/0oAwiF7.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5121, '000480044b434456', 'TWL-N-KCDV', 'Dictionary 6 in 1 with Camera Function', 'EUR', 12345140, 'dsiw', '50010000002801', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fe1f98ae48f6c2fcd60fce06f0fb75c38ca2b8fc460aade263dec3a2042e09c1.jpg', 'Dictionary 6 in 1 with Camera\nFunction is no ordinary dictionary; it\ntransforms your Nintendo DSi into a\nunique language tool. Enter a word by\nhand, or simply snap a photo of it, to\nreceive an instant translation.<br>\n<br>\nThousands of everyday words and\nexpressions in six different languages\nare included: English, French,\nGerman, Spanish, Italian and\nJapanese.<br>\n<br>\nUse the Touch Screen to enter a\nword via the on-screen keyboard or\nwrite the letters by hand using the\nstylus. Alternatively, use the camera\nto take a photo of a word – such as in\na magazine or on a sign – and the\nsoftware will do the rest and translate\nit.<br>\n<br>\nDictionary 6 in 1 with Camera\nFunction is useful when travelling, for\ncasual study, or anytime you need to\nbrush up your knowledge of foreign\nwords.<br>\n<br>\nThis product does not require age\nclassification.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6d058e03e38bdb63a361131b9d93d98e63adc0a61e76c638b355413c8c803667.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/jLAVv1v.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/NxPvuOp.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5122, '000480044b443956', 'TWL-N-KD9V', 'A Little Bit of... Dr. Mario™', 'EUR', 4086580, 'dsiw', '50010000002764', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/cdc1641f1354be38e375ba843f640ee00f8725c45756db38385e134657ecc889.jpg', 'Dr. Mario is back, to cure your\npuzzle fever! A Little Bit of... Dr.\nMario brings you this classic game in\nan easy-to-digest portable form for\nyour Nintendo DSi!<br>\n<br>\nEnjoy the original inspiration for\nGerm Buster (as seen in More Brain\nTraining from Dr Kawashima). Simply\ndefeat all the viruses in the bottle by\nlining up coloured capsules that match\nthe colour of the viruses. Watch out,\nbecause if the bottle fills to the brim\nwith capsules, it’s Game Over!<br>\n<br>\nChoose Classic Mode to play solo, or\nbattle against the computer in Vs CPU\nMode in a race to clear all the viruses\nfirst. You can also set the number of\nviruses and game speed, to tune the\ndifficulty level to your liking.<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously released software.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9b59b7b53a7290345a19b1fcebd29be82d3a117068f47db6716c35db7888bb8a.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/cHCJfQa.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ElyJ1Tu.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5123, '000480044b503656', 'TWL-N-KP6V', 'Pyoro™', 'EUR', 1419060, 'dsiw', '50010000004682', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/148b06130f2a1006b2408739ccb6cca98d3ff5344d7715e21695fdeaa5e9a43f.jpg', 'He’s a small bird with a very long\ntongue and an insatiable appetite for\nbeans. Luckily for Pyoro, beans drop\nconstantly from the sky. However, if\nPyoro lets a bean fall, it breaks a hole\nin the ground that he can’t cross.<br>\n<br>\nThis fast-paced action game requires\nskill and strategy to snatch all the\nbeans you can, while dodging the\nones you can’t and making sure you\ndon''t get trapped! The higher in the\nsky that you grab a bean, the more\npoints it will be worth.<br>\n<br>\nPlus – if you master Pyoro, you can\nunlock the even faster-paced Pyoro 2!\nIn this game, you can spit seeds at\nhigh speed to bring down more beans\nthan ever before!<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously-released software.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6122d429195d6005f4bf48e35db9a4a317de5a8b7b17fc22d114950920e0ac07.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/IiL4zGH.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/luPFyjD.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5124, '000480044b504650', 'TWL-N-KPFP', 'Pop Island Paperfield', 'EUR', 6245172, 'dsiw', '50010000004701', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/94840756129c2ae697d690b06b951164ed669840ef3732c8f633f2308eba1bdc.jpg', 'FUN IS DECLARED! Thanks to the\neasy pick-up and play control themes,\ndive into this fresh universe and have\nfun in almost no time!Join your team\nand race, surf or fly on three new\nislands. Get a maximum of flags to win\nthe victory in the "Race for flags" or\n"Capture the flag" mode.<br>\n<br>\nFURIOUS MACHINEWith the new\n"Magic Shooters" team, take control\nof eight land, sea and air vehicles or\nanimals, including tanks, hovercrafts,\nplanes, surfing penguins, eagles,\nblack cats!<br>\n<br>\n1-8 PLAYERSIn Solo Mode, rack up\npoints and unlock new playable\nvehicles and maps.Thanks to the DS\nDownload Play feature (available on\nALL Nintendo DS and Nintendo DSi) ,\nshare Pop Island - Paperfield and\ncompete joyfully with up to seven\nfriends!<br>\n<br>\nPLUS If you own Pop Island on your\nNintendo DSi , you can get three new\nmaps and four vehicles including the\nhelicopter and the submarine!<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously released software.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/76ee6dd2420df116dde0fecf5d2d3bcc88f2fa07a6cc7d29d0e63e2ee8749b37.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/CLvpAis.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/exDwivd.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5125, '000480044b534c56', 'TWL-N-KSLV', '2-in-1 Solitaire', 'EUR', 786228, 'dsiw', '50010000006242', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/88cc6a3a6519b7daa46e32556b335d3e3e402598f97e584d9e8cd209897ef905.jpg', '2-in-1 Solitaire features two of the\nmost popular versions of the\nworld-famous card game – Spider and\nKlondike – with simple Touch Screen\ncontrols.<br>\n<br>\nIn Spider, the aim is to arrange cards\nin piles of a single suit from King\ndown to Ace, thereby removing the\npile from play. When all cards are\nremoved, you win the game.<br>\n<br>\nThe goal of Klondike is to arrange\ncards from Ace to King in piles, one\nfor each suit, on the four foundations.\nYou win when all cards have been\nmoved to the foundations.<br>\n<br>\nVarious difficulty levels are available\nfor Spider and Klondike, allowing\nbeginners or experts to enjoy the\ngame at their own pace.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fe57ecf087be931d19a1b6e48de2b276203acf2208ff1b4b50bfb200d1792d5b.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/2iECyKm.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/YoRRuNg.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5126, '000480044b535256', 'TWL-N-KSRV', 'Aura-Aura Climber™', 'EUR', 5995316, 'dsiw', '50010000006246', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f172844991d0611b31694ba0bc0fcf48444a235e1d7679b39eb5a28549024950.jpg', 'Meet gaming''s newest ''star''!\nAura-Aura has fallen from the sky and\nlanded on Earth, and only you can\nreturn him to his home in the heavens.<br>\n<br>\nUse Aura-Aura''s grapple arm to\nswing from grapple points floating in\nthe clouds and reach the highest\npossible altitude before the timer runs\nout. You''ll find a variety of helpful\nitems on your way up, such as grapple\narm extensions and bombs that blast\nyou upwards. Watch out for the many\nenemies and hazards, though, and try\nnot to fall; it''s a long way down!<br>\n<br>\nThere are two play modes to choose\nfrom: Score Attack and Endless\nMode. In Score Attack, your aim is to\nreach each goal with as many points\nas possible. In Endless Mode, you\nhave to climb as high as you can\nwithin a set time limit.<br>\n<br>\nWith gameplay that''s simple yet\nsatisfying, lots of medals to unlock\nand classic ''just one more go''\nreplayability, Aura-Aura Climber will\nbring you to new heights of fun!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/dcac59d296786870b19408fd8d71d2c66ae4a72df5bb0f11db68563beae1950c.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/VFkkqjC.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/YjIXYsh.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5127, '000480044b574756', 'TWL-N-KWGV', 'Animal Crossing™ Calculator', 'EUR', 2478900, 'dsiw', '50010000006462', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b33b396358f0675ab9fcaf2c3050ffd66b91ddc4fdbadaad362b2d4a5415efb9.jpg', 'Make maths more fun with this Animal\nCrossing-themed calculator! Simply\nuse the Touch Screen to enter figures\nand make calculations, accompanied\nby classic Animal Crossing visuals and\nsounds.<br>\n<br>\nIn addition to a fully-featured\ncalculator, Animal Crossing Calculator\nalso includes a unit converter for\nconverting to and from a variety of\ndifferent measurements such as\nweight, length, speed, temperature\nand more. You can even convert\nhuman years to and from animal\nyears!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e8bd1cd28cf6d6e3c7c452f3182beb1da495441864b85e1aa9eaedde88c63b55.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/qHK6tXM.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/1kFO1nM.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5128, '000480044b5a3650', 'TWL-N-KZ6P', 'AfterZoom', 'EUR', 10087220, 'dsiw', '50010000007066', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7f2d98d593fc98c99ae628325bd3d86cd6d5b168719453342f67eae92b6d8a3f.jpg', 'Immerse yourself into a world of\nhidden creatures!<br>\n<br>\nAfterZoom turns the camera of\nyour Nintendo DSi or your\nNintendo 3DS systems\ninto a microscope.<br>\n<br>\nExplore your surroundings and\ndiscover new forms of life.<br>\n<br>\nCollect dozens of different species and\ntake good care of them at the\nSpecimens Bank.<br>\n<br>\nMix the formulas you''ll need to feed\nyour organisms at the Chemical Lab.<br>\n<br>\nBattle your colonies against more\npowerful ones to win them over and\ncomplete your collection.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/h7qdhEU.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5129, '000480044b555245', 'TWL-N-KURE', 'I Must Run!', 'USA', 5476148, 'dsiw', '50010000009771', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/811fca9545da62d8164d529bba04cf3296477b9b6bd0d5ad1951d9492bf6e670.jpg', 'I Must Run! is a skill-based action running game. Jump across gaps between jail buildings, run through a subway station, and test your reflexes in a deadly dash over construction site cranes. Reach the city center and save your wife. Remember, you have only 24 hours.\n\nLet''s hope your fitness level can cope, because you must run! Once you have completed story mode, try to achieve the highest score in the never-ending run in six available levels: Jail, Subway, Sewers, Construction Site, Suburbs and Rooftops.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/OW2tFzi.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5130, '000480044b525145', 'TWL-N-KRQE', 'Rytmik Rock Edition', 'USA', 13703988, 'dsiw', '50010000003441', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/71d010e916230a91b75323ad2f1c3139babcee92f61885cb3fd038e3ab8678fd.jpg', 'Rytmik Rock Edition is an application for creating rhythmical and melodic themes and for composing whole songs. It contains more than 130 carefully selected sound samples of drums, keyboards, bass, clean, lead and rhythm guitars.\n\nWith Rytmik Rock Edition you can quickly and easily create the basic building stone—an audio clip. It consists of musical notations for up to four instruments that you may transpose, select their location in the stereo field, and modify their volume, polyphony and echo. You may arbitrarily combine up to 128 such clips in four tracks and create complex pieces of music. Moreover you have a rhythm library and varied collection of 10 pre-made compositions at your disposal that you may quickly compose your own pieces from.\n\nFor the best musical experience we recommend connecting headphones or quality speaker system. You’ll become the king of the Rock party in no time...', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/OnhBOcx.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5131, '000480044b4e4150', 'TWL-N-KNAP', 'Petit Computer', 'EUR', 4435764, 'dsiw', '50010000015233', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9142af73496dfe8d914a7e8a91748040c7b379d3de9aa046eed6403c538c5731.jpg', 'Petit Computer is an easy-to-use\nprogramming tool that lets you create\neverything from music, to images, to\nyour very own original games using an\nadapted version of the classic BASIC\nprogramming language.\n<br/><br/>\nWhether you have experience of\nBASIC, or are a complete novice, you\nwill find that Petit Computer will give\nyou the skills you need to create your\nown programs. You can select\ncommands and run programs using the\nNintendo DSi™/Nintendo 3DS™ Touch\nScreen, and you can even share your\ncreations via Nintendo Network,\nallowing you to collaborate with other\nusers. You can also create special QR\nCode® patterns containing your\nprograms that other users can scan\nusing their Nintendo DSi/Nintendo\n3DS system camera. Petit Computer is\na perfect companion for anyone who\nhas ever wanted to delve deeper into\nthe world of computer programming.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5383d9663e1d7085f6f54deb7c7f459ea8b9d2446510a24984de3c730cc78116.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/j3MZUOT.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/gxqoi5g.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5132, '000480044b4d5a56', 'TWL-N-KMZV', 'Sleep Clock', 'EUR', 5466932, 'dsiw', '50010000004484', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9655b29800f2339fdbc5e9770a4f6c02a4f982048df4af8eb46934687eab0fa9.jpg', 'Sleep Clock is not just an alarm\nclock: you can use it to record and\nanalyse your sleeping patterns, which\nhelps you to manage your sense of\nwell-being.<br>\n<br>\nSimply start the timer when you go to\nbed, and put your Nintendo DSi into\nSleep Mode by closing it. Upon\nwaking, you will be asked how you\nfeel; did you have a refreshing night''s\nsleep, or did you toss and turn? Your\nanswers and the times you went to\nsleep and woke up will be plotted on\ndaily, weekly and monthly graphs,\nallowing you to closely monitor your\nsleep time and quality. Mr Sheep,\nrenowned ovine sleep expert, is also\non hand to offer advice and comments\nabout your sleep activity.<br>\n<br>\nSet up to three different alarm times,\nwith a choice between built-in alarm\nsounds or custom sounds recorded in\nNintendo DSi Sound. You can also\nhave the Nintendo DSi speak the time\nwhen the alarm sounds. And of\ncourse, no alarm clock would be\ncomplete without a snooze function\nfor those ''just five more minutes''\nmornings!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/55f90cf1464130a847745357c6a221827e5bfc5684608bd15762942e6718d356.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/pKnlO5o.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/pdS23LH.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5133, '000480044b435956', 'TWL-N-KCYV', 'Calculator', 'EUR', 1920820, 'dsiw', '50010000002762', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/777c0b025876ee88f82406407ca56a7736fb875a6ed50c693aa4e5e661e92106.jpg', 'Calculator handles 135 measurement\nunits and constants of most types\nwhich ordinary people use every day,\nincluding length, weight, temperature,\nspeed, volume, area, and time.<br>\n<br>\nFeatures:<br>\n<br>\n- The basic and scientific calculators<br>\n<br>\n- Calculate with degrees or radians<br>\n<br>\n- Supports decimal, hexadecimal,\noctal, binary numbers<br>\n<br>\n- Percent button will behave just like\non a basic calculator<br>\n<br>\n- Memory buttons will also behave\njust like on a basic calculator<br>\n<br>\n- Database of 135 most popular\nunits and physical constants<br>\n<br>\n- Reverse direction of any\nconversion<br>\n<br>\n- You punch in digits and Calculator\ndoes the conversion on the fly', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a37267737a319c056e3fc72718b95ebfde9ec12490192acc89af71be559454da.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/E6yp6QI.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/cDxUrxl.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5134, '000480044b4e4145', 'TWL-N-KNAE', 'Petit Computer', 'USA', 4733748, 'dsiw', '50010000011166', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e721cd4ea7f3789bf483886319788b0c48ad118559f5d5c3772fe8ff6ea458e3.jpg', 'Petit Computer is an easy-to-use programming tool that lets you create everything from music, to images, to your very own original games using an adapted version of the classic BASIC programming language.\n\nWhether you have experience of BASIC, or are a complete novice, you will find that Petit Computer will give you the skills you need to create your own programs. You can select commands and run programs using the Nintendo DSi Touch Screen, and you can even share your creations via DS Wireless Play, allowing you to collaborate with other users. You can also use QR codes to share programs with other users. Special software that can be accessed free of charge online will allow you to create QR codes which contain all the data from your program. Other users can scan these QR codes with their Nintendo DSi Camera, allowing them to enjoy your programs. Petit Computer is a perfect companion for anyone who has ever wanted to delve deeper into the world of computer programming.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/W2PMtzb.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47');
INSERT INTO `3dsgames` (`id`, `titleID`, `serial`, `name`, `region`, `size`, `type`, `contentID`, `iconURL`, `gdesc`, `thumb`, `scrcount`, `imgur_iconURL`, `imgur_thumb`, `count`, `time`) VALUES
(5135, '000480044b555756', 'TWL-N-KUWV', 'WarioWare™: Snapped!', 'EUR', 9954100, 'dsiw', '50010000006441', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bea149aa912db281f188b66a0a1a22c1616684f401a40fc84d5bc07d66b42c78.jpg', 'Wario returns with more manic\nminigames made especially for\nNintendo DSi!<br>\n<br>\nWarioWare: Snapped! uses the\ninternal camera to literally make you\nthe star of the show!<br>\n<br>\nTake part in wacky challenges simply\nby moving your face and body as you\nfly along four wild roller coasters,\nhosted by Wario and his wacky pals.\nWhile Wario’s games are all about big\nmovements, Mona’s require more\ndexterity. Kat & Ana’s challenges are\nplayed with a friend for double\nhilarity!<br>\n<br>\nWario has a few tricks up his sleeve\nthat keep the fun times flowing even\nafter you''ve finished moving!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/046e8e7510fc2718458a5ea63053be71dfb4c484ad72eb49828a59e0f106a1a5.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/7ESnvJc.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/gdOjYen.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5136, '000480044b543850', 'TWL-N-KT8P', 'GO Series: Tower of Deus', 'EUR', 4251444, 'dsiw', '50010000006302', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b84974018e6577ef47a3e56d15d495cec5ac024707146c0c7f94ce06f8f45b4c.jpg', 'GO Series presents Tower of Deus\nfrom Tom Create.<br>\n<br>\nOvercome a deadly curse as you race\nto the top of the tower in this dark,\natmospheric, 2D platform game.The\nonly way to release the curse is to\nrun, jump and fly your way to the top\nof the dreaded tower before the time\nruns out. There are 40 eerie levels\nwith 10 types of gothic-style\ngraphics, not for the easily scared or\nfaint hearted.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Vll68Uo.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5137, '000480044b564950', 'TWL-N-KVIP', 'Anonymous Notes Chapter 1', 'EUR', 6052660, 'dsiw', '50010000007362', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a9b1777dedd6e5a203f26f68bdf5d50dde71a8927cd536e7e07806578d3ff836.jpg', 'This is a full-on action RPG packed\nwith exhilaration which takes place\ninside an infinitely-extending dungeon.<br>\n<br>\nDo away with the monsters crawling\nabout the various dungeons, and try\nyour hand at defeating the terrifying\nboss monster lurking in the darkest\ndepths.<br>\n<br>\nUsing the attack known as "Soul\nCapture", the main character can steal\nmonsters'' magic and other skills, as\nwell as pick up weapons and shields\nto power up along the way..<br>\n<br>\nYou''ll get an exhilarating rush from\nstrengthening the character through\nthe combination of different equipment\nand skills, and then crushing the\nmonsters in a powerful sweep.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bf08489494edfad5434f9960b62ba442a422fbd48c881a96840e728ec75048da.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/dfwVxmA.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/82hoA6g.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5138, '000480044b563250', 'TWL-N-KV2P', 'Anonymous Notes Chapter 2', 'EUR', 5870388, 'dsiw', '50010000007363', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/21fe17a5d756b082ad0bfd219435b87ba109a20dc298f89013bbac78950fb99c.jpg', 'This is a full-on action RPG packed\nwith exhilaration which takes place\ninside an infinitely-extending dungeon.<br>\n<br>\nDo away with the monsters crawling\nabout the various dungeons, and try\nyour hand at defeating the terrifying\nboss monster lurking in the darkest\ndepths.<br>\n<br>\nUsing the attack known as "Soul\nCapture", the main character can steal\nmonsters'' magic and other skills, as\nwell as pick up weapons and shields\nto power up along the way..<br>\n<br>\nYou''ll get an exhilarating rush from\nstrengthening the character through\nthe combination of different equipment\nand skills, and then crushing the\nmonsters in a powerful sweep.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4c6929ac2fe7e1c58a3655ada30d6c2961cf0aaad8e38c7bfdc40e29d8caf798.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/PXoXW9f.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/3oANbEq.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5139, '000480044b555250', 'TWL-N-KURP', 'I Must Run!', 'EUR', 5523252, 'dsiw', '50010000009907', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1e8341dd624f3b3589d95ed40d3f233869407e9fbae8cc91f66be7f5f757f7e0.jpg', 'I Must Run! is a skill-based action\nrunning game. Jump across gaps\nbetween prison buildings, run through\nan underground station, and test your\nreflexes in a deadly dash over building\nsite cranes. Reach the city centre and\nsave your wife. Remember, you have\nonly 24 hours. Let''s hope your fitness\nlevels can cope, because you must\nrun! Once you have completed story\nmode, try to achieve the highest score\nin the never-ending run in six available\nlevels: Prison, Underground, Sewers,\nBuilding Site, Suburbs and Rooftops.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/tBjUNsN.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5140, '000480044b414156', 'TWL-N-KAAV', 'Art Style: AQUITE™', 'EUR', 11975476, 'dsiw', '50010000002002', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/aec1e0a25587b86dc5eb5b8205214ab62e42c10aa11df735fcdb1f060a0b5b81.jpg', 'The Art Style series brings you\nunique, simple-to-play games with\nstriking visuals and immersive sound.<br>\n<br>\nIn Art Style: AQUITE, feel the\npressure in a race against time to\nclear panels from an undersea pipe –\nthe more you clear, the deeper your\ndiver goes. Fail to clear panels and\nthe Pressure Line will descend,\nclouding your vision and increasing\nthe difficulty!<br>\n<br>\nAs well as the main Interval Dive\nmode, try Endless Dive to test your\nendurance, and even visit the\nAquarium to meet the many creatures\nthat share your ocean!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/70c6db5c7c979b2c82be9368530969e810bbe99d9cf00b616585c14dbec32b8e.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/MUcqEoW.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/pvopB2u.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5141, '000480044b414456', 'TWL-N-KADV', 'Art Style: CODE™', 'EUR', 12840756, 'dsiw', '50010000001706', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ca5e85393b76c599af25e2981765b55598bc0bca01623af9461d44f7f67c29c9.jpg', 'The Art Style series brings you\nunique, simple-to-play games with\nstriking visuals and immersive sound.<br>\n<br>\nArt Style: CODE is a fast-paced\npuzzle game that will test your quick\narithmetic skills. Line up the moving\ndigits with the stylus so that they add\nup to 10 in a horizontal or vertical\nline to clear them from the screen.<br>\n<br>\nThree single-player modes are\nincluded: Challenge (clear a set\nnumber of digits), Puzzle (clear the\nscreen in as few moves as possible)\nand Endless (keep clearing digits for a\nhigh score). You can also use DS\nDownload Play to challenge a friend\nin VS Mode. All they need is another\nNintendo DSi, or even a Nintendo\nDS/DS Lite system!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9555768e95638fe21c706bac94404b7ce4d38e9edec979c463f4da8953364b07.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/3yiYqkH.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/3h7C5mB.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5142, '000480044b414856', 'TWL-N-KAHV', 'Art Style: BOXLIFE™', 'EUR', 9043764, 'dsiw', '50010000001821', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6eb1e721b69de0960d4019f33046c249cc5f4898eeadcb18bd4650b0376d98d6.jpg', 'The Art Style series brings you\nunique, simple-to-play games with\nstriking visuals and immersive sound.<br>\n<br>\nBOXLIFE is a unique puzzle game that\ninvolves building boxes as quickly and\ncarefully as possible. Simply use the\nTouch Screen to cut and fold paper\ninto shapes that make boxes when\nfolded, using the stylus.<br>\n<br>\nIn R&D Mode, discover the many\ndifferent patterns that form boxes, and\nuse them to cut and construct boxes\nagainst the clock. In Factory Mode,\nturn a profit by making as many boxes\nas you can in a set time, using an\nendless sheet of paper. But wasted\npaper means lost cash, and less to\nspend on items for your home. So\nyou’d better box clever; you’ve got\nyour work cut out!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/91f95db51024e562033b3deddd5eb9eb31f864a5f8ad46c5faed9210e6ee46f3.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/aLMrM9j.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/WlcmM8y.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5143, '000480044b414956', 'TWL-N-KAIV', 'Art Academy™ First Semester', 'EUR', 14102324, 'dsiw', '50010000001711', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8d11fa40bf285851f76ff657bf6c2042ead8d970f3ff08b4c2ce22f5c7a88836.jpg', 'Learn how to draw and paint with this\neasy-to-use software that transforms\nyour Nintendo DSi system and stylus\ninto a canvas and brush!<br>\n<br>\nIn Art Academy: First Semester,\nfriendly tutor Vince takes you step by\nstep through the basics of artistic\ntheory and techniques. Start simple\nwith still-life pencil sketches before\nmoving on to watercolours. Soon\nyou’ll be putting your skills into\npractice, emulating classics from old\nmasters like Dürer and Cézanne.<br>\n<br>\nArt Academy also features a Free\nPaint mode for creating original\nworks. You can exchange images with\nthe Nintendo DSi Camera album, from\nwhere you can share your\nmasterpieces with friends and even\nupload to Facebook!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/41ebfc91a247298856ae67deed884beca5e54b2e698ef589ef2206908c754c43.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/nra0z3Y.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/QR8zviI.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5144, '000480044b414b56', 'TWL-N-KAKV', 'Art Style: KUBOS™', 'EUR', 7693108, 'dsiw', '50010000001712', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/432a1fcc10972a37bf3371a8531f4daabd41fe706d027bc9a40a41d6760c7fc6.jpg', 'The Art Style series brings you\nunique, simple-to-play games with\nstriking visuals and immersive sound.<br>\n<br>\nIn KUBOS your aim is to climb a\ntower of cubes which becomes higher\nas new cubes drop from above. Walk\nacross the cubes to score points,\navoiding being crushed by the falling\ncubes; but keep climbing or you’ll fall\nwhen the lower cubes disappear.<br>\n<br>\nIn TEN FLOORS mode, try to reach\nthe 10th floor while scoring as many\npoints as possible. In TOWER mode,\nsimply climb as high as you can.\nQuickly defuse bomb cubes before\nthey blow a hole in your tower, and\nremove obstructing cubes with a\ngentle push or a huge Cube Blast!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8712e35715ae8a744369871aa617cdb1c73e4b45b056bedcea22d07f5a1a467b.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/fIvBVAV.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/MWODPFV.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5145, '000480044b414d56', 'TWL-N-KAMV', 'Paper Plane™', 'EUR', 1521460, 'dsiw', '50010000001713', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/debdec752ec8c4b84ffded6746a575575bcf8b0c3fe9ccbaaccfa559e0ed0be9.jpg', 'Spread your wings with this\nirresistibly simple action game for one\nor two players! Simply manoeuvre the\npaper plane through a winding\ncourse - and don''t collide with the\nobstacles. But that''s easier said than\ndone!<br>\n<br>\nIn Endless Mode, the longer you\nsurvive through the\nrandomly-generated course, the\nhigher your score. Or try Time Attack\nMode to complete special courses as\nquickly as possible.<br>\n<br>\nYou can also play together with a\nfriend in Race Mode. Each player\ntakes one side of the Nintendo DSi\nsystem to control and race with their\nown paper plane!<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously-released software.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/530cf9ef1812b6cc3593ea3bffaa09f19755c8c3f197b835ccb856c99fea480b.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/B2A94we.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/aFdXCW5.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5146, '000480044b415056', 'TWL-N-KAPV', 'Art Style: PiCOPiCT™', 'EUR', 5819188, 'dsiw', '50010000001714', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/60f9e91b99940f7d2f16c21f2cf80e811334d304858072de33b2dd2134e5da7a.jpg', 'The Art Style series brings you\nunique, simple-to-play games with\nstriking visuals and immersive sound.<br>\n<br>\nIn PiCOPiCT, puzzle your way\nthrough a colourful, retro-themed\ngame with charming NES-era graphics\nand sounds. Build up pixel pictures of\nclassic Nintendo characters on the\nTop Screen by clearing the blocks\nthat fall onto the Touch Screen. Just\nuse the stylus to place blocks of a\nmatching colour in the path of the\nfalling blocks.<br>\n<br>\nEarn coins as you play, to unlock\nnew classic Nintendo\ncharacter-themed stages (including\nSuper Mario Bros., The Legend of\nZelda and more) and remixed music\narranged by renowned Japanese\n''chiptune'' band YMCK.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3c40d692cadd8c8d287ae3ff22521ec2f16c233e4c72a41b3983cd3f1bf1fb22.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/vYMOzS5.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/bed42Ak.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5147, '000480044b415356', 'TWL-N-KASV', 'Art Style: NEMREM™', 'EUR', 8839988, 'dsiw', '50010000001715', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2cf689bb57548e59005008f1385b5433aca57e1fdab558345999ad6b98d54798.jpg', 'The Art Style series brings you\nunique, simple-to-play games with\nstriking visuals and immersive sound.<br>\n<br>\nNEMREM is a relaxing logic puzzle\nwhere the objective is to match\ncoloured panels with spheres of the\nsame colour. Use your stylus to slide\nthe panels horizontally and vertically\nas you chill out to the soothing\nsounds of the game''s peaceful music.<br>\n<br>\nAlthough NEMREM is simple to play,\nlater levels offer deeper challenges to\ntest your logic powers, with multiple\ncolour combinations and even locked\npanels appearing. For the ultimate\ntest, can you complete each puzzle in\nas few moves as possible?', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/353ec8f220f872782a2ec8cd215ce8298c9f5bc4cf235daaf0a60b828a137191.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/v8Tju17.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/skuMv5r.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5148, '000480044b415656', 'TWL-N-KAVV', 'Art Style: INTERSECT™', 'EUR', 11779892, 'dsiw', '50010000005786', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1d20c65191d4e72e36ced8d162520b4a557882542988c46382fa39fae165a7ac.jpg', 'The Art Style series brings you\nunique, simple-to-play games with\nstriking visuals and immersive sound.<br>\n<br>\nINTERSECT is a puzzle game with a\ndifference, challenging your\nconcentration and reflexes. Direct\ndifferently coloured cars through a\ncrossroad so that only cars of the\nsame colour occupy a road. This will\ngenerate fuel, which is ignited to\npropel the precious Core away from\nthe approaching Spike. Earn high\nscores to win medals and even unlock\nnew visual themes and music tracks.<br>\n<br>\nPlay in Button Mode, using the\n+Control Pad to direct cars, or try\nTouch Mode and use the stylus. Each\nmode includes the single-player\nEndless mode, VS CPU mode and\nalso VS 2P for playing against a\nfriend using DS Download Play.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/dc1ce7a2db0180ef4586f0960f4a255283dfc65389aa71eb3967f32d5818ef6e.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/r5aU8qT.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/X1iJHf3.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5149, '000480044b415950', 'TWL-N-KAYP', 'ARMY DEFENDER', 'EUR', 4916020, 'dsiw', '50010000005801', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a7ea3a9570f706799c8e0be5b8e05c1bf45863dfe4685c73ffb2a0472e2aafa0.jpg', 'In ARMY DEFENDER, your mission is\nto defend your base against hordes of\ninvading enemies. Use all the weapons\nat your disposal to survive as long as\npossible.<br>\n<br>\nStanding in your way are soldiers,\ntanks, parachute troops, combat\nhelicopters, fighter planes, bombers\nand elite forces who will do\neverything in their power to stop you!<br>\n<br>\nIf the situation becomes desperate,\nyou can always fall back on the\natomic bomb to blow away the enemy\ninvasion!You have hours of gaming to\nlook forward to!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5cef723eda44a2075f8ff02ae089452587bda7ea8eaa9711e87e5b193e8e0f3a.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/2bkXtSp.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/L4sxhrf.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5150, '000480044b444c56', 'TWL-N-KDLV', 'Dragon''s Lair®', 'EUR', 16495412, 'dsiw', '50010000005841', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9f2725140fe3b15be218e73cf172a95fbe3a5053073883e0b7ae6d266a75ab10.jpg', 'You play the heroic Dirk the Daring, a\nvaliant knight on a quest to rescue the\nfair princess from the clutches of an\nevil dragon! Control the actions of the\ndaring adventurer, finding your way\nthrough the castle of a dark wizard,\nwho has enchanted it with treacherous\nmonsters and obstacles. In the\nmysterious caverns below the castle,\nyour odyssey continues against the\nawesome forces that oppose your\nefforts to reach the dragon’s lair.<br>\n<br>\nDragon’s Lair is a fully animated\nclassic arcade game from legendary\nanimator Don Bluth. You’ll make your\nway through the castle and caverns\nbelow by using your Nintendo DSi to\nmove and wield your sword. Beware\nof your foes, as they are numerous!<br>\n<br>\nLead on adventurer. Your quest\nawaits!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/93a672bee42194aaf3fc3b9d2695ae7446a0e7615659f3a8b2fffb2a3c2c1538.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/bkLU52U.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/cSZZFiP.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5151, '000480044b444d56', 'TWL-N-KDMV', 'Mario vs. Donkey Kong™: Minis March Again!', 'EUR', 16014132, 'dsiw', '50010000000723', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b8075ebfd2eb075c3b79c73f500eae1fe01e870892f60228bbf4a217a886b15f.jpg', 'The re-opening of Mario’s theme\npark, Super Mini Mario World, was\ngoing so well... until Donkey Kong\nburst in and kidnapped the hapless\nPauline once again! So it’s up to you\nand the Mini Marios – tiny mechanical\nMario toys – to rescue Pauline from\nthat crazed ape’s clutches.<br>\n<br>\nInstead of controlling the Mini Marios\ndirectly, you use the stylus to\nmanipulate objects in each trap-laden\nlevel, and lead the fragile toys safely\nto the exit. Once you clear all eight\nlevels on a floor, you’ll get a chance\nto pummel Donkey Kong with your\nMini Mario-launching cannon!<br>\n<br>\nAnother feature is the Construction\nZone, which allows you to create your\nown original levels, play levels that\nyou or others have made, and share\nor download levels via local wireless\ncommunications.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/448a7a6734f08303d6c1c2d152556cde4c8d6f7b81a915da8dddbebfe94ee74b.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/adewO7W.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/nYGYizm.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5152, '000480044b4d4756', 'TWL-N-KMGV', 'Mighty Flip Champs!™', 'EUR', 6901556, 'dsiw', '50010000004361', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/dfae7137ac39d50af6af2bece29de1e80cbd3186c31ebfff0e5dd13b005719c6.jpg', 'Are you ready to become a Mighty\nFlip Champ? Take control of Alta, and\nPage Flip through a series of action\npacked mazes! The Touch Screen\nreflects a preview of the next chamber,\nand shows Alta''s projected\ndestination within it. When it''s time to\nflip, use Alta''s Magical Warp Wand to\nreplace her world with the next one.\nWill she land safely on solid ground,\nor be crushed under it? By cycling\nendlessly through room after brain\nbusting room, you''ll match wits with\nsome of the most devious traps in \npuzzle/platforming history!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/729c41b125b785076f0e01f23ac49192f6a66fa5f28fbe2eb351a54b4cc881e1.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/wC5v1pu.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/S0xJMVy.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5153, '000480044b504956', 'TWL-N-KPIV', 'Pop+ Solo™', 'EUR', 3176244, 'dsiw', '50010000004702', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fea8d93815a7b2c7935849f3b3d0e2c23072f29967d3a75c3f00979ca4326bc5.jpg', 'Pop bubbles, build chains and try to\nkeep the timer alive in this addictive\npuzzle/shooter.<br>\n<br>\nPop your way through 16 waves of\nbubbles in Adventure, Normal or\nAdvanced. Test yourself against the\nclock in a 1, 2 or 5 minute run and\ntake on the new Bonus Round mode\nwhere each bonus round can be\nplayed in 3, 5 or 10 rounds of\nincreasing difficulty! Or just chill out\nin the relaxing Chill mode with no\nscore or time pressures to worry\nabout.<br>\n<br>\nPop+ Solo comes to the DSi with 8\nmodes and 5 bonus rounds plus\nplenty of new badges to collect!\nAdventure mode introduces some new\nelements to the game with mines,\ngolden fish and jets of water as well\nas 4 boss battles. The new Challenge\nmode lets you create and cutsomise\nyour own challenges to play again\nand again.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d47597a1c51eac66dad8bde955d9cbffb5c2ea8506293f19e6f283da015aa615.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/qN5MeiA.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/dR4v0Lp.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5154, '000480044b504e56', 'TWL-N-KPNV', 'A Little Bit of... Puzzle League™', 'EUR', 5717812, 'dsiw', '50010000004705', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6fd0100928971611b608984fbdf89398ae35286a4599bae114dcd9f9cd02f29c.jpg', 'The ever-popular Puzzle League\ncomes to Nintendo DSiWare! Like all\ngood puzzlers, the concept is simple:\nconnect blocks of the same colour to\nclear them from the screen, and\nprevent your stack from becoming too\nhigh.<br>\n<br>\nThere are four single player modes to\nchoose from: Endless (survive to earn\na top score), Clear (eliminate all\nblocks above the line), Score Attack\n(score as high as possible in two\nminutes), and Vs. COM (use items and\ncombos to attack a computer\nopponent).<br>\n<br>\nYou can choose from a variety of\nbackground music to get you ‘in the\nzone’, and even play in horizontal or\nvertical mode, holding the Nintendo\nDSi normally or like a book.\nWhichever way you play, you’re\nguaranteed maximum fun!<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously released software.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f241aaac27faa147ece4a981613367b58e1e7d6abc8eb9659948860b63a09f2e.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/o6RwJAe.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/lmmMSAj.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5155, '000480044b524d56', 'TWL-N-KRMV', 'RAYMAN®', 'EUR', 16140084, 'dsiw', '50010000006146', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/010185d47c087cb4cbeea909721a23966208e9304533c3419437182d43e841ce.jpg', 'The Legendary first RAYMAN\nadventure is now on DSi Ware.<br>\n<br>\nPlay as RAYMAN and try to save his\namazing world from the evil Mr Dark!<br>\n<br>\nDiscover a charming universe with\ncolourful landscapes and meet funny\ncharacters who will help RAYMAN\nthrough his quest! Experiment with his\nabilities as you punch, hang or fly\nthrough the air.<br>\n<br>\nTake advantage of the new DSi\nfeatures of the DSi photos and touch\nmap selection!<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously released software.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a9f44992d6435487e5209995669c10dfa4b4bdd395616210a822d4c37ac73b0c.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/v1wghmx.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/fAIDxGt.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5156, '000480044b564b56', 'TWL-N-KVKV', 'Viking Invasion', 'EUR', 13121332, 'dsiw', '50010000006443', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b120053bdf4796fcb620c4b49603626638b45493258dfbe5893bd76993474e58.jpg', 'Coming from the north, Olaf the\nViking''s comical horde is set to make\nwaves on your DSi!<br>\n<br>\nThe Viking drakkars are sailing up the\nrivers to your castles and it is up to\nyou to construct fortifications so they\ndo not pillage everything you own.\nBut watch out: the more you defend\nyourself, the greater the waves of\nVikings become. Fortunately the\nexperience you gain will help you to\nbuild even more powerful defences.\nThwart all your assailant’s ruses and\nunlock new kinds of buildings!<br>\n<br>\nCan you rise to the challenge and\nprevent Olaf from pillaging all your\nvaluables for his sweetheart Olga?', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a4c6313eda4157d34755a10d16532a3b9f3a3fd72e1828e35bfb67f01e0a6133.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/hzJgPP1.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/1j0Znhn.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5157, '000480044b574256', 'TWL-N-KWBV', 'Mario™ Clock', 'EUR', 2934580, 'dsiw', '50010000006447', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b2c9033b0764c30f9a9c6c619fe5bbd008ecc68d791dfd5778b4f792d854cff1.jpg', 'With Mario Clock, you''ll always have\nthe time wherever you go! Wake up\nwith classic Mario music, or simply\nuse the Nintendo DSi system as a\ndesktop clock complete with a Super\nMario Bros. background. You can\neven make Mario jump, bash blocks\nand collect coins!<br>\n<br>\nCustomise the clock to your liking:\nchoose from analogue or digital\ndisplays, 12-hour or 24-hour modes,\nand set up to three separate alarms\nwith different NES-style Mario tunes\nor use your own saved sounds from\nthe Nintendo DSi Sound application.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/23b5e09b9c157393fa0e6aabf7ef4eaefbe5951d1e451c928ff567ae5ec41c73.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/S09IaaR.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/sElSKGP.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5158, '000480044b574356', 'TWL-N-KWCV', 'Animal Crossing™ Clock', 'EUR', 2118452, 'dsiw', '50010000006448', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/481cf16f4674a979b4f615dd074386094817fa8c0df80ecd669146f1c1c43ae2.jpg', 'With Animal Crossing Clock, you''ll\nalways have the time wherever you\ngo! Wake up with your favourite\nAnimal Crossing music, or simply use\nthe Nintendo DSi as a desktop clock\ncomplete with an authentic Animal\nCrossing background. You can even\ncompose a Town Tune to play at the\ntop of every hour!<br>\n<br>\nCustomise the clock to your liking:\nchoose from analogue or digital\ndisplays, 12-hour or 24-hour modes,\nand set up to three separate alarms\nwith different Animal Crossing tunes or\nuse your own saved sounds from the\nNintendo DSi Sound application.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7480bcec5f74d405232d71692ceba78cb74c2de039ef04ca299877088ef6b072.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/OipI57u.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/N8lhTGH.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5159, '000480044b574456', 'TWL-N-KWDV', 'Photo Clock', 'EUR', 675636, 'dsiw', '50010000006449', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c71d3e28c1b38d73c989d4db75f5edbd939cae12d841a431b46882697d56cda5.jpg', 'Photo Clock turns your Nintendo DSi\ninto a photo frame with added clock\nand alarm functions. Choose from a\nrange of clock styles and alarms, and\nuse the photo feature to display a\nslideshow of pictures from the\nNintendo DSi Camera album.<br>\n<br>\nYou can opt for analogue or\n12-hour/24-hour digital clock\ndisplays, and set up to three separate\nalarms with three different tones.\nPhotos displayed on the top screen\nwill either be chosen randomly from\nyour album, or chosen based on the\nstickers they were tagged with.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fe0a08bb6ec607340e9b59f56c7f22b1344f17c8c47472f95b4b1da888237a53.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/ucqF6pD.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/uyHNLyN.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5160, '000480044b574656', 'TWL-N-KWFV', 'Mario™ Calculator', 'EUR', 1935156, 'dsiw', '50010000006461', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2814e950b9295f92d10ef0d968d0c1e3025440794b43b5bcb1ae22d25a11d7fc.jpg', 'Make maths more fun with this\nMario-themed calculator! Simply use\nthe Touch Screen to enter figures and\nmake calculations, accompanied by\nclassic Super Mario Bros. visuals and\nsounds.<br>\n<br>\nIn addition to a fully-featured\ncalculator, Mario Calculator also\nincludes a unit converter for\nconverting to and from a variety of\ndifferent measurements such as\nweight, length, speed, temperature\nand more. You can even convert\nhuman years to and from animal\nyears!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3df7565adab8911359b7c3eea1eb9c7559b704b44340dc147b7f87637d546b16.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/A0G60Gi.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/rxWL9Pc.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5161, '000480044b385545', 'TWL-N-K8UE', 'Nintendo Fan Network', 'USA', 1523508, 'dsiw', '50010000013696', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b2b132b53c42d09793bac75935b2afc6f1ed56049ddf60d56d11aad6a8c077f7.jpg', 'Nintendo Fan Network makes your Mariners game-day experience more interactive, social, and fun!\n<br><br>\nNintendo Fan Network enhances the live game by putting games, contests, stats, scores, news, and even the trajectory and location of each pitch directly on your Nintendo 3DS. Fill the time in between innings with special games and trivia, take part in the daily photo contest, or order food and beverages directly to your seat!\n<br><br>\nWant to share Nintendo Fan Network with your friends but need more Nintendo DS units? No problem! Check out additional units for free at the Nintendo Fan Network kiosk located near section 143 (credit card required).\n<br><br>\nNintendo Fan Network is a free application and is only available at Safeco Field in Seattle, Wa.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/B9akDZw.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5162, '000480044b51394a', 'TWL-N-KQ9J', 'ゼルダの伝説 4つの剣 25周年記念エディション', 'JPN', 14134068, 'dsiw', '50010000007448', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9d2dc9438c451668952b8f19bcb44c0a0787d9b295d31b0fa547a386ecdd8b4d.jpg', '『ゼルダの伝説 4つの剣 25周年記念エディション』は、2003年に発売されたゲームボーイアドバンス用ソフト『ゼルダの伝説 神々のトライフォース&4つの剣』に収録されている『4つの剣』のニンテンドーDSiウェア版。\n『ゼルダの伝説』シリーズ初のマルチプレイヤーゲームで、「風の魔人 グフー」にさらわれたゼルダ姫を救うべく、4人のリンクが冒険を繰り広げます。\n\n※本ソフトは2011年9月28日～2012年2月20日までの期間限定配信です。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f17642722afecd32d227fa8f4c69b288211a2ab4cd49670ea1f09465b816d378.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/irUlDhF.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/cbBMrXQ.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5163, '000480044b41444a', 'TWL-N-KADJ', 'Art Style™シリーズ DECODE™', 'JPN', 12051252, 'dsiw', '50010000004901', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ca5e85393b76c599af25e2981765b55598bc0bca01623af9461d44f7f67c29c9.jpg', '画面に表示される数字を並べ替え、数字の和が10になる組み合わせを作って消していくパズルゲーム。それが『DECODE』(デコード)です。\n\n本体をタテに持ち、右側のタッチスクリーンで数字をスライドして移動させ、合計が10になる組み合わせを作ります。\nあとはその両端の数字をタッチするだけというシンプルなルール。\n数字をきれいに並べ替えて、次々に数字を消していってください。\n\n一定数の数字を消すとクリアとなる\n「NORMA MODE」(ノルマモード)、ゲームオーバーになるまでにどれだけの数字を消せるかを競う「ENDLESS MODE」(エンドレスモード)、そして、あらかじめ決まった数の数字が表示された状態から、すべての数字を消すとクリアになる「PUZZLE MODE」(パズルモード)が用意されています。\n\nまた、DSダウンロードプレイでの通信対戦にも対応しており、もう1台のニンテンドーDSシリーズ本体(ニンテンドーDS、ニンテンドーDS Lite、ニンテンドーDSi)があれば通信対戦が楽しめます。\n対戦相手に数字を送ったり、相手の数字をシャッフルしたりしてゲームオーバーに追い込みましょう。\n\n7セグメント表示の数字によるビジュアルと、そのビジュアルにマッチしたアンビエントミュージックで構成されたデジタルな世界。\nArt Style 『DECODE』。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/90bee859f447ce5ddb57521b15fca8cec614e2615d0d404e8e3978860fdeb0fb.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/DgIrTDq.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/cQCc1tN.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5164, '000480044b41504a', 'TWL-N-KAPJ', 'Art Style™シリーズ PiCOPiCT™', 'JPN', 5679924, 'dsiw', '50010000004908', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/60f9e91b99940f7d2f16c21f2cf80e811334d304858072de33b2dd2134e5da7a.jpg', '画面に並ぶ赤・青・緑など、色とりどりのブロック「ピクト」(最大6色)。\nそのピクトをタッチペンで自由に配置して、画面上から降ってくる同じ色の「デカピクト」(＝ピクトの集合体)と組み合わせて消していくパズルゲーム。それが『PiCOPiCT』(ピコピクト)です。\n\n基本操作は、タッチペンでピクトを吸いとり、空いているところに置きなおすだけ。\n\nデカピクトとくっついて消えたピクトは上画面に打ち上げられ、ファミコンのゲームソフトに登場したなつかしのキャラクター達を自動的に描いていきます。\nピクトを次々に消していき、キャラクターの絵を完成させればステージクリアです。\n\nファミコンテイストの温かみのあるグラフィックと、ファミコンソフトのBGMをアレンジしたサウンドで構成された、なつかしさと新しさが共存する世界。\nArt Style 『PiCOPiCT』。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5e3e89c6bf7a20f5cb33acef7612cdd291d71551a2daf84fe9d24f6d78f8ea22.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/Qo7ytqX.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/wMB05bi.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5165, '000480044b564945', 'TWL-N-KVIE', 'Anonymous Notes Chapter 1 - From The Abyss -', 'USA', 6050612, 'dsiw', '50010000004165', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f78bca2f938e5d07589766b7c75c70b219bf4ed985601e9e0f6c26ba65616d22.jpg', 'A real action RPG with preeminent exhilaration set inside an infinitely-extending dungeon. Sweep away the monsters wriggling in many places and get at defeating a strong boss monster lurking at the deepest portion of the dungeon. Even after the boss monster is defeated, the dungeon re-creates itself using an automatic system, so the player can try new games over and over.\n\nUsing the skill called Soul Capture, the male character can take away the magic and other skills from the monsters, as well as weapons and shields to power up. It is very exhilarating to strengthen the character combining the equipments and skills, then crushing the monsters in a sweep. The player can enjoy the simple, and yet profound, world of From The Abyss, Anonymous Notes.\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/MNdCNPZ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5166, '000480044b415045', 'TWL-N-KAPE', 'Art Style™: PiCTOBiTS™', 'USA', 5686068, 'dsiw', '50010000001024', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/54d9809968037de2a7f3643a4563c9d6304abd941e2b03583939fc8bdfaf8771.jpg', 'Your goal in Art Style: PiCTOBiTS is simple: clear large blocks that fall from above (“megabits”) by combining them with “bits” (square blocks) of the same color. Add in the ability to pick up bits and place them anywhere on the Touch Screen, and you’ll quickly find that strategy is critical to your success. By clearing the bits, you gradually reveal each stage’s hidden game character—look for favorites from classic NES titles—and earn coins that can be spent to unlock DARK stages or to listen to the game’s soundtrack in MUSIC mode. This grand mix of familiar elements and new gameplay leads to the uniquely enjoyable experience that is PiCTOBiTS.\n<p>\nGames in the Art Style series feature elegant design, polished graphics, and pick-up-and-play controls, creating an experience focused purely on fun and engaging game play.\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/aRVSQUj.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5167, '000480044b4b5445', 'TWL-N-KKTE', 'Cut The Rope', 'USA', 12135220, 'dsiw', '50010000007758', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9dc83ff9b4bb309ec00c00da9537ef928eeac2513beef1a5bb64f78805f2463c.jpg', 'Think inside the box.\n\nA mysterious package has arrived, and the creature inside has only one request...CANDY! Help get the candy to Om Nom, the adorable monster, in this highly innovative and addictive puzzle game that combines outstanding physics, devilishly tricky levels, and bright colorful visuals.\n\nCut the Rope combines realistic physics with simple, yet accurate and precise controls. Cut the Rope employs the Touch Screen slide functionality seamlessly. Cut the ropes by simply sliding the stylus across them and collect the stars by touching them with the candy. Think before you slice and be sure to avoid the enemies and obstacles. Every level is ingeniously designed to give the player\nan extremely varied gameplay experience, which means getting that candy to Om Nom won’t be easy!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/RsTYzMT.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5168, '000480044b554145', 'TWL-N-KUAE', 'Amoebattle', 'USA', 11492148, 'dsiw', '50010000010069', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2113ee1ab014d8ffc99942a42e0e489973232baaf3b748d912a8bc8ee1e1fa20.jpg', 'A mysterious infection threatens the microscopic world and its inhabitants, and it’s up to you – and your group of loveable single-celled creatures – to stop it from spreading.  Built from the ground up for handheld devices, Amoebattle delivers a portable twist to the real time strategy genre and brings the experience to the palm of your hand. Intuitively command your troops using the Touch Screen as you discover interesting types of amoebas, journey through fantastic environments, and lead your amoebas to victory in battle…Amoebattle!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/1IDuQnh.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5169, '000480044b4e3945', 'TWL-N-KN9E', 'Brain Age™ Express: Sudoku', 'USA', 3161908, 'dsiw', '50010000003261', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/06ba3fdc971cb75714b588293cb5f6c4a0ac287a9e349e666ba0d23da9eaf0b6.jpg', 'Sudoku takes center stage in this edition of the popular Brain Age series. Solve a variety of puzzles in three different skill levels using the Touch Screen and an intuitive interface. You''ll effectively work your brain, but you''ll be having enough fun that you won''t even realize it. Never fear though: you can always track your progress by completing three tests and finding out your Brain Age. The unique charm of the Brain Age series and the challenge of sudoku make for an enjoyable combination. Prepare for another round of training your brain in minutes a day!\n\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/sN97kJj.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5170, '000480044b445945', 'TWL-N-KDYE', 'STARSHIP DEFENSE™', 'USA', 9354036, 'dsiw', '50010000002101', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d4573a853a5e72c5909238e806156ad6f1cbf380c23e968f78ae883fce1fc4a7.jpg', 'STARSHIP DEFENSE takes the tower defense genre into outer space! Defend your space fleet from wave after wave of enemy attacks by equipping a variety of weapons and using a combination of strategic skills and resource management. Attach weapons to your ships using the Touch Screen, making sure to place them for maximum effect when planning your defense—if you don’t, the relentless nature of your enemies could overwhelm you. Increase your chances of success by using energy collected from defeated enemies to install new and more powerful weapons, destroying particular enemies to obtain weapon upgrades, and watching for rare power crystals that unlock advanced attacks, including a devastating black hole! And if you still find yourself in trouble, select an SOS card to call on a special kind of assistance. You’ll have to defend your fleet across 30 intense sectors, some with specific challenges, while advancing your rank from lowly recruit all the way to fleet admiral. Are you up to the challenge?', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/fnOl7oG.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5171, '000480044b454d50', 'TWL-N-KEMP', 'Elemental Masters®', 'EUR', 16710452, 'dsiw', '50010000003367', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/996510191130ec26b6b59d54c8f2c3e1707dce1d2d54326ab5f977e13bf54164.jpg', 'In this Fantasy Card Game, stand\nyour ground in a quest full of magic\nand adventure and experience a\nthrilling combination of strategy and a\nrole-playing game.<br>\n<br>\nChoose your character, build up your\narmy in your card deck and fight the\nmystical creatures of Elendior. With\nthoughtful use of your cards, you\nobtain the monsters of your enemy\nand support your attacks by using\narcane spells and the rules of the dark\nmagic. Dive into this capturing story in\nthe quest mode, or duel with your\nfriends in the multiplayer.<br>\n<br>\nMore than 100 creatures in over 15\nmaps are waiting for you.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ec8225c3278316745b697c3048a9a756ea7cee88c96615af46e7c286705a1d8d.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/kg4NhdF.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/B57tbZw.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5172, '000480044b433556', 'TWL-N-KC5V', 'Castle Conqueror Heroes', 'EUR', 10284852, 'dsiw', '50010000008016', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/76c3ae820227040bd11dace5701fa43c7c73f617ded7f6443bb07d381dad599d.jpg', 'Be a hero; become a castle\nconqueror on "The Green Planet"!<br>\n<br>\nWhen, fearing the outbreak of war,\nthe government of the Green Planet\nsurrendered to “The Empire”, The\nEmpire sent a commander called\nVilost to the planet. The new rulers\nthen imposed heavy taxes and\nassumed military control, leaving the\npeople to suffer extreme hardship\nunder the strict regime.<br>\n<br>\nA revolt finally broke out, and a rebel\nleader emerged in the south of the\nplanet. With the leader, the revolt\ngrew in strength and number against\nThe Empire. The leader is a woman\ncalled Veronica, and she is attempting\nto release the citizens imprisoned by\nthe regime who are eager to join her\nrebel army.<br>\n<br>\nYou were once a great soldier. In\njoining the revolt, your objective, as\nwell as that of your new forces, is to\ndrive The Empire from your planet!<br>\n<br>\nGame Features:<br>\n<br>\nThe great essence of Castle\nConqueror combined with an all new\nSLG style, delivered in over 20 hours\nof play time.<br>\n<br>\nEnjoy 9 chapters in this story (2\nmodes of difficulty) as you collect\nitems and upgrade abilities. A slew of\nother features also awaits your\ndiscovery!!!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/teMhA0z.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5173, '000480044b344456', 'TWL-N-K4DV', 'SUDOKU', 'EUR', 3583796, 'dsiw', '50010000001381', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/93f5d80ff0da0c51fb67ce7ab76c840c00155b71f0ab2b69d1affca7045c443f.jpg', 'SUDOKU offers hundreds of\nnumber-crunching puzzles that will\nstretch your brain power to the limit!\nPlay in the exclusive Newspaper\nMode. Add puzzles from your\nfavourite newspapers and start your\nown collection!<br>\n<br>\nSUDOKU features a host of grid\ndesigns, stat tracking and an in-game\ntimer to test your reaction time. Play\non 5 different levels from Easy to\nInsane. This addictive game has been\npolished to perfection and renders a\nsleek design that’s easy on the eyes.\nSUDOKU. It’s the logical choice!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ec759e37acd9eb1f7613c26769c47e61c5898cee6c189ecb6ff11d8418425615.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/TAXt0iF.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/uci79U6.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5174, '000480044b5a4145', 'TWL-N-KZAE', 'ZENONIA®', 'USA', 13656884, 'dsiw', '50010000004767', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e12a35b078a1f5527c0f3fef495a24cb5fe8c656e1351908c3174f37287ca0ae.jpg', 'With ZENONIA®, the return of classic RPG action has arrived! Get ready for the endless journey of Regret, who is on a mission to find the reason for the death of his father at the hands of a demon. Regret’s quest begins by choosing one of three classes: Paladin, Warrior, or Assassin. There are hundreds different types of weapons and armors to equip and customize. There are tons of items to refine or combine from five different item classes: normal, magic, rare, unique and epic. There are even more astonishing features like full skill trees which you can level up, along with stunning visual and sound effects.\n\nZENONIA features extensive playtime including numerous main and side quests with a good and evil storyline path to choose from. Anime style graphics and innovative real life systems such as a day/night cycle and hunger/weight system make ZENONIA a unique gaming experience for everybody!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/1jEWzFF.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5175, '000480044b524d45', 'TWL-N-KRME', 'Rayman®', 'USA', 16140084, 'dsiw', '50010000003402', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ce1ace0a1eb4f1ee0c8653b38a60f8205ad8d53e017b4e97e3080257b7b42a16.jpg', 'The legendary first Rayman adventure is now available from the DSiWare service. Play as Rayman and try to save his amazing world from the evil Mr Dark! Discover a charming universe with colorful landscapes and meet funny characters who will help Rayman through his quest! Experiment with his abilities as you punch, hang or fly in the air and choose between two difficulty levels. Take advantage of new features in the Nintendo DSi version, such as the Nintendo DSi Camera, map selection on the Touch Screen, or playing against time to win bonuses!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Q3pI8Mb.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5176, '000480044b5a4c45', 'TWL-N-KZLE', 'Plants vs. Zombies', 'USA', 15742772, 'dsiw', '50010000004781', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/23cc79a8576d37c95b5656c92bd69e2636f7954be34c41f28a3174f8c5746c7c.jpg', 'Get ready to soil your plants in the zombie-zapping phenomenon! PopCap''s fun-dead action hit is now on Nintendo''s DSiWare™ service! A mob of fun-loving zombies is about to invade your home, and the only defense is your arsenal of home-guardin’ plants. You’ll have to think fast and plant faster as you fight the fun-dead through day, night, fog, in the swimming pool and on the roof. Dig into Adventure mode and get more zombie-zapping action in 20 mini-games, including the all-new Zombie Trap. The fun never dies!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/RwglnlB.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5177, '000480044b4f5145', 'TWL-N-KOQE', 'GO Series Portable Shrine Wars', 'USA', 4241204, 'dsiw', '50010000007058', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/11cc96725de89915343f41ad27f68fff423235c8971177457820783f6b5c46aa.jpg', 'GO Series presents Portable Shrine Wars from Tom Create, creators of Defense Wars.\n\nEver seen a summer festival in Japan where dozens of people carry a huge portable shrine on their shoulders called a "Mikoshi"? In Portable Shrine Wars, teams of Mikoshi carriers go head to head in a fast and frantic competition. Push opponent mikoshi''s into the crowd or fling team members at them to send them crashing to the ground. As you run past, grab any men that have fallen from their mikoshi to recruit them. The more men you have the faster you can run carrying the mikoshi and the more human-ammunition you''ll have. You’ll need to battle giant festival bosses and mikoshi ninjas while avoiding pit holes and other obstacles. Portable Shrine Wars is a fast and crazy game and there is almost certainly nothing else like it.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Ljh0f0L.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5178, '000480044b444c45', 'TWL-N-KDLE', 'Dragon''s Lair®', 'USA', 16481076, 'dsiw', '50010000001719', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a7899df7c8bc3de1bb4437e3841be8a1beb27c6962d8e1f5ed982c0ffa2e3d1f.jpg', 'You play the heroic Dirk the Daring, a valiant knight on a quest to rescue the fair princess from the clutches of an evil dragon! Control the actions of the daring adventurer, finding your way through the castle of a dark wizard, who has enchanted it with treacherous monsters and obstacles. In the mysterious caverns below the castle, your odyssey continues against the awesome forces that oppose your efforts to reach the dragon’s lair. Dragon’s Lair is a fully animated classic arcade game from legendary animator Don Bluth. You’ll make your way through the castle and caverns below by using your Nintendo DSi system to move and wield your sword.  Beware of your foes, as they are numerous! Lead on adventurer. Your quest awaits!\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/kMKubAW.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5179, '000480044b445a45', 'TWL-N-KDZE', 'Trajectile™', 'USA', 5399348, 'dsiw', '50010000001781', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/704cf55aadb3e4cbd54eb5b764d70db4c5b337a38e9f79d47fc297b4a6e1e830.jpg', 'Trajectile is a puzzle game that’s as much about firepower as it is about brainpower, requiring you to line up your shot and launch a flurry of missiles at enemy targets. Three types of missiles are at your disposal, each one with its own characteristics—but all of them can bounce off walls on their path to smash, blast, or drill through enemies and blocks. Along the way, you’ll find item blocks just waiting to be destroyed so that you can obtain special power-ups...and cause even more destruction. Be careful though, as missile type and position are predetermined and you get only a limited number of launches per stage. Complete multiple classes containing numerous individual stages, earning medals when you clear stages in fewer than the given number of turns. Are you ready to take aim at becoming a Trajectile master?', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/t8vMSsT.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47');
INSERT INTO `3dsgames` (`id`, `titleID`, `serial`, `name`, `region`, `size`, `type`, `contentID`, `iconURL`, `gdesc`, `thumb`, `scrcount`, `imgur_iconURL`, `imgur_thumb`, `count`, `time`) VALUES
(5180, '000480044b574445', 'TWL-N-KWDE', 'Photo Clock', 'USA', 631604, 'dsiw', '50010000004182', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f990b3bb196f83fc4c40a5816400235c2b0008e5bd2f6eebc3c436b30ee603d2.jpg', 'Photo Clock allows you to enjoy the photos taken with your Nintendo DSi Camera application in a brand-new way. Watch your images appear on the top screen of your Nintendo DSi system according to your chosen display settings (specific photos or all photos; in order or randomly shown). Select from either an analog or digital clock, utilizing the system’s internal clock or offsetting the time however you like. Program up to three alarms (with snooze functionality for those that need it) and assign them a preset ring or use a sound created in Nintendo DSi Sound. Experience all the enjoyment of a photo album while still guaranteeing that you won’t lose track of the time!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/x5m3F1G.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5181, '000480044b445245', 'TWL-N-KDRE', 'Mr. DRILLER®: Drill Till You Drop', 'USA', 7403316, 'dsiw', '50010000002021', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/10569ce50d2ca085b88baca56d425caf6bda88e5885de36e72d6749915d8bacc.jpg', 'Drill till you drop with the latest version of Mr. DRILLER exclusively for the Nintendo DSi system!  Featuring the classic gameplay that the series is known for, Drill Till You Drop has three different game modes and over 40 stages of non-stop drilling action! Go underground with Mission mode and dig in various locales with deeper and more challenging goals, race against the clock to reach the goal in Time Attack mode, or drill through a labyrinth of stones to collect the rare and precious Dristones in the Dristone mode, which is exclusive to the Nintendo DSi version. Choose one of the six different drillers, drill through a seemingly endless onslaught of colored blocks, avoid falling obstacles, and strategically manage your oxygen on the go!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/gjv2xII.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5182, '000480044b414845', 'TWL-N-KAHE', 'Art Style™: BOXLIFE™', 'USA', 8882996, 'dsiw', '50010000001261', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6a92773058d99df0250377eaaef8e9258a62c599ce0a4928b2aa2371a0e82425.jpg', 'Climb the corporate ladder in the world of BOXLIFE using your wits and… paper? Use the Nintendo DSi Stylus to cut and then manipulate the paper into a box shape. Be careful though: if you’re not efficient with your cuts, you’ll waste paper and be penalized. R&D mode teaches you new patterns and then challenges you to complete various ranks, while FACTORY mode gives you the chance to earn money by making as many boxes as possible from an endless sheet of paper. Success in each mode brings its own reward: clear ranks to be promoted and change your character’s appearance and use your earnings to acquire new items for your character’s miniature garden. With its stylish graphics and catchy sound, you may just find that thinking inside the box isn’t such a bad thing sometimes!\n\nGames in the Art Style series feature elegant design, polished graphics, and pick-up-and-play controls, creating an experience focused purely on fun and engaging game play.\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/wd8NIN7.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5183, '000480044b535045', 'TWL-N-KSPE', 'Spotto!™', 'USA', 2782004, 'dsiw', '50010000003781', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8d76c918f20b906cb5744a0579613a4484186b29d2c38c324ec3fbf5f5183b64.jpg', 'Meet Spotto, a plucky duck on a mission. Ill-behaved ghosts have kidnapped Chikkie Wowwow, President Wowwow’s daughter. Spotto, being the world’s foremost Bombirdier, must follow the ghosts to a haunted house and use his trusty bombs to blast the baddies. Take control of Spotto, adjusting his aim with the stylus and trying to toss bombs into the ghosts’ mouths in 50 “explosive” stages. Along the way, you’ll avoid obstacles (or use them to your advantage), find powerful Super Bombs to inflict even more damage, and even encounter a frighteningly large ghost or two. With multiple modes of play and numerous solutions for successfully blasting ghosts to pieces, this is one haunted house worth visiting often…', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/YFkqKgg.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5184, '000480044b354145', 'TWL-N-K5AE', 'Rhythm Core Alpha', 'USA', 6184756, 'dsiw', '50010000000985', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4fd4a1af53fdaf9cef0d63a47b79230a5fff672417e2b34dce2e50e156d68ed9.jpg', 'Make music with your Nintendo DSi system! Rhythm Core Alpha is an advanced music creation system, designed for creating and performing live music in-front of an audience; an electronic music instrument designed for performing!\n\nRhythm Core Alpha makes it easy to build drum and instrument loops, and then allows you to play solos over them using the stylus. It automatically detects the key and scale of the music you have created, and allows you to change chords at the press of a button! All notes in the solo match the selected key and scale, so you can never hit a wrong note! Rhythm Core Alpha also includes a powerful pattern mode that allows you to set up chord changes and arrange your sequenced parts allowing you to build a whole song, or make sections that you can switch to as you desire. Hundreds of adjustable drum and instrument sounds are included. You can edit while the song is playing, so you really can build the song in front of the audience!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/glRP0IB.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5185, '000480044b4c4245', 'TWL-N-KLBE', 'Rabi Laby', 'USA', 4187956, 'dsiw', '50010000003004', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a6d3d3581200301af5aaad5bd3d74a0c17bf7fa90a133bfcd3df5e8a4d4960b2.jpg', 'Rabi Laby requires teamwork, dedication, and the love of a great adventure.\n\nAlice is a spunky young girl who adores her fluffy pet rabbit named Rabi. One day Alice was looking for Rabi and finally found him right before he jumped into a small hole in a tree. Without thinking twice, Alice jumped in after him.\n\nThis is where their magical adventure begins! Alice and Rabi encounter intriguing animals and creatures that may lead them to the exit, or stop them from escaping. Together they will explore and discover things unlike anything they’ve ever seen before. They must work as a team to find the key and escape each area of the mighty labyrinth. Both Alice and Rabi have their own unique abilities and you must switch between them in order to complete each area and ultimately escape the labyrinth’s grasp.\n\nThe labyrinth awaits you...', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/o69sVyN.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5186, '000480044b574d45', 'TWL-N-KWME', 'Magical Whip', 'USA', 6007604, 'dsiw', '50010000007230', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3e01b23425dd741649a3dde0577b7ad60df985a188599e8243ddd71147e92b60.jpg', 'Defeat monsters! Slay dragons! Avoid the Grim Reaper and escape death!\n\nTwo apprentice wizards have become lost amid a tangled sea of trees. The Phantasmal Forest, a dark, dangerous place inhabited by monsters... It bewitches people with its strange power. The wizards can only use a single spell, one that turns their wands into a magical whip.\n\nDefeat enemies and collect valuable items as you battle your way through the forest in this exciting action game. You can select either the male or female character and use their magical whips to capture enemies and defeat them. Your magical whip doesn’t do much damage on its own, but with combos, it becomes a powerful weapon capable of defeating a mighty dragon with a single strike. Combos are performed by capturing a falling enemy with your magical whip and then using the captured monster to attack others.\n\nCan the wizards escape the evil forest before they become lost forever within its darkness?', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/k8YWWoX.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5187, '000480044b47424f', 'TWL-N-KGBO', 'Game & Watch™ Ball', 'ALL', 1553204, 'dsiw', '50010000003502', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b000195c2aabff2278d695e3fc19370534adc98616e38635460339f2f8f0dc4e.jpg', 'Nintendo first began releasing the Game & Watch series in 1980. This collection of games was available on portable LCD devices, and each title featured a game and a clock. Each Game & Watch title features two modes of play: GAME A (normal difficulty) and GAME B (more advanced play). While some controls have been changed in the DSiWare version to better suit the Nintendo DSi system, the appearance of the game itself has not been altered.\n\nBrush up your juggling skills with Game & Watch: Ball. Move the juggler’s arms to catch the balls. Drop a single ball, and it’s game over!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/FpavW3A.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5188, '000480044b5a3645', 'TWL-N-KZ6E', 'AfterZoom', 'USA', 9872180, 'dsiw', '50010000006904', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c1fe675d0a4161b5fdb1391889a0ba0a3dc408f88a9b45dc8fed491bdec38ffa.jpg', 'Immerse yourself in a world of hidden creatures! Our planet is full of life. Besides all the creatures that can be seen with the naked eye, there are millions of microscopic creatures with amazing features. To discover them, AfterZoom turns the camera of your Nintendo DSi or Nintendo 3DS system into a virtual microscope.\n\nExplore your surroundings and discover new forms of life. Collect dozens of different species and take good care of them at the Specimens Bank. Mix the formulas you''ll need to feed your organisms at the Chemical Lab. Battle your colonies against more powerful ones to win them over and complete your collection.\n\nAfterZoom, what''s hiding among your Ravioli?', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/L7w1EBT.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5189, '000480044b435a45', 'TWL-N-KCZE', 'Absolute Chess', 'USA', 6096692, 'dsiw', '50010000000589', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1db6f7460c52960e7587e84f0f20526124672117bf86e918ed122cf01b28677e.jpg', 'This easy-to-understand chess game explains everything from basic rules to aggressive strategies to help you advance in the game. There are two modes of play. In the Free Play, you can play against a number of preset characters, ranging from a young kid to a grouchy old man. The Challenge mode gives players multiple levels and missions to complete. Player support features include a function to indicate possible moves for the player and the opponent, as well as the ability to undo your previous move. You can also enjoy matches with friends via DS Download Play.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Ynm4m3d.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5190, '000480044b495745', 'TWL-N-KIWE', 'Inchworm Animation', 'USA', 4068148, 'dsiw', '50010000002426', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0fa11a4c51a45902d791f6fda48c4ff4fbf9af7fc2a61e362a47a8311e1729a1.jpg', 'Inchworm Animation is a full-featured paint and animation system for the Nintendo DSi system. After five years in development, Inchworm Animation lets you create mind-blowing digital paintings and animations in the palm of your hand.\n\nUse the Nintendo DSi Camera to record video, stop-motion animation, and time-lapse photography. Paint with transparency and smooth antialiased brushes. Create images up to 9999x9999 pixels! An easy-to-use pattern editor lets you make cool repeating patterns for use in your artwork. Other tools include onion skin, 6-level zoom, cut/paste/rotate, undo, and shape primitives.\n\nInchworm Animation''s sophisticated layer system allows you to create structured animated scenes. Each layer can have its own independent frame loop. You can even draw on your animation as it plays! Comprehensive tutorials will show you the ropes. Export your finished masterpieces to an SD card as Flash (SWF) or BMP image sequences.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/bXI0Gmf.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5191, '000480044b464d50', 'TWL-N-KFMP', 'Faceez: Monsters!', 'EUR', 5115700, 'dsiw', '50010000003361', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7939a3ef4bbcab37589e08432a982c26219c3164e38008638038adce405c541e.jpg', 'Faceez is back, and this time it\nwill...scare your friends to death!\nFaceez: Monsters! features new\ndisguises and accessories, each more\nfrightening than the other!<br>\n<br>\nLiving dead, werewolves, vampires,\nzombies... Take pictures of your\nfriends’ faces and turn them into\nabominable monsters!<br>\n<br>\nPlace them in your own settings!\nLaughter and fun guaranteed.<br>\n<br>\nThanks to the Facebook connection\nof your Nintendo DSi, share your\nmonstrous creations with the entire\nworld.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9966dcf11656514452b40d6c8ef9b5009dbed744aff86fdaa7c570fb978736a6.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/xx096g9.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/aZkTdf2.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5192, '000480044b4d4e50', 'TWL-N-KMNP', 'A Little Bit of... Magic Made Fun™: Psychic Camera', 'EUR', 4887348, 'dsiw', '50010000004441', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0dc6e924ba61fdd13a7f6c52b102c838ce859ec1cf440617897fa8f4f207bf5e.jpg', 'Impress your friends with mesmerising\nmagic using A Little Bit of... Magic\nMade Fun – a collection of\neasy-to-perform tricks that you can\ncarry wherever you go!<br>\n<br>\nPsychic Camera appears to bestow\nthe Nintendo DSi with incredible\ntelepathic abilities. Simply ask a\nspectator to think of a card, and then\ntake a photo of them using the\nNintendo DSi system''s camera\nfunction. The correct card will\nmagically appear next to the person''s\nface!<br>\n<br>\nYou can also perform a variation of\nthe trick in which the spectator thinks\nof a symbol instead of a card. Take\nthe spectator''s photo, and the symbol\nthey were thinking of will appear on\nthe screen - as if by magic!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/66036ee22b85581c5e505b7f27a8961e0c7d8f2969225c17deeb217aa4618147.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/hL8stCN.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/37GOSDu.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5193, '000480044b344445', 'TWL-N-K4DE', 'SUDOKU', 'USA', 3477300, 'dsiw', '50010000000747', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3c339acf4f429e5672b0a6bd6d3119d8aad279234a493b4dd89f6290c39771d5.jpg', 'SUDOKU offers hundreds of number-crunching puzzles that will stretch your brain power to the limit! Take it even further and play in the exclusive Newspaper Mode. Add a daily puzzle from your favorite black & white and build your very own collection! From Easy to Insane, a total of 5 different levels are available for novices and masters alike. Enjoy a host of grid designs that will keep you coming back for more. This worldwide phenomenon delivers an exhilarating game of logic that’s not only challenging, but surprisingly relaxing. It’s everything you want for a quick puzzle get-away! Make life easier. Take advantage of smart features like automatic annotation for effortless calculation of your achievements. Stumped? Get help with error checking tools and friendly cell hints. Track your stats and test your reaction time with the in-game timer.  This addictive brain-game has been polished to perfection and renders a sleek design that’s easy on the eyes. SUDOKU. It’s the logical choice!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/uIdma0k.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5194, '000480044b524845', 'TWL-N-KRHE', 'Music on: Retro Keyboard', 'USA', 3513140, 'dsiw', '50010000003384', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/554f255547b149b48684521d3971a3a4a20201311e07526512eaa16cdd5e8138.jpg', 'Turn your Nintendo DSi system into a full electronic keyboard with a carefully chosen selection of sounds and rhythms from the mythic computers and consoles of the 80s. Perfect for retro-lovers! If you are already an expert or if you are taking your first steps, Retro Keyboard will help you capture your inspiration wherever you are.\n\nCharacteristics:\n*Interface inspired by the 80s\n*Selection of keyboard, console and computer sounds from the 80s\n*Rhythms inspired by the first generation videogames\n\nAnd also featuring:\n*Automatic accompaniment function with chord recognition\n*Up to 8 user definable chords\n*5 different styles, each one with 4 variations\n*Independent drum, bass and chorus parts\n*6 octave keyboard (2 visible)\n*Pitch bend function\n*16 instruments\n*Integrated sequencer\n*Metronome\n*Recording and replay option', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/5bqtHOa.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5195, '000480044b47444f', 'TWL-N-KGDO', 'Game & Watch™ Donkey Kong Jr.', 'ALL', 1778484, 'dsiw', '50010000003541', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2c64120630d338a16c91d66baaef2881b4a88c1eac603329d631a64307fba8ee.jpg', 'Nintendo first began releasing the Game & Watch series in 1980. This collection of games was available on portable LCD devices, and each title featured a game and a clock. Each Game & Watch title features two modes of play: GAME A (normal difficulty) and GAME B (more advanced play). While some controls have been changed in the DSiWare version to better suit the Nintendo DSi system, the appearance of the game itself has not been altered.\n\nDonkey Kong is trapped! It’s up to Donkey Kong Jr. to snag the key and set his father free from Mario’s cage. Help Donkey Kong Jr. avoid crows and alligators as he swings his way to victory! Earn points by unlocking the cage, hitting crows and alligators with pieces of food, or jumping over alligators. Receive mistake icons by running into crows and alligators or missing a jump for the key; receive three mistake icons, and it’s game over!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/KNkEmGk.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5196, '000480044b554e45', 'TWL-N-KUNE', 'UNO™', 'USA', 8345396, 'dsiw', '50010000003574', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c3d78aefdba95d6a01ce6bb6c49da3dff43b3748ca707a42c592b6a116661e04.jpg', 'Get ready to call “UNO” on your Nintendo DSi system! The world famous card game is faithfully reproduced for the Nintendo DSi system, and also features exciting new rules. With a multiplayer mode that can be accessed by DS Wireless Play or with broadband Internet access and Nintendo Wi-Fi Connection, playing UNO™ has never been so fun and easy, so be the first to get rid of all your cards!\n• The #1 card game for friends and family fun recreated with the game’s classic identity and rules that are easy enough for anyone to understand! \n• Allows for customizing the game rules and discovering new ways to play UNO™ like “UNO 7-0”, “UNO Challenge”, “Jump In” and many others. \n• A thrilling online multiplayer mode allows up to 4 people to experience all the enjoyment of playing UNO™ with friends. For a truly immersive experience, use the microphone to call out “UNO” for real!\n• Progress through increasingly difficult challenges in Tournament Mode to collect prizes and unlock colorful deck themes to give the game a fresher look.', 'none', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/Sjr4fWe.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5197, '000480044b435645', 'TWL-N-KCVE', 'Cave Story™', 'USA', 5975860, 'dsiw', '50010000000587', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9a302211a3684772d3eb276f898112bf83db07305a59af757f97a859cd890ce8.jpg', 'Cave Story takes you into a rare world where a curious race of innocent rabbit-like creatures, called Mimiga, run free.\n\nYou wake up in a dark cave with no memory of who you are, where you came from or why you''re in such a place. Uncovering Mimiga Village you discover that the once-carefree Mimiga are in danger at the hands of a maniacal scientist.\n\nTheir only hope rests squarely on the shoulders of a quiet, amnesiac boy who can''t remember his own name. Take control and learn the origins of this world’s power, stop the delusional villain and save the Mimiga!\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/vHsny2V.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5198, '000480044b4a5545', 'TWL-N-KJUE', 'GO Series 10 Second Run', 'USA', 5447476, 'dsiw', '50010000002982', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9c79a8a4cac03f2f46b8abaf7c2f53b85033baf4fef69cb23bfcf1cf63fe851d.jpg', 'Run like the wind in this unique twist on the classic platform game! Take control of a stick man and run for your life across an obstacle course to reach the goal within 10 seconds. Move like your life depends on it, dashing across platforms, avoiding various hazards, desperately trying to reach the exit in time. 10 seconds is all you’ve got.\n\nGo flat out over 50 stages and three game modes. Do you have what it takes to reach the finishing line?', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/zX1ARKg.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5199, '000480044b504e45', 'TWL-N-KPNE', 'Puzzle League™ Express', 'USA', 5534516, 'dsiw', '50010000003174', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c1eda1aaafe7e8d1e5485f33c9b7730cd14d881477ba162c62d8740d9147b5d1.jpg', 'The ever-popular Puzzle League comes to Nintendo DSiWare! Like all good puzzlers, the concept is simple: connect blocks of the same color to clear them from the screen, and prevent your stack from becoming too high. There are four single player modes to choose from: Endless (survive to earn a top score), Clear (eliminate all blocks above the line), Score Attack (score as high as possible in two minutes), and Vs. COM (use items and combos to attack a computer opponent). You can choose from a variety of background music to get you ‘in the zone’, and even play in horizontal or vertical mode, holding the Nintendo DSi system normally or like a book. Whichever way you play, you’re guaranteed maximum fun!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/PGsNwlT.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5200, '000480044b455845', 'TWL-N-KEXE', 'Extreme Hangman', 'USA', 4484916, 'dsiw', '50010000002205', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4ea2c0482c19dd51df130af82a882be4898d7fecf1dce1d30afc5c1c9716559d.jpg', 'There''s never been a Hangman game like this before! The world''s favorite time-killer game takes an absurdist twist of comical proportions. Taking place in various settings, the gamer''s mission is to save the Hangman from his enemies by guessing the hidden word correctly. By guessing incorrectly, he is put one step closer to being shot, strangled, erased, or hanged by his enemies. Play single game or challenge your friend to a duel. Extreme Hangman features seven different settings with fun animations, over 2000 words in various categories, and three difficulty levels.\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/qrAZuIm.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5201, '000480044b475245', 'TWL-N-KGRE', 'Guitar Rock Tour®', 'USA', 10795828, 'dsiw', '50010000002501', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3359fa86c358797dc4ef9ed8118b46f4e7b9305e94d03b42fec5174d07b07a13.jpg', 'If you like rock music and have a sense of rhythm, your road to stardom starts here! Guitarist or drummer - choose your path and fire up the most famous concert stages with your band. Beginners or music experts, you will enjoy the addictive gameplay providing hours of fun: tap the Touch Screen or press buttons to the beat of your favorite songs. Keep your cool in front of a hyped-up crowd and don''t miss a note or you''ll hear it! Warm up your fingers and prepare your ears for the explosive tracklist of Guitar Rock Tour, mixing recent hits like Girlfriend, In the Shadow, and Banquet with Rock classics like Beat It, Rock You Like a Hurricane, and more! Thanks to the Nintendo DSi Camera, take a photo of you or your friends to display it on-stage and receive goodies at your effigy: a new rock idol is born!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/8i7JLb1.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5202, '000480044b424245', 'TWL-N-KBBE', 'Bomberman Blitz', 'USA', 6328116, 'dsiw', '50010000001181', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/77dd3e056e3282ad9516a66c1921ddd2f8a864a2d227b3842371f12cf5e0e49d.jpg', 'Bomberman makes his debut downloadable appearance on Nintendo DSiWare™ with Bomberman Blitz! Experience the classic Bomberman multiplayer experience with 8 player local and online multiplayer through Nintendo® Wi-Fi Connection. Hone your skills and learn the maps and when ready, take the battle online! Change multiple map and item preferences for tons of customization options to battle it out. Delivering unparalleled multiplayer gaming excitement, Bomberman Blitz gives everyone who picks up the Nintendo DSi system the addictive fun of Bomberman, anytime, anywhere! Bring friends!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/8EaUbXy.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5203, '000480044b513645', 'TWL-N-KQ6E', 'Spin Six™', 'USA', 13104948, 'dsiw', '50010000003179', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/639a21baee7bda7ac5e7cd8a77cce9c560f198cbe070ada3bb4019196e9cfc88.jpg', 'Spin Six is a puzzle game in which you rotate numbered panels to line them up and make them disappear. The real challenge of the game lies in your ability to create chains of uninterrupted changing or elimination of panels and connecting many chains to score big points.\n\nPuzzle mode offers nearly 200 puzzles to solve, either in the One-Turn or Chain categories, while Time Attack mode allows you to challenge yourself to see how quickly you can eliminate a set number of panels. If you’re more into points, the goal of Score Attack mode is to see how many points you can score within a set time limit (make the Spinnerator appear and get into Fever Time to really maximize your score!) and Chain Challenge mode is all about the number of chains you can make without interruption.\n\nGive Spin Six a whirl to discover its multiple modes and easy to master, but deep, game play.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/UBNwtng.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5204, '000480044b504145', 'TWL-N-KPAE', 'A Kappa''s Trail', 'USA', 10357556, 'dsiw', '50010000003161', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4edb6359dff71b92b2fce4f056d0cb5229ae3a9b3f9a910b73f2c70d5357f5e5.jpg', 'Step into the world of a kappa, a mythical river spirit famous in Japanese folklore, as he tries to make his way to the human world. In addition to the challenging main game, you’ll find three different minigames to further improve your kappa-related skills.\n\nYou’ll start your journey in Kappa Cove, a good place to go exploring, practice getting around, and munch on a few fish. The intuitive controls are all handled with the stylus (draw a trail and the kappa will follow it), but the helpful Chumfish is more than willing to teach you the basics. Once you begin your path down the Kappa Trail, you’ll encounter coins to collect, boulders to shatter, various mini kappas that can help in specific ways, and more. Just make sure that you avoid the Devil Hand, OK? And if you need a break, you can collect paintings or cassettes from the Chumfish Shack, count plates at a sushi restaurant, or test your mettle in the treacherous Trial of Tiles.\n\nWith its cute graphics and charming story, your time with the kappa will certainly be memorable. Who knows what you’ll find as you make your way through A Kappa’s Trail?', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/7xxZAMd.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5205, '000480044b4e5245', 'TWL-N-KNRE', 'Brain Age™ Express: Math', 'USA', 7674676, 'dsiw', '50010000003284', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3c362b0f319d37729553765cf2b499245bd4bf6ab7c562cee00254dc9c2ee584.jpg', 'In this math-focused edition of the popular Brain Age series, players can enjoy a mix of new and familiar exercises, including Change Maker, Triangle Math, Sum Totaled, and Multi Tasker. A new Themes mode challenges you in drawing, photography, and voice acting and lets you share your creativity with your friends and family. And if you need a break from things, the always-enjoyable Virus Buster makes its return. Prepare for another round of training your brain in minutes a day!\n\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/uOkkpif.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5206, '000480044b524745', 'TWL-N-KRGE', 'Looksley''s Line Up™', 'USA', 9141044, 'dsiw', '50010000003383', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/637aecc6d5ca3cf6804d2dc7d89bffc4670d10e69651fe23ef92ec290c2e82db.jpg', 'Looksley the rabbit needs your assistance to finish the story he’s writing. Guide him through a world based on famous fairy tales and folk stories from around the globe, helping him to gather inspiration by finding hidden items along the way.\n\nIn this unique take on hidden picture games, you’ll move the Nintendo DSi system to change your view of various 3-D dioramas. Peer deeply into the scene as you shift the system, watching as layers within the diorama move to reveal previously unseen letters and objects. As you collect these letters and objects, you’ll meet new characters and spell words that will open additional stages with more sets of hidden items to find. Particular stages contain secret pictures, offering your observation skills an even greater test.\n\nScour each scene’s incredible depth and detail as you lend Looksley a hand in completing his masterpiece. Players of all ages will love this visual puzzle challenge and be amazed to see that even the same spot can look different from another angle!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/S61Vevd.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5207, '000480044b535545', 'TWL-N-KSUE', 'NUMBER BATTLE™', 'USA', 4689716, 'dsiw', '50010000003804', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d0fcdc1e7886d6a6a35485c9b71f2c793e1909c7eb076b59e887e070f81bf3c8.jpg', 'From Japan comes NUMBER BATTLE, a board game that invokes the ancient art of feng shui while challenging players to clear the playing field. Take turns against human or computer opponents to reach a target score by placing numbered tiles on the board and linking the arms of each tile in various ways. Watch for the Winds of Change to possibly blow over the board during a battle, resulting in special squares that will score bonus points or affect game play in new ways. Items that aid you in your pursuit of points can also be found, but cost points to use and must be placed strategically. Go it alone in the main Story or Puzzle modes, or battle against up to three opponents from around the world via Nintendo Wi-Fi Connection. You can even learn from your past with History mode, which shows the moves recorded during previous Nintendo WFC contests. This unique combination of puzzle and strategy elements result in an exciting battle of wits—can you guide your Warrior to victory?', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/lfrVrOg.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5208, '000480044b595556', 'TWL-N-KYUV', 'Yummy Yummy Cooking Jam', 'EUR', 12499764, 'dsiw', '50010000006583', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fbbdfa75a35d37223d8a62e9dc9dd4045e35de292d3747cc2151cbf6e9fe81be.jpg', 'Have you ever asked yourself what it\nwould feel like to be among the\nstoves of the best restaurants in the\nworld? Do you want to become the\nbest chef there is, preparing\nscrumptious dishes? Jump right in and\nenter the world of Yummy Yummy and\nits mixture of flavours and aromas.<br>\n<br>\nIn Yummy Yummy, you''ll become the\nbest of cooks in an entertaining game\nwhere you have to satisfy the hunger\nof the most diverse, colourful set of\nhungry diners: Vampires,\nExtraterrestrials, Mafia Thugs, Vikings,\nand so forth. Prepare hot dogs,\nhamburgers, pizzas and Mexican\nburritos as quickly as you can before\nyour customers get tired of waiting\nand decide to leave the restaurant\nwithout giving you a good tip.<br>\n<br>\nRoll up your sleeves, clap your chef''s\nhat on and have a great time being\nthe best of cooks.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ccfa6da9941ab43b961fd4b0bce49e138b2d0e6df2fd288273fcbee5ebbb6a8b.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/cKp92UH.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/AzAayfF.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5209, '000480044b344350', 'TWL-N-K4CP', 'Just SING! Christmas Songs', 'EUR', 6185780, 'dsiw', '50010000001362', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/eeb42661b6b26b460cbd21eac2fd8ed992c6b8813f7fba347566c43f6c7b84e0.jpg', 'Get ready for Christmas karaoke\nwhere you are the star! The famous\nChristmas tunes "Jingle Bells" and\n"Silent Night" are waiting for you.<br>\n<br>\nDressed up as jolly Santa Clause,\nenter a stage covered in snow. Just\nsing into the Nintendo DSi microphone\nand get into magical Christmas mood.<br>\n<br>\nWhile singing, receive feedback. Did\nyou hit all the right notes and sing in\ntime? It’s a real challenge! Compare\nyour high score with previous singers.\nJust sing till your holiday heart’s\ncontent!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/555ae682e2ead43c39d0b93ca45de5df8d656a80ccd218399f8ccb4584ccf1b4.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/AzbLMul.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ElqkvTb.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5210, '000480044b4d5956', 'TWL-N-KMYV', 'MySims™ Camera', 'EUR', 4981556, 'dsiw', '50010000004483', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/11855e4b54f6a25b6ed62bd9acfbfb6e13b94cfbae3120968f139155668c0ceb.jpg', 'MySims™ Camera is a camera\napplication that utilizes popular\nMySims characters. You can take\nphotos and overlay 3D MySims™\ncharacters to bring them into the real\nworld. The 3D characters can be\nanimated, moved, scaled, rotated and\ncropped. You can also draw on the\nphotos with the stylus pen or use the\nstamp tool to add more art and style.\nCreate a unique frame and save the\nphotos to the DSI photo album to\nshare with friends.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d114b6bb268f95251828715de6f457a668578db604891aa0eab037dd151a6c05.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/82DBSa1.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/Bv8AZ9U.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5211, '000480044b4c5056', 'TWL-N-KLPV', 'Littlest Pet Shop™', 'EUR', 14837556, 'dsiw', '50010000004283', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b652b84639ed5ce5ae6188b5c3bf19134cbf51e9e07e0c389d8762b0f07de93a.jpg', 'Experience your favourite Littlest Pet\nShop pets in a whole new way! Now\nyou can enjoy Littlest Pet Shop on\nthe goon your DSi. Play catch with\nyour pets and their favourite toys,\ndress them up in adorable new\naccessories, and keep them happy by\nbrushing and feeding them treats! You\ncan even throw a little dance party for\nyour pets and help them rock out to\ncool songs!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/903344d8076df0d8556fd3e436fbd5d95e31988b5e57610a8268345e4852bd51.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/7HsqKqe.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/oLOBegp.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5212, '000480044b4e4256', 'TWL-N-KNBV', 'myNotebook: Blue™', 'EUR', 2313012, 'dsiw', '50010000004501', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b9082cdcef0eb8ef96726914921169049628df08710ca73f43906fce327ef27c.jpg', 'myNotebook allows you to take\nnotes wherever you are. Just pop open\nyour Nintendo DSi and jot down your\nthoughts! Make a list and cross it off.\nOr even play your favourite pen and\npaper games (games not included).<br>\n<br>\nYou can even personalise your\nnotebook by drawing on the cover and\nchanging the paper type with 18\ndifferent unlockable squared and lined\npaper styles.<br>\n<br>\nUse the pen or pencil to make your\nnotes or doodles and then erase the\nbits you don''t like. With 5 ink colours\nyou''ll always be able to make your\nnotes and doodles look stylish.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6841110905d1cae2d0cdfa46bf2889e5b9029c374df3ebd4c3417b0a112d20e8.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/M5P7gtJ.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/I0qh7dp.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5213, '000480044b4d4d56', 'TWL-N-KMMV', 'Mixed Messages™', 'EUR', 6076212, 'dsiw', '50010000004423', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f3607c4a200992bbf266a7c1de36e4466bc06bc5be7286e5d9c0590d52aebb30.jpg', 'Mixed Messages is the hilarious party\ngame of mixed-up miscommunication.\nSketch a picture to capture your\nfriend''s sentence, or try to figure out\nwhat in the world they''ve drawn! You\nmight start with, "The quick brown fox\njumps over the lazy dog," and end up\nwith, "A crazy surfer outruns flying\nsticks of dynamite while his fans\ncheer!" Two to twenty-one players\ntake turns writing sentences and\ndrawing pictures to pass along a\nmessage. This isn''t a game about\nwinning and losing - it''s all about the\nfunny miscommunications that happen\nalong the way. You''ll laugh when you\nsee just how wacky things can get!\nGet together with your friends and mix\nit up!<br>\n<br>\nThis game requires at least two\nplayers and is played by passing\naround a single Nintendo DSi system\nbetween players.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2f936d4bcc43dfc4af27e40b04befa6419d1b205d276ea84aa9b392b795c9699.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/4eYirCF.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ljVziZT.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5214, '000480044b345456', 'TWL-N-K4TV', 'Foto Face™: The Face Stealer Strikes', 'EUR', 14721844, 'dsiw', '50010000001703', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3cdb7f45b95d01166ed56d95e7ec60514721d8d2ea27986d006fcbada811690f.jpg', 'Your face, your game, you’re the\nhero!<br>\n<br>\nIn Foto Face: The Face Stealer\nStrikes YOU get to be in the game!\nUsing the camera and microphone,\nyou become the hero in your own\ngame! Unlock a variety of hero\ncostumes as you battle the baddies,\nsearch for stars, and solve platforming\npuzzles.<br>\n<br>\nThe Face Stealer has stolen your\nidentity and is creating trouble—and\neveryone is blaming you. You have to\ntrack him down across 15\naction-packed stages. Along the way,\nyou’ll come across many memorable\ncreatures, both friend and foe. Use\nthe camera and microphone to create\nfaces and voices for every character in\nyour game.<br>\n<br>\nFoto Face: The Face Stealer\nStrikes—a game starring YOU!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b80669defea0b0c2106713fe225df070d989f9efda9d392100ffed8320a1f1e7.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/KBmr1U0.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/1c4k9tY.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5215, '000480044b4d3950', 'TWL-N-KM9P', 'A Little Bit of... Magic Made Fun™: Deep Psyche', 'EUR', 2377524, 'dsiw', '50010000004321', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/80dbf8637f4b0de8228bb33c82378cb0e7ed9539f89de36e92f3250759f8d3f0.jpg', 'Impress your friends with mesmerising\nmagic using A Little Bit of... Magic\nMade Fun – a collection of\neasy-to-perform tricks that you can\ncarry wherever you go!<br>\n<br>\nDeep Psyche uses the Nintendo DSi\nsystem to reveal a person’s current\ncondition through a series of fun\npsychological questions. The result\nmay surprise you!<br>\n<br>\nAlso included are two additional\ntricks: Today’s Special, which makes\nspookily-accurate predictions based\non random numbers, and Vanishing\nCard, which appears to turn your\nNintendo DSi system into a\nmind-reading machine!<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously-released software.<br>\n<br>\nIn game text is available in English\nand Spanish.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/17c87be155ea550095576c0c9a1cd9cf31627a03339077e9a1886ca1b2fbec5d.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/SOAVObn.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/bhPTGex.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5216, '000480044b4d4450', 'TWL-N-KMDP', 'A Little Bit of...Magic Made Fun™: Matchmaker', 'EUR', 6079284, 'dsiw', '50010000004383', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3f8f3fe3eedf516645c52d950c588da9ff2d869a672e4d466093e23f36779289.jpg', 'Impress your friends with mesmerising\nmagic using A Little Bit of... Magic\nMade Fun – a collection of\neasy-to-perform tricks that you can\ncarry wherever you go!<br>\n<br>\nMatchmaker is a fortune-telling trick\nthat might just help you break the ice\nwith that special someone. Simply ask\na spectator to choose their favourite\nfun places or foods while you do so\nas well. When you''ve finished, your\nNintendo DSi will reveal that the\nspectator''s choices match your own!<br>\n<br>\nAlso included is the bonus trick\nPhoto Diagnosis. Use the Nintendo\nDSi''s camera to take a photo of a\nperson''s palm and face, and the\nsoftware will correctly guess their\nage. How does it work?!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4e61acbfcfbd366b610c62df0f07046b61940f3d548db5292281d588222d4e72.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/C7jExPl.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/SWutwFP.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5217, '000480044b4d4650', 'TWL-N-KMFP', 'A Little Bit of...Magic Made Fun: Funny Face', 'EUR', 3125044, 'dsiw', '50010000004385', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bc18a37763d8a4e21ce5d419acb76d610d5f8016aefd5f28637822fbf38095fc.jpg', 'Impress your friends with mesmerising\nmagic using A Little Bit of... Magic\nMade Fun – a collection of\neasy-to-perform tricks that you can\ncarry wherever you go!<br>\n<br>\nDid you know that the Nintendo DSi\nsystem can read minds? Astound your\naudience with the Funny Face trick\nwhen the smiley face you sketch on\nthe Touch Screen speaks the name of\na secretly-chosen card. Only you will\nknow its secret!<br>\n<br>\nAlso included is the bonus trick\nVanishing Card. Picture one of the five\nrandom cards on the screen and the\nNintendo DSi system will tell you\nwhich card you’re thinking of!<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously-released software.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/11046520b94f838e2fc4134b57a0e602fff1812bb861513a0afea4355d1372c4.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/uxBTyYM.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ExG5Dwm.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5218, '000480044b554e56', 'TWL-N-KUNV', 'UNO™', 'EUR', 8423220, 'dsiw', '50010000006403', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6c4012d0f167d2af2aa991b2a1513e4b002712fa0934854f487b16bd4d220dc4.jpg', 'The world famous card game is faithfully reproduced for the Nintendo DSi system, with the game’s classic identity and rules that are easy enough for anyone to understand!<br>\n<br>\nWith a multiplayer mode that can be accessed by DS Wireless Play, playing UNO with friends has never been so fun and easy.<br>\n<br>\nCustomise the game with your own house rules and penalties, throw down Action Cards like Skip and Reverse in furiously thrilling games!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bf29dd26e3a66fbc0fa4b29d20a27430f552060eabc876473fb3d9ef72f18da4.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/fpmLm8M.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/HmbIbHz.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5219, '000480044b4d5350', 'TWL-N-KMSP', 'A Little Bit of... Magic Made Fun™: Shuffle Games', 'EUR', 2567988, 'dsiw', '50010000004463', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3a6637466ca784398590274c5881c13f67051742b739e02ab77b4591aa380dd5.jpg', 'Impress your friends with mesmerising\nmagic using A Little Bit of... Magic\nMade Fun – a collection of\neasy-to-perform tricks that you can\ncarry wherever you go!<br>\n<br>\nShuffle Games turns your Nintendo\nDSi system into a magical,\nmind-reading assistant. Ask a friend to\nchoose their birth month, favourite\nholiday destination or activity. Even\nwhen the results are shuffled you’ll\nstill be able to choose the right one!<br>\n<br>\nAlso included is the bonus trick\nVanishing Card. Picture one of the five\nrandom cards on the screen and the\nNintendo DSi system will tell you\nwhich card you’re thinking of!<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously-released software.<br>\n<br>\nIn game text is available in English\nand Spanish.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e2ff5cd0793c2839c37c709106dc97766dd0aca12fbfdfcbd65abe5d075af7bf.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/WxeZSTe.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/0y9TlEa.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5220, '000480044b4e4456', 'TWL-N-KNDV', 'A Little Bit of... Brain Training™ Arts Edition', 'EUR', 12611380, 'dsiw', '50010000004543', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/761d596ab26b8ea2e74556680f52041a31a7d833666f57c5f028c7cf3d021f82.jpg', 'Dr Kawashima brings his popular brain\nexercise software to Nintendo DSi,\nwith fun, new features and the return\nof many Brain Training favourites!<br>\n<br>\nA Little Bit of... Dr Kawashima’s\nBrain Training: Arts Edition features\nvarious challenges based on words,\npictures and music that you can use\nregularly to keep your brain sharp in\njust a few minutes a day.<br>\n<br>\nAs well as training, you can also\nrelax with a game of Germ Buster. Or\ntry the new Themes Mode, where you\ncan practise your acting and drawing\nskills using Nintendo DSi''s camera\nfunctionality, Touch Screen and\nmicrophone!<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously-released software.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/98f2fb56d89e2b87c6a0e1715c9e925e2e187c9a38bfd71ff0ecdd492f9a3aed.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/QavpU5m.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/RGxVCSj.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5221, '000480044b4e4c56', 'TWL-N-KNLV', 'myNotebook: Red™', 'EUR', 2314036, 'dsiw', '50010000004521', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7a2e93b900894ec429761b0f80fe7217678520c5088c5f3a613dd5aa44b5376a.jpg', 'myNotebook allows you to take\nnotes wherever you are. Just pop open\nyour Nintendo DSi and jot down your\nthoughts! Make a list and cross it off.\nOr even play your favourite pen and\npaper games (games not included).<br>\n<br>\nYou can even personalise your\nnotebook by drawing on the cover and\nchanging the paper type with 18\ndifferent unlockable squared and lined\npaper styles.<br>\n<br>\nUse the pen or pencil to make your\nnotes or doodles and then erase the\nbits you don''t like. With 5 ink colours\nyou''ll always be able to make your\nnotes and doodles look stylish.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ffa5780b81c13e9196a70975ed6705474915b5ebce0cc389b9154df1add123ee.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/iYs10cL.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/5khFbXM.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5222, '000480044b4e5256', 'TWL-N-KNRV', 'A Little Bit of... Brain Training™ Maths Edition', 'EUR', 10692404, 'dsiw', '50010000004524', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/feee874c577d8a9928f8263146212471ba78f90c2448b7cce0f1cb559e71e004.jpg', 'Dr Kawashima brings his popular brain\nexercise software to Nintendo DSi,\nwith fun, new features and the return\nof many Brain Training favourites!<br>\n<br>\nA Little Bit of... Dr Kawashima’s\nBrain Training: Maths Edition features\nmathematical challenges and other\nfun exercises that you can use\nregularly to keep your brain sharp in\njust a few minutes a day.<br>\n<br>\nAs well as training with\nmaths-oriented exercises, you can\nalso relax with a game of Germ\nBuster. Or try the new Themes Mode,\nwhere you can practise your acting\nand drawing skills using Nintendo\nDSi''s camera functionality, Touch\nScreen and microphone!<br>\n<br>\nScreen text can be set to English,\nGerman, French, Spanish or Italian.\nThe language displayed during the\nuse of the software does not depend\non the one set on the console, rather\nthe one selected in the software at\nthe first start-up.<br>\n<br>\n(Please note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously-released software.)<br>\n<br>\n* Within the context of this software,<br>\n<br>\n"Brain Age" refers only to a game\nscore. It is not a scientific value.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8553e7a9e502770b11cf4235a8dd71c692a3fb2a81ecfa5b8902ba642e678b95.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/PKsAxuW.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/xPZagSn.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5223, '000480044b465350', 'TWL-N-KFSP', 'Flashlight', 'EUR', 2951988, 'dsiw', '50010000003565', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ad30a1536d5fd546b6405e739d1b3a9169a012508b2eb5e0c8798f0c8488957a.jpg', 'When it is dark, people need a simple\nsource of light. Flashlight changes the\ndual screen of your Nintendo DSi into\na torch with added features. Change\nthe colour and intensity of the light.\nUse your Nintendo DSi to read under\nthe duvet or to get a serious source\nof light while taking night hikes.<br>\n<br>\nFlashlight will also be helpful if you\nare stranded. You can use the warning\nlight if your car breaks down, or the\nS.O.S. function if your plane has to\nland on a deserted island.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5b0b29cc19f0fe0af2b0234c77a943b1311c7690a05cfaa179fe0cab7ec439dc.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/ND9xoy8.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/zEK1Mlo.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5224, '000480044b535056', 'TWL-N-KSPV', 'Bird & Bombs™', 'EUR', 3250996, 'dsiw', '50010000006245', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6c40bcac26338f1a866871b3ddd0cb764fc3cc4e1d5f4b328210ec9e6a2bacf7.jpg', 'Wicked ghosts have kidnapped the\npresident’s daughter, trapping her in a\nhaunted mansion! As a plucky young\nbird trooper you must use your\nbomb-throwing abilities to defeat the\nghosts and rescue the girl.<br>\n<br>\nGhosts can only be destroyed by\nthrowing bombs into their mouths. Use\nthe stylus to set your throwing angle\nand take your best shot! Bounce\nbombs off walls and eerie floating\nfurniture to defeat all the spooks in\neach stage, but make sure not to run\nout of bombs or you''re in for a fright!<br>\n<br>\nIn addition to the main Story Mode,\nyou can really put your skills to the\ntest in Challenge Mode with only a\nlimited number of bombs to last you\nthrough to the end. But never fear;\nwith perseverance and accuracy,\nyou''re sure to replenish your supply\nand stay in high spirits!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/438c88af8975698450aac7afd51a39eed9d271d42d7042a884afe07abf32c588.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/TNjJjLO.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/GGqaGoA.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47');
INSERT INTO `3dsgames` (`id`, `titleID`, `serial`, `name`, `region`, `size`, `type`, `contentID`, `iconURL`, `gdesc`, `thumb`, `scrcount`, `imgur_iconURL`, `imgur_thumb`, `count`, `time`) VALUES
(5225, '000480044b4f4956', 'TWL-N-KOIV', 'Where''s Wally?® Travel Pack 1', 'EUR', 15862580, 'dsiw', '50010000005962', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/85f1b344f56d96ec15230c45fc9938ca527f37469ea492b72037b890e0f61f19.jpg', 'Begin the search for Wally, his\nfriends and more in Travel Pack 1!\nBased on the hit publishing series,\nWhere''s Wally? The Fantastic Journey\nTravel Pack 1 is the ultimate SEARCH\n& FIND FUN inside the magical worlds\nof The Gobbling Gluttons, The Battling\nMonks and The Carpet Flyers.\nChallenge friends or play solo as you\nsearch for hidden items, and be ready\nfor surprises and sabotage to fuel the\nfun!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/364d813e0e681f32ec3d433c5997c3832f4449d734fc6d5503ce5ed05935d18e.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/55TEbMW.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/AGBxoKg.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5226, '000480044b47564f', 'TWL-N-KGVO', 'Game & Watch™ Vermin', 'ALL', 1596212, 'dsiw', '50010000003921', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2b16734189d23bb9633579a00387011cb3024e2dbb62ee919a675ff2ed6a5bd2.jpg', 'Nintendo first began releasing the Game & Watch series in 1980. This collection of games was available on portable LCD devices, and each title featured a game and a clock. Each Game & Watch title features two modes of play: GAME A (normal difficulty) and GAME B (more advanced play). While some controls have been changed in the DSiWare version to better suit the Nintendo DSi system, the appearance of the game itself has not been altered.\n\nTime to clean up the neighborhood! Move the player to the left and the right, and hit the moles that pop out of holes in the ground. Moles appear from four holes in GAME A and from five holes in GAME B. The moles in GAME B move faster than those in GAME A, and they also appear more frequently. Earn one point for each mole hit, or receive a mistake icon for each missed hit. Receive three mistake icons, and it’s game over!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Y6npJB5.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5227, '000480044b47434f', 'TWL-N-KGCO', 'Game & Watch™ Chef', 'ALL', 1716020, 'dsiw', '50010000003521', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c870dba02b2ba449aa9e2b2692be1d5712e2f58afb84064cec1f44b89a0980e8.jpg', 'Nintendo first began releasing the Game & Watch series in 1980. This collection of games was available on portable LCD devices, and each title featured a game and a clock. Each Game & Watch title features two modes of play: GAME A (normal difficulty) and GAME B (more advanced play). While some controls have been changed in the DSiWare version to better suit the Nintendo DSi system, the appearance of the game itself has not been altered.\n\nMove the chef to catch and flip the falling ingredients before they can hit the floor! Contend with three ingredients in GAME A and four in GAME B. Earn one point for every ingredient the chef successfully flips into the air, or a mistake icon each time you drop an ingredient. Receive three mistake icons, and it’s game over!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/0pq3LqH.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5228, '000480044b47474f', 'TWL-N-KGGO', 'Game & Watch™ Flagman', 'ALL', 1682228, 'dsiw', '50010000003601', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/be8d5bbecb57b80442f3bdebd09db380f5e361fa244bae3f484925476d7490ef.jpg', 'Nintendo first began releasing the Game & Watch series in 1980. This collection of games was available on portable LCD devices, and each title featured a game and a clock. Each Game & Watch title features two modes of play: GAME A (memorize the order of raised flags) and GAME B (raise flags as quick as you can). While some controls have been changed in the DSiWare version to better suit the Nintendo DSi system, the appearance of the game itself has not been altered.\n\nMemorize the order in which flags are raised, then raise them in the same order (GAME A) or raise the correct flag according to the corresponding number (GAME B). Earn one point each time you raise the correct flag, but lose one of your remaining tries if you raise a flag out of order or if you let the time bar run out. The game ends when you have no tries left.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/4Oqj3Wc.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5229, '000480044b47484f', 'TWL-N-KGHO', 'Game & Watch™ Helmet', 'ALL', 1642292, 'dsiw', '50010000003602', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d2248024dceca39e6618be26a47410d0664fdcb31a9258e738e245de87a248d6.jpg', 'Nintendo first began releasing the Game & Watch series in 1980. This collection of games was available on portable LCD devices, and each title featured a game and a clock. Each Game & Watch title features two modes of play: GAME A (normal difficulty) and GAME B (more advanced play). While some controls have been changed in the DSiWare version to better suit the Nintendo DSi system, the appearance of the game itself has not been altered.\n\nTools are falling from the sky! Help the worker at the construction site move from the building on the left to the office on the right while avoiding the hammers, wrenches, and pliers dropping from above. Earn five points for entering the office and one point for every three tools that hit the ground. Receive a mistake icon each time the worker gets hit with a falling tool; receive three mistake icons, and it’s game over!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/9vVl9Br.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5230, '000480044b474a4f', 'TWL-N-KGJO', 'Game & Watch™ Judge', 'ALL', 1668916, 'dsiw', '50010000003621', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/dbb1ce28e3d30e22a8da08823584c445d7f721fd695590601921de8897a6e087.jpg', 'Nintendo first began releasing the Game & Watch series in 1980. This collection of games was available on portable LCD devices, and each title featured a game and a clock. Each Game & Watch title features two modes of play: GAME A (one player) and GAME B (two players). While some controls have been changed in the DSiWare version to better suit the Nintendo DSi system, the appearance of the game itself has not been altered.\n\nYou have a split second to decide: whack your opponent, or duck out of the way? Numbers appear on two large signs. If you think your number will be as big or bigger than your opponent’s, whack him with a mallet! Dodge if you think your number will be smaller. Earn points based on correctly whacking your opponent or dodging an attack; the first to reach 99 points wins!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/JVuy84J.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5231, '000480044b474d4f', 'TWL-N-KGMO', 'Game & Watch™ Manhole', 'ALL', 1700660, 'dsiw', '50010000003623', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5826ebd2880bcfcd512f673e4970ffed878196448ae1a5656b9065e48cb91f3a.jpg', 'Nintendo first began releasing the Game & Watch series in 1980. This collection of games was available on portable LCD devices, and each title featured a game and a clock. Each Game & Watch title features two modes of play: GAME A (normal difficulty) and GAME B (more advanced play). While some controls have been changed in the DSiWare version to better suit the Nintendo DSi system, the appearance of the game itself has not been altered.\n\nMove quickly and use your manhole cover to prevent the pedestrians from falling through the holes! Pedestrians appear from the left on the upper path and from the right on the bottom path. Earn one point every time a pedestrian walks safely over a covered manhole, or receive a mistake icon for every pedestrian who falls down an uncovered manhole. Receive three mistake icons, and it’s game over!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/aOHwUHQ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5232, '000480044b4b3245', 'TWL-N-KK2E', 'Crazy Hamster', 'USA', 5527348, 'dsiw', '50010000007193', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/12f1c0944ade81ce76413a5f6f2ae47379f86215551c4d520ec70bec30fa8ca8.jpg', 'So cute, so crazy! It''s Crazy Hamster! Help him to store his supplies and get home safely.\n\nThe winter is coming. Crazy Hamster forgot to store his supplies. Now he has to visit different lands to get them before winter. Crazy Hamster is so crazy, that he sees nothing but the fruits. The lands he visits are full of traps and obstacles that he won''t even notice. Touch the desired tool icon to select it. Then touch the trap in Crazy Hamster''s way to neutralize it. Be careful: each tool can only be used a limited number of times. You have to help him and neutralize those traps. There''s no time to lose! Crazy Hamster has already set off!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ADCKDIU.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5233, '000480044b595045', 'TWL-N-KYPE', '1st Class Poker & BlackJack', 'USA', 4569908, 'dsiw', '50010000009730', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/564474b22463458490f163ac46a495c0240c928aa117246dbadbc9a62bda5857.jpg', 'Welcome on board our casino ship for first-class poker and blackjack!\n\nRarely have there been so many variations of Poker, BlackJack and Videopoker in a single collection: Texas Hold’em, Double Flop Hold’em, Omaha, Pineapple and many more classics are waiting for you. Win the tournament or challenge your friends in local multiplayer mode with up to five participants. You can extensively adjust the game according to your own rules, choosing computer opponents from beginners to pros. Celebrate your victories and communicate with the aid of the integrated voice and text chat. The amusing graphics and even your own photo in the game make this collection a first class poker package. Enjoy 1st Class Poker & BlackJack!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/u0irFX3.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5234, '000480044b534c45', 'TWL-N-KSLE', 'Touch Solitaire', 'USA', 579380, 'dsiw', '50010000003741', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1e17f368fda2ffde25ee67574c60a71cc474ba540380fb1dbe07aa616db7eeea.jpg', 'Touch Solitaire features two of the most popular versions of the world-famous card game—Spider and Klondike—with simple Touch Screen controls and an easy to understand interface. In Spider, the aim is to arrange cards in piles of a single suit from King down to Ace, thereby removing the pile from play. When all cards are removed, you win the game. The goal of Klondike is to arrange cards from Ace to King in piles, one for each suit, on the four foundations. You win when all cards have been moved to the foundations. Various difficulty levels are available for Spider and Klondike, allowing beginners or experts to enjoy the game at their own pace.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/23zEeKk.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5235, '000480044b574745', 'TWL-N-KWGE', 'Animal Crossing™ Calculator', 'USA', 2180916, 'dsiw', '50010000004221', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e3d53ae7bdaa8b1c2f02f9888adac0a5d686e5033a75cf6a6af90b786df46865.jpg', 'Need to figure out what you owe Tom Nook or the amount in your savings account? Animal Crossing Calculator features the full functionality of a traditional calculator, including a Memory key and the ability to display up to 13 digits, and adds a layer of atmosphere unique to Animal Crossing. Use the Unit Converter to turn one unit of measure into another (such as length, weight, volume, age, and others), or track the history of calculations you’ve performed with ease. Listen to the Animalese pronunciation of numbers when you press them and watch for a favorite Animal Crossing character to appear when your result meets certain criteria. Look no further for a fun, but practical, way to experience the charm of Animal Crossing!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/qcO0tlF.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5236, '000480044b414645', 'TWL-N-KAFE', 'Airport Mania®: Non-Stop Flights', 'USA', 6279988, 'dsiw', '50010000001241', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f46fbc86c6c929d84c98ad0259dcee23398cfd2d01a95a7b950f524e4839486a.jpg', 'Hundreds of airplanes are on their way to your airport! In Airport Mania: Non-Stop Flights, you''ll face the challenge of coordinating an endless number of incoming flights for as long as you can. You''ll need to care for each plane by bringing them safely to the airport. Send them to a gate to drop off and pick up passengers and schedule them for a runway to ensure that they make an on-time departure. Doing all this will maximize both customer satisfaction and your score! Upgrade your airport at anytime to make sure you are ready for every color and type of plane. It''s frantic time-management action with an airport twist that you won''t want to miss!', 'none', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/aL3hsqC.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5237, '000480044b414145', 'TWL-N-KAAE', 'Art Style™: AQUIA™', 'USA', 11822900, 'dsiw', '50010000001183', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e74ad9d0af63ff505941ab27ed7e23e49b344ba280dd93a0d9f5bd67b3b306b5.jpg', 'Dive into Art Style: AQUIA, a fast-paced underwater puzzle game that asks you to think fast and move even faster. Help the scuba diver reach the ocean’s floor by matching three or more colored blocks horizontally or vertically. The more blocks you match, the faster the diver will descend. Fail to clear blocks and the diver’s air supply will start to run out, causing darkness to creep in from above and cloud your vision. Race against time in TIMED DIVE, dive deep in FREE DIVE mode, or visit the AQUARIUM to view various sea creatures.\n\nGames in the Art Style series feature elegant design, polished graphics, and pick-up-and-play controls, creating an experience focused purely on fun and engaging game play.\n\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/v754KEw.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5238, '000480044b464145', 'TWL-N-KFAE', 'Airport Mania®: First Flight', 'USA', 5943092, 'dsiw', '50010000002226', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9b86f7deb23e46089049c436c9743b441de4a86f3fef52641e09ec352c9e2379.jpg', 'Pack your bags for a trip through the skies in Airport Mania! Travel through eight amusing airports while you land a variety of planes, purchase upgrades, and avoid delays. Stay on your toes as some planes carry precious cargo and will need to land in a hurry, while others might need a trip to the repair shop. But, with good planning, you''re sure to make it to the gate on time! With unique challenges, whimsical characters, and fun that will put a smile on your face, Airport Mania is one flight you can''t miss!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/kV3hsDf.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5239, '000480044b574345', 'TWL-N-KWCE', 'Animal Crossing™ Clock', 'USA', 1938228, 'dsiw', '50010000003577', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/de16883e6b734d023d85d818913556cdca0f0811d12af4b4bcc4fb496d5daf53.jpg', 'Enjoy the atmosphere of Animal Crossing in a whole new way with Animal Crossing Clock. Select from either an analog or digital clock and set up to three alarms (with snooze functionality for those that need it). Make your own Town Tune or use sounds created in Nintendo DSi Sound, and assign them to the alarms you’ve set. Use the system''s internal clock or offset the time however you like. Then sit back and watch as different characters from Animal Crossing appear and the color of the sky changes as time passes. Never miss an important appointment with one of your Animal Crossing friends again!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/FaKQt4l.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5240, '000480044b514f56', 'TWL-N-KQOV', 'Castle Conqueror Against', 'EUR', 8420148, 'dsiw', '50010000008962', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/26addc8ac2329079bfcbf5fd677a4c822a8a5648c494f406930a5e09f1c1e966.jpg', 'The god of the island bestows his\nblessing upon you, and you have his\npower to curse the invaders and save\nyour tribe.<br>\n<br>\nYou are a great warrior from an\nancient tribe on the island. Your island\nis a beautiful place where you worship\nthe god of the island and he grants\nyou and your tribe the powers that\nthe island can bestow. The Empire\nsuddenly arrived from the other side\nof the ocean, found gold mines\nand hunted down many innocent\npeople; the fear of the Empire even\nmade some tribes betray their faith.\nThis has incurred the wrath of your\ngod, and you must leave the safety of\nyour hut to curse and punish the\ninvaders.<br>\n<br>\nGame features:<br>\n<br>\nCastle Conqueror (for advanced\nplayers) - Increased strategy, tactics\nand weather conditions.<br>\n<br>\nUse mysterious powers on the\nbattlefield, and obtain achievements\nafter successfully completing\nchallenges.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/CqU0yPN.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5241, '000480044b434f56', 'TWL-N-KCOV', 'Crystal Monsters', 'EUR', 9494324, 'dsiw', '50010000002015', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ded89e115af2191422af72e75575427738874588b1f9e8fa29ffadedf97a942f.jpg', 'As a Neo-Seed with the power to see\nand train monsters, it''s time to set off\non a journey to collect over 160\nmonsters and become the greatest\nMonster Breeder! Explore a vast\nworld, meet new friends and rivals and\nbattle with skill and strategy to win!\nMaster the 9 elemental types, train\nyour monsters through battle, teach\nthem new moves and team attacks\nand fuse them together to unlock their\ntrue potential. You can even customise\n3 of your favourite monsters using the\ninner camera.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/26018b41ebe35cb98eb548f5df29b674399f6729fdb6cd6af9cc99180eeccf28.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/LVcJQ5k.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/VBZDJl8.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5242, '000480044b4b5456', 'TWL-N-KKTV', 'Cut the Rope (DSiWare)', 'EUR', 12135220, 'dsiw', '50010000007378', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/03cfb27ef25a98a4c440cc056806626bb9635c289b5ff68bc3e115f4e8d025b1.jpg', 'A mysterious package has arrived,\nand the creature inside has only one\nrequest...CANDY! Help get the candy\nto Om Nom, the adorable monster, in\nthis highly innovative and addictive\npuzzle game.<br>\n<br>\nCut the Rope combines realistic\nphysics with simple, yet accurate and\nprecise controls. Cut the Ropes by\nsimply swiping the stylus across them\nand collect the stars by touching them\nwith the candy. Every level is\ningeniously designed to give the\nplayer an extremely varied gameplay\nexperience, which means getting that\ncandy to Om Nom won’t be easy!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/RfnTxgH.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5243, '000480044b473556', 'TWL-N-KG5V', 'DodoGo! Robo', 'EUR', 5605172, 'dsiw', '50010000003171', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e42b9eae3004c2710d63be1258fe2550df669c870391ecbef279af661d19182f.jpg', 'Entertaining and accessible to\neveryone, DodoGo! Robo is a puzzle\nwhere you have to use your head to\navoid getting broken. No need to have\nany knowledge of previous games to\nexplore this new episode of the\nfamous "DodoGo!" series: become\nthe well-known Robo-Egg and collect\nthe maximum number of icons\nscattered around at new puzzle levels!\nIt’s your go! Use the stylus to help\nyour Robo progress then click on the\n"play" button to see the result. You\ncan even change your route until your\nRobo picks up all the icons for the\nlevel you are playing!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e0cbddcb9a421ef4259e63ef04fc3986b894b346dd89e40fc0caf4e4e59784f1.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/dfi2NGz.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/arhN2oK.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5244, '000480044b365145', 'TWL-N-K6QE', 'Absolute BrickBuster', 'USA', 4965172, 'dsiw', '50010000001003', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2054532e7b1aab027c474d37464c1f796bf4fa5ecd78af6f927c6ea93850a99d.jpg', 'Classic brick game action is here on the Nintendo DSi system! There are two modes of play: Free Play and Challenge. You pick one of eight characters and set special items to play at your own pace in Free Play Mode. The special items include different balls with special attributes, expandable paddle, and paddle tilt. There are 10 stages in all. Each even-numbered stage gives you a mission, and the result of the mission will determine the level of the next two stages you will play. In Challenge Mode, different levels of missions are given—clear them to advance in the game.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/xmtQTsB.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5245, '000480044b595256', 'TWL-N-KYRV', 'Rytmik Retrobits', 'EUR', 13612852, 'dsiw', '50010000007911', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/992b441e1ab14ba5ef8372829c03da5a28a31d18fcf1010d1fc8787d7f4b2a9a.jpg', 'Rytmik Retrobits is an application for\ncreating rhythmical and melodic\nthemes and for composing whole\nsongs. Its user interface blends the\nfast and well-arranged interface of\nclassic drum machines with the flexible\npattern interface of popular trackers\nand with a modern sound library. It\ncontains more than 180 carefully\nselected authentic retro sound\nsamples of electronic drums,\npercussion, bass, melodic instruments\nand effects from 8-bit and 16-bit\ncomputers and classic consoles.<br>\n<br>\nWith Rytmik Retrobits you can\nquickly and easily create the basic\nbuilding stone – an audio clip. It\nconsists of musical notations for up to\nfour instruments that you may\ntranspose, select their location in the\nstereo field, and modify their volume,\nreverse, shuffle (rhythm twist) and\npolyphony (with extended polyphony\nhandling), chorus/widening stereo\neffect, echo and arpeggiator. You may\narbitrarily combine up to 128 such\nclips in four tracks and create\ncomplex pieces of music. Moreover,\nyou have a collection of 10 pre-made\ncompositions at your disposal from\nwhich you may quickly compose your\nown pieces.<br>\n<br>\nRytmik Retrobits is not only for\nplaying with sounds; in the hands of a\nskillful musician it can become a\nserious musical instrument – a\nsurprisingly powerful pocket music\nstation. For the best musical\nexperience we recommend connecting\nheadphones or a quality speaker\nsystem. You’ll become the king of the\nretro party in no time...', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/WlDSMoy.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5246, '00040000000bcc00', 'CTR-N-JUEP', 'TOKYO CRASH MOBS™', 'EUR', 171871076, 'eshop', '50010000012531', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/45eaa43da94c8dba647ff7aec740af41bcbd3d3dce5ff2995b2e23f2c3a5260c.jpg', 'Queues: an annoying fact of life or,\nas in Tokyo Crash Mobs, the\ninspiration for a new type of puzzle\ngame!\n<br/><br/>\nThis wacky action puzzler lets you\nindulge your queue-busting desires by\nthrowing or rolling people into\nqueues; match three of the same\ncolour together and they disappear -\nmoving you a step closer to the front.\n<br/><br/>\nPlay in Story Mode as would-be\nbargain hunters Grace and Savannah,\nor Team Battle using the\nNintendo 3DS gyro sensor to fend off\nshopaholic ninjas and UFOs!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/987888777342193d54bbe94980d10bf0b426a97b3bc0ac2814e0a8cb7db1f544.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/m3zRyTM.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/4GZX0L6.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5247, '0004000000108800', 'CTR-N-BHDJ', '逆転裁判123 成歩堂セレクション', 'JPN', 385186660, 'eshop', '50010000019954', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8226bb2385b8208ca1b987580d1caccced0f4b04e256595123f304abf3eedbd7.jpg', '本作は、プレイヤーが、主人公の新米弁護士となって法廷に立ち、無実の罪を着せられた依頼人を救うべく、事件の真相を暴いていく法廷バトルゲームです。\n<br>\n<br>『蘇る逆転』『逆転裁判2』『逆転裁判3』の『逆転』シリーズ初期3作品を1本に収録! さらにグラフィックの高解像度化や立体視に対応しています。\n<br>\n<br>さらに本作は英語版を完全収録。日本語と英語を切り替えて遊ぶことができます。『逆転裁判』シリーズの魅力である、セリフ回しやシナリオの妙味などの個性的な表現の数々が、英語訳ではどう表現されているのか？ かつて遊び尽くした人も最新作しか触れていない人も、新生した法廷バトルをお楽しみください。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/76ca04a6b46b592ab436d7b0bf279bca76f7cdc13bef284c13bf4e00a33d2808.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/hdNPxxx.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/DWgK8nF.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5248, '00040000000ba800', 'CTR-N-APDE', 'Pokémon Mystery Dungeon: Gates to Infinity', 'USA', 883080036, 'eshop', '50010000013070', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/96f8b9944062ad8864a9102727438c08d229128e8be78ac596c7e87d7c38f6d7.jpg', 'Explore the infinite possibilities of Mystery Dungeons as they come to life with vibrant 3D graphics and detailed environments!\n<br><br>\nBecome a Pokémon and travel through a fantastic land inhabited only by other Pokémon! Enlist their help as you build Pokémon Paradise!\n<br><br>\nPlay as Pikachu™, Snivy™, Oshawott™, Tepig™, or Axew™, and talk with other Pokémon!\n<br><br>\nThere’s a new adventure around every corner as you battle and befriend Pokémon, collect treasure, and explore Mystery Dungeons that change each time you enter!\n<br><br>\nUse the Nintendo 3DS Camera to discover Magnagates in the real world that lead to new Mystery Dungeons!\n<br><br>\nExperience even more Mystery Dungeons with downloadable content available for purchase in the Nintendo eShop.\n<br><br>\nPlay with up to 3 other people and explore Mystery Dungeons together in Companion Mode!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/BNpdiRl.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5249, '0004000000194800', 'CTR-N-JVAE', 'Pocket Card Jockey™', 'USA', 110930788, 'eshop', '50010000040176', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ec6f569fcabd59b48e1a31e074399ccf8cd51d4e1f260c71e461b5da49037b1b.jpg', '3, 2, 1… Go! Stack cards like it’s a race to the finish. And it is! In this fast-paced mash-up of solitaire and horse racing, you’ll jockey your way to victory by clearing cards to energize your horse. You can even level up your noble steed through strategic positioning on the track. Can you master solitaire and horseback racing…at the same time?!\n\n<br><br>After you get a dozen races under your belt, you can retire your horse—a sad moment for any jockey. However! You can relocate your horse to your very own farm and pair them with other retired horses to breed new ponies...that are completely adorable! Eventually these babies will pony up by maturing into horses that you can ride in competitions for prizes. You can then get items at Chirp’s shop, such as puzzle pieces or temporary bonuses. After completing certain puzzles, your horse will gain even more stats when leveling up. That’s some next-level jockeying!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/r1jOrWz.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5250, '0004000000194900', 'CTR-N-JVAP', 'Pocket Card Jockey™', 'EUR', 110938980, 'eshop', '50010000040137', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/94b66f47d7df4a25044bf4611ff2c358df023179498a0069f14b9cb03974aade.jpg', 'Pocket Card Jockey is a unique crossbreed of a game that combines the thrill of horse racing with the classic card game solitaire.\n<br>\n<br>• A diverse range of characters\n<br>You can expect to meet horse owners, trainers and other interesting individuals along the way to liven up your career!\n<br>\n<br>• Unusual breeds to discover\n<br>The more you race, the more horses you''re bound to come across, some of which can be rather striking!\n<br>\n<br>• Think you can conquer the G1 rank?\n<br>If you want to live up to your sponsors'' expectations, you''ll need to ride your horses to the top and take first place in all 20 of the highest-ranked G1 races!\n<br>\n<br>• QR Code help is at hand\n<br>Having trouble with a specific race? You can always get a more skilled horse from another player via QR Code and create a foal capable of dominating the leaderboards!\n<br>\n<br>With colourful characters and intuitive controls, you don''t have to be a pro jockey to experience the thrill of the race.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/0jfTqBL.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5251, '0004000000159500', 'CTR-N-ADXE', 'Shin Megami Tensei: Devil Survivor 2: Record Breaker', 'USA', 2988702564, 'eshop', '50010000031776', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c787a93181f8ba68cbdec2d42440abc0f67cdff6c1dfff8ed6c0c5152705ba77.jpg', 'Offers in-game purchases\n<br><br>\nYour days are numbered. Your character in Shin Megami Tensei: Devil Survivor 2 Record Breaker is stuck in a world that has been invaded and is on the brink of non-existence. At the same time, you and your friends have gained the ability to summon demons via your cell phone, and with it, a power to fight against fate. The countdown begins; will you be able to save the future of mankind? \n<br><br>\nWith new abilities and demons, a brand new character, fully voiced English story dialogue, and over 100 hours of gameplay, the new content in Record Breaker greatly expands on the original Nintendo DS game. Most importantly, Record Breaker will introduce a brand new chapter to the captivating story. Both newcomers and veterans alike will have a chance to learn more about the world of Devil Survivor 2, with the option of skipping to the new content right away or playing through the original game first. Either way, hard decisions will have to be made in order to survive. \n<br><br>\nCheck out the theme inspired by this game in the Theme Shop. Just tap the icon in the upper left corner of your Nintendo 3DS HOME Menu to get started.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/7qXj6iY.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5252, '0004000000031c00', 'CTR-N-AWAE', 'Pilotwings Resort™', 'USA', 97082212, 'eshop', '50010000000261', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/58f20dbb09ab1aba01e271fa7a7232da157381cf9a2c90dbfaded1adf0a111c9.jpg', 'Step into the pilot''s seat with glasses-free 3D! Fly a plane, rocket belt, or hang glider through over 40 missions, or for free flying fun. Use your Mii™ character and explore Wuhu Island from the Wii Sports Resort™ game. Take amazing in-game 3D photos, and save them to your Nintendo 3DS photo album!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/g4o4pnn.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5253, '000400000010c600', 'CTR-N-JBSE', 'ARC STYLE: Baseball 3D', 'USA', 238406548, 'eshop', '50010000022456', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/46a77f3ecdcd72dc61e662d006096741ff209dd17c135ed5a397e6b52a2b1712.jpg', 'This is a fun, full-scale baseball game that anyone can easily enjoy, with a 3D display that makes it easy to control.\n<br><br>\nEnjoy 3 different game modes including Tournament, Exhibition and Custom.\n<br><br>\nTournament play consists of 7 teams. Defeat your opponents and aim for the championship.\n<br><br>\nIn Exhibition, you can select any team and play a quick game. You can also enjoy Network Matched via Download or Local Play.\n<br><br>\nIn Custom Mode you can customize your players in many ways including their names and even their appearance.\n<br><br>\nThere are 5 different ability types including defensive and offensive-oriented types, so you can configure your team exactly how you want.\n<br><br> \nYou can also attach pictures from the internal camera to a player so you can model them after yourself and have them compete.\n<br><br>\nEnjoy baseball anywhere, and at anytime on the 3DS!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/3YxSzjh.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5254, '00040000000d6b00', 'CTR-N-AZEE', 'Batman: Arkham Origins Blackgate', 'USA', 722385764, 'eshop', '50010000017314', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/285ea7fe4420951311badd2720cbe80ac3d95801626dc5cba8e951a3d5056b5c.jpg', 'Become the Batman<br>\nUncover the sinister plots inside Blackgate Prison. Use stealth, Bat gadgets or brute force to take down your rivals.\n<br><br>\nInvestigate the Scene<br>\nEmploy Batman''s unprecedented detective skills to scrub a crime scene clean with an all-new environment analysis system.\n<br><br>\nContinue the Story<br>\nSee what happens after the events of the Arkham Origins console game, told in an innovative 2D presentation and comic-style cut scenes.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/wq8PE97.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5255, '0004000000127300', 'CTR-N-JEPE', 'PICROSS e4', 'USA', 18877284, 'eshop', '50010000022216', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3888cc292c46fef5548c7e932b899e2331b698164f1766525c7b67c9ad5a6df2.jpg', 'The 4th game in the Picross e series, with a Navigation Feature!\n<br><br>\nAs fans requested, new 20x15 puzzles have been added.\n<br><br>\nMicross and Mega Picross modes are also included, with 150+ new puzzles!\n<br><br>\nTutorials and rule options let newcomers to the series start playing with ease.\n<br><br>\nWith save data from previous games, you can also play additional Special Puzzles.\n<br><br>\nPicross is a "Picture Crossword Puzzle Game" where numbers act as hints to complete images.\n<br><br>\nThe rules are simple and easy to grasp. Anyone can do it!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/6rVBboU.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5256, '0004000000149800', 'CTR-N-KPQE', 'PICROSS e5', 'USA', 19020644, 'eshop', '50010000027655', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/dd295493e5550f8f18b31cccd0dad7806da45c9bc28a8b56ac717ebfa72f9fd7.jpg', 'The 5th game in the Picross e series, with a Navigation Feature!\nFeaturing Micross, Mega Picross and 20×15 Picross, all three modes from the previous game.\nAlso includes more than 150 satisfying, all-new puzzles to solve.\nTutorials and rule options let newcomers to the series start playing with ease.\nPicross is a "Picture Crossword Puzzle Game" where numbers act as hints to complete images.\nThe rules are simple and easy to grasp. Anyone can do it!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Rkfh7XZ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5257, '0004000000096700', 'CTR-N-AKGE', 'Zero Escape: Virtue''s Last Reward', 'USA', 862055268, 'eshop', '50010000012033', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4a632a0c6d84bf16fcfb86d3bbd981aed94f24f1cced8d1c9958972c14fbbcae.jpg', 'Nominated for Best Story at the 2013 GDC Awards and named IGN’s Best 3DS/DS Story of 2012, Zero Escape: Virtue’s Last Reward is a thrilling visual novel and spiritual sequel to the critically-acclaimed hit, Zero Escape: Nine Hours, Nine Persons, Nine Doors, also known as 999.\n<br><br>\nAfter being kidnapped by a masked figure, Sigma awakens in an elevator with a girl named Phi. They soon learn that they, along with seven others, are about to play a game of life and death—The Nonary Game: Ambidex Edition. Each participant is equipped with a bracelet that will kill them if they break the rules. Controlled by a mysterious rabbit named Zero III, the Nonary Game will force its players to decide who to trust and who to betray.\n<br><br>\nIf they can solve a series of fiendishly difficult puzzles, then perhaps they can uncover the mystery behind Zero III. Sigma will need all his wits to survive and escape alive, but who can he trust and who must he betray?\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/JKxZfdD.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5258, '0004000000041400', 'CTR-N-RAEE', 'Qix™', 'USA', 3357540, 'eshop', '50010000007031', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ebfe8bd33849c70d2b790342f420358af5fa32fc23c2d35550d5553aa3900bcb.jpg', 'Your objective: to claim as much of the screen as possible. However, Qix will try to disrupt you at every turn--it will rotate, stretch, shorten, and change directions. It''s sneaky, it''s snaky, it''s an unpredictable energy field!\n<br><br>\nQix will try to catch your diamond cursor before you can complete a box. Once the box is complete, you''ve taken over that part of the screen. But watch out for the moving Sparx and the Fuse! If they catch you, it''ll be over in an instant!\n<br><br>\nTo complete a level, claim 75% or more of the screen. Each level will be more difficult than the last, with more enemies to dodge and challenge you!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/VK0iKfY.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5259, '00040000000d3200', 'CTR-N-TCZE', 'The Mysterious Murasame Castle', 'USA', 6576996, 'eshop', '50010000024755', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8a0c2415c0e2f80b3959250a12226c2e38b53ca83b91567625a97cfe129215ec.jpg', 'One stormy night in feudal Japan, a mysterious force begins to take control over Murasame Castle and its lands. Each lord in four neighboring castles has taken possession of a dark sphere of power, allowing them to summon ninja armies and monsters that wreak havoc in the villages.\n<br><br>\nTakamaru, a brave and young samurai apprentice, has been sent to investigate. He must infiltrate all four castles and defeat the lords before making his way to Murasame Castle. Use sword and shuriken attacks against the swarms of enemies, and unlock the secret behind the source of evil.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/n3KCfsU.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5260, '00040000000f8200', 'CTR-P-ATSP', 'Mario Party™: Island Tour', 'EUR', 257813396, 'eshop', '50010000017559', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/67aac915a3fbdc8ad5c636db9f43cc8909a4f231316cffd791b351758992c2c8.jpg', 'Are you prepared for the ultimate\nportable party? Join Mario and his\nfriends as they head off into the\nclouds for not just the most exciting\ninstalment of the Mario Party series\nyet, but the first to appear on the\nNintendo 3DS family of systems! And\nwith this being a Mario Party game,\ndon''t forget that the focus is firmly on\nbringing your friends into the action!\nMario Party: Island Tour offers\nmultiplayer hijinks through Download\nPlay, meaning you only need one\nGame Card to enjoy four-player fun in\nnearly all of the game''s modes.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/af18064945a2151ed096b1ed927aca386f865d50278a1fe9cec9ca90e90521ac.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/PpxuOvV.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/qvYuzKE.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5261, '000480044b424b45', 'TWL-N-KBKE', 'Bookworm™', 'USA', 6631220, 'dsiw', '50010000000597', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/cd28a728141d8a7af4cded08fa42eeb3ece9e49cfec1c52e3479ef52ed086422.jpg', 'Spell F-U-N on the run with Bookworm for DSiWare!\n\nFeed your appetite for wordy fun in this download version of PopCap’s hit word-puzzle game! Link letter tiles left, right, up and down to build words and feed Lex in Bookworm Classic mode. But watch out for burning letters—they could spell disaster for you and Lex! Use Reward Tiles and spell Bonus Words to boost your score and link your best words to enter the Hall of Fame. Play unlimited levels of word-puzzle fun and learn new words on the go. You’ll relax and tune up your brain every time you play!\n\nFeatures\n• Enjoy Classic Bookworm fun with unlimited levels \n• Pick up and play—start working wordy wonders in seconds\n• Boost scores and advance faster with Bonus Words and Reward Tiles\n• Learn the meanings of words you may not know along the way\n• Save your high scores and best words for posterity\n• Take the brain-boosting fun of this hit word game anywhere you go!', 'none', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/AwZUxum.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5262, '0004000000174100', 'CTR-N-BMME', 'Mega Man® Legacy Collection', 'USA', 486194020, 'eshop', '50010000039496', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2331bcf16f9e5f85695e4c96a2fff0ee670402f74c6dc59c651acedf27dbf248.jpg', 'Mega Man Legacy Collection is a celebration of 8-bit history. Featuring faithful reproductions of the series’ origins with the original six Mega Man games, the Legacy Collection will remind long-time fans and introduce newcomers to what made Mega Man such a popular and iconic character. Mega Man Legacy Collection will feature all six games and much more.\n<br><br>\nIn addition to the six Mega Man games, Mega Man Legacy Collection features new ways to experience the classic games with the Museum Mode and new Challenge Mode. Challenge Mode remixes gameplay segments from all six games, with plenty of scaling difficulty objectives for experienced players to conquer yet serving as a good starting point for new players, too. Museum Mode contains a comprehensive collection of history, high-res art and original concept pieces – a mega treat for any fan of Mega Man and video game history.\n<br><br>\nUse your Mega Man amiibo™ to unlock new challenges created by Mega Man fans just like you!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/42aU3Zu.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5263, '00040000000f0000', 'CTR-N-QA2E', 'Mega Man™ Xtreme 2', 'USA', 4754276, 'eshop', '50010000022076', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b7143a394e9c9c933d103fc745b2d175e5687e8e44dcde8fcf0e218cbdef619d.jpg', 'It is an age where humans and intelligent robots known as Reploids co-exist peacefully. "Maverick Hunters" have been assembled to hunt down broken Reploids, or "Mavericks", to maintain order in society.\n<br><br>\nIn the Reploid research facility on Laguz Island, Reploids are being turned into lifeless shells as if their souls have been erased... Maverick Hunters Mega Man X and Zero have been dispatched to investigate and solve this mysterious turn of events.\n<br><br>\nPlay as either Mega Man X or Zero as you jump across gaps and platforms, gather new abilities by collecting DNA souls, and blast through the evil forces that haunt the island. Solve the case, and restore the Reploids their missing souls!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Icq6Pj6.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5264, '000400000018f800', 'CTR-N-BD7E', '7th Dragon III Code: VFD', 'USA', 1669704548, 'eshop', '50010000040099', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/81849f64e1f14490aec07add345134306159ece9c433f878112a39a8d2dcc22b.jpg', 'The apocalypse is heralded by the appearance of seven dragons. One after another, they have invaded earth and are beginning to ravage the human race. Once the seventh appears, there’s no hope for mankind… unless you turn back time in 7th Dragon Code: VFD.   \n<br><br>\nFight dragons and experience the long-awaited series making its way out of Japan for the first time! Travel through three different eras with your team of dragon hunters and get ready for some turn-based, dungeon-crawling RPG action! Build your team and fight for your life! With eight classes, many voice options, and numerous appearance variations, customizing your team has never been easier. When your team needs a break between dungeons, make time for side quests, base building, dating, and a cat café. Do you have what it takes to take down the True Dragons? ', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/8oiDzZm.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5265, '000480044b464445', 'TWL-N-KFDE', 'Fieldrunners', 'USA', 13331252, 'dsiw', '50010000002241', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/90f80c7b0d55c8794e4f41e08b1b2c58be66979c8e6e20f0b080cb992549a752.jpg', 'Descend into the world of FIELDRUNNERS, one of the most anticipated and visually stunning games in mobile Tower Defense history! Defend and control the field using a diverse selection of upgradeable towers, using a wide array of tactics and strategies against countless waves of unique land and air combatants! Enjoy hours of entertainment and replayable challenges! Do you have what it takes to dominate the fieldrunners and rise to the top as the ultimate Tower Defense master?\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/gvwcjLp.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5266, '000480044b505a45', 'TWL-N-KPZE', 'Puzzle Quest: Challenge of the Warlords', 'USA', 15697716, 'dsiw', '50010000006042', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4533d897564c72b2573fc80eb521fc7fa9c8ff70e32c7822c841202c3d4d8ac7.jpg', 'Puzzle Quest: Challenge of the Warlords delivers classic puzzle-game action backed with an epic story of good versus evil. Enter the world of Etheria, a land quickly becoming swamped with evil. Help protect the kingdom of Bartonia from the undead invasion and seek out the source of these vile creatures to ensure the safety of your countrymen!\n\nChallenge your skills in single-player campaign mode or battle your friends via wireless multiplayer. Experience a puzzle game like nothing you have played before. Are you up to the challenge? Match gems and unleash devastating spells to defeat your opponents. Complete over 150 quests in the expansive and immersive story mode.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/232TNVB.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5267, '000480044b493645', 'TWL-N-KI6E', '16 Shot! SHOOTING WATCH', 'USA', 1807156, 'dsiw', '50010000002012', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/54209a48d486a6a5112b4f13b93de5de5deb957e2b6d2ca2c8529c19e37f41b0.jpg', 'Challenging fun and excitement in just ten seconds! Back in the 8-bit glory days, Hudson''s own "Master Higgins" a.k.a. Takahashi Meijin, made a splash in the gaming world with his astonishing trigger finger speed of 16 shots per second. Can YOU break the Master''s record?\n\nWhat''s more, there''s a graph analysis feature that breaks down your stats and indicates your weak spots. Use it effectively to improve your trigger finger performance!\n\nIf you get a high score, you can leave your customized signature using the Touch Screen. Get your family and friends to compete for some serious rapid-fire fun!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/90OaY53.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5268, '000480044b504a45', 'TWL-N-KPJE', 'Paul''s Shooting Adventure', 'USA', 4153140, 'dsiw', '50010000003481', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a407c3a9026ac9eb3d8190414a6706e5749d5083f7bc7ffd4a0e2ad3ea17c171.jpg', 'Super Baby Paul, the Ultimate Pacifier, stars in this classic side-scrolling shooter. The player controls Paul, the son of a super hero family who was born with innate super powers. Paul has the ability to take flight and attack with powerful projectile energy. But, most importantly, and unique to Paul is that he’s gifted with the ability to take the form and harness the weaponry from fallen enemies.\n\nPaul is summoned to take on an alien invasion force bent on conquering Earth’s oceans. It’s up to Paul to use both his own powers and the weapons obtained from the aliens to fight back and protect Earth’s most vital resource. His action-packed adventure goes from the seas to the stars themselves. Let’s hope Paul can save our oceans before nap time!\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/CsJuhaR.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5269, '000480044b514145', 'TWL-N-KQAE', 'Arctic Escape', 'USA', 4676404, 'dsiw', '50010000003180', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d9b884a13214c13dab54b4db5b89bf06ba9d6dea39b452fb43653199a3f127c4.jpg', 'Take control of a bunch of penguins always getting into all sorts of trouble all the time! They were abducted from Antarctica by a cunning scientist and now they need your help to go back home. Lead them safely through over 100 frosty levels by placing commands such as walking, jumping or waiting. Without you they have no chance of survival so guide them to avoid broken ice areas, falling cages, wolves and other dangerous obstacles. This special top-down view puzzle is easy to pick up but impossible to put down! \n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/rb5CSHU.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5270, '000480044b324f45', 'TWL-N-K2OE', '505 Tangram', 'USA', 3519284, 'dsiw', '50010000000725', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/864ddd29e1f5de118289b3c1371baa13edb0674006e357f54e1e3e5d2e75feb4.jpg', 'Solve 505 tangram puzzles from different groups and become a Tangram Master! Numerous challenges await you! Tangram is the puzzle for purists. Assemble seven pieces of the puzzle correctly to create a preset shape. Animals, humans or objects...can you complete them all?\n\nStatistics are available for players who love to track their wins. Save the game status at any time for play later. The game''s style and interface has been designed for easy, intuitive operation with the stylus or the +Control Pad.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/n9mbMvG.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5271, '000480044b344245', 'TWL-N-K4BE', 'Arcade Bowling', 'USA', 3400500, 'dsiw', '50010000000745', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0a38b6961d1264174f3d9e2f98ffa715d2b949077fa2398203e080058dc1fcfa.jpg', 'From Skyworks® comes another addictively classic game, ARCADE BOWLING!  Designed by video game legend David Crane, one of the original founders of Activision, and one of the most critically acclaimed game designers of all time! In the tradition of everyone’s favorite Boardwalk bowling game, use your stylus and steady aim to flick “laser” balls down the alley and up the ramp into the scoring holes.  The further the scoring hole is, the more points you’ll get! ARCADE BOWLING features three futuristic sound tracks, state of the art 3D graphics, and two addictive game modes, Classic and Progressive!  In Classic Mode, roll up to nine balls to score as many points as you can.  In Progressive Mode, enjoy multiple levels of game play with increasing score plateaus and bonus targets.\n\nKEY FEATURES:\n- CLASSIC MODE\n- PROGRESSIVE MODE\n- CHOICE OF MUSIC TRACKS\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/cS7z96x.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47');
INSERT INTO `3dsgames` (`id`, `titleID`, `serial`, `name`, `region`, `size`, `type`, `contentID`, `iconURL`, `gdesc`, `thumb`, `scrcount`, `imgur_iconURL`, `imgur_thumb`, `count`, `time`) VALUES
(5272, '000480044b393945', 'TWL-N-K99E', '99Bullets', 'USA', 6179636, 'dsiw', '50010000000981', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4e6bc46463cedcbecac5add17513b697a7fdfecc86e31dec90c6fb9813a88f33.jpg', '99Bullets, a fun space shooter game with a retro look, where to lose a bullet is to lose a life, and to lose a life is to lose a bullet. The galaxy IRATA 2601 is threatened by Black Eye and his minions, but V-99 is ready to stop him with his 99 bullets.\n\n*Control V-99, avoiding, shooting and taking care of your 99 bullets available on each level.\n*Arcade Mode like in classic arcade titles!\n*More than 10 levels of retro style!\n*Incredible final bosses!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/1zSt8ZF.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5273, '000480044b414345', 'TWL-N-KACE', 'Advanced Circuits', 'USA', 5982004, 'dsiw', '50010000001201', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6fabbfd125253203e38fb267d0eee4954e71653376c11c5068ff7809fd929fc9.jpg', 'Whether with a train, a car, or a tank, are you ready for a new challenge? This brain-boggling puzzle game will put your powers of deduction to the test. Complete the circuits by connecting squares on the game board with pieces of track. Some pieces of track are already shown on the board at the beginning of the game to give you a head start. There is only one solution to each puzzle. The rules are simple but the challenges are tough!\n\n• Challenge mode features 60 predefined game boards of increasing difficulty.\n• Free Play mode lets you select the game board size and practice on any number of randomly-generated puzzles.\n• 72 awards to be won.\n• Also features a tutorial, hints and tips and even the solution if you feel like giving up!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/2HDTQbM.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5274, '000480044b424a45', 'TWL-N-KBJE', '21: Blackjack', 'USA', 6201140, 'dsiw', '50010000000596', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/de4a0e244c5b8d6be6553ec091ffccf98b5dd47541a72f77bc68bcc2c22d5593.jpg', 'Now you can take the thrill of the casino on-the-go with 21: Blackjack. Whether you’re a seasoned player or a rookie at the table, 21: Blackjack has a variety of gameplay options to take your skills to the next level. You can change the payouts, number of decks in play, splitting options and even if the dealer hits on a soft 17, but these are just a few of the many advanced gameplay options. If you want to know how well you’ve been playing or how many Blackjack’s have taken you to a winning hand, then check out a full range of player stats available for viewing at any time. Now’s your chance to Hit, Stand or Double Down with 21: Blackjack.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/xmugEVN.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5275, '000480044b4c4545', 'TWL-N-KLEE', 'Legends of Exidia', 'USA', 9631540, 'dsiw', '50010000003006', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d5001d74e3ab0f700464371ef143f5a082a95f5515d2272fef94c8bc19ac6512.jpg', 'An army of demons, the Morgost, has invaded Exidia. They have defeated Princess Sofia and captured the Orb of Spell. Their intentions are dark: the resurrection of the almighty Daraka. Listen only to your courage and help Sofia drive back this threat. As a fearless warrior, you’ll fight the most evil creatures and, with every quest, you’ll get closer to discovering the source of the plague.\n\n- All the greatness of an authentic action RPG: use your ancient sword or perform spells, and make your attacks more powerful thanks to the level-up system.\n- An epic adventure: numerous main chapters and side quests through 22 varied environments to explore, from the Elf forest to the city of Minasdril, the temple of Santinor, and more. \n- Tons of items, weapons and armors to find: the hero''s equipment will change his appearance and abilities\n- Amazing production: polished isometric 3D graphics and a soundtrack inspiring heroism and mythical legends', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/S7PItk4.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5276, '000480044b504f45', 'TWL-N-KPOE', 'American Popstar: Road to Celebrity', 'USA', 16208692, 'dsiw', '50010000003175', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/759ec60109b326523c489b0e92c5535566aa413b5df32f2699131e9a16c99eb5.jpg', 'This is your enthralling and interactive success story as a young hopeful in the music milieu. The adventure begins when you get the chance to audition at your Hollywood high school. But the road to celebrity is not a highway: your secret crush is also auditioning, and so is your evil rival. This unique mix of social adventure and music game will let you meet lots of people who may help you build your career, show your talent skills to the world, and take your best photo with the camera to the delight of your fans. You''re about to be the greatest pop star in the world! Talk, share activities, and be friendly or unfriendly with numerous characters! Customize your character''s name and appearance, and develop skills and personality through your actions. Four musical minigames: Guitar, Singing, Drums, and Dance. Record your voice, take your own photos, and sign autographs! Two multiplayer modes for 2-4 players.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/DnMSFxP.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5277, '000480044b563245', 'TWL-N-KV2E', 'Anonymous Notes Chapter 2 - From The Abyss -', 'USA', 5868340, 'dsiw', '50010000004163', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ec996fe1ce9db252790b8f639425476628c492ce5380e64a684a161b0169bea8.jpg', 'A real action RPG with preeminent exhilaration set inside an infinitely-extending dungeon. Sweep away the monsters wriggling in many places and get at defeating a strong boss monster lurking at the deepest portion of the dungeon. Even after the boss monster is defeated, the dungeon re-creates itself using an automatic system, so the player can try new games over and over.\n\nUsing the skill called Soul Capture, the male character can take away the magic and other skills from the monsters, as well as weapons and shields to power up. It is very exhilarating to strengthen the character combining the equipments and skills, then crushing the monsters in a sweep. The player can enjoy the simple, and yet profound, world of From The Abyss, Anonymous Notes.\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/h9av6dT.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5278, '000480044b584945', 'TWL-N-KXIE', '101 MiniGolf World', 'USA', 8731444, 'dsiw', '50010000004788', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5920a488a43d179e8d10982a59fca5b44d0c1e7b1c4bdef1a4d29d3439df720b.jpg', '101 MiniGolf World is one of the first ever “true 3D” miniature golf games for Nintendo DSiWare™! Your stylus becomes the putter for an incredibly fun minigolf experience! Play over 100 fun and challenging holes solo or with up to 8 friends on one system. What will be your record to finish all courses with the lowest number of strokes? The intuitive 3D Virtual Play eases the use of controls with just a stylus to sink putts as you send your ball flying through loops, pipes, arches, extreme ramps and mind-blowing obstacles! With a combination of real golf rules and wacky MiniGolf fun, it''s the ultimate challenge for Nintendo DSiWare!', 'none', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/z4k7Evs.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5279, '000480044b413245', 'TWL-N-KA2E', 'Art Academy™: Second Semester', 'USA', 15351604, 'dsiw', '50010000006842', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/320eb2fa7aa77b9a98bca227f42cedfc88392c90298d3179be30e55f5c4ae655.jpg', 'Art Academy is a portable art course that anyone can join to replace the lecture-like structure of art school, or the trial and error on canvas, with a Nintendo DSi system.\n\nArt Academy: Second Semester provides new and returning students with a larger set of tools and another set of in-depth lessons designed to encourage the creation of more complex artwork. By gaining an even deeper understanding of colors and techniques used by famous impressionist artists, you will be taking on more challenging themes that include moving objects and vast landscapes with distant objects. Combined with the openness of Free Paint mode, you’ll find plenty of opportunities to hone your skills and boost your confidence as an artist.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/QehDQSK.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5280, '000480044b414445', 'TWL-N-KADE', 'Art Style™: BASE 10™', 'USA', 12529460, 'dsiw', '50010000001221', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/88aee716b98f70533cd0d23c0a3337aac4612279ab9f0addecafa7f423572543.jpg', 'Art Style: BASE 10 is a game of numbers. Your goal is simple: create combinations equaling 10 by sliding numbers around the playing field. Move them horizontally or vertically, but be careful not to create an unusable non-number in the process. Choose from one of three modes: eliminate a set amount of numbers as quickly as possible in ZEROSUM MODE, get rid of prearranged groups of numbers in as few moves as possible in PUZZLE MODE, or continue removing numbers until your game is over in INFINITE MODE. In addition, you can challenge an opponent to a two-player wireless battle in VS MODE and see whose number-crunching skills reign supreme. If you think you’re a master with numbers, the straightforward yet challenging world of Art Style: BASE 10 gives you the opportunity to prove it in a unique way.\n\nGames in the Art Style series feature elegant design, polished graphics, and pick-up-and-play controls, creating an experience focused purely on fun and engaging game play.\n\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/KN5wNuk.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5281, '000480044b424145', 'TWL-N-KBAE', 'Battle of Giants™: Dragons - Bronze Edition', 'USA', 15670068, 'dsiw', '50010000001161', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/07edd0662786e9822cecc9a9bf9eb1afacbd014f1605a61f1d5074f6d8d4adff.jpg', 'As last of the noble and rare Bronze Dragons, you must defeat the evil SALMU dragons and reclaim the 25 exclusive bronze gems they stole. Explore 10 maps, travel through the great jungles of Earth, the scorched grounds of Fire, the frozen wastelands of Ice and the floating islands of Wind. Customize your dragon''s appearance by changing its body, wings, tail shape, colors and even add stripes. Test your dragon''s fighting skills against your friends in head-to-head combat or 4 player tournaments.', 'none', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/uB7TfxL.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5282, '000480044b424345', 'TWL-N-KBCE', 'Brain Challenge®', 'USA', 14803764, 'dsiw', '50010000001182', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/895d3271e6dff701ace97d9b17929544ee6e88b577d23e5940806fbff7b84be1.jpg', 'Just like your body, your brain needs exercise to stay in shape!\n\nBrain Challenge is a simple, entertaining solution for stimulating your neurons that goes way beyond logic tests. Thanks to a complete range of 48 mini-games, Brain Challenge provides an exceptional variety of exercises. Not only can you train your brain for Math but also for 4 other categories: Logic, Focus, Memory and Visual!  Plus an original Stress Mode, featuring multitasking and authority challenges.\n\nPlus, you can now personalize your profile and some exercises with your own photos!\n\n', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/25020a28b25b1fffb2859ca8c5fba588ee427b681baf0c78b93420f7def2877e.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/PlsUy2I.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/chaOcPT.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5283, '000480044b424d45', 'TWL-N-KBME', 'Boom Boom Squaries', 'USA', 3748660, 'dsiw', '50010000001621', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0a09384551385cd9f00ed74f128913711748cc6058bf1f4f0149bfa656620650.jpg', 'Furries are cute, happy, round beings that enjoy rolling around in the sun all day long. But the bad-tempered, stone-cold Squaries, hating everything that is round and fluffy, attack the unsuspecting Furries! Now it is up to you to create chain reactions that will pop the evil invaders. Prove your skill in four different game modes: Classic, Challenge, Time Trial, and Endless. Use Squaries'' special abilities like gravity, air blast and split to plan your blasts for maximum efficiency! When you are done with 40 levels of Classic mode and 40 Challenges, you can enjoy the never-ending fun of Endless mode and beat your high score in the Time Trial.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/669tPJh.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5284, '000480044b435945', 'TWL-N-KCYE', 'Calculator', 'USA', 1910580, 'dsiw', '50010000007231', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c819ff1b1a34d48a2a07aa60f1e487d60a25ccc4ee5139302a7d38ca15b42f12.jpg', 'Calculator is the one and only calculator that you will ever need. Calculator combines basic and scientific calculators with a unit conversion utility. Calculator handles 135 measurement units and constants of most types which ordinary people use every day, including length, weight, temperature, speed, volume, area, and time. Plus, it''s always available in your pocket!\n\nFeatures:\n- Basic and scientific calculators\n- Calculate with degrees or radians\n- Supports decimal, hexadecimal, octal, and binary numbers\n- Percent button will behave just like on a basic calculator\n- Memory buttons will also behave just like on a basic calculator\n- Database of 135 most popular units and physical constants\n- Reverse direction of any conversion\n- Punch in digits and Calculator does the conversion on the fly', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/oVr5mTJ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5285, '000480044b545254', 'TWL-N-KTRT', 'Clubhouse Games™ Express: Card Classics', 'USA', 4044596, 'dsiw', '50010000006362', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1fdb932e7113539ab87e032e1048e7c3626a7f969d4e7ac7fd0da7e4b33c51b9.jpg', 'Clubhouse Games comes to DSiWare with a collection of five fun card games in Clubhouse Games Express: Card Classics. Play familiar favorites like Blackjack and Five Card Draw or test your ability in the fast-paced Last Card, Last Card Plus, and President. DS Download Play allows players to host as many as seven friends.\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/AKbIjQ9.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5286, '000480044b383845', 'TWL-N-K88E', 'Music on: Learning Piano', 'USA', 4451124, 'dsiw', '50010000000963', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9f167f6823a6443e4f6f3f3a0b28df6217b2f92d187b5ed4ede4d7ad88c05afd.jpg', 'Bravissimo! The entire orchestra follows your performance of 15 great classics. By playing each day, your ability may increase. Earn the bronze, silver and gold medals for each song, completing all different levels. A simplified music score is shown on the upper screen and a full piano keyboard on the touch screen, guiding beginners note by note on their first steps.\n\nSongs included: \n*The Entertainer (S. Joplin)\n*For Elise  (L. Beethoven)\n*In the hall of the mountain king (E. Grieg) \n*Ode to joy  (L. Beethoven)\n*Canon (J. Pachelbel)\n*Hungarian dance No. 5 (J. Brahms)\n*Radetzky march (J. Strauss I)\n*La traviata (G. Verdi)\n*Opus 10. 2. (L. Beethoven)\n*Musette in D major (J. S. Bach)\n*Wedding March  (F. Mendelssohn)\n*The blue Danube (J. Strauss II)\n*The infernal galop "Can Can" (J. Offenbach)\n*Brahm''s Lullaby (J. Brahms)\n*Minuet in G major (J. S. Bach)', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/zUesWsA.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5287, '000480044b415645', 'TWL-N-KAVE', 'Art Style™: DIGIDRIVE™', 'USA', 11775796, 'dsiw', '50010000001082', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5160fda28b8d95bac9ab3e69f57f16cce713a81dd8c396f096ccc3af12ac10ad.jpg', 'It’s traffic control with a twist as you try to direct identical cars down the same road in Art Style: DIGIDRIVE. This constantly moving puzzle game combines an easily understood playing field (an intersection) and a simple goal (create fuel) and then challenges you to properly guide a never-ending stream of cars. Stack similar cars five deep to create some fuel, and then use that fuel to continue your progress in the game. Take on ENDLESS mode to see how long you can last or compete against the computer or a human opponent in VS mode. Utilize combos to your advantage and see if your reflexes can handle the intensity of Overdrive mode. When all is said and done, you may find that you can never look at gridlock quite the same way again!\n\nGames in the Art Style series feature elegant design, polished graphics, and pick-up-and-play controls, creating an experience focused purely on fun and engaging game play.\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/yO2WX2W.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5288, '000480044b423845', 'TWL-N-KB8E', 'GO Series EARTH SAVER', 'USA', 4117300, 'dsiw', '50010000001141', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c627ebae5c89c55d55d21bf35a39ce1b12e4654737b7931c2285e2119eae831e.jpg', 'THE EARTH IS DOOMED!\n\nA giant meteorite is headed straight for Earth! Land your spaceship on the meteorite and set explosives to break off small pieces so the rock breaks up in the earth''s atmosphere. Chunks of meteorite that are too big will smash into Earth, wiping out mankind!\n\nAs an explosives expert, you can plant a series of bombs to create chain reaction-combos, blasting off chunks of rock the size of houses with ease. You''ll also need to tackle the many strange alien lifeforms you come across, by either blowing them up or by cunningly blasting around the piece of rock they are standing on so they fall with the meteorite. Can you save the earth from being obliterated and secure the future of mankind?\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/PaKGz1e.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5289, '000480044b434d45', 'TWL-N-KCME', 'Castle Of Magic', 'USA', 12181300, 'dsiw', '50010000001741', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7594dd95b9034df6fddfe1d4e002316a57f627133273f878c7fe7397484cca14.jpg', 'Be prepared for anything as you try to save your friend from the clutches of the horrifying magician Nefastax! Stand up to the wildest monsters in environments that directly influence your movement. As you navigate this universe, the ground will make you stick, slide, sink, swim, levitate, and even walk on the ceiling when gravity disappears! Never before seen use for the Nintendo DSi Camera: Transform yourself into new powerful forms! Visit a Photo Cabin in the game and search for an object in real life that matches the color of the character you want to transform into. Take a picture of a blue object with your Nintendo DSi system and presto! You’re transformed into a swordfish! Plus, you can customize game items, from coins to enemies, with pictures of your choice! Our cute hero’s adventure is just too big and immersive for one screen! So he’ll have to jump between the top and bottom screens of your Nintendo DSi system. Ready to dive into the adventure of Castle of Magic?\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/JbQL2bc.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5290, '000480044b444345', 'TWL-N-KDCE', 'Crash-Course Domo™', 'USA', 2281268, 'dsiw', '50010000009341', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c110681a3ee852c961b41ffe53417e248363ff7d92b57c4efe4a1226fc4586a4.jpg', 'Domo is a strange creature who hatched from an egg. His favorite food is Japanese-style meat-and-potato stew, and he has a strong dislike for apples (due to an unexplained mystery). He is also known as the popular mascot of Japan’s NHK television station.\n\nIn Crash-Course Domo, you’ll guide Domo across the finish lines in six increasingly difficult bicycle races. Steer Domo around other racers and patches of rough terrain, pedaling as fast as his stubby legs will allow.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/bKtzKFV.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5291, '000480044b444845', 'TWL-N-KDHE', 'Hard-Hat Domo™', 'USA', 1527604, 'dsiw', '50010000009342', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9f00ca8fa9c070e5a0b80fe2744497ff07e9e1669e2ef776cbf65b169f0ee33d.jpg', 'Domo is a strange creature who hatched from an egg. His favorite food is Japanese-style meat-and-potato stew, and he has a strong dislike for apples (due to an unexplained mystery). He is also known as the popular mascot of Japan’s NHK television station.\n\nIn Hard-Hat Domo, Domo is a construction worker trying to get to the top of a building. Match ladder colors to floor colors, using cans of paint if necessary, to earn points and continue climbing higher. Reach the top floor to clear each of the four levels of difficulty.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/XYNmlX7.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5292, '000480044b445145', 'TWL-N-KDQE', 'DRAGON QUEST® WARS™', 'USA', 11003700, 'dsiw', '50010000001720', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5ac5a219d88a7c2ea02e90f19674c130a85013e280d5460a5880962898fe6456.jpg', 'DRAGON QUEST WARS is a Nintendo DSiWare grid-based strategy game featuring all of your favorite, quirky DRAGON QUEST monsters. Choose from several modes and get ready for battle in pure DRAGON QUEST fashion! While the rules are simple, strategy is the key to victory. Features single-player and DS Wireless Play, as well as battles with foes worldwide via Nintendo Wi-Fi Connection.\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/YFkHqVk.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5293, '000480044b454145', 'TWL-N-KEAE', 'Electroplankton™ Trapy', 'USA', 2911028, 'dsiw', '50010000001708', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3a681984cbf134fb0e079e465390bdd4a33a2169d21f2b4ac133fe5c791188dd.jpg', 'A strange electronic sea awaits you. In this sea, you’ll encounter unique species of tiny Electroplankton that respond to your touch and voice to create unforgettable sounds and melodies. Enjoy getting to know these fascinating plankton as you relax to their sights and sounds!\n\nTrapy plankton make sounds as they swim over graceful lines made up of linked triangles. The creatures follow the lines you trace along the water. There are six types of Trapy in all, each with a unique color and sound. All Trapy plankton produce different tones depending on the direction they swim. They produce the lowest-pitched sounds when they swim to the right and produce higher-pitched sounds as their path veers to the left.\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/S1KJ0Jp.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5294, '000480044b454345', 'TWL-N-KECE', 'Electroplankton™ Luminarrow', 'USA', 2891572, 'dsiw', '50010000001710', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5917ac66675595b2e75c1cdc09999174640fd531454268fdad7e1bab62e184a8.jpg', 'A strange electronic sea awaits you. In this sea, you’ll encounter unique species of tiny Electroplankton that respond to your touch and voice to create unforgettable sounds and melodies. Enjoy getting to know these fascinating plankton as you relax to their sights and sounds!\n\nLuminarrow plankton are famous for their habit of perfectly following arrow-shaped formations. The plankton spin as they move, changing directions as soon as they come in contact with an arrow that’s pointing in another direction. The pitch of the sound they make changes depending on where the arrows are positioned. There are four types of Luminarrow—red, yellow, green, and blue. Each type floats at a different speed and makes a distinctive musical tone. The four types of Luminarrow drift together to create beautiful melodies. Completely alter the direction of the arrows to change their sound dramatically.\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/wuF5bbS.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5295, '000480044b454445', 'TWL-N-KEDE', 'Electroplankton™ Sun-Animalcule', 'USA', 2850612, 'dsiw', '50010000001841', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ef5516421d80c17a5331b8200ead6d452f2e91fda08a99e2bbb2cf5b9c8f3eae.jpg', 'A strange electronic sea awaits you. In this sea, you’ll encounter unique species of tiny Electroplankton that respond to your touch and voice to create unforgettable sounds and melodies. Enjoy getting to know these fascinating plankton as you relax to their sights and sounds!\n\nSun-Animalcule plankton get their name from their tendency to emit light in a sphere around them. The plankton begin as eggs and gradually grow, emitting light and fascinating sounds throughout their entire life cycle. The sounds they make change as they grow from infancy to maturity, growing very quickly until they disappear completely. Sun-Animalcule plankton only emerge in the morning, noon, and evening. Sun-Animalcule plankton lose strength as the night wears on; that is when the crescent-shaped Falcato plankton take their place. The pitch of the plankton changes depending on where they grow.\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/iP8eoxa.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5296, '000480044b454545', 'TWL-N-KEEE', 'Electroplankton™ Rec-Rec', 'USA', 3387188, 'dsiw', '50010000001861', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/45509f447183d300d1682e827bb49512ca7e6e9100f90c7c21d9e07e44395879.jpg', 'A strange electronic sea awaits you. In this sea, you’ll encounter unique species of tiny Electroplankton that respond to your touch and voice to create unforgettable sounds and melodies. Enjoy getting to know these fascinating plankton as you relax to their sights and sounds!\n\nRec-Rec are fishlike plankton that feed on sound waves. They absorb sound waves transmitted through water and use them as a form of nutrition. The sound waves that the Rec-Rec eat are then stored inside their bodies until they have been digested. Once the digestion process is complete, they play back the sounds in perfect four-second intervals. While these sounds are playfully emitted, the wave patterns can be observed pulsating on their bodies. Rec-Rec always swim side by side in schools of four. When they swim at different speeds, the frequency with which they emit sounds also changes.\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/UgavFPQ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5297, '000480044b454645', 'TWL-N-KEFE', 'Electroplankton™ Nanocarp', 'USA', 2661172, 'dsiw', '50010000001881', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3d67b89326f014a7cf932e4e73a51ec8b155d6c9344a12cee4067ca99255f3dc.jpg', 'A strange electronic sea awaits you. In this sea, you’ll encounter unique species of tiny Electroplankton that respond to your touch and voice to create unforgettable sounds and melodies. Enjoy getting to know these fascinating plankton as you relax to their sights and sounds!\n\nNanocarp have very sensitive hearing. Sensing vibrations coming through water with the two ears on their head, these plankton can distinguish sound quality and frequency. They display very interesting reactions to the sound of humans clapping and breathing. Nanocarp are also excellent swimmers. They have a tendency to swim in formations of sixteen and react together to sound they detect. These plankton emit sounds on their own when they sense waves on the water’s surface. When this happens, the pitch of sounds they produce changes depending on where the Nanocarp is currently located.\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/rIMW5JN.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5298, '000480044b454745', 'TWL-N-KEGE', 'Electroplankton™ Lumiloop', 'USA', 3360564, 'dsiw', '50010000001901', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7fea983d89fb4a3956d6ccbf75c1ff625dd1ad1bd88523055186325748be457b.jpg', 'A strange electronic sea awaits you. In this sea, you’ll encounter unique species of tiny Electroplankton that respond to your touch and voice to create unforgettable sounds and melodies. Enjoy getting to know these fascinating plankton as you relax to their sights and sounds!\n\nLumiloop plankton are curious, donut-shaped aquatic creatures. While stationary, they have the ability to spin at a very high rate of speed. As they spin, the Lumiloop emit unique sounds and a fascinating ring-shaped glow. Lumiloop plankton seem to always grow in clusters of five. They produce sounds at different pitches as they spin together, creating a beautiful harmony. This is called a pentatonic scale. Depending on where they live, Lumiloop plankton that produce several different sounds have been identified.\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/BLqIPWo.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5299, '000480044b454845', 'TWL-N-KEHE', 'Electroplankton™ Marine-Crystals', 'USA', 2747188, 'dsiw', '50010000001902', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0f73e1a80da145e5e31de7d881084b2109787441635b9b22d8fc1043112b4a06.jpg', 'A strange electronic sea awaits you. In this sea, you’ll encounter unique species of tiny Electroplankton that respond to your touch and voice to create unforgettable sounds and melodies. Enjoy getting to know these fascinating plankton as you relax to their sights and sounds!\n\nResembling delicate snow crystals, Marine-Crystal plankton elegantly float on the surface of the water. The plankton get their name from their distinctive snowflake shape. They grow in clusters of 35 and line up in very orderly formations. When stimulated, Marine-Crystal plankton spin and produce vibrant sounds. While the plankton do grow in size if they are repeatedly tapped, they gradually return to their original size over time. They are born in four polygonal shapes: triangle, square, pentagon, and hexagon. The ends of the crystalline protrusions also take on the same shapes. The tone of the sound they make changes depending on the shape of the Marine-Crystal plankton’s body.\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/hXaIHRx.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5300, '000480044b454a45', 'TWL-N-KEJE', 'Electroplankton™ Varvoice', 'USA', 2443060, 'dsiw', '50010000001921', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a2205b27f8e36700bf19c8e2754ec7c4826fa8fd8b0841a3fc15066c17b959c4.jpg', 'A strange electronic sea awaits you. In this sea, you’ll encounter unique species of tiny Electroplankton that respond to your touch and voice to create unforgettable sounds and melodies. Enjoy getting to know these fascinating plankton as you relax to their sights and sounds!\n\nVarvoice plankton memorize the sound of human speech and repeat it over and over. They accomplish this amazing feat by oscillating the long flagellum that extends from their head. By resonating the vibration with their water-droplet-shaped body, the plankton produce sounds that closely resemble the human voice. The body can expand and contract at will. By changing shape, they can easily manipulate the sound of the voice. Words that the Varvoice memorize and play back in reverse have a particularly strange ring to them. Researchers refer to this phenonmenon as Varvoice inversion.\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/FKbP2Sn.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5301, '000480044b455345', 'TWL-N-KESE', 'Escapee GO!', 'USA', 5487412, 'dsiw', '50010000002204', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7ce0b51642c8e1e9ee2919d99b7686d75b1d1584f7e143a0f9a32b0e8fc599fe.jpg', 'Feel the thrill of the escape! In Escapee GO!, you will take the role of Claire, who awakes with no memory of who she is. Save for her name, all information about her has been destroyed. In its place, something within her has changed. Hunted down by an unknown enemy, she must find a way to escape her pursuers using her new found powers. Will she be able to survive? Using her heightened senses, Claire is able to detect incoming pursuers before they come into visual range. During her daring escape, Claire will find mysterious items which will temporarily enhance her abilities, allowing her to even the playing field between her pursuers and herself. Supporting up to 4 players with DS Wireless Play, Escapee GO! promises endless fun for your group of friends!\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/0ItMIHx.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5302, '000480044b464245', 'TWL-N-KFBE', 'GO Series Fishing Resort', 'USA', 5698356, 'dsiw', '50010000007247', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/17240fd639b0f605fa59fa9fe2957f34b1235ecf45ff62cbe7e51bab0cae9e41.jpg', 'GO Series presents Fishing Resort from Mechanic Arms.\n\nFeel the swing of the fishing rod as you cast, the tension in the line as you reel in the fish and its weight as you catch it with the net. Use the stylus to feel every bite, tug and pull. Buy new rods, lines, floats and bait, take part in challenges and trade Member''s Cards and Rankings with friends via DS Wireless Communications. Developed in Japan with anime graphics and style, Fishing Resort oozes charm and is a delight to play.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/iWu4n3D.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5303, '000480044b464945', 'TWL-N-KFIE', 'Flight Control™', 'USA', 7065396, 'dsiw', '50010000002263', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8d81d7e1935ff17c969a855bdebaee1233258058868cb90b1a032436445920af.jpg', 'Keep the skies safe in Flight Control, the insanely popular worldwide hit from Firemint! In this action-packed game, take on the role of an air traffic controller at an increasingly busy airport. In complete control of the airspace, direct aircraft to their appropriate landing zones while avoiding collisions. Travel to airports set among green fields, a beachside resort, the Australian Outback, a winter wonderland and even an aircraft carrier. Learn how to land ten different kinds of aircraft, including jets, seaplanes and helicopters. To direct aircraft, simply touch and drag them to their landing zones with the stylus without letting them collide. Sounds easy? You’ll need smart strategy, keen eyes and a smooth touch to keep the chaos under control! You can even work alongside a friend in cooperative multiplayer mode, and guard the airways together. Flight Control only takes a minute to learn – just don’t expect to put it down as quickly as you’ll pick it up!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/9PYysjv.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5304, '000480044b465345', 'TWL-N-KFSE', 'Flashlight', 'USA', 2941748, 'dsiw', '50010000002123', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bde600b8eb30557a8022793f3964f5e3731d9fed9dc372e77386a3cc9e0f456b.jpg', 'When it is dark people need a simple source of light. Flashlight changes the dual screens of your \n\nNintendo DSi system into a flashlight with added features. Change the color and the intensity of the light. Use your \nNintendo DSi system to read under a blanket or to get a serious source of light while taking night hikes. Flashlight could also be helpful in other situations, such as using the warning light when your car has broken down.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/OPlFYJV.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5305, '000480044b474c45', 'TWL-N-KGLE', 'Glow Artisan', 'USA', 8230708, 'dsiw', '50010000002441', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/455ccc7dab7a879d57d4d3ab03fc31fb11899f5699deecb083f96a27124f9d8b.jpg', 'Solve mind-bending puzzles in this unique and colorful game! Use your wits and ingenuity to solve over 100 puzzles and earn over 300 medals. Play Time Trial, Randomizer, and Multiplayer modes for an endless supply of new challenges! Create new puzzles with the built-in editor or use the Nintendo DSi Camera to turn your photos into puzzles.\n\nPLAY\n* Over 100 pre-built levels!\n* Endless user-created and randomly-generated puzzles!\n* Earn Trophies and Medals!\n* Unlock Time Trial and Randomizer modes!\n* Get help from the Auto Solver when you are stuck!\n\nCREATE\n* Build your own puzzles from scratch with the Puzzle Creator!\n* Turn your world into Glow Puzzles by transforming photos into colorful challenges!  \n* Use stored photos or take new pictures from within the game!\n\nCONNECT\n* Challenge other players in Handoff, a fun and competitive wireless battle of wits!\n* Wirelessly swap puzzles you''ve created with friends!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Pj5HCFz.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5306, '000480044b484545', 'TWL-N-KHEE', 'DotMan', 'USA', 4469556, 'dsiw', '50010000007249', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/013f29bed3b488e8c4fad6fbddbf8afe3f46c6a3e521a4f737232ca003042c3d.jpg', 'Finally, a chance to drive as fast as you can with no regard to the law. Put the pedal to the metal and drive with both confidence and precision as you speed around collecting all the coins on each stage as quickly as possible. Execute evasive moves and collect essential items to help you dodge the police and escape being caught. Watch out for the three strikes and you are out rule—if you are caught by the police three times, the game is over.\n\nIt’s up to you to perform last minute lane changes, stealthy u-turns and determine the rate of speed. However, keep in mind that once you start going, there is no stopping. DotMan is a non-stop action game that takes you back to the golden years of arcade gaming. Strap yourself into the driver’s seat and prepare yourself for the ride of your life.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/yvXn6KZ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5307, '000480044b4d3954', 'TWL-N-KM9T', 'Master of Illusion™ Express: Deep Psyche', 'USA', 2277172, 'dsiw', '50010000004322', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/091ca916f3f619a482bc35d789498cf6db8fead55193dc99ad1f459d0d0bde1f.jpg', 'Master of Illusion Express titles are mind-bending magic tricks pulled from the popular Nintendo DS game. Learn the illusions, practice up and then amaze your friends. Master of Illusion Express: Deep Psyche asks a series of pointed questions and then reveals to you a startling truth.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/2uM8iEf.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5308, '000480044b543245', 'TWL-N-KT2E', 'G.G Series HORIZONTAL BAR', 'USA', 2818868, 'dsiw', '50010000003807', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b0ce5240784c97468ed9d7aac04e9e2054f3cd9f0c08b166593f7a1831d16dda.jpg', 'Swing, jump, and spin in this gymnastics action game!\n\nThis is a new type of action game that will have you swinging and jumping from bar to bar, just like the parallel bars in gymnastics. The controls are simple. Grab onto a bar, add momentum to your swing by pressing left or right on the +Control Pad, and then jump and spin to the next bar by pressing the A Button. Gauge the force of your swings and the timing of your jumps just right to cross the course in the fastest time possible. Do you have what it takes to be a star gymnast?', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/tzBi07k.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5309, '000480044b544354', 'TWL-N-KTCT', 'Clubhouse Games™ Express: Family Favorites', 'USA', 4699956, 'dsiw', '50010000006305', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f5e7599bff864c3324b70c5e96fd7cf99a33cd2ac409d57c7a8c0dac40d9d9f8.jpg', 'Choose from five family-friendly games in this Nintendo DSiWare version of the popular Clubhouse Games. Play classic card games like Hearts and Contract Bridge, connect bones to other bones in Dominoes, think strategically in the simple, but addictive Dots and Boxes, and move your pieces towards a common goal in Ludo. Play by yourself or use DS Download Play to host as many as seven friends.\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ga0KkJb.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5310, '000480044b544454', 'TWL-N-KTDT', 'Clubhouse Games™ Express: Strategy Pack', 'USA', 4731700, 'dsiw', '50010000006321', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/de9da1bdc36646f62e2f9cb54a4cf824c7932c7bd86e4adda2014ecd515f220a.jpg', 'Prepare yourself for a lesson in tactics as you play through five strategy-based games in this Nintendo DSiWare version of the popular Clubhouse Games. Take on an opponent in the classic Backgammon, invade an enemy base in Field Tactics, sandwich your opponent’s pieces to capture them in Turncoat, create strings of five in a row in Connect Five, and guess where to attack your opponent’s pieces in Grid Attack. Play by yourself or use DS Download Play to host as many as seven friends.\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/WaKVQtA.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5311, '000480044b325245', 'TWL-N-K2RE', 'Primrose', 'USA', 5489460, 'dsiw', '50010000000722', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2eeeaa4af7a2d2fd24719e8b2dc2916100a8d3ea0f503c3cbeede7eaf9d7d52a.jpg', 'Take your time, set your own pace, establish your own goals, and adapt your play style to whatever you feel is more fun. Primrose rules are easy: there are no time limits, no levels or arbitrary objectives and no constrains. \n\nYou must place pairs of tiles on a game grid and attempt to corral groups of tiles with pieces of a different color. When that happens, surrounded tiles disappear and surrounding tiles change colors, allowing chain effects to trigger combos for massive points. You can play for long matches, surviving against the increasing difficulty, or just go all out on a huge single move combo for millions of points.\n\nRelax, enjoy and welcome to Primrose.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/a7JGM0C.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5312, '000480044b414b45', 'TWL-N-KAKE', 'Art Style™: precipice™', 'USA', 7580468, 'dsiw', '50010000001281', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0078bd11fc5c6a507471fc6363d1643317ce5e1851dc99577e6975a4661e56b5.jpg', 'The sky is literally falling, in the form of cubes, in the action-oriented Art Style: precipice. Watch for the telltale shadow to avoid seeing your character be crushed by a falling cube while climbing the stacked cubes to ascend to the floors above. Push, pull, or shove cubes to make your climb easier and try to gain extra points by stepping on five cubes in a row on the same floor. In addition, you’ll encounter special cubes that can either be helpful or harmful to your effort. Choose from either TEN FLOORS mode, which challenges you to reach the tenth floor while scoring as many points as possible, or TOWER mode, which gives you the chance to climb as high as you can. Do you have what it takes to make it to the top or will you be crushed?\n\nGames in the Art Style series feature elegant design, polished graphics, and pick-up-and-play controls, creating an experience focused purely on fun and engaging game play.\n\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/4ugo5HX.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5313, '000480044b445045', 'TWL-N-KDPE', 'Pro-Putt Domo™', 'USA', 3237684, 'dsiw', '50010000009361', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a9670d33877130aeb402da36a46082bb9415f918b0eca1b44c21ef8fee03c32f.jpg', 'Domo is a strange creature who hatched from an egg. His favorite food is Japanese-style meat-and-potato stew, and he has a strong dislike for apples (due to an unexplained mystery). He is also known as the popular mascot of Japan’s NHK television station.\n\nIn Pro-Putt Domo, Domo hits the green in an effort to win the world putt-putt golf championship. Domo competes to finish with the lowest number of strokes in either the nine-hole Small Classic or the 18-hole Big Open tournament. Along the way, he’ll collect coins and earn bowls of meat-and-potato stew, while avoiding bunkers and water hazards.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/xCimW0T.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5314, '000480044b445745', 'TWL-N-KDWE', 'White-Water Domo™', 'USA', 2543412, 'dsiw', '50010000009362', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/66ca239fbeb9c639a0f1364948f6e49fd5c17387c4ca044b83b0e9d52eddceb0.jpg', 'Domo is a strange creature who hatched from an egg. His favorite food is Japanese-style meat-and-potato stew, and he has a strong dislike for apples (due to an unexplained mystery). He is also known as the popular mascot of Japan’s NHK television station.\n\nTake control of Domo as he hops into his kayak and races the river rapids in White-Water Domo. Jump and paddle as you steer Domo through the treacherous rapids in an effort to cross the finish line as quickly as possible. Finish with one of the top three times to proceed to the next stage.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/AXcVdc4.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5315, '000480044b453345', 'TWL-N-KE3E', 'PictureBook Games™: The Royal Bluff', 'USA', 6071092, 'dsiw', '50010000001782', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1dc69d14aa00245dcaeb7e3a73305853a47759e44b82f40011da4b9a78e1abec.jpg', 'Aristocratic opponents square off in PictureBook Games: The Royal Bluff, a game of strategy and deceit. Compete for points by adding or subtracting colored chips from rows on the game board and trying to guess each of your opponent’s secretly assigned chip colors. Once you’re confident in your deduction, issue a Call Out attempt to earn bonus points—at the risk of giving your opponent an extra point if you’re wrong. Three modes of play (Tournament, Free Play, DS Wireless Play) offer a variety of options, from facing off against an assortment of computer opponents to competing in a wireless match with up to four players. Throw Trick Cards, with their variety of effects, into the mix and you’ve got a winning combination of tactics and trickery that is sure to score points with players!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/6lBvE1v.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5316, '000480044b494345', 'TWL-N-KICE', 'Music on: Playing Piano', 'USA', 4557620, 'dsiw', '50010000002421', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c63f465662a901a1b6e518dc0c3490b6701929cab145e7a9490a7285f5c38b0d.jpg', 'Playing the piano has never been so easy and so much fun! This new collection of 15 popular songs allows you to enjoy a complete musical experience even if you have no prior knowledge of the piano. Notes transformed into rectangles appear over the piano keys to show you where, when and how to play them. The song speed increases depending on the game''s level. Music on: Playing Piano is an easy and intuitive game that will challenge your auditory and visual coordination.\n\nSongs included:\n*For Old Times (Traditional)\n*Red River Valley (Traditional)\n*Greensleeves (Traditional)\n*Yankee Doodle Dandy (George M. Cohan)\n*El Condor Pasa (A. Robles)\n*Old Black Joe (Stephen Foster)\n*The Saints (Traditional)\n*Alouette (Traditional)\n*Camptown Races (Stephen Foster)\n*Katyusha (Traditional)\n*Guantanamera (Traditional)\n*The Easy Winners (Scott Joplin)\n*The Banana Boat Song (Traditional)\n*Oh! Susanna (Stephen Foster)\n*La Cucaracha (Traditional)', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/4JXm28U.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5317, '000480044b4a4f45', 'TWL-N-KJOE', 'Magnetic Joe', 'USA', 16577332, 'dsiw', '50010000002429', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9606d35e6fb3250193906e2dfef74b107e175496cc3c31f0505a4bf3daa1e91f.jpg', 'Take control of Magnetic Joe, everyone''s favorite little magnetic sphere. Guide him through 100 exciting mazes full of spikes, enemies, and other obstacles. Help Joe as he pursues his nemesis, Dr. Magnevil, who is on his way to conquer the world. The mazes are full of magnets that push and pull Joe in different directions. Your task is to skillfully use their magnetic force to get Joe to the exit unharmed. Use the magnetic force carefully, the levels are filled with surprises and a boss could be lurking!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/pGu3gsp.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5318, '000480044b4d4654', 'TWL-N-KMFT', 'Master of Illusion™ Express: Funny Face', 'USA', 2342708, 'dsiw', '50010000004386', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ae734966eb84058a5aa94e8f4c93a1e8eae53638af015cf8bc70a933f980f28b.jpg', 'Master of Illusion Express titles are mind-boggling magic tricks pulled from the popular Nintendo DS game. Learn the illusions, practice up, and then amaze your friends. Master of Illusion Express: Funny Face uses your Nintendo DSi system as a prop in a card trick. Draw a face on the Touch Screen and astound your audience as the face tells them which playing card they picked. Also included is the bonus Vanishing Card trick, which the Nintendo DSi system performs for your enjoyment.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/uq3Pix1.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5319, '000480044b4d4d45', 'TWL-N-KMME', 'Mixed Messages™', 'USA', 6028084, 'dsiw', '50010000002921', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f1725e43c955e8424a061074ef180a0e4f9b42a9887712c80aabb90400f51353.jpg', 'Mixed Messages is the hilarious party game of mixed-up miscommunication. Sketch a picture to capture your\nfriend''s sentence, or try to figure out what in the world they''ve drawn! You might start with, “The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog,” and end up with, “A crazy surfer outruns flying sticks of dynamite while his fans cheer!” Two to twenty-one players take turns writing sentences and drawing pictures to pass along a message. This isn’t a game about winning and losing—it’s all about the funny miscommunications that happen along the way. You''ll laugh when you see just how wacky things can get! Get together with your friends and mix it up!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/iOLI6Iw.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5320, '000480044b4d5354', 'TWL-N-KMST', 'Master of Illusion™ Express: Shuffle Games', 'USA', 2280244, 'dsiw', '50010000004464', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ffbec8bbf029f3772045be34f13d01f2c72f9a549e6ab05623b09b72279f78c1.jpg', 'Master of Illusion Express titles are mind-boggling magic tricks pulled from the popular Nintendo DS game. Learn the illusions, practice up, and then amaze your friends. Master of Illusion Express: Shuffle Games will boggle your audience members’ minds as they try to figure out how you know exactly what they’re thinking. Also included is the bonus Vanishing Card trick, which the Nintendo DSi system performs for your enjoyment.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/RWLqt7A.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47');
INSERT INTO `3dsgames` (`id`, `titleID`, `serial`, `name`, `region`, `size`, `type`, `contentID`, `iconURL`, `gdesc`, `thumb`, `scrcount`, `imgur_iconURL`, `imgur_thumb`, `count`, `time`) VALUES
(5321, '000480044b4d5945', 'TWL-N-KMYE', 'MySims™ Camera', 'USA', 4830004, 'dsiw', '50010000002963', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/02b2eb726bbec5abc6e19d8c2b9e878c97c10c351b87e0cd7586d79db5937821.jpg', 'MySims™ Camera is a camera application that utilizes popular MySims characters. You can take photos and overlay 3D MySims™ characters to bring them into the real world. The 3D characters can be animated, moved, scaled, rotated and cropped. You can also draw on the photos with the stylus or use the stamp tool to add more art and style. Create a unique frame and save the photos to the Nintendo DSi photo album to share with friends. With MySims™ Camera, you make picture taking with the MySims a fun creative experience for the entire family.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/lb8rPvE.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5322, '000480044b4f5445', 'TWL-N-KOTE', 'Oscar in Toyland', 'USA', 4760372, 'dsiw', '50010000003289', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1dd80c593f735dcdb2fb35ceb68d894c58a51ad04bbc1686c36e2fe459a3978d.jpg', 'Meet OSCAR—The new kid on the block. This fabulous jump & run game is easy to play, packed with hours of fun & non-stop action, 100''s of collectables & surprises. In psychedelic worlds of candy, soda pop, amusement park rides, board games, fairytales and more, meet lots of cool toys and animals in hidden rooms, bonus & bogus mini games. Use Wings to fly, Springy Shoes to jump and Oscar''s secret weapon—his magical Yo-Yo to swing on and zap enemies in some of the craziest platform levels you''ll ever play. Oscar in Toyland—not to be missed!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/bnawl4r.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5323, '000480044b504645', 'TWL-N-KPFE', 'Pop Island - Paperfield', 'USA', 6211380, 'dsiw', '50010000003165', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/726437a05fbcad12333cb3689e1ea28232bde6bdf047e4197140b6d99b1836d1.jpg', 'FUN IS DECLARED!\nThanks to the easy pick-up and play control themes, dive into this fresh universe and have fun in almost no time! Join your team and race, surf, or fly on three new islands. Get a maximum of flags to win the victory in the “Race for flags” or “Capture the flag” mode.\n\nFURIOUS MACHINE\nWith the new “Magic Shooters” team, take control of eight land, sea, and air vehicles or animals, including tanks, hovercrafts, planes, surfing penguins, eagles, and black cats! Get even more involved in the action with the impressive graphics engine that runs fast and smooth at 60 frames per second.\n\n1-8 PLAYERS\nIn Solo Mode, rack up points and unlock new playable vehicles and maps. Use DS Download Play to share Pop Island - Paperfield and compete joyfully with up to seven friends!\n\nPLUS\nIf you own Pop Island on your Nintendo DSi system, you can get three new maps and four vehicles, including the helicopter and the submarine!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/1AjmZRU.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5324, '000480044b504945', 'TWL-N-KPIE', 'Pop+ Solo™', 'USA', 3017524, 'dsiw', '50010000003221', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fb2739c463b51c226a094af3ed8ad1bf92decbfac849367b5527b75d25bcb164.jpg', 'Pop bubbles, build chains and try to keep the timer alive in this addictive puzzle/shooter. Pop your way through 16 waves of bubbles in Adventure, Normal or Advanced. Test yourself against the clock in a 1, 2 or 5 minute run and take on the new Bonus Round mode where each bonus round can be played in 3, 5 or 10 rounds of increasing difficulty! Or just chill out in the relaxing Chill mode with no score or time pressures to worry about. Pop+ Solo comes to the Nintendo DSi with 8 modes and 5 bonus rounds plus plenty of new badges to collect! Adventure mode introduces some new elements to the game with mines, golden fish and jets of water as well as 4 boss battles. The new Challenge mode lets you create and customize your own challenges to play again and again.', 'none', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/mQcCyOs.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5325, '000480044b545545', 'TWL-N-KTUE', 'Nintendo DSi™ Instrument Tuner', 'USA', 1921844, 'dsiw', '50010000003570', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5f6b38af7c139487da7d1b9e86b411abbabf8f9c33d9cec78273b0d7e62ade71.jpg', 'The Nintendo DSi Instrument Tuner software can be used to tune an instrument by aligning tonal pitches. The software offers two methods of handling this: feeding sounds into the microphone to measure the difference with a target pitch or listening to a sample tone. In addition, the standard musical pitch and notation can be changed, as well as the design of the tuner (choose one of three designs). And if you’re feeling especially in-tune, test your ear by taking on the Tuner Fight minigame’s challenge: balloons with notes on them rise from pipes, and can only be popped by making a tone that matches the pitch shown.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/NyHSH3E.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5326, '000480044b415345', 'TWL-N-KASE', 'Art Style™: ZENGAGE™', 'USA', 8757044, 'dsiw', '50010000001041', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9f5430a9e80e202bcb7b6563c3e97a6d09388a0ee0d10dfa5c985f64ad1b5621.jpg', 'Do you dream of relaxing with a great puzzle game? Gameplay in Art Style: ZENGAGE revolves around sliding cells (squares) to match colors with cores (beads) located on the board. Clear each stage by matching all of the cores and cells. As you progress further into the game’s 100+ stages, you’ll encounter cells with special characteristics (such as ones that can’t be moved), which further add to the challenge. To truly master ZENGAGE though, you must keep your mind sharp and employ careful strategy to complete stages in as few moves as possible. By combining wistful graphics and mesmerizing sound, ZENGAGE creates a surreal world that should be experienced by all puzzle game fans.\n\nGames in the Art Style series feature elegant design, polished graphics, and pick-up-and-play controls, creating an experience focused purely on fun and engaging game play.\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/XSOvWyJ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5327, '000480044b443645', 'TWL-N-KD6E', 'Rock-n-Roll Domo™', 'USA', 3744564, 'dsiw', '50010000009363', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/dec0c91c42afa4e5133647789bc9481e829db90b4953f729f555b47cf52a187b.jpg', 'Domo is a strange creature who hatched from an egg. His favorite food is Japanese-style meat-and-potato stew, and he has a strong dislike for apples (due to an unexplained mystery). He is also known as the popular mascot of Japan’s NHK television station.\n\nIn Rock-n-Roll Domo, you’ll control Domo as he takes the stage in search of fortune and fame. Hit the right notes in rhythm (using the Touch Screen, if desired) to rock the house. Or, if your timing is in need of work, use the mixer to listen to and practice songs. Complete five different songs at a series of increasingly larger venues to help Domo become a superstar.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Wb7IDF3.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5328, '000480044b525445', 'TWL-N-KRTE', 'Robot Rescue', 'USA', 4047668, 'dsiw', '50010000003461', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/68908ead1f09fde2586aef33c27976aab7f685b8d1ef8e9969ba33ccc1fadf93.jpg', 'Robot Rescue is a fun logic game based on a simple but entertaining concept. Your mission is to free robots trapped in 45 evil computer labyrinths while avoiding deadly traps. Sound easy? Not so fast! Each robot shares linked controls... so when you move one, you move them all! It will take clever planning and nerves of steel to pull off this electronic escape. You will need to avoid many traps, like mines or electrical circuits, and use to your advantage special elements like glue stains. Choose one of 3 levels of difficulty and get ready for a challenge!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/LDRaPwZ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5329, '000480044b545745', 'TWL-N-KTWE', 'Thorium Wars™', 'USA', 14594868, 'dsiw', '50010000003571', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9cadeaccbe5186a7dc2619eb00c30a3a3bc15f1f3929b48043695bb2fad1d7c6.jpg', 'In Thorium Wars, stop the Thorions—a super species of Thorium-based machines—from destroying mankind. Blast through waves of Thorions by controlling an arsenal of tanks, skyfighters, hovercrafts, gunboats, and starfighters with either the standard or Touch Screen controls. In twelve exciting missions, navigate through a variety of combat environments viewing 360 degrees of the battlefield, fully rendered in 3-D. Toggle between first and third person views as you destroy the terrifying army of Thorium beasts, ranging from swarms of Redeye Drones to the bone-crushing Manticore Walker. Take control of the outcome in this extreme man vs. machine battle as Thorium Wars proves to be the ultimate test for the survival of the fittest.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/6ItrlKV.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5330, '000480044b564b45', 'TWL-N-KVKE', 'Viking Invasion', 'USA', 13024052, 'dsiw', '50010000004166', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8de4ea784e9f43d71845378bf3bb8a4306a889c91fe910c7e4b2d14202c3c751.jpg', 'They come from the North, and they’re about to invade your Nintendo DSi system! Beware, it’s Olaf the Viking and his motley crew! Even now, their drakkars are sailing up the rivers to attack your castles. And it is up to you to construct fortifications so they do not pillage everything you own! The more you defend yourself, the more ferocious they’ll become. Before you know it they’ll be invoking legions of fantastic creatures straight out of the mythical land of Asgard. Fortunately the experience you gain will help you to build even more powerful defenses. Thwart all your assailant’s ruses and unlock new kinds of buildings: tornado blowing windmills to repel the ships, monoliths that strengthen your fortifications or canons firing studded shells. Discover over ten levels, tons of units, a Campaign mode as well as a Survival mode and three difficulty levels - there’s even a little surprise at the end... Can you rise to the challenge and stop Olaf from taking your treasure home to his sweetheart Olga?', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/VYYmyWr.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5331, '000480044b563445', 'TWL-N-KV4E', 'ANONYMOUS NOTES CHAPTER 4 - FROM THE ABYSS -', 'USA', 7662388, 'dsiw', '50010000023655', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fefc858678dfdc7d9864fd7e24fa7de2598183b444ffaa13ccb027378673bb6c.jpg', 'It''s a real action RPG with preeminent exhilaration set inside an infinitely-extending dungeon. Sweep away the monsters wriggling in many places and get at defeating a strong boss monster lurking at the deepest portion of the dungeon. Even after the boss monster is defeated, the dungeon re-creates itself with automatic system so the player can try new games over and over.\n<br><br>\nUsing the skill called "Soul Capture," the mail character can take away the magic and other skills from the monsters, as well as weapons and shields to power up. It is very exhilarating to strengthen the character combining the equipments and skills, then crushing the monsters in a sweep.\n<br><br>\nThe player can enjoy a simple and yet profound world of From The Abyss, Anonymous Notes. The items, skills, and the magic collected in Chapter 2 can be shared between other titles of this series.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/GnZtiBA.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5332, '000480044b563345', 'TWL-N-KV3E', 'Anonymous Notes Chapter 3 - From The Abyss -', 'USA', 6355764, 'dsiw', '50010000012737', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/414960c1748afe7a3794c58f0c9dcb548b6a29518145ee3f75e171cf1e4a60e7.jpg', 'It''s a real action RPG with preeminent exhilaration set inside an infinitely-extending dungeon.\nSweep away the monsters wriggling in many places and get at defeating a strong boss monster lurking at the deepest portion of the dungeon.\n<br><br>\nEven after the boss monster is defeated, the dungeon re-creates itself with automatic system so the player can try new games over and over.\n<br><br>\nUsing the skill called "Soul Capture," the character can take away the magic and other skills from the monsters, as well as weapons and shields to power up.\n<br><br>\nIt is very exhilarating to strengthen the character combining the equipments and skills, then crushing the monsters in a sweep.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/L0AjH9z.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5333, '000480044b355045', 'TWL-N-K5PE', 'Penguin Patrol', 'USA', 5727028, 'dsiw', '50010000009772', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5a2d5309f3c2df4b5d9faa5a418668cde45b94ff0f761f40254de76d50236bab.jpg', 'Baby penguins have been stranded on thin ice by the evil (but oddly stylish) Walrus, and it''s up to the Penguin Patrol to rescue them!\n\nEncounter several types of penguins, such as the stubborn Bratty Penguin or the sleepy Fatty Penguin, as you trek across over 75 puzzling levels. But watch out! With each step you take, the thin ice behind you breaks. Without careful planning, you could cut off your own escape route!\n\nFeaturing a charming pixel art style, delightful music, and thoughtfully designed levels, Penguin Patrol will entice players of all ages.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/3Zpg7mw.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5334, '00040000000fd500', 'CTR-N-BTHE', 'THEATRHYTHM FINAL FANTASY CURTAIN CALL', 'USA', 1756744548, 'eshop', '50010000025075', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a4bb9c8f98b908670ae1163af044c536c8e021ef43a7ac3fc97b06d528865238.jpg', 'Offers in-game purchases\n<br><br>\nTap Into a Timeless Legacy of Music!\n<br><br>\nA sequel to the first FINAL FANTASY rhythm action game, THEATRHYTHM FINAL FANTASY CURTAIN CALL™ expands on the original in every way with new gameplay modes, 221 songs, and over 60 playable characters.  Featuring music that spans the full breadth of the storied FINAL FANTASY franchise, players tap along to the memorable beats and harmonies as the adorable, stylized characters battle and quest through their worlds. The music of over 20 titles is brought together in one package, fusing together the moving scores, cinematic visuals, and role-playing elements the series is known for.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/k5z1gs2.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5335, '000480044b5a4c56', 'TWL-N-KZLV', 'Plants vs Zombies', 'EUR', 16612148, 'dsiw', '50010000006641', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d1fcfaa53657257e84c11726374deef5533bbd4f4925dca4cf93b73c2a7cd4e9.jpg', 'Get ready to soil your plants in the\nzombie-zapping phenomenon from\nPopCap!<br>\n<br>\nA mob of fun-loving zombies is about\nto invade your home, and the only\ndefence is your arsenal of\nhome-guardin’ plants.<br>\n<br>\nYou’ll have to think fast and plant\nfaster as you fight the fun-dead\nthrough day, night, fog, in the\nswimming pool and on the roof. Dig\ninto Adventure mode and get more\nzombie-zapping action in 20\nmini-games, including the all-new\nZombie Trap.<br>\n<br>\nThe fun never dies!<br>\n<br>\nAvailable languages: English,\nGerman, French, Spanish and Italian.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c6c3f7e76857cd672d3615473f8d76463e9d74e6271694ace9ee969d58726ca4.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/ZIDPNAx.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/RRbsQYj.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5336, '000400000009a100', 'CTR-N-TA6P', 'PAC-MAN™', 'EUR', 6978404, 'eshop', '50010000013134', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6efec25d865b53b044744ea3db79f03086525065c04ddc4a63929a9e34d6b34c.jpg', 'Pac-Man needs no introduction; it’s\none of the most popular video games\never made!\n<br/><br/>\nMove Pac-Man through the mazes,\navoiding ghosts and eating all the\npellets. Beware though; each of the\nghosts behaves differently!\n<br/><br/>\nWhen Pac-Man chomps a power\npellet, he becomes invincible, and is\nable to eat the blue ghosts. The more\nghosts Pac-Man eats in a row, the\nhigher the score. Don’t forget to eat\nthe bonus fruit, too!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/074df924b51908e67a17a8b2615ca42c5ed11d20bdf9930ae0b4646b3784f040.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ruwHXlG.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ZRH8ADp.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5337, '00040000000c5d00', 'CTR-N-MBBP', 'The 3D Machine Series: Episode 4', 'EUR', 29297460, 'eshop', '50010000012619', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2977301b82172479eb92815f850519b8be7185e0d31d111b48d455b141ec040c.jpg', 'In Egypt a mummy runs amok in an\nancient pyramid. Igor and the\nprofessor fly to the rescue and chase\nthe monster down a maze of tunnels.\nWill they emerge victorious or forever\nbe caught in this tomb of doom?\n<br/><br/>\nLength 2:30 min', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bc1ce02521266806eab433f1e4e12ebe4d0ec659c5a30372b43ab34c85177b2c.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/Hy6QtBQ.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/yiTCumZ.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5338, '0004000000147f00', 'CTR-N-JVXP', 'Kirby Fighters™ Deluxe', 'EUR', 131652500, 'eshop', '50010000030195', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e47aeb5d5f76cbafc8feb720d0ed56868817d43814449518c9f9f3a784711531.jpg', 'Fight it out with your favorite pink\npuffball in a fierce four-player battle\naction game! Team up or go solo as\nyou battle in new and classic Kirby™\narenas. Choose from powerful copy\nabilities like Sword, Ninja, Hammer\nand more as you take your fighting\nskills to the limit!\n<br/><br/>\nBased on the wild battle mode\nintroduced in Kirby: Triple Deluxe, this\nstandalone game contains expanded\ngameplay features, the ability to play\nas a team, new arenas and more. Join\nup with a friend and fire the powerful\nnew Team Cannon to blast opponents\nwith mega-damage! Earn rare copy\nability hats for defeating Kracko and\nthe King Dedede army in the\nsingle-player gauntlet.\n<br/><br/>\nOwners of Kirby: Triple Deluxe can\nalso access two bonus copy abilities\nplus an exclusive arena – Waddle Dee\nTrain Tracks!\n<br/><br/>\nThis software supports up to 4\nplayers for both Local Play and\nDownload Play.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/77a99ecfa73e34c9e37f5ce15f4955be3b2515a2a714c1ebd699d5fd3d7ba5c6.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/TOlwgFk.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/6InakX5.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
