(5378, '000480044b414356', 'TWL-N-KACV', 'Advanced Circuits', 'EUR', 6045492, 'dsiw', '50010000002003', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3ae8b7bbdc73bcd326904a383a1b5fc8993bc911fcc620905033f987740e0415.jpg', 'With a train, a car or a tank, are you\nready for a new challenge? This\nbrain-boggling puzzle game will put\nyour powers of deduction to the test.<br>\n<br>\nComplete the circuits by connecting\nsquares on the game board with\npieces of track. Some pieces of track\nare already shown on the board at the\nbeginning of the game to give you a\nhead start. There is only one solution\nto each puzzle. The rules are simple\nbut the challenges are tough!<br>\n<br>\n• Challenge mode features 60\npredefined game boards, of increasing\ndifficulty.<br>\n<br>\n• Free Play mode lets you select the\ngame board size and practise on any\nnumber of randomly-generated\npuzzles.<br>\n<br>\n• 72 awards to be won.<br>\n<br>\n• Also features a tutorial, hints and\ntips and even the solution if you feel\nlike giving up!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/71a8a6b5f537cfc00d138a58291693324b0500b8fdb3beae283109a922155ba6.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/hw9PNRC.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/B80rmQg.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5379, '000480044b435150', 'TWL-N-KCQP', 'Crazy Cheebo: Puzzle Party', 'EUR', 6016820, 'dsiw', '50010000009121', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5f7d53bed4eb1b28e15aab062800cb86577b6b3fbb1b67a7baaaae98ab2ceb9a.jpg', 'The objective is to switch two\nobjects to make a horizontal or\nvertical set of three or more objects\nof the same colour. The player can win\nvarious awards by matching more\nobjects and creating combos. The\ngame contains colourful graphics, a\nCrazy Cheebo character and lots of\nhumorous videos.<br>\n<br>\nYou will have even more fun when\nyou compete against your friends in\nmultiplayer games where you can\nshow everyone who is the best player!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/uCmlVxC.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5380, '000480044b445856', 'TWL-N-KDXV', '3D Space Tank™', 'EUR', 16522036, 'dsiw', '50010000004801', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/deee4f34e98a62e3ae1bd074ef511f18cda7d8d408c1b19c598ff05689100e19.jpg', 'Space year XXXX: humanity leaves\nEarth for the stars... A mere 20 years\nlater, the oppressive Kiisan Empire,\nled by your former commander, is\nthreatening galactic peace. Our last\nhope is VIXIV, a state-of-the-art space\nbattle tank capable of all-range\nsurface combat and interplanetary\ntravel. Taking control of VIXIV, you\nmust engage in daring land and aerial\ncombat, in thrilling first-person view,\nand restore peace to the galaxy!<br>\n<br>\nWith the help of your support bot,\nVIX-529, travel around the Kiisa\nSystem via high-speed interplanetary\nwarp tunnels and take to the skies or\nplanet surfaces in all-range sections.\nUse the radar to track enemies and to\nlocate vital power crystals, which\nallow you to open new warp tunnels\nand explore new planets!<br>\n<br>\nComplete missions and side quests to\nincrease your rank and gain powerful\nnew weapons to assist you in your\nfight for freedom!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f6882c3258f30cd63ce65c5a74705913a87b651d93924a7e7603245dab4e8233.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/goiE14a.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/OCsK5pt.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5381, '000480044b464f50', 'TWL-N-KFOP', 'Frenzic', 'EUR', 4631348, 'dsiw', '50010000003641', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ab0945b5d7d00cdd8d1352184dcbf515558e0b5a4a35e796246ebe307ea603a6.jpg', 'Frenzic is a unique puzzle game that\ndazzles the eye, teases the brain and\nkeeps you coming back for more! It\ntakes only minutes to learn, but\nmonths to master as you devise new,\nimpressive play strategies to push\nyour brain to its limit. Compete\nagainst your personal best and climb\nthrough six levels of Devotion from\nNewbie all the way to Frenzic Master.\nFrenzic is a must have for puzzle\nenthusiasts of all ages!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/423ed01d455696e9d130e8a69b4dce4565e296f0d4554600dfa838cf6e5bca4b.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/5MuaUnt.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/OSiisYb.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5382, '000480044b494f50', 'TWL-N-KIOP', '1001 BlockBusters', 'EUR', 6069044, 'dsiw', '50010000009578', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ae04835bff0d22760b8ae89a35c4045e3860341a56f759642bcfdad87cd93f5d.jpg', 'Think you''ve seen the ultimate\nbrick-breaking game? Think again!\nEnjoy classic gameplay, amazing 3D\ngraphics and surprising bonuses as\nyou smash through 1001 levels of\nblockbusting excitement! Use the\nstylus to catch, bounce and bust balls\nthrough complex 3D constructions in\n4 eye-popping worlds: Stone Age,\nAncient Greece, Candy World and\nFantasy Forest. Beat your best score\nby collecting wild powerups, including\nweapons, magnetic paddles, shields\nand more. But watch out for hidden\nhazards and booby traps- unless you\nlike extra-small paddles and crazy\ncamera angles! With over a dozen\nbonuses, 300 kinds of blocks and\n1001 incredible 3D levels, 1001\nBlockBusters is non-stop,\nno-holds-barred, action-packed fun!<br>\n<br>\nFeatures:<br>\n<br>\n- 1001 levels in 4 different worlds\n(Ancient Greece, Stone Age, Candy\nWorld and Fantasy Forest)<br>\n<br>\n- More than 15 power-ups and\npower-downs<br>\n<br>\n- 3 shooter types<br>\n<br>\n- Eye-catching 3D graphics<br>\n<br>\n- 3 game modes<br>\n<br>\n- High score list', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/qlfGNdf.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5383, '000480044b4b5150', 'TWL-N-KKQP', 'Bugs''N''Balls', 'EUR', 6275892, 'dsiw', '50010000007965', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a13508b754a043233ef81f28c6e0af74b899a6ac166355a1710b5c144d130d95.jpg', 'Bugs''N''Balls is the most played\ngame in the Bug''s World. Our goal is\nto play against all the opponents from\nthe Cucumber League and win the\nmaximum number of matches to gain\naccess to the professional league.<br>\n<br>\nBugs''N''Balls is very easy to play.\nThrow the balls on your side of the\ntable into your adversary''s. Dodge\nthe balls from your opponent or you''ll\nget knocked out for a while.<br>\n<br>\nWith luck we can become champions\nof the professional league. But it''s not\nthat easy...we''ll need to train hard.<br>\n<br>\n* 2 Game Modes<br>\n<br>\n* 2 Leagues<br>\n<br>\n* 4 Characters<br>\n<br>\n* Mini-games<br>\n<br>\n* ...and more surprises!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ksf3gKM.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5384, '000480044b4b5250', 'TWL-N-KKRP', 'Flip the Core', 'EUR', 9358132, 'dsiw', '50010000011066', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b475ef4472dda4ffa18f15bfba8deeb4eed57b05b04dcf2aa352da6491fc2978.jpg', 'Before the Big Bang shaped the\nuniverse as we know it, a place\nexisted with fewer dimensions than we\nhave today. It is there that our hero''s\njourney began. Carrying with him a\nspecial device that allowed him to flip\nbetween these flat dimensions...<br>\n<br>\nFlip the Core is an artistic and unique\ntake on the classic Shoot ''em up\ngenre and combines fast shooting\naction with strategic thinking. In this\nside-scrolling action game, you can\nliterally flip your screen at will,\nchanging walls into tunnels, a death\ntrap into a passage way, move an\nenemy from one spot to the\nnext... Unless you truly believe in\ndead ends... there are none.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/TOreslY.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47');
