(5385, '000480044b4d3656', 'TWL-N-KM6V', 'Maestro! Green Groove', 'EUR', 11758388, 'dsiw', '50010000004301', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/31890547f69f7641572129576e00b2178fbddb89c00b2cab0cf9f2a3575c2938.jpg', 'You like Music?\nYou like Platforms?\nYou like the Jungle?\nYou''ll love "MaesYou like Music?\nYou like Platforms?\nYou like the Jungle?\nYou''ll love "Maestro! Green Groove"!\nSo jump in and enjoy this wonderful\nfeeling of being a virtuoso using your\nheart, stylus and voice!<br>\n<br>\nEverything you do is music,\nEVERYTHING! Hit the spiders to play\nsome drums, shoot the fruit to bring\nout the melody, pinch the strings to\nplay the tune...<br>\n<br>\nChallenge the mischievous Staccato\nthe Spider in a battle in which the\nmost talented one will win!tro! Green Groove"! \nSo jump in and enjoy this wonderful feeling of being a virtuoso using your heart, stylus and voice!\nEverything you do is music, EVERYTHING! Hit the spiders to play some drums, shoot the fruit to bring out the melody, pinch the strings to play the tune...\nChallenge the mischievous Staccato the Spider in a battle in which the most talented one will win!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/34d26f0681b93f0a6e563ce3032cdbca7c9c49cf8077c4afbfff9057e1986e60.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/xCRUY73.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/lE6vfuF.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5386, '000480044b544556', 'TWL-N-KTEV', 'Tetris® Party Live', 'EUR', 12084020, 'dsiw', '50010000006322', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/065c0ebb3809eea36e1709636e26ed0bb31be9e35eadf70e381d43ef4e0e9e9c.jpg', 'Now you can party with Tetris\nwhenever and wherever you want!\nTetris Party Live features several\nexciting game modes from the popular\nTetris Party series, including Marathon\n(1P), Computer Battle (1P vs CPU),\nVS Battle (2P), and Duel Space (2P).', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f4457125b544d9b3db6977da5517bbe4947b34de1253cc086c52f6dd4a86a069.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/JCQDyH7.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/MbUrhw2.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5387, '000480044b584550', 'TWL-N-KXEP', 'Escape the Virus: Swarm Survival', 'EUR', 5277492, 'dsiw', '50010000010876', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1ad9f48ad61dfaeb26b2b83965f41128d4d6d6a9b343aa47cb628b5aedc2d0f2.jpg', 'Dodge, wind and jump to link all\npieces of DNA and build the longest\nchain ever while fighting off vicious\nviruses. Look at your surroundings\nand get one off bonuses such as a\nvaccine or a micro-world equivalent of\na rocket-launcher! Put your survival\nskills to the test in this\nreflex-awakening action featuring 2\nmodes of gameplay!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/1hZMFX4.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5388, '000400000016be00', 'CTR-N-MBUJ', 'ベイマックス 3D', 'JPN', 2222467892, 'eshop', '50010000032775', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d52647b8e43c0bbe1745eed4f18af9de8254eb8ab0ba5ec9680771329c92c91b.jpg', 'キミがいてくれてよかった。\n<br>孤独な少年と彼を守ろうとする戦えないケア･ロボットの、かけがえのない絆と限りない勇気を描いた感動アドベンチャー。\n<br>\n<br>収録時間：約102分\n<br>音声言語：日本語\n<br>\n<br>謎の事故で最愛の兄タダシを失った天才少年ヒロ。深く傷ついた彼の心を救ったのは、人々の心と体を守るために兄が開発したケア･ロボットのベイマックスだった。兄の死の真相をつかもうとする二人だったが、彼らの前に未知なる強大な敵が立ちはだかる。ケア･ロボットとして人を傷つけることを禁じられているベイマックスに、大切なヒロを守り切ることはできるのだろうか? そして、兄がベイマックスに託した、驚くべき“使命”とは……?', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ed3b033d2fe79768fc02d16e93457cfe1c1f3eb3352619b4d2070d3e1591944d.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/mtRchQU.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/fQxnZZG.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
