(5392, '000400000008bf00', 'CTR-N-JK3E', 'Family Tennis 3D', 'USA', 64944996, 'eshop', '50010000010453', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/700609694ed51571b9f9ce8ca78abf9e9a8ac898e6601a4d569205ff8b4154ad.jpg', 'The Family series comes to Nintendo 3DS with a casual tennis game!\n<br><br>\nNew characters join in to bring the number of playable characters to eight and there are six different courts, all exploding with variety. With the addition of Easy Mode, absolutely anyone can play with the press of a button and look great while doing it. Start with the Tournament to unlock everything in the gallery, then why not try the minigames: Roulette Rally, Human Backboard, and Survivor? Play some doubles and make it a real show!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/BG8GuUO.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5393, '000480044b4b5245', 'TWL-N-KKRE', 'Flip the Core', 'USA', 9306932, 'dsiw', '50010000010766', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8af5badb778eed309e337f0879f46984c860de80f15c4c65bd9385afea377505.jpg', 'Before the Big Bang shaped the universe as we know it, a place existed with fewer dimensions than we have today. It is there that our hero''s journey began. Carrying with him a special device that allowed him to flip between these flat dimensions...\n\nFlip the Core is an artistic and unique take on the classic Shoot ''em up genre and combines fast shooting action with strategic thinking. In this side-scrolling action game, you can literally flip your screen at will, changing walls into tunnels, a death trap into a passage way, move an enemy from one spot to the next...Unless you truly believe in dead ends...there are none.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/7PgDMrc.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5394, '000480044b4d4c45', 'TWL-N-KMLE', 'Don''t Cross The Line', 'USA', 4437812, 'dsiw', '50010000002901', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7518f915bac1a319999d6afb8b22867d74854ff7be9a627ba73aacb33fd1a1ba.jpg', 'Don''t Cross The Line is a puzzle game where the player must connect lines to various boxes, from one identical box to another, without crossing the lines they drew in the process. There are roughly 50 stages in all. Depending on how quickly each stage is completed, the player will be awarded with either a bronze, silver, or gold award. To unlock further stages, the player must get a certain ranking in previous stages in order to move on. Can you outwit the puzzles at hand and receive gold awards all around? Remember, Don''t Cross The Line!\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/3EPgNrm.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5395, '000400000014ee00', 'CTR-N-KC2E', 'The Legend of Dark Witch', 'USA', 138074980, 'eshop', '50010000026635', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/964a887f391c6b232d0c185dfaecb0ae4393b73db6d428d8d6e6c8f712a25081.jpg', 'Syega Crystals gave their powers to the people of the world, but somebody has stolen all of them...<BR>\n<BR>\nAfter all the Syega crystals are missing, the world plunges into darkness. As the dark witch Zizou, you must retrieve the missing Syega Crystals.<BR>\n<BR>\nThe Legend of Dark Witch is a 2D platform action game. Zizou can learn new attacks by defeating bosses. She will need every one of those attacks if she is going to save the world.<BR>\n<BR>\nOther Features:<BR>\n<BR>\nA magical world beautifully depicted through in-game graphics.<BR>\nDiverse levels that provide a fair challenge.<BR>\nAdditional bonuses that reward those who replay the game.<BR>\n3 difficulty modes.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/X5Kh0Up.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5396, '00040000000f5600', 'CTR-N-JZPE', 'Zombie Panic in Wonderland DX', 'USA', 130141028, 'eshop', '50010000027196', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/53ac36148b57d59b844aca9d0e00a01c22f31d582e7745e092fad7b480f99e1d.jpg', 'The Deluxe Version for Nintendo 3DS of the successful Zombie Panic in Wonderland!<BR>\n<BR>\nDon’t miss it! The game is completely renewed for this version!<BR>\nAmazing graphics!<BR>\nExtra stages and extended story!<BR>\nExclusive enemies!<BR>\nYou can use 2 different control systems which are perfectly adapted for the Nintendo 3DS!<BR>\nMaximized playability!<BR>\n<BR>\nLet’s set out on a grand adventure to save the Wonderland from the zombies destroying all in your way!<BR>\n<BR>\nThe world of the fairy tales has been invaded by a plague of strange zombies wondering and spreading an amorous and unpleasant scent. Returning home for the first time in years, Momotaro (Peach Boy) comes upon this weird scent and feels urged to get to the bottom of the problem. <BR>\n<BR>\nArmed with powerful weapons, Momotaro goes through the most popular fairy tales, where also he meets allies who help him to defeat the craziest zombies full of love you have ever seen. ', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/B35Esiz.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5397, '0004000000132b00', 'CTR-P-AYXP', 'Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL® World Duel Carnival', 'EUR', 871414628, 'eshop', '50010000023315', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3c90ce3838d46fdaeea42bf99c6994dd54213ff210e1a66e7408a64e16466a3e.jpg', 'Enter the World Duel Carnival and\ncompete against 40 opponents from\nthe Yu-Gi-Oh! Zexal universe. Defeat\nthem all to be crowned champion.\nEach playable character has their own\nunique deck allowing players to jump\nstraight into the action while more\nexperienced player can build their own\nfrom a pool of over 5,500 cards. For\nnew players there is an easy mode\nand tutorial to guide them through the\nbasic rules and techniques.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/76822bedaaf04c6a6c3c0f52d7ef13e3cf17a0571376fe0282788a76532e6473.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/fqHmdHK.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/b1Xavfx.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5398, '0004000e00186600', 'CTR-U-KMJE', 'The Legend of Dark Witch 2 Update Ver. 1.1', 'USA', 16137012, 'update', '50010000040435', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8f51719f7cbc6e23cfaaf7fe1c9a2903d5f332add42eed0a785f9fe72e4c158c.jpg', 'This is an update for The Legend of Dark Witch 2 game. This download does not contain the full version of the title. In order to use this update, you must have the full version of The Legend of Dark Witch 2.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1ea894cb3df76e41693efe07cf5b5f40d67ead317b00fb00a127506fd3f7bbe9.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/Zz5byus.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/4ksNNex.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5399, '000480044b495750', 'TWL-N-KIWP', 'Inchworm Animation', 'EUR', 4716340, 'dsiw', '50010000010047', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0f66bbdf766c7b45258e0e07750342323b063bf4e78c98b283eef65b82b649a3.jpg', 'Inchworm Animation is the\nfull-featured paint and animation\nsystem for Nintendo DSiWare.\nBeginners and professionals alike can\ncreate mind-blowing animations with\nthis incredible handheld tool!<br>\n<br>\nRecord video, stop-motion and\ntime-lapse photography. Paint on top\n(and underneath!) with transparency,\nsmooth brushes, and thousands of\ncolours.<br>\n<br>\nOther tools include onionskin, zoom,\nand a pattern editor.<br>\n<br>\nIncluded tutorials show you the\nropes. Export your finished\nmasterpieces to the SD card.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fbd63de478c789665869b0535aec1107807976d278cf3221f0fe58da690e6b07.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/35WHsPH.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/cnUu0m6.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5400, '000480044b464250', 'TWL-N-KFBP', 'GO Series: Fishing Resort', 'EUR', 5748532, 'dsiw', '50010000007186', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/08c52b7b2a50e97fc0061a08d205619fd115d2c8bdd7ab39c1092cf787431681.jpg', 'GO Series presents Fishing Resort from\nMechanic Arms.<br>\n<br>\nFeel the swing of the fishing rod as\nyou cast, the tension in the line as you\nreel in the fish and its weight as you\ncatch it with the net. Use the stylus to\nfeel every bite, tug and pull. Buy new\nrods, lines, floats and bait, take part\nin challenges and trade Member''s\nCards and Rankings with friends via\nwireless communications. Developed\nin Japan with anime graphics and style,\nFishing Resort oozes charm and is a\ndelight to play.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/aWxWvxF.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
