(5405, '000400000f702500', 'KTR-N-UAMJ', 'ロックマンX', 'JPN', 4426596, 'eshop', '50010000040219', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3be64b8ee314dbea3b1a8d6b2e03e01831086a20c5db122460ac3ce70fc8a0f5.jpg', 'このソフトは、1993年に発売されたスーパーファミコン用のアクションゲームです。\n<br>主人公エックスが、戦友であるゼロとともに、同じ部隊にいた隊長･シグマの野望を阻止するために戦います。8つのステージは好きな順番で挑戦でき、ステージの最後で待ち構えるボスを撃破すると相手の武器を入手できます。8体のボスには弱点があるので、有効な武器を探すことがクリアへの近道です。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/853844d0082c42035ab0b65bb4850f7e0355d48cc7e18736c9cfd0882d5f7946.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/gZfvQmr.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/NmLoXr7.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5406, '000480044b445645', 'TWL-N-KDVE', 'Dark Void™ Zero', 'USA', 9529140, 'dsiw', '50010000002081', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f6bce45a3e32ed7cfd9279b17b9816f5276a5febb0946619258903e31ff84e57.jpg', 'As the ‘80s were drawing to a close, the developers at Capcom began work on a top secret project that aimed to set new standards for the platformer genre. That game was called “Dark Void”. Alas, Capcom suspended development on Dark Void as it began to evaluate the SNES™. Before long, the game was shelved and drifted, unnoticed, into the annals of gaming history. Dark Void became a legendary “lost project” at Capcom.\nNow, nearly twenty years later, Dark Void is back! To commemorate the game’s humble origins, Capcom has commissioned this recreation of the original 8-bit classic, now re-titled\n“Dark Void Zero”, on the Nintendo DSi system. You play Rusty, the first human born in the Void, who must take on the Watchers in a quest to stop their domination of Earth. With the aid of Nikola Tesla, and his state-of-the-art rocket pack, Rusty must take down the Watchers and their minions across three intense levels of action and intrigue.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/t8f7qm6.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5407, '00040000000efb00', 'CTR-N-RCGE', 'Mega Man™ V', 'USA', 3996516, 'eshop', '50010000022058', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a77274f0642aab4d66acb244fd2ed5e2080f0c09f68bb857889753d0eaa18cd7.jpg', 'After another of Dr. Wily''s failed attempts at world domination, peace reigns on Earth once more. Or so it would seem...\n<br><br>\nDuring a peaceful stroll with his sister Roll, Mega Man is confronted by a powerful robot called Terra that drops from the sky! The enemy easily defeats Mega Man, then quickly dispatches an army of robots to conquer Earth.\n<br><br>\nWaking up in Dr. Light''s laboratory, Mega Man is given a new and powerful weapon to defeat the alien invasion--the Mega Arm. Now equipped to take down his enemies, Mega Man sets off to restore peace once. Use the aid of weapon upgrades and companion assists as you blast your way through waves of robotic foes, and solve the mystery behind this alien attack!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/JGHaaPJ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5408, '00040000000efe00', 'CTR-N-QAZE', 'Mega Man™ Xtreme', 'USA', 4545380, 'eshop', '50010000022075', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/397e58efb9b84b875349af4b546c852c228fcd072f51faa3fe3f5477f27ceeee.jpg', 'Many years ago, Mega Man X--a blue robot possessing a high intelligence, a kind personality, and formidable power--was found and studied by Dr. Cain. The scientist attempted to create more in the likeness of the robot, calling them "Reploids". However, some of the Reploids began to malfunction, and these were called\n"Mavericks". The "Maverick Hunters", a group of capable Reploids like Mega Man X, Zero and Sigma, was assembled to fix the situation. However, one day, Sigma revolts and hacks into the Mother Computer, causing the Mavericks to grow in power.\n<br><br>\nWith chaos brewing on the horizon, Mega Man X must join forces with Middy, a genius hacker, and his partner Zero to restore peace. Blast through the past, defeat strong robotic enemies and obtain new abilities as you clean up crime in this action-packed platformer!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/zvlQcUU.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5409, '0004000000148900', 'CTR-P-BRXP', 'Hatsune Miku: Project Mirai DX', 'EUR', 2336815972, 'eshop', '50010000036375', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/28bd578c248dd15d6782df3af6b31acd75495b8cc9c27cb145a374dfdfa81286.jpg', 'Hatsune Miku: Project Mirai DX is a\n3D rhythm action game starring the\nworld’s most famous virtual singer\nHatsune Miku. Project Mirai DX\nfeatures 48 full length versions of\nfan-favorite songs with multiple play\nstyles and game modes that people of\nany age or skill level can enjoy. Join\nthe Miku phenomenon by expressing\nyourself through fun creative tools,\nsharing your cute customizations, and\nexperiencing some of the best music\nfrom the world’s favorite digital diva!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/lxQcIxW.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5410, '00040000000f8600', 'CTR-N-TDME', 'Mighty Final Fight®', 'USA', 6576996, 'eshop', '50010000028176', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/895a5e33d1d4e88b03e3d18b447ea85f3c0f5bb387db1244bb2602a7f90b714f.jpg', 'The Mad Gear Gang has been battling with Mayor Mike Haggar for years over control of Metro City. One day, the gang of misfits takes it too far by kidnapping the mayor''s daughter, Jessica. That is one mistake that will be their undoing!\n<br><br>\nClean up the streets in five levels of intense, hard-hitting action! Choose the pro wrestler Haggar, the street brawler Cody, or the Ninjutsu master Guy, each with his unique fighting abilities and special moves. Find power-ups that will replenish health, give extra lives, or provide extra chances to keep fighting!\n<br><br>\nWeapons provide another alternative for knocking the living daylights out of the thugs that stand in your way. Join Haggar and his friends in a fight against crime as they free their loved one and the city from the evil clutches of the Mad Gear Gang.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/T6An8vA.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5411, '00040000000a4800', 'CTR-N-TBKE', 'Ninja Gaiden II™: The Dark Sword of Chaos', 'USA', 6761316, 'eshop', '50010000015913', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c9479b9363c673112e83c507fde9d0755e5b5cc6400b52d75e5a7e7434b99a28.jpg', 'Upon hearing of Jaquio''s death, a new villain Ashtar rises in the pursuit to take over the world. Guide Ryu Hayabusa in his rescue mission for Irene Lew, friend and former CIA agent. Destroy the Sword of Chaos, a weapon of great power forged from the bone of a demon. Use techniques such as the Fire Wheel or the Windmill Throwing Star and attack while holding on to walls and ladders. Utilize the most innovative technique of all--the ability to create Shadow Clones, orange shadow versions of Ryu that will constantly follow him and repeat his actions. Defeat evil henchmen, creatures, and bosses as you progress through multiple stages on your way to destroying Ashtar, the Realm of Chaos and others that may lurk in the dark...', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/At9XlK4.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5412, '00040000000a6b00', 'CTR-N-TBRE', 'Ninja Gaiden™ III: The Ancient Ship of Doom', 'USA', 6597476, 'eshop', '50010000018354', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/06503882aeb478dc0baa8517dca23dd21562f5f7846c8617e749539339154ceb.jpg', 'Join master ninja Ryu Hayabusa, last member of the famous Dragon Clan, in the third and final chapter of the legendary Ninja Gaiden saga.\n<br><br>\nRyu is framed for FBI agent Irene\n<br>Lew''s murder, and it''s up to him to clear his name. Defeating superior life-forms created out of “life energy” called BIO-NOIDs and avoiding enemy ambushes are among the many obstacles which Ryu faces in this unpredictable adventure of mystery, deceit, and destruction. Ryu''s techniques have improved from last time—his ability to grab on to horizontal surfaces, his reduced falling speed and altered jumping maneuvers, as well as using power-ups give Ryu that extra advantage against his foes.\n<br><br>\nHelp Ryu defeat the forces of evil once more and discover the real culprit behind Irene’s death as one of the most loved trilogies in video-game history comes to a close!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/gxmWQ7b.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5413, '000400000f702c00', 'KTR-N-UAQE', 'Contra III The Alien Wars', 'ALL', 5794660, 'eshop', '50010000040315', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ad858373b6d486184b0d3498d37490bcaf4899b294f02ce32f297c803b980f89.jpg', 'In the year 2636, the alien war continues on and it’s up to two soldiers, Bill Rizer and Lance Bean, to put a stop to the alien invasion. The aliens have ravaged the Earth with their powerful organic and technological weapons. Battle through 6 stages of non-stop run-and-gun action collecting power-ups including bombs, flamethrowers, spread shots, lasers and machine guns to take out the aliens. Bill and Lance travel through war-torn cities, on air bikes, riding missiles and ultimately into the alien base to defeat the alien boss once and for all.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/IpZIKBn.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5414, '0004000000169600', 'CTR-P-BDVP', 'Dragon Ball Z: Extreme Butoden', 'EUR', 378133348, 'eshop', '50010000037435', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c9bacc8b870a5abfe0748b0edd05c01be6498bf001c75790853576895636af74.jpg', 'Dragon Ball Z: Extreme Butoden is a\nfighting game including the most\nfamous characters of Dragon Ball Z\nseries. You can even play with\ncharacters from the latest movie\nDragon Ball Z: Resurrection "F".\n<br/><br/>\n2D Fighting action: Anime-like\ngraphics thanks to 2D effects.\n<br/><br/>\nHours of Gameplay: The “Story\nmode” follows the original story of the\nManga and in the “Adventure mode”\nplayers aim to gather all the Dragon\nballs. A Versus mode is also part of\nthe game to fight the computer or a\nfriend.\n<br/><br/>\nA huge Roster: More than 120\ncharacters playable/assists are\navailable.\n<br/><br/>\nCrazy Team Battle: Possibility to\nchoose 5 playable/assists characters\nfor one fight. Up to 10 characters can\nfight each other on the screen!\n<br/><br/>\nStrong moves: Enjoy variety of\nspecial moves depending on the\nsituation, Ultimate Moves and Even\nRush effects are more incredible than\never!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ce84627e50e96214a0494e2e44d807be336e9c45cbc278d81f012501ac79fe06.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/xEqpPoN.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/d9AYFIj.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5415, '000480044b555650', 'TWL-N-KUVP', 'Bloons® TD 4', 'EUR', 7068468, 'dsiw', '50010000013512', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/40b488ef158df306cc9eebb9d8f64ead0e5e1dc57d95231820e5051ccce08581.jpg', 'The monkeys are getting serious and\nare ready to take down the enemy\nfrom the land, air and sea in the style\nof classic tower defence. Utilising a\nranking system you can build up your\nexperience and gain access to\npowerful towers and upgrades. Call in\nmortar strikes, deploy the monkey\naces and harness the power of banana\nfarms as you bid to take down the\nenemy in true bloon popping fashion.\nBloons TD 4 features a mix of classic\ntracks from the online game as well as\na whole host of new tracks for you to\nmaster. The medal ranking system\nadds an extra level of difficulty to the\nchallenge. Can you battle through all\n75 rounds to earn the gold medal?', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/zJ0vuh8.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5416, '000480044b5a4f50', 'TWL-N-KZOP', 'GO Series: Undead Storm', 'EUR', 6337332, 'dsiw', '50010000009141', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f0a86dd06bbd3ecd03da458689e452c6694d32788f2c4f87822f7dd2a2b93a66.jpg', 'The explosive action is non-stop as\nyou take the fight to the zombie\nhordes.<br>\n<br>\nAfter a meteorite strike, the undead\nhave taken over the city. Play solo, or\njoin up to three friends via DS\nWireless Communications to take on\nthe killer zombies using some serious\nfirepower. Choose from four\ncharacters, face the zombies in a\nhospital, a chemical plant and the\ndowntown area, and discover the\nterrifying truth...', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/t9gM0Jl.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5417, '00040000000a5f00', 'CTR-N-AG5P', 'Paper Mario™: Sticker Star', 'EUR', 559868772, 'eshop', '50010000012486', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e584eb99daf096131578b61929c247643f8c9c4f4fdd1b14e512d7fa2b70cad0.jpg', 'Paper Mario is back, and finds\nhimself in another sticky situation!\nTake Mario on an exciting paper\nadventure and help him repair the\nmess Bowser has created using the\npowers of brand new stickers. A cast\nof colourful characters will keep you\nlaughing along the way as the familiar\nworld of Paper Mario is brought to life\nin Paper Mario: Sticker Star for\nNintendo 3DS! The visually stunning\n3D effects make it seem as though\nyou’re looking into and exploring a\nworld made up of shoebox dioramas!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/IMBoREW.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5418, '000400000007af00', 'CTR-N-ABEP', 'New Super Mario Bros.™ 2', 'EUR', 358767460, 'eshop', '50010000011307', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3b2ff1aec65f48533cd8fc6c5281a7ac0358449eb9273362514f329b21165544.jpg', 'Mario returns to Nintendo 3DS in a\nside-scrolling action adventure,\npacked with great power-ups and\ncrammed with coins! Players can\nexpect classic Mario action with a\ngolden twist - an extra challenge to\ncollect one million coins! As well as\nplaying solo, or teaming up with a\nfriend via Local Play, there''s Coin\nRush mode, where the aim is to grab\nas many coins as possible in the time\nlimit, adding a strategic edge to the\nfun!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a677ffe145c77d971574d1e3163131f4d6178b64d266d706677061da0927cfbe.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/w2a7ZIf.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/C3yBeAH.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5419, '000400000f700200', 'KTR-P-CAFP', 'Xenoblade Chronicles 3D', 'EUR', 3945581412, 'eshop', '50010000031095', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/46076b46a982471a268d682a64f4459847c0e88a0ecc8b03a2a92f07df1d9e4d.jpg', 'In a vast world of adventure, where\nthe action stretches as far as the eye\ncan see, you must battle evil in the\nsprawling RPG Xenoblade Chronicles\n3D, only for New Nintendo 3DS and\nNew Nintendo 3DS XL.\n<br/><br/>\nAn almighty crash heralded the\nsudden arrival of the Bionis and the\nMechonis to this world, for the two\ntitans were locked in a timeless\nbattle. Once the dust had settled,\nonly their corpses remained. Now, the\nBionis'' enormous body, covered in\nlush plains, is home to a developed\ncivilisation, the Homs. But life on\nBionis was not destined to flourish\nforever. One day, a horde of\nmechanical life forms from the\nMechonis launched an all-out attack\non the inhabitants of Bionis. The\nHoms'' only remaining hope is a\nlegendary sword, Monado, said to be\na gift from the titan itself.\nUnfortunately, whosoever wields the\nsword must endure a great toll on\ntheir body...\n<br/><br/>\nVisit amiibo.nintendo.eu for\ncompatible amiibo™ and the latest\ninformation. To use amiibo on\nNintendo 3DS, Nintendo 3DS XL and\nNintendo 2DS systems a\nNintendo 3DS NFC Reader/Writer is\nrequired. The Nintendo 3DS NFC\nReader/Writer will be available later\nthis year.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4adff6d72ca3858437120929cb0369813deb500f40b83aac8c190a92bd53255b.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/K5yDZBi.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/JPF0EhC.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5420, '000400000012a300', 'CTR-N-JDPJ', 'スター★シリーズ: キュートウィッチ', 'JPN', 22293348, 'eshop', '50010000021614', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1580c94f5f23cc4be8cd42937687e7cd631fc34e0cd32e32da82639a7e7106e3.jpg', 'かわいい女の子が手軽に作成できるのが特徴のゲームです。\n<br>女の子の特徴は「肌の色/目の形と色/髪型と色/シャツ/ズボン･スカート/靴/アクセサリ」といった豊富なアイテムの中から選ぶことができます。\n<br>衣装を変更してもゲームには一切影響しないので、プレイヤーの好みだけで自由に変更することが可能です。\n<br>\n<br>ゲームは障害物を避け続けるだけの、シンプルなゲーム性ですので子供でも手軽に楽しむことができます。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9ab20e5caca0e26b54bea92afc84c242d6b47e402e314727a1b2081b7ef5e4f2.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/foTHCXr.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ISDqf2X.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5421, '0004000000164b00', 'CTR-N-JWGJ', 'ガンマンストーリー2', 'JPN', 74693476, 'eshop', '50010000031036', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5176c19655dd4e92cc1da07c21ecb668ec6f366133a490c6cac092c75ee02909.jpg', '『ガンマンストーリー2』は、ガンマンの「クライブ」を操作し、ガンを片手に、ステージをクリアしていく「ガンマンアクションゲーム」です。\n<br>\n<br>ゲーム全体を彩るウェスタンテイストなビジュアルとサウンド、そしてオーソドックスなアクションが魅力です。\n<br>\n<br>宇宙から突如襲ってきた「ダークメカニック」。さすらいのガンマン「クライブ」たちのウェスタンタウンを一瞬で闇に陥れてしまう。\n<br>\n<br>手元の拳銃一丁で、行く手を阻む敵を倒し、あと、重力をあやつり(?)、パンダを乗りこなし(??)、恐竜を倒し(???)、夕日に向けて駆けるのだ!\n<br>\n<br>シンプルながらも、サプライズにあふれる「ガンマンアクションゲーム」です。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/971b111a98ab0cf21f8795285585b973139bdff04e2396ae5b36b8f4afff01ff.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/8CuCLXN.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/WSNUlKW.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5422, '00040000000fec00', 'CTR-N-TDVJ', 'ファイナルファンタジーIII', 'JPN', 6744932, 'eshop', '50010000020833', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/76c6039ece5eb1a373a823574f6c8e3b453014a42969e907b96f67d8c25a9c55.jpg', 'このソフトは、1990年に発売されたファミリーコンピュータ用のロールプレイングゲームです。\n度胸だめしに訪れた洞窟の奥でクリスタルを発見した4人の少年たちは、クリスタルの啓示により光の戦士となり、闇に包まれようとする世界を救う旅に出ます。本作では経験値によるレベルアップと、選択したジョブの熟練度により、キャラクターが成長していきます。移動中であればいつでも職業が変更できる「ジョブチェンジシステム」、召喚者のジョブによって異なる効果を発揮する「召喚魔法」などが本作で初めて登場し、のちのシリーズへと継承されていきます。高速飛行型、空海両用可変型、山を越えて飛ぶ大型飛空艇など、多彩な飛空艇も見どころのひとつです。\n', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9e76186783dbe74a0f921e867816a2be5dc2294d3597027d935534decb096a92.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/X7VdfWe.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/5hUaFEt.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5423, '000480044b575950', 'TWL-N-KWYP', 'Mighty Milky Way', 'EUR', 11449140, 'dsiw', '50010000006504', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0ac51d66efe08d8d4a6aaa6b60cb1342e6bc7a9e28b8678958212b1e35808b82.jpg', 'Are you ready to destroy some\nplanets and soar through space? With\na pocket full of planet candy and a\nlife full of boredom, green-skinned\ncutie-pie Luna needs your help to\naccomplish her secret mission!\nPrepare for fever-pitched puzzles in\nanother mighty game from\nWayForward!<br>\n<br>\nLuna uses her magical staff to create\nand destroy planets on a whim.\nExplode vicious space monsters, avoid\nsizzling electric barriers, and grab all\nthe delicious planet candy you can.\nBut watch out for the T-Rex, Luna’s\narch-nemesis! The power of his laser\neyes is matched only by the animosity\nhe has for Luna as a result of their\nsketchy past.<br>\n<br>\nBut enough incessant blathering!\nLet’s stare unblinking into the sun and\nembrace the chaotic journey that is\nlife!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1659a1b91e632e2ddc8e12c57a0c5faa98ee122368c5129af956979969551548.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/C3q0Wmr.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ZXoWpji.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5424, '000480044b533350', 'TWL-N-KS3P', 'Shantae: Risky''s Revenge™', 'EUR', 16742196, 'dsiw', '50010000006181', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/98b7b3f76ff0e96dd5079007f2d4931b033f9d6c13a11e6e54a05cc37c0ec9c9.jpg', 'This is it! The sequel to the critically\nacclaimed Shantae! Fans asked, and\nWayForward answers with a powder\nkeg of high octane, hair-whipping, hip\nshaking action available only on\nDSiWare. Shantae sets the bar even\nhigher with thousands of frames of\nanimation, huge multi-sprite bosses,\nand a quest so big it’s bursting at the\nseams.<br>\n<br>\nGuide "half-genie" Shantae through\nhaunted wastes, burning deserts,\nenchanted forests, dripping caverns\nand deadly labyrinths. Discover\nmagical attacks, brew zombie coffee,\nsave golden babies, and master the\nart of belly-dancing to transform\nShantae into more powerful creatures.\nUse your powers to foil the lady pirate\nRisky Boots and save Sequin Land\nfrom certain doom!<br>\n<br>\nWith its infectious characters,\nflirtatious humour and deliciously\noutlandish action, Shantae: Risky’s\nRevenge offers up all the\nhair-whipping, belly-dancing action\nyou can handle!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/TzaKYdG.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5425, '00040000000f7600', 'CTR-N-JPMP', 'Chibi-Robo!™ Let’s Go, Photo!', 'EUR', 514104164, 'eshop', '50010000017558', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3bb118137a9c9da6397fd309a48604398fd83fac495ae3441949003dc4e9ef14.jpg', 'The Curator dreams of immortalising\nreal-world objects as NostalJunk to\nput on display, and it’s your job as\nChibi-Robo to help him fill his\nExhibition rooms with your very own\nphotographs! Using your\nNintendo 3DS or 2DS cameras, line\nup in-game shapes with real-life\nobjects, take a snap, then watch them\nbe transformed into the coveted\nNostalJunk!\n<br/><br/>\nExplore the human world as the\nhelpful robot hero and see things from\na new – and Chibi – perspective, as\nyou meet a cast of colourful and\nhilarious characters, including a\nsushi-slinging squid, a high-flying\nsuper hero, and an eccentric pair of\nchefs. Solve their problems and clean\nup the world to earn Happy points to\nbuy Silhouette films for your camera.\nThe more happiness you spread, the\nfaster you can realise The Curator’s\ndream of having as many NostalJunk\naficionados admire his exhibits as\npossible.\n<br/><br/>\nLook out for NostalJunk Contests and\nwin exclusive costumes for Chibi-Robo\nto flaunt in-game: starting at launch,\nSpotPass contests will take place for\na limited time, and players can submit\ntheir prized photos as NostalJunk to\nNintendo!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Sav7xke.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5426, '00040000000c0700', 'CTR-N-JSHP', '3D Space Harrier', 'EUR', 12266340, 'eshop', '50010000013492', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f434b438d9adbbd6d421491da46770ea97fc287fa267f215dccd4f4b2bb6a600.jpg', 'As a resourceful, extra-terrestrial\nwarrior, your mission is to save the\npeaceful Land of the Dragons from\nvicious creatures.\n<br/><br/>\nAided by the dragons, you must use\nevery trick in the book and every skill\nat your command in order to stave off\nthese alien invaders and save the day!\n<br/><br/>\nIn addition to its all-new 3D\npresentation, 3D Space Harrier also\nfeatures touch control functionality\nand an Arcade Cabinet mode!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/79tx0OU.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5427, '000480044b504249', 'TWL-N-KPBI', 'Photo Dojo™ (Testo in italiano)', 'EUR', 2544436, 'dsiw', '50010000004643', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5428, '00040000000db500', 'CTR-N-JHJP', '3D Sonic the Hedgehog', 'EUR', 9448292, 'eshop', '50010000015396', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/41511735c81bcd75270b8e9e991a9b0f2e9c6dd23c9a40c06d94057a605f26a0.jpg', 'The evil scientist, Dr. Eggman (aka\nDr. Robotnik), has snatched the\nanimals of South Island, turning them\ninto robot slaves. Only one hero can\ndefeat Dr. Eggman and rescue the\nanimals from his vile clutches – it’s\nthe super-cool hedgehog with the blue\nspiky hair, Sonic!\n<br/><br/>\nRace at lightning speeds across\nseven classic zones as Sonic the\nHedgehog. Run and spin through\nloop-de-loops as you collect rings\nand defeat enemies on your mission to\nsave the world!\n<br/><br/>\nIn addition to its all-new 3D\npresentation, 3D Sonic The\nHedgehog™ now features Zone Select\nand the classic Spin Dash move to\nhelp you zoom through Zones and\ntake down Badniks!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/vbJrrS2.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5429, '00040000000de200', 'CTR-N-JSNP', '3D Shinobi III', 'EUR', 14621540, 'eshop', '50010000015696', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1f6d82fb561bef5cf0fd9727cfb61eaa34b8d37dfcf8ceb8d220aef7c0e9c46c.jpg', 'Joe Musashi’s sworn enemies, the\nNeo Zeed, have returned! Controlled\nby Shadow Master, a formidable ninja\ncloned from Joe’s own bloodline, the\nsyndicate holds the city captive with\nits vicious crime ring. Utilize deadly\nweapons and lethal ninja arts in order\nto stand against the hordes of\nbio-ninja and save your city!\n<br/><br/>\nIn addition to its all-new 3D\npresentation, 3D Shinobi III features a\nRound Select Mode and customizable\ninput setting which allows you to\nassign each action to specific buttons.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/D0W1vez.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5430, '0004000000157a00', 'CTR-N-JVNP', '3D After Burner II', 'EUR', 9382756, 'eshop', '50010000029255', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/743eeb1fdb5cc02a2586658a55470f107fa49b23b8dc0cfedd47ca672728930e.jpg', '3D After Burner II is a completely\nre-mastered version of the arcade\nclassic.  Pilot your F-14D fighter\nthrough enemy territory blasting away\nsquadrons of enemy fighters.  This\narcade masterpiece now features\nstereoscopic 3D, a choice of real\narcade cabinets, new difficulty\nsettings as well as visual adjustments\noptions.  Blast your way through 23\nstages to unlock a special mode with\neven more gameplay enhancements. ', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/N1zVWUf.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5431, '000480044b524756', 'TWL-N-KRGV', 'Tales in a Box: Hidden shapes in perspective!™', 'EUR', 9936692, 'dsiw', '50010000006121', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bc2ebb494d3b93b6f5b0873a198a1f02e23b47399b0d8097167bc573474672ee.jpg', 'In Tales in a Box, discover a new\nslant on hidden-object games! Via\nclever use of the Nintendo DSi\nsystem’s inner camera, you can peer\n‘into’ the screen, tilting your head to\nview a scene from different angles,\ncreating an impression of real depth.<br>\n<br>\nJourney through a fairy-tale world\npopulated by characters from famous\nfolk stories, and search each themed\ndiorama by looking around from all\nangles to find hidden letters and\nobjects.<br>\n<br>\nAs you collect letters and objects,\nyou will meet new characters and form\nwords that will open new stages with\neven more hidden items to find. Some\nstages contain secret pictures, testing\nyour observation skills even further.<br>\n<br>\nPlayers of all ages will be amazed by\nthis unique visual spectacle, where a\nsimple-looking picture can reveal a\nwhole world of stories, if you just\nknow where to look!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b2702417c15e872b57041915ef07629e7ff7cecb638ba567bdf6bc1b7840c85c.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/BADYzwH.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/NxTlt3e.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5432, '00040000000de300', 'CTR-N-JDLP', '3D Ecco The Dolphin', 'EUR', 14543716, 'eshop', '50010000017529', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d50c4ecb74ec16a36b13de07a67c06eaab6754a649b67cab6701bbc507572e15.jpg', 'After a mysterious storm sweeps your\nfamily from the sea, it’s up to you to\nfind them and uncover the mystery\nbehind the forces that took them.\n<br/><br/>\nThe search to find them will take you\nthrough vast underwater realms of\ntreachery, beauty and adventure. Use\nyour sonar to discover hidden caverns\nand unlock the secrets of crystal\nglyphs, but beware of packs of\nbloodthirsty sharks that search the\nocean for unwitting prey!\n<br/><br/>\nIn your quest, you’ll discover that\nmore than your family’s safety is at\nstake. The fate of the whole world\nrests on your wits and fins.\n<br/><br/>\nIn addition to its all-new 3D\npresentation, 3D Ecco the Dolphin\nalso features Super Dolphin Mode\nwhere your health and breath never\ndeplete!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ALR5gtC.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5433, '00040000000dc200', 'CTR-N-JA7P', '3D Altered Beast', 'EUR', 12495716, 'eshop', '50010000015453', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b675f69199de550d26901bbb17dab551ae8e90a83d7a874725a3d0901f57eb8c.jpg', 'Summoned from the dead by Zeus,\nshape shift into various beasts and\nfight off hordes of demons to rescue\nthe captured Athena from the clutches\nof Neff.\n<br/><br/>\nTransform into a variety of beasts and\nfight off throngs of demons sent forth\nby the evil Neff. The mighty\nshape-shifting god will challenge you\nin various, hideous forms in each\nlevel, but you are armed to the teeth\nwith transformative tricks of your own!\n<br/><br/>\nIn addition to its all-new 3D\npresentation, 3D Altered Beast also\nsupports local multiplayer, and a\nRandom Transformation Mode.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/1iEFlcc.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5434, '000480044b543550', 'TWL-N-KT5P', 'Topoloco - crazy about topography', 'EUR', 11002676, 'dsiw', '50010000010881', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/742c9ff0522912f24af3cf5c1dab31a0fd4dcbee6cf68be246868b31b5ba9776.jpg', 'Meet professor Topoloco. He''s\nabsolutely crazy about topography\nand he is glad to have you in his\nworld topography class! For each of\nthe 5 continents he covers you can\npractise your skills in a series of\nmini-games like locating cities and\ncountries, dragging flags, and more!\nYou can practise as much as you want\nin order to prepare for a final exam\nwhich you can take whenever you\nthink you''re ready. Topoloco is both a\nfun topography learning game and a\ndigital atlas for all ages.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/663502ce37e32a12c0c27f8dcf393cf1fe5e921534fe2fffffbe810b014c7746.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/kSpF7sR.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/rcIFDBy.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5435, '000480044b5a4250', 'TWL-N-KZBP', 'Little Red Riding Hood''s Zombie BBQ', 'EUR', 15821620, 'dsiw', '50010000006602', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9f9c483b41f0988f9269e0cb4a24fa8b5a122121f3589c754840de428b284df6.jpg', 'Can you save fairy tale land or will\nyou let its creatures live an\nunhappy-ever-after-life?<br>\n<br>\nZombie BBQ is a really fun shooter,\nwhere you have to move forward by\nshooting down every living (or dying)\ncreature in your path! Use the great\narsenal of weapons at your disposal\nto do away with the savage hordes of\nzombies.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/fYYREwK.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5436, '0004000000152400', 'CTR-N-JF8P', '3D Fantasy Zone', 'EUR', 12512100, 'eshop', '50010000030435', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2db77194a5275e6654b440dfaefa3e6400c2b22fc9fca90e2a5484d2df0e133b.jpg', '3D Fantasy Zone™ is the popular\nscrolling shooter, first released for the\nSEGA System 16 board in 1986, in\nwhich players control a sentient\nspaceship named Opa-Opa to fight\nbizarre invader enemies. The\nre-mastered version combines\nstereoscopic 3D visuals with a host of\nadditional features to deliver cutting\nedge gameplay with a classic feel.\nAdditional features include: adjustable\ndifficulty settings, the ability to save\nyour game for later review, inclusion\nof both the Japanese and Overseas\nversions of the original game, a Stage\nSelect feature that allows players to\nsave and resume progress mid-game.\n3D Fantasy Zone™ also offers players\nan unlockable mode with new\nweaponry and gameplay and an\noriginal song called UPA-UPA.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/xLitRB7.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5437, '000480044b534b56', 'TWL-N-KSKV', 'Soul of Darkness', 'EUR', 9937716, 'dsiw', '50010000006241', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9547a4430d774bb2c38e814e706f2300dc839dcd9e3b46006ffba0d4af2cfeb7.jpg', 'Enter a fascinating gothic world as\nKale: try to save your beloved''s life\nand soul from an evil vampire''s\nclutches.<br>\n<br>\nExplore dark woods and caves, huge\ncastles and cathedrals under the full\nmoon''s light. Master and upgrade\nyour sword and spear, and learn how\nto control your powers: use the Fire\nand the Ice, or transform into your\nenemies. Face and defeat werewolves,\ngargoyles, zombies, and more, thanks\nto the exclusive camera features.<br>\n<br>\nGood or evil - be the sole master of\nyour destiny!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7ff7663630fe1a29a7ac28905e512e8879ea3dbf204e927b81d8fcf9cf2f3bc8.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/U6U5snK.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ssUfdkH.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5438, '0004008c0016f200', 'CTR-M-BC4E-00', 'SAMURAI WARRIORS:\nChronicles 3 Update Ver. 1.0.2', 'USA', 27398144, 'dlc', 'none', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5439, '000400000016f200', 'CTR-N-BC4E', 'SAMURAI WARRIORS: Chronicles 3', 'USA', 2971560804, 'eshop', '50010000034795', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b46d2c70112069d523bbcabc77d06b4cacd17ac3535d9a8103bb922580885c89.jpg', 'Offers in-game purchases\n<br><br>\nSwitch between up to four playable characters in real time, and use the "Hyper Attacks" introduced in "SAMURAI WARRIORS 4" to make this the most strategically rich title in the series to date!\n<BR><BR>\nThe new "Challenge Mode" allows you to tackle a series of objectives, one after the other, with a time limit, and reach your final goal! You can even check your rankings against other warriors online!\n<BR><BR>\nWeapon upgrades, custom parts and more make this a truly immersive title. ', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/4w9azt1.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5440, '000400000012d900', 'CTR-N-JY5E', 'SteamWorld Heist', 'USA', 185932644, 'eshop', '50010000038678', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/614c1a6a76da906db39b3b0491d65a99134d52d201fd6457d11d8760b7c835b3.jpg', 'Prepare for boarding! SteamWorld Heist is a space adventure with turn-based tactical shootouts, where you aim in real time and perform awesome bullet-bouncing trick shots.\n<br><br>\nFrom the makers of SteamWorld Dig:\n<br><br>\nJoin Captain Piper Faraday, smuggler and occasional pirate, as she recruits a rag-tag team of steam-driven robots and sets out on a daring adventure. With your hearty crew, you’ll board, loot and shoot your way through enemy spaceships. Overcome the challenges of the vast frontier by upgrading your robots with unique abilities, weapons - and even stylish hats!\n<br><br>\nKey features\n<br><br>\nTurn-based strategy focused on skill rather than chance\nFree aiming lets you perform clever trick shots\nMaster 100+ weapons\nKind to newcomers, deep and challenging for veterans\nRandomly generated levels\n15-20 hours of playtime, followed by New Game+\nSteampunk tunes by legendary Steam Powered Giraffe\nFearsome bosses and a playful narrative\n60 fps and C Stick support on New Nintendo 3DS and New Nintendo 3DS XL', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/2xcnWJs.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47');
INSERT INTO `3dsgames` (`id`, `titleID`, `serial`, `name`, `region`, `size`, `type`, `contentID`, `iconURL`, `gdesc`, `thumb`, `scrcount`, `imgur_iconURL`, `imgur_thumb`, `count`, `time`) VALUES
(5441, '0004000000033400', 'CTR-N-AQEJ', 'ゼルダの伝説 時のオカリナ 3D', 'JPN', 471862116, 'eshop', '50010000006746', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7bd2e21278765c630b238347ac673e56c3569df6d3b6594064afe97bbc0c57a1.jpg', '1998年にニンテンドウ64用ソフトとして発売した『ゼルダの伝説 時のオカリナ』。ハイラルの地に語り継がれる冒険と成長の伝説が、新たに描かれたグラフィックと共に、ニンテンドー3DSで蘇ります。\n', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0a4a8a8b11605ea85e386d3118fff2265ebbe788246dfa2d6f2235c189456e09.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/XKo0njN.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/xJQ5pIg.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5442, '000480044b44524a', 'TWL-N-KDRJ', 'サクッとハマれるホリホリ アクション ミスタードリラー', 'JPN', 7414580, 'dsiw', '50010000007983', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8b42ab6ee74b1e8805744bef066cf4401604845d6494855e308c59b6667829b8.jpg', '簡単操作でブロックを掘って地底のゴールを目指す穴掘りアクションゲームです。空気の入ったエアカプセルをとりつつ、崩れ落ちるブロックをよけながら掘り進みます。\n\n自分のレベル、空いている時間、練習したいこと、その時の気分にあわせて楽しめるように、多彩なステージをご用意!初心者の方から上級者の方までどなたにも楽しんでいただくことができます。\n', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e0b5cd3bc832dfb8f4165b15c6e4f90f8e4be583849a8b46637ef8dd2553177a.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Mk0Tb9O.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/SAXft91.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5443, '0004000000186500', 'CTR-N-JT6E', 'Parascientific Escape Cruise in the Distant Seas', 'USA', 96901988, 'eshop', '50010000039735', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c3883b1c04b10cd32a223492ef344d9a554da1626132719d09ce98bb2cd8ae40.jpg', 'Hitomi Akeneno is a 16 year old high school student with a little secret - she has not one, but two psychic powers.\n<br><br>\nAfter receiving an invitation, she boards a luxury cruise ship with her friend, Chisono Shio. As soon as she enters a suite room, a loud explosion sounds...and she finds herself stuck, unable to get out. Is this an accident? Or something far more sinister...?\n<br><br>\nThe only way to find out is to escape, with the help of her powers.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/w5VmoUC.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5444, '000480044b4a5245', 'TWL-N-KJRE', 'Alt-Play: Jason Rohrer Anthology', 'USA', 5828404, 'dsiw', '50010000002430', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/73e0a8174e4938c706c7947e811f87974043e8776302c49d40d86ebb148ade4c.jpg', 'Alt-Play brings the best of independent gaming to the Nintendo DSiWare service, introducing players to some of the most unique experiences this medium has to offer. In this compilation, award-winning game auteur Jason Rohrer’s work comes to the Nintendo DSi system, including three of his best games to date: Passage, Gravitation and Between.\n\nThe deep themes contained and the manner in which they are presented in Rohrer’s work helps to blur the line between what we consider art and games, evoking thoughts and emotions rarely associated with gaming.', 'none', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/CXJ4Rtc.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5445, '000480044b575145', 'TWL-N-KWQE', 'Whack-A-Friend', 'USA', 2005812, 'dsiw', '50010000003566', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/67305576cb182a8afaac405c7b36d5f048a36a1ec72864f5c91502db1276fd5e.jpg', 'Revenge has never been so fun!\n\nThe player is able to use their Nintendo DSi system to capture a picture of their friend or anything else they desire. The picture will be used as targets that pop up from various holes and the player must use the stylus to tap them back into their holes. The faster this can be done, and without making mistakes, the more combos are achieved. As the player continues earning combos, the picture displayed on the top screen will begin to display graphical changes, such as bruises, bugs, black eyes, bandages, and scars. The simple game design and easy, intuitive controls make it a game that the whole family can enjoy.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/AQlfZbY.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5446, '000480044b535245', 'TWL-N-KSRE', 'Aura-Aura Climber™', 'USA', 4865844, 'dsiw', '50010000003801', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4f9e72aae8ad2464319456b49805a863b79772b252446522a4d27fe6f2fb4be6.jpg', 'Aura-Aura has fallen out of the sky and landed on Earth! He is determined to return to his rightful place in the universe and become a bright star. Take control of Aura-Aura, and help him to accomplish this by using his grapple arm to grab a variety of grapple points and continuously climb higher in the sky. Along the way, collect items to aid him (bombs, extensions for his grapple arm) and avoid enemies that damage Aura-Aura’s health. Two modes of play offer very different challenges: Score Attack, in which you try to get to the goal with as many points as possible, and Endless, in which your aim is simply to help Aura-Aura climb as high into the sky as possible within the time limit. And even if you think you’ve mastered the art of climbing, both modes offer numerous medals to find or earn by completing specific tasks. With its intuitive controls, straight forward game play, and incredible replay value, Aura-Aura’s journey is arcade-style gaming at its best...or should that be its highest?\n\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/o1aZM4u.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5447, '000480044b4d4454', 'TWL-N-KMDT', 'Master of Illusion™ Express: Matchmaker', 'USA', 2599732, 'dsiw', '50010000004384', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0d413a634b8c9c0fc636dc24d43702b68709c59b0d2c026c51f50bec12b6cc62.jpg', 'Master of Illusion Express titles are mind-boggling magic tricks that you perform with your Nintendo DSi system. Learn the illusions, practice up, and then amaze your friends. Master of Illusion Express: Matchmaker includes two tricks that use your Nintendo DSi system as a way of revealing information about others. Use the Photo Diagnosis trick and stun others when only taking two simple photos pinpoints their exact age. Or have the Matchmaker trick show that another person has similar choices for favorite dates or favorite foods as you do—who knows, you could even land a date or make a new friend!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/rJlZvTk.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5448, '000480044b465045', 'TWL-N-KFPE', 'Flipper', 'USA', 7654196, 'dsiw', '50010000002121', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/179f16e023cf717641a4a1cb5d8d4eba372ba2f1fd1e678b1596f64d58dfdd44.jpg', 'The hero of the game is a courageous young boy. You  must lead him through various worlds full of obstacles to retrieve his stolen goldfish called Flipper! Get ready for a 3D puzzle platform game set over 4 different worlds with 5 levels each! The game features beautiful pixel-art backdrops, cheerful cartoon characters and catchy music. The voxel engine technology allows you to change the environment with some cool power-ups. You can pick up power-ups that let you blast holes in the environment while other power-ups restore it or build platforms. It''s up to you to use the limited amount of power-ups wisely to complete each level. Flipper is a fun and challenging puzzle game that is suited for all ages.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/bnLx9yy.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5449, '000480044b494f45', 'TWL-N-KIOE', '1001 BlockBusters', 'USA', 6075188, 'dsiw', '50010000007681', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3a29e4a30b3e893bc29abb2d536252eef461632f2e257c2f7214584288a1449f.jpg', 'Think you''ve seen the ultimate brick-breaking game? Think again! Enjoy classic gameplay, amazing graphics and surprising bonuses as you smash through 1001 levels of blockbusting excitement! Use the stylus to catch, bounce and bust balls through complex constructions in four eye-popping worlds: Stone Age, Ancient Greece, Candy World, and Fantasy Forest. Beat your best score by collecting wild power-ups, including weapons, magnetic paddles, shields and more. But watch out for hidden hazards and booby traps—unless you like extra-small paddles and crazy camera angles! With over a dozen bonuses, 300 kinds of blocks and 1001 incredible levels, 1001 BlockBusters is non-stop, no-holds-barred, action-packed fun!\n\nFeatures:\n- 1001 levels in four different worlds (Ancient Greece, Stone Age, Candy World and Fantasy Forest)\n- More than 15 power-ups and power-downs\n- Three shooter types\n- Eye-catching graphics\n- Three game modes\n- High score list', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/YXOfOvk.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5450, '000480044b535945', 'TWL-N-KSYE', 'System Flaw Recruit', 'USA', 5949236, 'dsiw', '50010000003806', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b4c1b84fca9ae159b2bff5623626d024cea66873bf277a766dba6a07a7061d1d.jpg', 'This innovative, action shooter uses the Nintendo DSi Camera to turn your surroundings into the playing environment! Your Nintendo DSi system turns into a weapon against attacking enemies! Truly unique and totally physical with 360 degrees of intensity, System Flaw Recruit is the future of handheld gaming excitement. You have been chosen to take part in the most arduous training program to combat the threat we call the Flaw. The invasion could take place at any time, so we need the best there is!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/VF088fj.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5451, '000480044b424c45', 'TWL-N-KBLE', 'Bloons®', 'USA', 6696756, 'dsiw', '50010000001601', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/416a48edbf7c7636689d4e4e70cd818fa1e57da48bab672831e8936c79cc4083.jpg', 'BLOONS is an exciting puzzle game based on the simple fact that popping balloons is fun. Pop your way through dozens of puzzling levels in this exciting puzzle adventure. Each level will have a different arrangement of balloons - try to pop as many as you can with the darts you are given. Look out for special balloons, blocks and darts, and have fun discovering what they do. Bloons is a great game that you can pick up and play for a few minutes while you’re in line at the store, or you can sit on the couch for hours as you work your way through the 70 levels included in the game. And as an added bonus, we’ve included a level editor where you can create your own balloon puzzles!', 'none', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/q8HuWEg.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5452, '000480044b474e45', 'TWL-N-KGNE', 'Gangstar 2: Kings of L.A.', 'USA', 11680564, 'dsiw', '50010000002461', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f96a124d6da18ca552cd29f976f9d4574493b3e458ae0cef2e3f75d70a01da71.jpg', 'Move to the West Coast and immerse yourself in Los Angeles gang life with Gangstar 2: Kings of L.A. Complete 75 different missions that combine the best of action games and driving games.\n\n- Explore Los Angeles and its famous neighborhoods, including Hollywood, Beverly Hills, downtown, the suburbs and the harbor.\n- A unique feeling of freedom: drive or walk anywhere in massive, open environments. Feel free to complete missions at your own pace, or just do absolutely anything you want.\n- A thrilling storyline with flashbacks and unexpected developments: go from rags to riches, connect with relatives and help out their gang until you’re living the golden life.\n- Improved driving experience: drive cars, quads, motorcycles and use the environment to perform unbelievable stunts.\n- Use the inner camera or outer camera to decrease your wanted status, take a new photo of your face and fake your ID card to remain incognito.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/xrCyjE5.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5453, '000480044b594945', 'TWL-N-KYIE', 'myDiary™', 'USA', 1679156, 'dsiw', '50010000004764', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b77b520a577f4d87d6ef1d9474ee5f63fec94609cc97e0a9da1da8487b693e74.jpg', 'myDiary allows you to keep your own personal diary on your Nintendo DSi system. Just open your Nintendo DSi system, tap on a day, and write a note! Set alarms for important events. You can even lock your notes away from prying eyes.\n\nTry keeping track of important dates, to do lists and more! You can even personalize myDiary with 12 different unlockable themes and ink colors. Use the stylus as a pencil to make your notes or doodles and then erase the bits you don''t like. myDiary will help you organize your life.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/NKGiiS5.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5454, '000480044b505445', 'TWL-N-KPTE', 'Link ''n'' Launch™', 'USA', 4693812, 'dsiw', '50010000003177', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1f31a78b0d8d798dda4bbd43c75abc51cd41abb50f3a6d2e623c05ce8ad6031a.jpg', 'Take your puzzle-solving skills to new heights in Link ‘n’ Launch, a puzzle game in which you move tiles to create a path that connects fuel to your rocket, blasting it through space. Complete the basic training mode to learn how to play Link ‘n’ Launch, and then buckle in for the ride through the robust Missions and Puzzles modes. Missions mode has you propelling the rocket through space to reach the target planet within the three-minute time limit, while Puzzles mode challenges you to clear all fuel and pipe tiles from the screen. In both modes, not only do you need to create a path to keep your rocket fueled, but you’ll have to also account for immovable tiles and special tiles that add parts to upgrade your rocket or give you additional time to complete the level. All while keeping your rocket’s flight path within the established boundaries. The countdown to launch has started—are you prepared?', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/u5cL4hC.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5455, '000480044b585545', 'TWL-N-KXUE', 'Publisher Dream', 'USA', 5323572, 'dsiw', '50010000014392', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e59f1084ef5dfb57627cb46964d3620565cb1895cbcbf3853cb65567c7c3365d.jpg', 'Ever dream about making and publishing your digital games? Now you can!\n<br><br>\nPublisher Dream is a simulation game that places you in the owner’s seat of a company called "Triangle". Triangle focuses on a digital platform called\n"cShop" for development and publishing endeavors.\n<br><br>\nYou can hire people to develop various game genres, and control the game budgets and quality to safeguard limited resources. Do you want to be one of the biggest publishers on cShop? This may be a great way to test your skills before you actually starting your own game company.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/vuH9VTk.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5456, '000480044b345445', 'TWL-N-K4TE', 'Foto Face™: The Face Stealer Strikes', 'USA', 14692148, 'dsiw', '50010000000881', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0657dca60cf0a2558639499cff8fe0658b647b83e813d39f3e1303a681e8fc36.jpg', 'Your face, your game, you’re the hero! In Foto Face: The Face Stealer Strikes YOU get to be in the game! Using the camera and microphone, you become the hero in your own game! Unlock a variety of hero costumes as you battle the baddies, search for stars, and solve platforming puzzles. The Face Stealer has stolen your identity and is creating trouble—and everyone is blaming you. You have to track him down across 15 action-packed stages. Along the way, you’ll come across many memorable creatures, both friend and foe. Use the camera and microphone to create faces and voices for every character in your game. Foto Face: The Face Stealer Strikes—a game starring YOU!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/1Wb0fhA.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5457, '000480044b414545', 'TWL-N-KAEE', 'Ancient Tribe', 'USA', 6260532, 'dsiw', '50010000001222', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/28b04cb21d7af18aa4bdecadb1d3a798d07eca25ada9af0436fbb2de9492e05c.jpg', 'In the ancient world of Savage, you play the god of an ancient tribe in this real-time strategy game. Expand your village by guiding its inhabitants on the hunting grounds to find food and resources. Use them to upgrade your village and increase its population. When the primitive tribe develops to a certain level, they will build a temple to pay tribute to your mightiness. You can recruit new troops and research new classes of tribal people by upgrading the existing tribe''s equipment and technology. Besides improving your tribe you can improve your godly powers by sacrificing some of your tribesmen and resources. On the hunting ground your tribe will explore forests, deserts, volcanoes and frozen lands. They will meet various kinds of beasts such as boars, elephants and even dinosaurs. You can help trap and tame them so your tribe can ride on them as part of your army and hunting troop. ', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/eCYjvMW.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5458, '000480044b584845', 'TWL-N-KXHE', 'Extreme Hangman 2', 'USA', 4933428, 'dsiw', '50010000007038', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7d7447629ccfa638b00588c2facce1b3e19dab8fb82ffc4a2328fb39f1a88538.jpg', 'Extreme Hangman 2 is coming! New categories, worlds, animations, and backgrounds are waiting just for you. The goal in Extreme Hangman 2 is to save the hangman by guessing the word. If you guess the word, the hangman lives. If you guess wrong, the hangman dies. You only have a limited number of times you can miss, so guess carefully! The sequel Extreme Hangman 2 boasts over 3000 words in 14 totally new categories, with 10 funny animations and 4 eye-catching backgrounds to choose from. Check your skill and try to save the hangman by guessing words in three difficulty levels.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/UMudNxd.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5459, '000480044b4d5445', 'TWL-N-KMTE', 'Nintendo DSi™ Metronome', 'USA', 1485620, 'dsiw', '50010000002943', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f7c9f3d02fb6adfb4360d94519beb887cddf01341ec2e17295fe0638b5d3de6c.jpg', 'The Nintendo DSi Metronome software can be used to help keep tempo—when playing an instrument, for example. It creates a rhythm by playing sounds based on beat and tempo settings, which both allow a wide range of possible adjustments. In addition, choose from three metronome designs (including one based on Nintendo’s Game & Watch: Ball title!) and record your own beat sounds for the metronome to use. Or, if you want to take a break, enjoy a unique minigame: Donkey Kong Metronome, in which you make sounds into the microphone to match the beat and have Mario jump over Donkey Kong’s barrels. ', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/154PrfG.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5460, '000480044b515645', 'TWL-N-KQVE', 'BOOKSTORE DREAM', 'USA', 4428596, 'dsiw', '50010000011806', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/85b45a631d36123f3b4af0590c671fc6adda11f8c41f93c6ec9134d372f48e73.jpg', 'Ever had a dream of owning you own bookstore? Now you can!\n\nBookstore Dream is a simulation game that allows you to manage your lovely bookstore. \n\nGet connected with publishers and put the best books on your shelf! Be sure to keep stocks at a good level when demands go up! If you do everything right you will become a well-known brand in the community!\n\nGame Features:\n\nManagement is not an easy task, you have to choose what books fit your store the best! Can you handle it?\n\nCreate a good running bookstore and become rich!\n\nWant demand soaring through the roof? Get authors to your store to meet and greet their fans!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/MoVva2u.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5461, '000480044b4c4e45', 'TWL-N-KLNE', 'Bloons® TD', 'USA', 4335412, 'dsiw', '50010000007939', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/86678f5062bcbfe2be5686e52a0cdf5249157c81b2ff50b3e5638db6f89c1c2f.jpg', 'It is time, once again, to achieve total Bloon popping satisfaction, this time in the form of classic tower defense. With a whole army of dart monkeys and a multitude of towers at your disposal, can you pop all of the Bloons® before they escape?\n\nBloons® TD features all of your favorite towers and upgrades including the almighty Super Monkey! Can you battle your way through 50 challenging levels taking place over 15 exciting tracks and unlock all of the gold medals to become the TD master? Good luck!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Y6CD0fG.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5462, '000480044b474b45', 'TWL-N-KGKE', 'Glory Days - Tactical Defense', 'USA', 6201140, 'dsiw', '50010000002432', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ccea6c8290b8ffaa5b417defcd57f6fff607fa0d9c4722ecdfdd211768977966.jpg', 'TIME TO GET TOUGH!\nThe howling sandstorms blaze across the barren plains. A violent storm is brewing on the horizon. Get ready to repel the waves of enemies amidst the finely orchestrated chaos.\n\nEXPERIENCE 3D COMBAT ACTION\nAs the ground trembles, artillery is being massed in the distance. If you are outnumbered by the enemy, move your units to high ground for a strategic advantage.\n\nVERSATILITY, RESPONSIVENESS\nUse your AAA to shoot down enemy planes, fight off tanks with your guns, and sink subs with your missile launchers. Master the battlefield by using the "Big One," a gun that will terrify and cause devastation among all units, enemies and friends alike.\n\nMORE INTENSE, MORE TACTICAL\nExpect your units to suffer losses under enemy fire! Repair and improve them because the show must go on. When the dust settles, you may have attained glory, even if the battle is lost.\n\nSPECIAL FEATURES\n3D field management\n60 frames/second 3D engine\nDynamic music\nUp to 300 units in real time', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/rDCazdh.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5463, '000480044b5a4645', 'TWL-N-KZFE', 'Zoo Frenzy', 'USA', 11276084, 'dsiw', '50010000004770', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fa222da664448cb8647662a7ee9608592010483f26a2906ea08b5be215194930.jpg', 'Create the zoo of your dreams and try to maximize your profit by managing tons of parameters! Enjoy five fun mini-games to train and support your Animals: feed them, heal them and even play soccer or hockey themed games with them! Your best trained pets will go back into the wild to fight dangerous monsters and find new cute animals for your zoo! Enjoy use of the microphone and inner camera: wake up the hero by shouting at him and see yourself in the game!(Content available in English, French, and Spanish.)', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/4fJqNhn.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5464, '000480044b534b45', 'TWL-N-KSKE', 'Soul of Darkness', 'USA', 9937716, 'dsiw', '50010000003721', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5e0bfccd247541cc67401320fbb82a6933d9888df52c285430539568b7d15bdb.jpg', 'Enter a fascinating gothic world as Kale, a mysterious, powerful man. Try to save your beloved''s life and soul and get her out of an evil vampire''s clutches. Explore dark woods and caves, huge castles and impressive cathedrals under the full moon''s light. Master and upgrade your sword and spear, and learn how to control your powers: use the Fire and the Ice, or transform into your enemies to get over the numerous obstacles in your way. Face and defeat werewolves, succubi, gargoyles, zombies, and more. Thanks to the exclusive camera features, use your environment to gain power-ups and upgrades, and become the hero himself! Good or evil—be the sole master of your destiny!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/2wHnHl8.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5465, '000480044b575445', 'TWL-N-KWTE', 'GO Series Defense Wars', 'USA', 3559220, 'dsiw', '50010000004784', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f0974b2794e5d78e8ee02f8b838559cfbd126ccd28603dfbdb4e4d8a1917ce49.jpg', 'Defend your base from attack until the reinforcements arrive! Take control of a mini arsenal of weapons and fight off wave after wave of enemy attack. Hold your base until the reinforcements arrive by flicking bullets and bombs at the oncoming enemies using the stylus. Arm your base with guns, cannons and tanks in preparation for the onslaught and then attack with everything you’ve got. Your mission is to survive... Good luck!\n\n\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ixaKR9R.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5466, '0004000000175b00', 'CTR-N-KWPE', 'Word Puzzles by POWGI', 'USA', 9841508, 'eshop', '50010000039476', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ad1d25f2937daa92c574a3052a65ac2e3819b0a63a550e2d8aab031a14012405.jpg', 'Purchase this game at full price through Nintendo eShop and get a free digital version of Word Puzzles by POWGI for Wii U. The same Nintendo Network ID must be linked to your Wii U and Nintendo 3DS systems as well as your eShop account prior to purchase in order to be eligible for the offer.\n<br><br>\nEnjoy more great POWGI word puzzles with this bumper collection of six new games!\n<br><br>\nSolve hundreds of pencil-and-paper style puzzles using the stylus and intuitive touch-screen controls.\n<br><br>\nGet extra challenges by touching any amiibo™ to generate special puzzles, just for you!\n<br><br>\nThe puzzles included are:\n<br><br>\nWord Maze\nLike a wiggly word search! Find the words and solve the maze!\n<br><br>\nMixups\nA fiendishly difficult anagram puzzle with three words all jumbled together!\n<br><br>\nOne Word\nThe word search puzzle where there''s only one word to find!\n<br><br>\nFlowers\nPlant pairs of letters around the flower to grow six words with a common middle.\n<br><br>\nCircles\nThree overlapping circles hide three connected words. Find the missing letter to unscramble them all!\n<br><br>\nCrossovers\nCrossword puzzles with only one letter missing, which come together to solve a clue!\n<br><br>\nPOWGI puzzles are all expertly hand-crafted for your enjoyment and puzzling pleasure!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/gukVHR8.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5467, '000480044b4a5945', 'TWL-N-KJYE', 'JellyCar 2', 'USA', 15108916, 'dsiw', '50010000002983', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/966b439fce2dd5640ccc2dc5118519d3715337ba883a59d3edbf72c6eb487923.jpg', 'JellyCar 2, the hit driving platform game is here and fully loaded with more than 30 levels, three game modes, and much more! Post high scores, best times and longest jumps in the Hall of Fame. With so much squishy goodness, you’ll want to drive JellyCar 2 all around town!\n\nClassic:\nDrive your squishy car and use your special abilities to drive through squishy worlds!\n\nFactory:\nWhere does all this squishy goodness come from? The Jelly Factory, of course! In this puzzle game your goal is to guide the falling parts into matching chutes. Tap the levers to open different pathways to guide each part down the conveyor belts.\n\nLong Jump:\nYou’re going for distance, so go for speed! Watch out for objects that can slow you down, and look for objects that can help give you a boost!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/hDmGz9p.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5468, '0004000000163f00', 'CTR-N-KDVE', 'Dragon Fantasy: The Volumes of Westeria', 'USA', 85883748, 'eshop', '50010000035695', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4657f11b5aef9ec7e113b83460c07e99c6f06100fd73263946d871b86e48c9ef.jpg', 'Get a free download code for the Wii U digital version of the Dragon Fantasy: The Volumes of Westeria game with the purchase of the Nintendo 3DS version. \n<BR><BR>\nOffer applies to US, Canada, and Mexico only.\n<BR><BR>\nExperience an all-new old adventure! Fight your way through hordes of strange, silly, and scary monsters! Explore the caves, castles, and dungeons of an ancient evil! Meet warriors, princes, pirates, zombies, and crazy old woodsmen in a huge world of epic retro adventure! Authentic 8-bit artwork and an original soundtrack by renowned Bay Area 8-bit musician Crashfaster keeps the game true to its retro roots.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/8wKJbbA.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5469, '0004000000064200', 'CTR-N-JEXJ', 'ピクロスe', 'JPN', 9943908, 'eshop', '50010000007079', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f09e26e0c136452342f149a3cdd9f7d5c74dba918df0f392556b3a320b712230.jpg', '1995年以降、任天堂ブランドのゲームソフトとしてシリーズ展開された、数字をヒントにイラストを完成させる「ピクチャークロスワードパズルゲーム」です。\n<br>シンプルで分かりやすいルールで、誰でも手軽に楽しめます。\n<br>本作では新たにナビゲーション機能が搭載され、より快適に解けるようになりました。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d7ef004ea0d690fb1081c92745405dfece54219eb4df1d602404cee282d7a1f8.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Yhl4faD.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/yefl0Se.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5470, '0004000000084600', 'CTR-N-JP2J', 'ピクロスe2', 'JPN', 18561892, 'eshop', '50010000008442', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8349f927d1dd96cc5bc1f475b01ee8ef1b9b4ea2be6a63ef8c165b97e0aabe2c.jpg', 'ナビゲーション機能を搭載し、より快適に楽しめるようになったピクロス「ピクロスe」の続編です。本作では、前作同様150問の新規問題に加え「ミクロス」というまったく新しい遊びを提供します。\n<br>『ピクロス』は、数字をヒントにイラストを完成させる「ピクチャークロスワードパズルゲーム」です。シンプルかつ分かりやすいルールで、誰でも手軽に楽しめます。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8be7d59f1b3a496e06d488e92773944dbc16eb36c62b6ed8690048f53df39784.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/WsgiwNF.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/a5kpAx8.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5471, '0004000000139e00', 'CTR-N-KPQJ', 'ピクロスe5', 'JPN', 18029412, 'eshop', '50010000023015', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/82e45f186438a7bfccbda31ce7c434a047208c34276504b425b5a76b18b17cbf.jpg', 'ナビゲーション機能を搭載した、ピクロスeシリーズの第5弾です。\n<br>前作から引き続き「ミクロス」「メガピクロス」「20×15ピクロス」の全モードを搭載。\n<br>充実の完全新作問題150問以上をじっくりと遊べます。\n<br>チュートリアルやルールのカスタムも充実。\n<br>シリーズ初心者の方でも安心してプレーしていただけます。\n<br>『ピクロス』は、数字をヒントにイラストを完成させる「ピクチャークロスワードパズルゲーム」です。\n<br>シンプルで分かりやすいルールで、誰でも手軽に楽しめます。\n<br>また、過去の『ピクロスe』シリーズのセーブデータがあれば、追加のスペシャル問題が遊べます。\n<br>※スペシャル問題は『ピクロスe』『ピクロスe2』『ピクロスe3』のセーブデータがあれば追加されます。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f98161a0c9c8c06ac60d82ff5c257e3484f0b7f861cc98e69ffb70eca28f952a.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/6Y3xGDg.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/iOtDc3T.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5472, '000400000015e200', 'CTR-N-KP6J', 'ピクロスe6', 'JPN', 22346596, 'eshop', '50010000028964', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d3262fce30ad443653c8944cecbc11280186c580d935a563e2f05bae55f87d29.jpg', 'ナビゲーション機能を搭載した『ピクロスe』シリーズの第6弾です。\n<br>本作から1つの問題をピクロスとメガピクロスお好きなモードを選んで遊べるようになりました。\n<br>スペシャル問題を含めると実質300問の問題を楽しめます。\n<br>また、パズル解答画面の塗りアニメーションを選択できるようになりました。\n<br>『ピクロス』は、数字をヒントにイラストを完成させる「ピクチャークロスワードパズルゲーム」です。\n<br>シンプルで分かりやすいルールで、誰でも手軽に楽しめます。\n<br>本作も『ピクロスe』『ピクロスe2』『ピクロスe3』のセーブデータがあれば、追加のスペシャル問題が追加されます。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d00e2b42659993bbbac334cd0977c803bab7b8b671b6cf3a9cc3c953cbb1d17d.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/G2dm7ej.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/rZjwXxE.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5473, '000480044b4e3556', 'TWL-N-KN5V', 'myNotebook: Carbon™', 'EUR', 2708276, 'dsiw', '50010000004485', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/36de2dd141644cd8f9b8f738f11ea78300996f1f6bc35574375c2bf9031064e6.jpg', 'myNotebook allows you to take\nnotes wherever you are. Just pop open\nyour Nintendo DSi and jot down your\nthoughts! Make a list and cross it off.\nOr even play your favourite pen and\npaper games (games not included).<br>\n<br>\nYou can even personalise your\nnotebook by drawing on the cover and\nchanging the paper type with 24\ndifferent unlockable squared and lined\npaper styles.<br>\n<br>\nUse the pen or pencil to make your\nnotes or doodles and then erase the\nbits you don''t like. With 5 ink colours\nyou''ll always be able to make your\nnotes and doodles look stylish.<br>\n<br>\nmyNotebook also includes 128\npages to write on and the ability to\nexport your pages to your Nintendo\nDSi Photo Album!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b48f4d285326c22b0ef0ac60a08e108fe43962b56ecca61816e561a271c63e06.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/tuqA4bM.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/7q0fu9T.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5474, '000480044b454456', 'TWL-N-KEDV', 'ELECTROPLANKTON™ Sun-Animalcule', 'EUR', 4121396, 'dsiw', '50010000003102', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7185c832b9e06914801d717301547f8ef4c74d7a65557b53603275e157b739c1.jpg', 'Dive into a unique audio-visual\nexperience where technology meets\nart. Created by multimedia musician\nToshio Iwai, Electroplankton are living\naquatic ''instruments'' that you interact\nwith to produce a variety of sounds\nand images limited only by your\nimagination!<br>\n<br>\nSun-Animalcule start life as eggs,\nemitting lights and sounds as they\nprogress through their brief life cycle.\nTheir pitch changes depending on\nwhere they grow. Experience their\nrapid growth from morning to night;\nwhen they are replaced by\nmoon-shaped Falcato.<br>\n<br>\nUse Performance mode to create\nyour own unique compositions, or\nrelax with Audience mode and let the\nElectroplankton run wild.<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously-released software.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b5a901f6aa948cea44da8d77233faf0cc5178318e8b2a35461ceedeb94ab0f73.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/1Xk0WcI.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/JOkyTZ2.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5475, '00040000000c5a00', 'CTR-N-MA8P', 'The 3D Machine Series: Episode 1', 'EUR', 29444916, 'eshop', '50010000012617', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bc591821cc912d55ed9cf3baf9d73ca067512a044984ae45c78ca9b01f5b1e66.jpg', 'A giant lizard wreaks havoc in a\nJapanese metropolis. Igor and the\nprofessor must chase this menacing\nmonster through the concrete jungle\nin order to zap it back to its comic\nbook.\n<br/><br/>\nLength 2:30 min', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bc1ce02521266806eab433f1e4e12ebe4d0ec659c5a30372b43ab34c85177b2c.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/70rThuq.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/KwvYi6w.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5476, '00040000000bc200', 'CTR-N-JAPP', 'AERO PORTER™ ', 'EUR', 34134884, 'eshop', '50010000012615', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6a0df8846e8c585c200054736e2da35cd03c9d11c5b245f4a5b05ae766871b32.jpg', 'LEVEL-5 and Yoot Saito, from\nVIVARIUM Inc., team up to bring you\nAERO PORTER, an airport simulation\nand puzzle game that will have you\nsorting luggage, expanding your\nairport''s operations and avoiding\nsecurity mishaps!\n<br/><br/>\nAs your airport gains passengers and\nprestige, you''ll be faced with more\nand more planes to load and luggage\nto colour code. And that''s to say\nnothing of all the special requests and\nsuspicious packages you''ll have to\ndeal with!\n<br/><br/>\nIt''s your job to put your airport on\nthe map to help it grow from a few\nsleepy regional terminals to a bustling\ninternational hub. Exchange aircraft\nwith your friends via StreetPass, get\nthose planes loaded and check your\nluggage on time!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/PAoTKSu.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5477, '000480044b5a4156', 'TWL-N-KZAV', 'ZENONIA®', 'EUR', 13774644, 'dsiw', '50010000006601', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d75d68d4ec0e356084ee0d7753b6a1fc6297a9dc373eb378c035a1e0d00d394f.jpg', 'ZENONIA features anime style\ncharacters and graphics with numerous\nquests following an epic storyline\nwhich offers playing time of over 40\nhours to conquer the quests. The\nplayer can choose from 3 different\nclasses; warrior, paladin and assassin,\nand customize attributes. The game\nprovides hundreds of different\nweapons and skill trees. The game\nalso provides items that can be\ncollected from 5 different classes\n(normal, magic, rare, unique and epic)\nto enchant or combine them for\nupgrades. <br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously released software.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/98c75db9339bbc11fa3051406884c5d247b95fee77f177f0d2a051fe1dd7a7a2.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/NJuWiGb.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/jO43LJ1.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5478, '000400000015b400', 'CTR-N-JEJP', 'Excave II: Wizard of the Underworld', 'EUR', 77433700, 'eshop', '50010000033135', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fe01cb3544c78c858d1a39c64ce2a1b46b69522df4de712f3fd397e33901fc0b.jpg', 'Excave II : Wizard of the Underworld\nis the exciting sequel to the Excave\nDungeon RPG.\n<br/><br/>\nBring back order to the Imperial City\nby crushing a wide varied of\nmonstrous foes and discovering the\ncause of chaos!\n<br/><br/>\nDiscover hundreds of weapons and\nitems as you embark on a quest which\nis bigger, more varied and challenging\nthan ever before!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5e2a4398c61d9452325daa8737e69802f253b93252b79a0dbb1df0b411f98af5.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Dc5Xc01.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/JlqqW1F.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5479, '0004000000100500', 'CTR-P-AVSP', 'Professor Layton vs. Phoenix Wright: Ace Attorney', 'EUR', 1732332388, 'eshop', '50010000020393', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e348661e81b99b6e27e21d444bc20d3e241681b573dff600552d762a0087228b.jpg', 'The puzzle professor and the ace\nattorney unite in Professor Layton vs.\nPhoenix Wright: Ace Attorney, only on\nNintendo 3DS! Solve puzzles to\ninvestigate as Professor Layton,\npresent evidence to the judge as\nPhoenix Wright, and crack the\nultimate case!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fdba5bffae16b9035db6884fe2310363b3c35c87f4713cac002d0d614a7355ea.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/g84rTHB.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/NCmgkIx.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5480, '0004000000186000', 'CTR-N-JT6P', 'Parascientific Escape Cruise in the Distant Seas', 'EUR', 97061732, 'eshop', '50010000039501', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/727b4ae4ded0aa789930e79057d21ac88e279fec1abb221befe283b4fd59dfe0.jpg', 'Hitomi Akeneno is a 16 year old high\nschool student with a little secret -\nshe has not one, but two psychic\npowers.\n<br/><br/>\nAfter receiving an invitation, she\nboards a luxury cruise ship with her\nfriend, Chisono Shio. As soon as she\nenters a suite room, a loud explosion\nsounds…and she finds herself stuck,\nunable to get out. Is this an accident?\nOr something far more sinister…?\n<br/><br/>\nThe only way to find out is to\nescape, with the help of her powers.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/RfmhVr1.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5481, '00040000000ead00', 'CTR-N-AK8E', 'Kokuga', 'USA', 34716564, 'eshop', '50010000014944', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/82342c75faca63ba0bb1e5bf41bd1915770ee4b60bc90334054986a933cfed45.jpg', 'After months of bitter conflict with its neighbor, country A is preparing to unleash its latest machine of war, code-named Kokuga. With access to 9 destructive weapons and an array of power-ups, the compact mobile tank is an elite military machine.\n<br><br>\nHighly-reputed boutique game studio G.rev is pleased to offer this old-school strategic shooter for the Nintendo 3DS.\n<br><br>\nPlayers are tasked with piloting Kokuga, and must destroy tanks, drones, gun towers and other mecha in 12 different training missions. Each stage culminates with a boss fight, pitting the player against massive heavily-armed bosses. Upon receiving orders for active duty, the player is thrust into action against enemy forces.\n<br><br>\nStructured so gamers have maximum freedom in their game experience, Kokuga is great for both casual game sessions or long challenges.\n<br><br>\nLocal and Download Play is supported, so assemble your squad of up to four players! Develop new strategies and help out your teammates by coordinating card use.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/40WbhAH.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5482, '000480044b505145', 'TWL-N-KPQE', 'GO Series Picdun', 'USA', 12186420, 'dsiw', '50010000006864', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b3849876195e071ba1cbcb4cdef041eb0ffedfd6650c7eaa54bfa51926a8cd7e.jpg', 'PICture DUNgeon is a very unique action RPG. Every step you take to explore the dungeon will fill in the blanks of a hidden picture. Use your head to solve puzzles that unveil hidden passages and use your pedometer to help find every step that will reveal the hidden images. Attack and counter with your sword and shield, charging up attacks to unleash killer blows. Upgrade your weapons and equipment and fight through hordes of creatures as you explore deeper into the dungeon. There''s a picture on each of the 60 floors to unlock, each more detailed than the last. Picdun will keep you playing for a very long time.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/OdNsqET.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5483, '000480044b434e45', 'TWL-N-KCNE', 'Castle Conqueror', 'USA', 11877172, 'dsiw', '50010000001421', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/029a84bd32947324b81fe124bb095980e7c09de8686714be965eacbccdb48fbe.jpg', 'You are a great commander! Castle Conqueror is a real-time strategy game for casual gamers. You play a commander who must resist the empire and save the lives of the people. Lead your soldiers into battle, seize the enemy’s castle and gain victories until you destroy the empire on the mainland!\n\nEasy game rules for fun gaming. Play this game using the stylus on the Touch Screen. Select the player’s castle, and then send your army to storm the enemy’s castle in real time. Capture the castle and destroy your enemies to earn gold that you can use to upgrade your commander’s abilities and to buy items that will help you win more battles. Select commanders and different cards to upgrade your army or castle. If, at the end of a battle, you have managed to occupy the enemy''s castle, you win the game!\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/WvMS9Bc.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5484, '000480044b4a4845', 'TWL-N-KJHE', 'Antipole', 'USA', 10996532, 'dsiw', '50010000007037', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0d91d992091e6a6e18d46f210d17c878e333726bb1d75f8da7dff9700802f665.jpg', 'Arm yourself with the ability to reverse gravity in this action-packed side-scrolling adventure! With the power to flip the force of gravity, you can run on the ceiling, leap incredible distances, and even use gravity to vanquish your enemies!\n\nTry your skills at multiple difficulty levels and unlockable Challenges. Channel your inner speed-runner and find the fastest way through each level to beat their target times. Also features a special bonus mode for owners of Cosmos X2!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/tS2prcN.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5485, '00040000000a8900', 'CTR-N-AKKS', 'El profesor Layton y la máscara de los prodigios', 'EUR', 832363364, 'eshop', '50010000011893', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5486, '000400000015f300', 'CTR-N-JUZP', 'Zombie Incident', 'EUR', 25844580, 'eshop', '50010000030995', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/07c6447dfb051d78d5ce15b7cce1fb0ab7db6905e1b277cd7f3387fbc16016e9.jpg', 'Hamartia, the great citadel, became\nthe symbol of human sin. After\ncenturies of excesses its penance was\ngoing to come. In the darkness of the\nnight, chaos invaded everything.\nBeasts started to scream. Nothing\nwas like before! No one sane would\ngo to that place.\n<br/><br/>\nJoin our heroine to explore the\ncitadel, find the eight golden stars,\nand run away from there!\n<br/><br/>\nFeatures:\n<br/><br/>\n- CoderChild and NeneFranz bring\nyou this adventure, awarded in 2011,\nto your Nintendo 3DS™ consoles.\n<br/>\n- Enjoy an experience full of retro\nflavour all around.\n<br/>\n- With stunning pixel-art graphics\nand an amazing chiptune soundtrack.\n<br/>\n- And so you can get challenged by\nand with your friends, register your\nhigh scores on the online leaderbords!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/gkR7gUM.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5487, '00040000000dc400', 'CTR-N-JLHP', 'League of Heroes', 'EUR', 90684260, 'eshop', '50010000031297', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/10c85edf43b77317ad575b1361ca9080f97818682e680d39aff8ae6b1dfc260d.jpg', '"Become a true hero and save the\nvillagers of Frognest!"\n<br/><br/>\nA NEVER-ENDING STORY\n<br/><br/>\nHack, slash and pummel your way\nthrough the endless Frognest Forest!\n<br/><br/>\nGEAR UP AND CUSTOMIZE YOUR\nCHARACTER\n<br/><br/>\nKit out your character with numerous\narmor and weaponry options – then\ndesign the best strategy to defeat\nyour enemies!\n<br/><br/>\nEVOLVE AS YOUR ADVENTURE\nUNFOLDS\n<br/><br/>\nEarn experience, discover treasure\nand unlock a slew of cool items,\nincluding magic!\n<br/><br/>\nCOMPLETE QUESTS\n<br/><br/>\nComplete 60+ daunting quests and\nearn valuable silver coins!\n<br/><br/>\nBEAUTIFUL HAND-DRAWN\nGRAPHICS AND ANIMATIONS\n<br/><br/>\nImmerse yourself in spectacular 2D\nvisuals and awesome animations!\n<br/><br/>\nPERSONALIZED, WEATHER EFFECTS\n<br/><br/>\nIn League of Heroes, you can enjoy\nchanging weather and time-of-day\neffects! You’ll experience\nthunderstorms, cloudy skies, fog,\nnighttime and much more!\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/iPYnXZH.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5488, '0004000000090000', 'CTR-N-JKFE', 'Johnny Kung Fu™', 'USA', 48286564, 'eshop', '50010000010076', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/685d2809d178716df6c770fd38244baf63b4519f3d69741bf8885fc0cdd66896.jpg', 'Updated 11/30/2012. Updates Include:<br>\nAdded new variations to the B&W stages.<br>\nAdjusted gameplay balance.\n<br><br>\nJohnny Kung Fu™ is an old school action game that mixes the old with the new! Johnny Kung Fu™ puts you into the Kung Fu garb of a seemingly everyday man Johnny. The local organized crime group Mr. Wang, led by the mysterious man known as Mr. Wang, seems to have a bone to pick with Johnny and has captured his girlfriend Paula. Knowing that an ambush awaits him, Johnny chases the kidnappers into one of Mr. Wang’s hideout towers regardless. Will Johnny be able to save Paula? Or will the Mr. Wang Gang prevail?', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/OHYX6TR.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5489, '000480044b505050', 'TWL-N-KPPP', 'Pop Island', 'EUR', 12486452, 'dsiw', '50010000004722', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3155afc5847c6869d08e724740563b8146a209ee4c3378d1530296678534de05.jpg', 'Discover a joyful universe where\nplaying is always a pleasure!<br>\n<br>\nColourful and fun, Pop Island is an\nall-action capture the flag game where\nyou pick which team to compete on\nbefore running, jumping and spinning\nyour way around the island in an\nattempt to collect the priceless flags\nhidden throughout it.<br>\n<br>\nBecome a surfing penguin, a flying\nfish or a waterskiing crocodile as you\ngo all out for victory – unlocking 12\nmore joyful animals as you rack up\npoints across 8 different planets. You\nmight even end up competing as a\nskateboarding mammoth!<br>\n<br>\nPlaying alone is plenty of fun, but the\nmadcap action reaches a new level\nwhen your friends get involved. By\nsharing the demo of the game via DS\nDownload Play, up to seven more\npeople can join you for some\nhead-to-head or cooperative action.\nWith plenty of power-ups, you’ll need\nto concentrate on capturing more than\njust the rival team’s flag to claim\nvictory!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/171c62f25a18696dbf3fc6d4904a7e1c232c9c53764446a94aeb3684050cd9fa.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/i2rayZb.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/0frVHz0.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
