(5697, '0004000000183600', 'CTR-N-AT3A', 'Kirby: Planet Robobot™', 'ALL', 696400788, 'eshop', '50010000039739', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5f844a48958b37b476d0db90f7ac4b55215b131e2c517e93ca002826f54662a5.jpg', 'Harness the power of a mysterious mech to stop ruthless invaders from mechanizing Kirby’s home world. Smash through tough obstacles, lift heavy objects with ease, and scan enemies to shape-shift into new Modes with powerful abilities in this supercharged action-platformer!\n<br><br>\nThat’s right—Kirby’s Robobot Armor can shape-shift into different modes by scanning enemies to copy their moves—like the new Jet Mode. Not to mention, Kirby™ can copy abilities the old-fashioned way too—by inhaling them! After saving the world, team up with three friends to defeat foes in Team Kirby Clash, an RPG-styled 4-player brawl where you choose from varied roles and level them up.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ydSHh9m.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5698, '000400000010eb00', 'CTR-P-BSKP', 'Etrian Odyssey™ Untold: The Millennium Girl', 'EUR', 822541156, 'eshop', '50010000019554', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0414e7810bb3cefb0ab26ebf8e7c66c2bf4e97550a5a7352a9e4a36695d4ad7b.jpg', 'Etria is a land that has long\nwelcomed explorers, yet even they\nwill discover stories untold. In Story\nmode, you will encounter the mystery\nof the maiden who has lived a\nthousand years.\n<br/><br/>\nShould you brave Classic mode,\nyou''ll experience the beautifully\nupgraded version of the original Etrian\nadventure, with new 3D graphics and\ngameplay improvements.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/22978d106d42ed07a80a7c424f3222d8c9fae0476d2c12e4300923593d98473a.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/6sAj6ss.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/xrPPW22.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5699, '0004000000077e00', 'CTR-N-JD8J', '電波人間のRPG', 'JPN', 49642340, 'eshop', '50010000009102', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6f380d99422fdd72261af5d76b8c1b7d765d2881a36ebc6acfb5c272b02d785d.jpg', '日常の電波のまわりを漂う電波人間たち。\n<br>彼らを探し、捕え、チームを組んで冒険させる、新しいロールプレイングゲームです。\n<br>\n<br>電波人間たちは、電波の縄張りごとに違います。\n<br>現実のいろいろな場所からいろいろな特技を持った電波人間を集め、魔王にさらわれた大事な人をとりもどす冒険に出かけましょう。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7b291acb2a8d62d7a06350541bc84b19d861ba1740265145a9f7987995a349cb.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/pEjCaIy.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/3GrJB5w.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5700, '00040000000ef000', 'CTR-N-JDRJ', '電波人間のRPG3', 'JPN', 205900644, 'eshop', '50010000015401', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d1513dacedb5308d36c5e7e933f31e2d5344709d75a0bdff8f566956f0b6c3db.jpg', 'このゲームは、キャッチした電波人間たちでチームを組み、さらわれた大切な人を取り戻すために世界を冒険するRPGです。本作では、モンスターをつかまえることのできる電波人間が登場します。つかまえたモンスターはバトル中に助っ人として召喚することができます。強力なモンスターをつかまえて、バトルを有利に進めましょう。\n<br>\n<br>仲間になった電波人間たちは、それぞれ自分の家に住むようになりました。彼らの家はインテリアコーディネートをお楽しみいただけます。\n<br>\n<br>また、インターネットを使った遊びも充実。全国のプレイヤーとアイテムの売買をしたり、電波人間の貸し借りをしたりすることができます。\n<br>前作や前々作を遊んでいただいた方は、主人公を引き継いだり、仲間を連れてくることも可能です。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4a7df44d9912727d4c87951c9cc191cf07e9420f0fc399b5c453921791828c80.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/i5E1QGC.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/rDBNsrS.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5701, '0004008c0007ad00', 'CTR-M-ABEJ-00', 'New Super Mario Bros 2.', 'JPN', 782336, 'dlc', 'none', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5702, '000400000009fa00', 'CTR-N-ATQE', 'Freakyforms™ Deluxe: Your Creations Alive!', 'USA', 80866196, 'eshop', '50010000012043', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8833570f1a69f48940a3bdc704a94d8dcce597f54866907558584c939b1cbcb3.jpg', 'Create wacky creatures called “formees,” and bring them to life on your Nintendo 3DS™ system to populate your very own planet! Choose from over 600 different forms to complete your creation— like wings for flying or wheels for rolling. The choices you make will determine what abilities your formee will have and how it will move around the world.  The possibilities are nearly endless! The more formees you make, the bigger the planet becomes and the more ways you will have to play in it. This deluxe version of the game contains all the content of the original Nintendo eShop release and some new features, such as dungeons to explore plus enhanced creating and sharing capabilities.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/CYB4A2e.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5703, '000400000017ba00', 'CTR-N-BSEE', 'BRAVELY SECOND™: END LAYER', 'USA', 2665225060, 'eshop', '50010000039137', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/eec937dbfa888b947b2a947a728291186eb674cbf80a7d48a4fb5c4963e01343.jpg', 'Steel yourself for the next evolution of the series that reinvented turn-based RPGs—the successor to Square Enix’s Bravely Default™ game. In this standalone adventure, Agnés Oblige has been imprisoned, and as a knight in her service, it’s up to the hero, Yew, to save her! Form the ultimate team and strategy, then risk it all in this fast, fresh RPG.\n<br><br>\nThe innovative Brave and Default battle system is back and deeper than ever. Balance risk and reward in turn-based battles: characters can make multiple moves in one turn, but then they may be unable to move for a while. Win a battle in a single turn and you can instantly start a more difficult encounter to earn better rewards. Level up characters and jobs quickly, but be careful—defeat means losing anything earned along the way. Select from 30 jobs and over 300 skills and abilities to customize each party member in the most strategic manner. The more you learn, the more tactics you’ll wield. ', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/syTWKu6.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5704, '000480044b454756', 'TWL-N-KEGV', 'ELECTROPLANKTON™ Lumiloop', 'EUR', 4644660, 'dsiw', '50010000003363', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/587db155c1d99c3b9b9bf15b64c76e7d94b8fcb2c97bf972106baf25373a0630.jpg', 'Dive into a unique audio-visual\nexperience where technology meets\nart. Created by multimedia musician\nToshio Iwai, Electroplankton are living\naquatic ''instruments'' that you interact\nwith to produce a variety of sounds\nand images limited only by your\nimagination!<br>\n<br>\nRing-shaped Lumiloop have the ability\nto spin at a very high speed. As they\nspin, they emit unique sounds and a\npulsating glow. Usually seen in groups\nof five, Lumiloop produce sounds of\ndifferent pitches as they spin together,\ncreating a beautiful harmony.<br>\n<br>\nUse Performance mode to create\nyour own unique compositions, or\nrelax with Audience mode and let the\nElectroplankton run wild.<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously-released software.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/155d1bcfe1ac202735dfc03588422dffc5333359998b89e2a9d1131236548193.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/jlZCpSt.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/G5kv1XK.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5705, '000480044b454a56', 'TWL-N-KEJV', 'ELECTROPLANKTON™ Varvoice', 'EUR', 4273972, 'dsiw', '50010000003366', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f53a8b900dd54af2cdc8e108a2b8eef3fb2c6d2af0d84e2ef917f3f625047a24.jpg', 'Dive into a unique audio-visual\nexperience where technology meets\nart. Created by multimedia musician\nToshio Iwai, Electroplankton are living\naquatic ''instruments'' that you interact\nwith to produce a variety of sounds\nand images limited only by your\nimagination!<br>\n<br>\nVarvoice are clever plankton that can\nmemorise human voices and repeat\nthem over and over. As their shape\nchanges, so too does the tone of the\nvoice they play back. As well as\nadding their own unique sound to\nvoices, Varvoice can also play back\nvoices in reverse.<br>\n<br>\nUse Performance mode to create\nyour own unique compositions, or\nrelax with Audience mode and let the\nElectroplankton run wild.<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously-released software.Dive into a unique audio-visual\nexperience where technology meets\nart. Created by multimedia musician\nToshio Iwai, Electroplankton are living\naquatic ''instruments'' that you interact\nwith to produce a variety of sounds\nand images limited only by your\nimagination!<br>\n<br>\nVarvoice are clever plankton that can\nmemorise human voices and repeat\nthem over and over. As their shape\nchanges, so too does the tone of the\nvoice they play back. As well as\nadding their own unique sound to\nvoices, Varvoice can also play back\nvoices in reverse.<br>\n<br>\nUse Performance mode to create\nyour own unique compositions, or\nrelax with Audience mode and let the\nElectroplankton run wild.<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously-released software.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a41c608a1cdaa689dda7b4ee42e72a67f5b4a28993d3074c6d2355657c6608cb.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/2mQ1PVU.jpg', 'http://i.i