(5710, '000480044b454956', 'TWL-N-KEIV', 'ELECTROPLANKTON™ Beatnes', 'EUR', 4394804, 'dsiw', '50010000003365', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d6edb5b31822d0e4955aba30f81289bd1c0ac15af7a2c41f73aca4ae0653fb8c.jpg', 'Dive into a unique audio-visual\nexperience where technology meets\nart. Created by multimedia musician\nToshio Iwai, Electroplankton are living\naquatic ''instruments'' that you interact\nwith to produce a variety of sounds\nand images limited only by your\nimagination!<br>\n<br>\nBeatnes are curious creatures that\nemit sounds closely resembling those\nof the classic NES game console.\nTapping the eight unique parts of a\nBeatnes’ body produces different\nsounds. Tap rhythmically to produce a\nrepeating note in perfect time.<br>\n<br>\nUse Performance mode to create\nyour own unique compositions, or\nrelax with Audience mode and let the\nElectroplankton run wild.<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously-released software.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5c988b6b49796486eda037082cf2683cf68ee9b6f2da3210970d3fb9720fb0e8.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/4Qlr8YK.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/3AnUvAu.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5711, '000480044b454656', 'TWL-N-KEFV', 'ELECTROPLANKTON™ Nanocarp', 'EUR', 4105012, 'dsiw', '50010000003141', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/410a0ac2970710eaaa059cbd1270d40727434b6945ec0109d4f4d8aeef7ab4f6.jpg', 'Dive into a unique audio-visual\nexperience where technology meets\nart. Created by multimedia musician\nToshio Iwai, Electroplankton are living\naquatic ''instruments'' that you interact\nwith to produce a variety of sounds\nand images limited only by your\nimagination!<br>\n<br>\nNanocarp have very sensitive hearing,\nand they react to sounds like clapping\nor whistling. They swim in formations\nof 16 and emit sounds when they\nsense ripples on the water’s surface.\nTheir pitch changes depending on their\nlocation on the water.<br>\n<br>\nUse Performance mode to create\nyour own unique compositions, or\nrelax with Audience mode and let the\nElectroplankton run wild.<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously-released software.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e0894137ef1f352e0d8259f5eab0bb750a903dd2c1df147e8758546bf22e0490.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/yd8iu0j.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/YrrmxoY.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5712, '000480044b454156', 'TWL-N-KEAV', 'ELECTROPLANKTON™ Trapy', 'EUR', 4135732, 'dsiw', '50010000003061', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/cb9451d6511b949d3cedf16142d3d8ccdbb0b8989e7a7dbbca8bcb19a0b53707.jpg', 'Dive into a unique audio-visual\nexperience where technology meets\nart. Created by multimedia musician\nToshio Iwai, Electroplankton are living\naquatic ''instruments'' that you interact\nwith to produce a variety of sounds\nand images limited only by your\nimagination!<br>\n<br>\nTrapy are graceful swimmers and love\nto emit sounds as they follow lines\ntraced along the water. Each of the\nsix types of Trapy produce different\ntones depending on the direction they\nswim; they produce low pitch sounds\nwhen they swim to the right and high\npitch sounds when they swim to the\nleft.<br>\n<br>\nUse Performance mode to create\nyour own unique compositions, or\nrelax with Audience mode and let the\nElectroplankton run wild.<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously-released software.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2c7f1ac3efd39473b985acd76c6c3b56f7966019ef53ab23ff23966796b3de19.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/kYtkuA3.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/8htSzrr.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5713, '000480044b454556', 'TWL-N-KEEV', 'ELECTROPLANKTON™ Rec-Rec', 'EUR', 4676404, 'dsiw', '50010000003121', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bc55fa493f6b4caf1f177e964e5f3c12922eebb15d77c93d108290c3dcb605c9.jpg', 'Dive into a unique audio-visual\nexperience where technology meets\nart. Created by multimedia musician\nToshio Iwai, Electroplankton are living\naquatic ''instruments'' that you interact\nwith to produce a variety of sounds\nand images limited only by your\nimagination!<br>\n<br>\nThe fish-like Rec-Rec feed on sound\nwaves, which they digest and then\nrepeat back at perfect intervals,\nmaking them perfect for reproducing\nany sounds you like. They swim in\nschools of four; their frequency\nchanges depending on how fast they\nswim.<br>\n<br>\nUse Performance mode to create\nyour own unique compositions, or\nrelax with Audience mode and let the\nElectroplankton run wild.<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously-released software.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b238ab629958cb048e9b31ea1e3c397548060bab0d800ce0e008f679b04515d6.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/SZLwCPZ.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/Xusa5Oc.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5714, '000480044b454256', 'TWL-N-KEBV', 'ELECTROPLANKTON™ Hanenbow', 'EUR', 4008756, 'dsiw', '50010000003081', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5719e995958a3c0356878aca007cd3d4f06a4b15ed92fe03f97a25de18ba006d.jpg', 'Dive into a unique audio-visual\nexperience where technology meets\nart. Created by multimedia musician\nToshio Iwai, Electroplankton are living\naquatic ''instruments'' that you interact\nwith to produce a variety of sounds\nand images limited only by your\nimagination!<br>\n<br>\nHanenbow launch themselves out of\nthe water towards floating plants,\ncreating strange sounds and melodies\nas they bounce off the leaves. When a\nleaf is repeatedly hit by a Hanenbow,\nit changes colour, altering the sound\nproduced. No-one knows why\nHanenbow display this strange\nbehaviour.<br>\n<br>\nUse Performance mode to create\nyour own unique compositions, or\nrelax with Audience mode and let the\nElectroplankton run wild.<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously-released software.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6023d46fda943040674e27b60c9c7185fa8512cadce56fc3c6551193d7fb608f.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/0QwayGj.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/z9kQCRB.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5715, '000480044b4d4845', 'TWL-N-KMHE', 'myPostcards™', 'USA', 4000564, 'dsiw', '50010000002861', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/053d64d654944cc08a0e550b948c8a2c94863ab2e8c2317cbdcc8c4ad13b0beb.jpg', 'Create your own postcards and send them to your friends! With myPostcards, you can take a picture, write a quick note on it, then save everything as a postcard. To do this, simply open your Nintendo DSi system, take a photo and go! You can even customize your postcards by changing the background using 32 themes to start with, plus unlockables and various collectible stamps. You can then create postcards for all occasions. Use the pen or pencil tools to write or draw, then erase what you do not like. And thanks to the five different inks, you''ll have something to give color to your words and your drawings.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Cjq2VM1.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5716, '000480044b554d45', 'TWL-N-KUME', 'Quick Fill Q', 'USA', 3859252, 'dsiw', '50010000008761', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5abeb20f07c581fc09aa58795d253327448cb42190a80a1611168eaa6fba39a5.jpg', 'Q is a spherical creature who rolls on without stopping. However, holes appear in the way to try and stop Q''s progress. Fill the holes using swift thinking and precise controls so Q can keep on rolling...\n\nBreak blocks in the shape of various holes, so Q can roll safely over them. The size of the holes will depend on the difficulty level. When Q rolls past a certain distance, Q begins to speed up. When the game ends, the distance traveled by Q is recorded. The top five records for each difficulty level will be saved.\n\nQuick Fill Q is a non-stop, easy to learn puzzle game that provides hours of fun for the entire family...', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ay0QpZ7.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5717, '000480044b484a45', 'TWL-N-KHJE', 'Hidden Photo', 'USA', 12215092, 'dsiw', '50010000006899', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/741acebf5a9f58750290542da547837febc32f7dafcce7a32b7c6a4cc38341f5.jpg', 'Snap - Create - Play!\n\nHidden Photo tests your powers of observation using fun and brain-twisting challenges. Locate hidden objects, words, and faces in a variety of photos or spot the difference between two photos. Use your Nintendo DSi™ Camera to make your world the centerpiece of unique challenges. Release your creative talents, snapping photos of yourself, friends, objects, pets, or anything in your environment. Hidden Photo will create new puzzles for you to solve and share with your friends! The clock is ticking, so don’t admire your photographic genius for too long!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/6iqVy9g.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5718, '0004000000091300', 'CTR-N-ATQJ', '大盛り! いきものづくり クリエイトーイ', 'JPN', 69733268, 'eshop', '50010000011888', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e4d81ee6d90f6b89f0a7051c8ba21fa85ed23606d23722bc03820d3731303799.jpg', '【このソフトは配信を停止しています。】<br>\n<br>\nお絵かき感覚でいろいろな形を組み合わせ、"クニャペ"と呼ばれる自分だけのキャラクターを作って遊ぶ、『いきものづくり クリエイトーイ』が内容盛りだくさんになって新たに登場。\n<br>これまでの遊びに加えて、新たにダンジョンを冒険できるようになったり、みんなで楽しめるモードが追加されるなど、さらに遊びの幅が広がりました。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/390292f046729f2f5e7bc0b5eb3de43a01180b7ef227c6f7f06b1e213eec314d.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/w7wum8D.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/45Z7jYg.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5719, '000400000014c600', 'CTR-N-KXCP', 'Smash Controller', 'EUR', 40561508, 'eshop', '50010000024255', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3091079f430638f059314c6ab5dc42278a42201b004f4203c941f36ee3b88135.jpg', 'No more passing around controllers!\n<br/><br/>\nYou never have to sit out in a couch\nsession of Super Smash Bros.™ for Wii\nU again, as Smash Controller\ntransforms your Nintendo 3DS™\nsystem into your own controller for\nthe game. It also enables you to\nconveniently bring along your own\ncustomized fighters, no matter whose\nWii U™ console you''re playing on.\n<br/><br/>\nAny system from the Nintendo 3DS™\nfamily can be used as a Smash\nController. All of the up to eight\nplayers in a game of Super Smash\nBros.™ for Wii U can play using their\nown Nintendo 3DS system, each with\na copy of Smash Controller or Super\nSmash Bros.™ for Nintendo 3DS.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c044c2f4837d4150830cd7fdd6fc794333bd1bc1c0a79d910b03a19aea861f2f.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/ZhGL5Ce.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/trwMHRx.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5720, '000400000005a500', 'CTR-P-ARMP', 'Rayman® Origins', 'EUR', 203729764, 'eshop', '50010000010211', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6bbb0a5f2c02c7a69970d0425f02037e8abf3d5a916326d6d5651717e7892c45.jpg', 'Rayman is back! Jump into this\nall new adventure full of surprises\nand epic boss battles.\n<br/><br/>\n-Play as Rayman or Globox and\nexplore Rayman''s magical universe\n<br/><br/>\n-Discover over 60 platforming levels\n<br/><br/>\n-Share your progress, unlocked\nachievements and more via\nStreetPass™', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/55PisL8.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5721, '0004000000165600', 'CTR-N-JV7P', 'Azure Striker GUNVOLT', 'EUR', 529140580, 'eshop', '50010000032335', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/174f162852a2732e9470d5341a87dd4969368ee3f27f6351e04db5b8c0eda9d9.jpg', 'Azure Striker GUNVOLT is a 2D\naction/platforming game in the style of\nthe Japanese classics of yesteryear.\nGreat controls, crisp graphics, unique\nplay mechanics, epic boss battles —\nit''s all here, and better than you\nremember!\n<br/><br/>\n* Obliterate foes with the power of\nlightning!\n<br/><br/>\nTag enemies with your weapon, then\nshock them into oblivion with\nGunvolt''s lethal "Flashfield"\ntechnique! Advanced players can try\nfor bonuses and higher scores by\ndefeating two or more enemies at\nonce.\n<br/><br/>\n* Gain power from Lumen''s anthem!\n<br/><br/>\nLumen, aka the Muse, has the power\nto revive Gunvolt if he falls in battle.\nAnd if you rack up enough Kudos by\ndefeating enemies without taking\ndamage, she''ll sing for you during\nplay, giving you an added boost!\n<br/><br/>\n* Defeat the Sumeragi Seven!\n<br/><br/>\nPowerful bosses and an intriguing\ntale await. Will Gunvolt be able to put\na stop to the Sumeragi Group''s\nambitions before it''s too late? The\ntime to strike is now!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/dV1D1S9.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5722, '000400000009c000', 'CTR-P-AMTP', 'Shin Megami Tensei: Devil Survivor Overclocked', 'EUR', 1202678628, 'eshop', '50010000013426', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/42a7b39c187d35223d7b1f0d548ac298c146ad477c43ee5de19a2de4a60f7926.jpg', 'One of 2009''s best RPGs returns\nyou to Tokyo in the midst of a\nlockdown, the government''s\ncold-blooded response to a demon\ninvasion. Armed only with a\nmysterious COMP, will you survive this\nchaos?\n<br/><br/>\nLive to see the brand new 8th Day\nchapter!\n<br/><br/>\nCollect and fuse demons to create\nmore powerful creatures\n<br/><br/>\nMany possible endings await in this\nhybrid of traditional and strategy RPG\n', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3cace2f947b5378eccb10c974cf7c16a29b5c2229c035878a5c107c8e2149191.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/sDd2DBF.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/W458sMQ.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5723, '00040000000bfd00', 'CTR-N-JUWJ', '@SIMPLE DLシリーズ Vol.7 THE 浮気彼氏 ～突撃!浮気現場～', 'JPN', 24968036, 'eshop', '50010000013110', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9027acfe9a7737ed38501cd5d65ddcb0dba152c06d38311f73f9cb7589cc916c.jpg', '証拠を集めて彼氏の浮気を暴く、ガサイレ修羅場ゲーム。\n<br>彼氏の部屋を探索して浮気の証拠の数々を集めたら、シラを切る彼氏に証拠を突きつけて矛盾を証明し浮気を暴きます。\n<br>登場する浮気彼氏はタイプもストーリーも異なる4人を収録。\n<br>\n<br>【収録シナリオ】\n<br>･突撃!浮気現場\n<br>･冷たい浮気男\n<br>･女を連れ込む男\n<br>･二次元に浮気する彼氏', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/73e7f335456acf385fa0fbf0859757a03fc3b0d79d00f3df064abe1617d699a2.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/U0Fo1Lw.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/kDw2VfK.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5724, '000400000016f700', 'CTR-N-KPNJ', 'プチコンマガジン 創刊号', 'JPN', 24263524, 'eshop', '50010000035715', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9997f78050baea975e03cb2359f93a6cef5af2e3f7a7f5fe164ab977f3e6499e.jpg', '『プチコンマガジン 創刊号』はプログラムコンテスト「第3回プチコン大喜利」で集まった、優秀なゲームや実用ソフトをプチコン3号なしでも楽しめるようにした作品集です。\n<br>･『プチコン3号 SmileBASIC』を使ったユーザージェネレートコンテンツ集\n<br>･小規模ながら、斬新なアイデアで楽しめる38個の作品(うち4個は作品紹介のみ)\n<br>･『プチコン3号 SmileBASIC』がなくても、プレイすることができます。\n<br>･SmileBASICで作った新作シューティング『SOLID GUNNER』も搭載', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3e7b8c46ae0d449de321f41a242e8107614b366711b144db4607d9f8fff03e83.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/o1ZfFtE.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/3QaBedS.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5725, '00040000000fca00', 'CTR-P-BTHP', 'THEATRHYTHM Final Fantasy Curtain Call™', 'EUR', 1757379428, 'eshop', '50010000024556', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2d7fe301bf1b8c0be3c184f20f32ecc855ebb545f30c47d5b7465351cc8cd030.jpg', '221 Songs & Over 60 Characters\nfrom FINAL FANTASY®\n<br/>\nGo head-to-head in Versus Mode\n<br/>\nRhythm Meets RPG in Quest Medley\nMode', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bdcaa5a1aa32c2d25441d4ae29e1b5e24c5dbaacc45c2862a63fced3189a0721.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/IucsTsq.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/GpgtLIF.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5726, '0004000000147b00', 'CTR-N-JVQP', 'Dedede’s Drum Dash™ Deluxe', 'EUR', 63007588, 'eshop', '50010000030175', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/93947a7692cc0537463c83e9e7f0db959bc64b4a0afe3bcc5070bce026711e47.jpg', 'Bounce to the beat as Kirby’s\nlong-time rival in King Dedede’s\nrhythm action game! Jump on drums\ncollecting coins, avoiding enemies and\ntapping buttons in sync with catchy\nKirby tunes! This standalone deluxe\ngame includes content not found in\nKirby™: Triple Deluxe, including\nall-new stages, new obstacles and\nmore!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9caa470c856b759846efca0ccae0aa70fdbb20da899c43efe95e4e6ca94c689b.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ebMi5kj.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/FvNM5KZ.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5727, '0004008c00162000', 'CTR-M-BX2P-00', 'Project X Zone 2', 'EUR', 593920, 'dlc', 'none', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5728, '000400000019a600', 'CTR-N-KEXP', 'Epic Word Search Collection 2', 'EUR', 8272740, 'eshop', '50010000040475', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d2ac67d1f535bd8dbaefb36f51dff1014b00b7074850840fa4aff5137bfb43cb.jpg', 'Epic Word Search puzzles are huge -\nand they’re back in this second epic\ncollection!\n<br/><br/>\nThe Epic America Word Search\n<br/><br/>\nCelebrate the very best of America -\nwith fireworks! Travel Route 66, head\nwest for the Gold Rush and explore\nAmerica''s parks and beaches; take in\na ball game, eat the ultimate\nhamburger and look up at\nskyscrapers. They even put a man on\nthe moon - can you find him?\n<br/><br/>\nThe Epic Ancient Word Search\n<br/><br/>\nBy Zeus, it’s historic! Encounter\nleaders and deities from ancient\nGreece, Rome and Egypt; visit\nStonehenge, Pompeii and the Great\nWall of China and take part in the\nancient Olympic games.\n<br/><br/>\nThe Epic Animals Word Search\n<br/><br/>\nThe furriest word search you''ll ever\nmeet and want to tickle the tummy of!\nGo "eww" at creepy crawlies and\n"aww" at baby animals; visit the\ndepths of the ocean and make a\nwhole bunch of animal noises.\n<br/><br/>\nThe Epic Journeys Word Search\n<br/><br/>\nFasten your seatbelt! Travel in luxury\non the Orient Express, go off-road\nthrough the Australian outback,\nexplore the ancient Silk Road and\nembark on an expedition to conquer\nMount Everest.\n<br/><br/>\nThe Epic Shakespeare Word Search\n<br/><br/>\nShall I compare this puzzle to a\nsummer’s day? Enjoy the verbal wit of\nthe Bard of Avon with this puzzle\nbased on Shakespeare’s best known\nplays. Friends, Romans, countrymen,\nfind me some words!\n<br/><br/>\nEach epic puzzle contains over 1,500\nwords, hidden in a grid that''s much\ntoo large to fit on screen! It takes\nmany hours of gameplay to solve each\none. Scroll with the +Control Pad or\nCircle Pad, then touch with the stylus\nto highlight words.\n<br/><br/>\nJump straight in and get solving right\naway with this fast-loading game.\nSwitch between puzzles at any time\nand share your progress with other\nplayers using StreetPass™.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/IfBfRVr.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47');
INSERT INTO `3dsgames` (`id`, `titleID`, `serial`, `name`, `region`, `size`, `type`, `contentID`, `iconURL`, `gdesc`, `thumb`, `scrcount`, `imgur_iconURL`, `imgur_thumb`, `count`, `time`) VALUES
(5729, '000400000016a400', 'CTR-N-KEWP', 'Epic Word Search Collection', 'EUR', 6617956, 'eshop', '50010000035195', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2ed436cd3b51629baa8c5541199ed8fab3ec7069eda66815263f1799bd88d94e.jpg', 'Epic Word Search puzzles are huge!\n<br/><br/>\nEach puzzle contains over 1,500\nwords, hidden in a grid that''s much\ntoo large to fit on screen!\n<br/><br/>\nTo solve the word search you''ll have\nto scroll around the puzzle looking for\nwords. Use the D-Pad or Circle Pad\nto move the grid and touch with the\nstylus to highlight words.\n<br/><br/>\nThis is a challenge like nothing\nyou''ve ever seen before with many\nhours of gameplay in each enormous\npuzzle.\n<br/><br/>\nJump straight in and get solving right\naway with this fast-loading game.\nSwitch between puzzles at any time\nand share your progress with other\nplayers using StreetPass.\n<br/><br/>\nEpic Word Search Collection contains\nfive gigantic puzzles!\n<br/><br/>\nThe Epic Food Word Search<br/>\nMunch your way from breakfast to\ndessert, sample the wares of farmers,\nbutchers and bakers and top it all off\nwith a selection of seasonings and\nsauces.\n<br/><br/>\nThe Epic Movie Word Search<br/>\nFind words about sixteen classic\nmovies. There''s nothing ''R'' rated in\nthere, it''s suitable for the whole family.\n<br/><br/>\nThe Epic Rock Word Search<br/>\nCheer on your favourite bands, play\nthe drums, choose a new guitar and\nrock out to some classic anthems.\n<br/><br/>\nThe Epic Sports Word Search<br/>\nScore a home run, hit a hole in one,\ncarry the ball all the way for a\ntouchdown and catch a fish "this big".\n<br/><br/>\nThe Epic TV Word Search<br/>\nGet ready for some channel surfing\nas you find words from more than a\ndozen popular TV shows.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ppTjyA9.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5730, '0004000000169300', 'CTR-N-KWBP', 'Word Search by POWGI', 'EUR', 4922212, 'eshop', '50010000032675', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f15d8318b397cc7bfb3eff636e37e56b07b3be7f324ff674542b47feff07ed1c.jpg', 'With more than 300 puzzles to solve,\nWord Search by POWGI will keep you\npuzzling for hours!\n<br/><br/>\nAn intuitive touch-screen interface\nputs you straight into the action with\nno complex controls to learn!\n<br/><br/>\nFollow your progress through 28\ndifferent categories, from animals,\nnature and science to school life,\nhobbies and careers.\n<br/><br/>\nPOWGI''s word search puzzles are\nexpertly hand-crafted for your\nenjoyment and are stuffed to the brim\nwith words in every direction!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/7faKZhp.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5731, '000400000007c800', 'CTR-N-AGAP', 'MARIO TENNIS™ OPEN', 'EUR', 270674836, 'eshop', '50010000009911', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d48de5cd7f3f65aaa944d457e5cffe20b027a7de2b58c74acc0afb8d11d89951.jpg', 'MARIO TENNIS OPEN on\nNintendo 3DS offers players tactical\ntennis with depth like never before!\nUse buttons, the Touch Screen or new\ngyro controls - perfect for beginners!\nPlay online against friends or\nchallengers from your region and work\nyour way up the leaderboard to\nbecome champion. Exchange data with\nother users via StreetPass and\ncustomise your player with any coins\nyou win.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/yYIv8FR.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5732, '0004000000069200', 'CTR-N-RBKP', 'Kirby''s Block Ball™', 'EUR', 5073764, 'eshop', '50010000009132', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/eb231ec0d7a41477557fb07a40814b5488e0fae18e4a866b5de0c79ce47be479.jpg', 'Kirby breaks into new territory in\nKirby’s Block Ball – a fast-paced\naction game in which Kirby becomes\nthe ball in a crazy contest to clear all\nthe blocks in each stage, to earn the\nhighest score.<br>\n<br>\nKirby can bounce off paddles on all\nfour sides of the screen, so you’ll\nneed quick reactions. You can also\nmake use of Kirby’s powers like Spike,\nBurn or Stone which will help in the\nfinal showdown with King Dedede!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a4b91040bff63fdee325341f3ed8335e2901ee0373b68d86dc4dbd88f42048a7.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/bJE4BdQ.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/79sNZF3.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5733, '000400000015ba00', 'CTR-N-KSNP', '3D Sonic The Hedgehog 2', 'EUR', 39402340, 'eshop', '50010000037338', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/70465868593dea886a51116606411c436a19532996e2d8910fd01f6a237410bd.jpg', 'Sonic is here to save the day, and\nthis time he’s got help from his friend\nTails! Dr. Eggman (AKA Dr. Robotnik)\nis back and is planning on building his\nultimate weapon, the Death Egg. To\ndo so, he’s going to turn the animal\ninhabitants of Mobius into his own\npersonal army of Badniks. Can Sonic\nobtain the 7 Chaos Emeralds and stop\nhim once and for all?\n<br/><br/>\n3D Sonic The Hedgehog 2 is\nremastered in 3D and full of new\nfeatures! Is the Chemical Plant Zone\nyour favorite stage? Use “Stage\nSelect” and start running wherever\nyou want! Run fast without worrying\nabout your rings. Cut your losses by\nchoosing Ring Keeper Mode—only half\nyour rings will be lost after taking\ndamage!\n<br/><br/>\nKeeping your rings and stopping Dr.\nEggman’s evil scheme is important,\nbut don’t forget to take some time off\nfrom saving the world to play against\nyour friends in the 2 Player VS and\nCO-OP Mode using Local Play!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/227d85c13f7f0f05d2431e8cc782041ce06dc25a25562a281b9523f1200cad44.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/hmxAJCj.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/oZFphSE.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5734, '00040000000bc600', 'CTR-N-JLLP', 'Hana Samurai Art of the Sword™', 'EUR', 60156772, 'eshop', '50010000012053', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b8b285121fecc124f8266e77289f23eac514517977ad09d924406a910c56ccbf.jpg', 'Leave button mashing behind. Hana\nSamurai: Art of the Sword is about\nprecision swordplay, battlefield\nfinesse, and martial-arts style.<br>\n<br>\nAs the heroic title character, you’ll\ntravel a world rife with cherry-blossom\nbeauty and deadly danger to rescue\nthe legendary Princess Cherry\nBlossom. Her kidnapper has set\ndozens of blade-wielding henchmen in\nyour path, and you’ll have to exercise\nyour best battle senses to defeat them\nand save her. Learn to predict your\nfoes’ moves, deftly dodge their\nattacks, and create opportunities for\ndevastating counterattacks.<br>\n<br>\nStart with the Sakura Sword, a little\nhealth, and some basic training from\nyour water-spirit guide. Make your\nway from battleground to\nbattleground fighting wave after wave\nof increasingly cunning enemies. Fight\nthrough huge castles to duel epic\nbosses. And don’t forget to stop at\nsmall villages along the way to get\nhelp, gear, encouragement (and\ndistraction) from the quirky townsfolk.<br>\n<br>\nProve that you truly are the Sakura\nSamurai!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/999d5a881fa626964bc28537845b91351a166900b8f155d8727b1ec437898294.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/SiDkHlK.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ayt43AJ.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5735, '0004000000111c00', 'CTR-P-ATAP', 'Yoshi''s New Island™', 'EUR', 440818580, 'eshop', '50010000020434', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8a12fb396cbf05663c65693f5031062175403fcfb570b54e45c2fac53a62c226.jpg', 'Yoshi’s New Island is the first\ninstalment in this series since Yoshi’s\nIsland DS was released in 2006.\n<br/><br/>\nYoshi’s good old Flutter Jump,\nGround Pound and egg-throwing\nreturn, along with new abilities and\nchallenges that take advantage of the\nfeatures of the Nintendo 3DS. You\ncan use massive eggs called\nMega-Eggs to destroy blocks and\npipes, revealing secrets such as coins\nand hidden keys. The more things you\ndestroy, the higher the Mega-Egg\ngauge goes, netting you extra lives in\nthe process!\n<br/><br/>\nThe beautiful art is based on many\nclassic styles, such as oil painting,\nwatercolours and crayon drawings.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5f853f5264c10e534ce77238011ed6627a19a8e65a1535e95fb497375b2a43d3.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Xzzp6fS.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/UxxeZQU.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5736, '000480044b494b56', 'TWL-N-KIKV', 'GO Series: Ivy the Kiwi?™ Mini', 'EUR', 8097588, 'dsiw', '50010000004141', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0b0d4782125471fc7925df55695051360d76df57fd9d3f2c3f364e842beff73b.jpg', 'GO Series presents Ivy the Kiwi?\nMini.<br>\n<br>\nIvy the Kiwi? is a new game designed\nby Yuji Naka, the creator of Sonic,\nand developed by PROPE. Draw lines\nusing the Stylus and guide Ivy on her\nway home as she bounces, spins and\nsmashes her way past obstacles.\nIncludes 50 levels with beautiful\ngraphics in a hand drawn\nstorybook-style.<br>\n<br>\nPlease note that elements of this\nsoftware may have been featured in\npreviously released software.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/R86zCW8.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
