(5740, '000400000008ad00', 'CTR-N-RBYP', 'Kirby''s Star Stacker', 'EUR', 4582244, 'eshop', '50010000010546', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3adb80fc92042c284f5203bbb25b77b8faeff11b8b4fd78a49fa48da15d350fc.jpg', 'Join Kirby in this action-packed\npuzzle game, as he teams up with his\nfriends Rick, Kine and Coo to stack\nfalling stars.<br>\n<br>\nAs friend blocks and star blocks rain\ndown randomly from the top of the\nscreen, you must arrange the star\nblocks between identical friend blocks\nto remove them.<br>\n<br>\nYou''ll need quick reflexes and\nstrategic thinking to outwit King\nDedede who''s out to stop you.<br>\n<br>\nAs well as the main game mode you\ncan also pit your wits against the\nChallenge Mode and Time Attack\nMode. Let''s get stacking!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/372172d84a5e6455c1a270c17b5e1729ff845f07b330a694b02578f02a36ea06.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/7vQfWSs.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/BVmEc2s.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5741, '000400000015b800', 'CTR-N-KSRP', '3D Streets of Rage 2', 'EUR', 41306980, 'eshop', '50010000035196', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c2d5ee07f86a39a4180477c13d501b95e495709a61cd23d471c5b365890e9731.jpg', 'The sequel to the original rumbler is\nback and re-mastered in 3D. Slam the\nasphalt with bigger, better and totally\ndevastating attacks. Skull crushing\nex-wrestler Max Thunder joins up with\nAxel and Blaze to throw earth\nshattering body slams and fist\nattacks. New thrasher Skate slices\npunks with high speed inline attacks\nand spinning jump kicks. Use secret\nweapons to bash your way through\ngangs of bikers to rescue your friend\nand defeat Mr. X.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/WeTJ5N8.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
