(5748, '000400000015ce00', 'CTR-N-JWGP', 'Gunman Clive 2', 'EUR', 74419044, 'eshop', '50010000030095', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e0a9bedbe5c164103c5593d959cfc466236f92ec056506aa5049e3ec13cd71e0.jpg', 'Gunman Clive returns in an all new\nadventure. Now in Colour!\n<br/><br/>\nAfter rescuing Ms Johnson, Gunman\nClive returns to again find the town\nunder attack by bandits. To stop them\nonce and for all he must chase after\ntheir leader; an adventure that takes\nhim all the way around the world,\nfacing bigger and deadlier enemies\nthan ever before.\n<br/><br/>\nGunman Clive 2 retains the same\nclassic gameplay formula, but dials\nthe action up a notch further, with\nimproved and more colourful graphics,\nmore dynamic levels and richer, more\ndiverse environments, bigger bosses\nand tons of new enemies.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/HN29pcx.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
