(5754, '00040000000a9000', 'CTR-N-ACLP', 'Nintendo presents New Style Boutique™', 'EUR', 1688324964, 'eshop', '50010000012390', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/40b75f46811ac249820cf7b1979332e5469601c2af33937d7e31fe2dc2c58a81.jpg', 'In Nintendo presents: New Style\nBoutique, players take on the role of\na shop assistant and must work their\nway up to eventually owning their own\nboutique by giving customers advice\nand putting a look together for them.\n\nThere are thousands of items and\naccessories to choose from, and\nplayers can also get judged on the\nlooks they put together, great for\nanybody wanting to unleash their inner\nfashionista!\n\nReach the top of the style stakes and\ntake the fashion world by storm!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d8881ad0bf0c9b9c43628b00b0929b2085536daceb713b08802ca35e7b9bcbcf.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/JpnHA51.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/AA7pkQf.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5755, '000400000017a400', 'CTR-P-BFWP', 'Fire Emblem™ Fates', 'EUR', 1575279460, 'eshop', '50010000039797', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/892a79716b7509293f73ee2d990fa249aeacc7cff253178477dafc9f640163ba.jpg', 'Two kingdoms are on the brink of war – and you must decide whose side to take in Fire Emblem Fates for Nintendo 3DS family systems. As a Hoshidan prince raised by Nohrian royals, you’re torn between two families. The path you choose determines the fate that awaits you and the army you lead. Command them with expert precision and form stronger relationships in this ambitious turn-based strategy game.\n<br>\n<br>Join Hoshido in Fire Emblem Fates: Birthright, or fight alongside Nohr in Fire Emblem Fates: Conquest. Later on, you can explore the depth of the story in a third path, available to purchase as add-on content – Fire Emblem Fates: Revelation. After selecting your path, you can then choose to purchase the other story paths as downloadable content from Nintendo eShop.\n<br>\n<br>For the first time ever, your customised avatar is the main hero. Guide your army through challenging turn-based battles, and devise your plan of attack based on your allies'' classes, weapons and support levels. Each unit and weapon has strengths and weaknesses that you must balance against the foes they face. Partner your allies on the battlefield so they can support one another in combat. Building relationships is key – the closer your allies become, the better they’ll fight together.\n<br>\n<br>Visit amiibo.nintendo.eu for\n<br>compatible amiibo™ and the latest\n<br>information. To use amiibo on\n<br>Nintendo 3DS, Nintendo 3DS XL and\n<br>Nintendo 2DS systems a\n<br>Nintendo 3DS NFC Reader/Writer is\n<br>required.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/tWQeKaP.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5756, '00040000000e6700', 'CTR-N-JMYE', 'Skater Cat', 'USA', 35285860, 'eshop', '50010000021394', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5e1e8fbbaf769fe57713d5dcfc9802d687f13e0b9b01e46f1575aab84fc8c63a.jpg', 'Ride the streets with Ollie, the sleekest cat on the block and put your reflexes to the test as you make spectacular tricks in the air to collect scrumptious treats and fleeing stray cats. Skate faster and faster as you lead the clowder and keep them keen with a topped up supply of treats! The addition of StreetPass and SpotPass will allow you to exchange best times and ghost runs with other players and the game makers themselves! With over 25 levels to complete, 90 medals to collect plus bonus in-game features to unlock, you’ll be purring with so much excitement!\n<br><br>\nFeatures:\n3 worlds with over 25 levels to complete and 90 medals to collect!\n<br><br>\nExciting in-game bonuses to unlock including the ability to play as your Mii!\n<br><br>\nStreetPass feature included to exchange best times and ghost runs from other Skater Cat players\n<br><br>\nReceive news updates and available ghost runs from the game makers via SpotPass\n<br><br>\nAn awesome pick up and play action game!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Yfj1XQL.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5757, '000480044b565845', 'TWL-N-KVXE', 'Cat Frenzy', 'USA', 4086580, 'dsiw', '50010000010346', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ae716adfd3ef8c126ecf4a291b0115706fe6a2eb4862c8185b09aa2a3a09454d.jpg', 'Little kittens are trapped in a well, and it’s up to you to figure out how to get them out of trouble! This adorable and relaxing puzzle introduces totally new twists to the popular slide and match-3 mechanics and, of course, lots of cats. Slide rows or columns of cute, cuddly cats until you create a chain of three or more cats of the same kind to pull them out of the well. The game features a Mission and Quick-play mode with a combined 140 levels and an explanation of all the rules in a quick tutorial. The Mission mode provides new challenging objectives in each level, such as: clear the board with only one sidle or pull out all the shining cats. You need to accomplish the objective in order to advance to the next level. The Quick-play mode is all about beating your high score, and there are no restrictions on how to play. Just remember that longer chains can trigger funny bonuses and score you more points. The game will engage you in hours of fun, even if you are not a cat person!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ZivCu16.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5758, '000480044b585445', 'TWL-N-KXTE', '99Seconds', 'USA', 6048564, 'dsiw', '50010000010361', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/73d5d07a957db8811e99262e1fd8f22ebfaf0fb90dd460a76d28d402a6b867f0.jpg', '99Seconds, a fun, retro-style video game, where you can modify time to avoid all kinds of dangers.\n\nAfter finishing off Black Eye, V-99 entered a mysterious zone called Bit 8, without knowing why V-99 could modify time, slow it down and even stop it. But everything became complicated with the appearance of the BLACK VECTORS: mysterious beings that aim to destroy any intruder who reaches Bit 8.\n\n*Control V-99, dodging, using SLOW DOWN to slow, stop and even go back in time!\n*Arcade mobility like in the classic arcade games!\n*Retro-style levels!\n*Incredible enemy patterns!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/xF6MYKK.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5759, '0004000000082e00', 'CTR-N-RBUE', 'Tumble Pop™', 'USA', 3582820, 'eshop', '50010000011247', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/72e9eedb45a0e0574c0e91d65b7b41f7516e4949fd2f2cf7f108f21ceddd70e7.jpg', 'Thanks to pollution and other global calamities, Earth is overflowing with strange creatures. And what’s more, aliens from outer space have come to crash the party too! It’s your job to exterminate all the monsters plaguing the planet, but you’ll need some real muscle to accomplish that task. Good thing you have a secret weapon: a turbo-charged vacuum cleaner!\n<br><br>\nArmed with your trusty vacuum, work your way through eight monster-infested worlds. Special items, power-ups, and a password system will help you on your way, but at the end of the day, it’s all up to you! Hungry for even more action? Have no fear. You can create your own custom-built stages in Construction Mode!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/cL1000t.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5760, '0004000000059a00', 'CTR-N-RBGE', 'Lock''N Chase', 'USA', 3378020, 'eshop', '50010000008944', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5359967234f461c5d7a892f36af4c552721084a8f96e93b7ecfc51e5acc002ca.jpg', 'In this classic arcade game, play as a thief who is trying to score big by collecting his weight in gold. Duck in and out of alleys while scooping up coins along the way, and maybe you’ll get lucky and find some extra treasure! But being on the wrong side of the law is never easy, as the police are hot on your tail! If you think they’re coming too close, try using a sliding door or power-up items to block their chase.\n\nThink you can make a clean getaway? Test your skills in this game of Lock''N Chase!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Dnze0uZ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5761, '000400000008bc00', 'CTR-N-GACE', 'Shinobi™', 'USA', 5811044, 'eshop', '50010000009722', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/035c23a714f788f015873efcd432b1fd832e89a1d13a65e11f60ec976381061d.jpg', 'Only you can save them.\n<br><br>\nAs Joe Musashi, Red leader of the Oboro School of Shinobi, your destiny awaits. An evil force emanating from Neo City has captured your fellow students. Attack with your powerful katana as you battle for their freedom. Each ninja you rescue adds their formidable weaponry, training and Ninjutsu magic to yours.\n<br><br>\nDestroy the enemies with bombs, shurikens, a crescent blade and more. Use the magic of the ninja to wreak havoc with the force of a tornado or the blinding glow of lightning. When all else fails, turn your body into a living bomb and explode with concussive damage. Do not stop until the City of Fear is annihilated! Are you ready for the challenge of Ninja warfare?\n<br><br>\nSpecial abilities include running on water, swinging from a crescent blade and walking on ceilings<br>\nNinjutsu magic includes tornadoes, earthquakes and energy fields', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/jywWR7G.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5762, '000480044b4e4c45', 'TWL-N-KNLE', 'myNotebook: Red™', 'USA', 2257716, 'dsiw', '50010000003282', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/085ef2238d71e7727abcb2dfbb73f4e1e1f1f4f2140810b023eba332202b49ec.jpg', 'myNotebook allows you to take notes wherever you are. Just pop open your Nintendo DSi system and jot down your thoughts! Make a list and cross it off, or even play your favorite pen and paper games (games not included). You can even personalize your notebook by drawing on the cover and changing the paper type with 18 different unlockable squared and lined paper styles. Use the pen or pencil to make your notes or doodles and then erase the bits you don''t like. With five ink colors, you''ll always be able to make your notes and doodles look stylish.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/xfbiC95.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5763, '0004000000094700', 'CTR-N-TAXE', 'Ninja Gaiden®', 'USA', 6810468, 'eshop', '50010000012628', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2251b4849c1e9d27ed9b36f5411e0f1eb27d01e508556d3681e975ae60b8ad53.jpg', 'Original Release Date:  March 1989\n<br><br>\nPlayers take the role of Ryu Hayabusa, a rising warrior in his family''s clan whose main role in the world is to protect the Dark Dragon Blade from getting into the hands of evil. Ryu Hayabusa travels to America to seek vengeance for his father''s death.\n<br><br>\nPlayers fight their way through ten challenging side-scrolling levels while defeating gangs of street thugs, battling evil ninjas, and fighting barbarian bosses by using the deadly Dragon Sword, ninja skills, and ninja magic. Players can run, crouch, jump, and climb as they make their way through each stage and collect items to gain points, strength, and weapons.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/kSQ0Cbz.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5764, '0004000000094000', 'CTR-N-TAUE', 'Mighty Bomb Jack™', 'USA', 6609764, 'eshop', '50010000012629', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/67bf741f0fdeb9e2cca94781b9e40b555722de35091f9d642a4dc493eaafbd1d.jpg', 'Original Release Date:  July 1987<br>\nThe hero of the game, Jack, must make his way through 16 levels of a pyramid in order to defeat the demon Belzebut and rescue the royal Pamera family.  Each level is split into two parts: an action zone and a Royal Palace room.  Action zones can be split up into several portions, and contain power-ups, such as money bags, Mighty Coins, and Mighty Drinks, usually hidden in treasure chests.  Mighty Coins allow Jack to change colors, and Mighty Drinks add 10 seconds to the game''s timer.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/iPTCbFJ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5765, '000400000009e100', 'CTR-N-TBAE', 'Super C™', 'USA', 13155220, 'eshop', '50010000013117', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/77f5d9a7642f9115cee842b29f79165050aa96880ba6ff717e2a9865d65e4aa5.jpg', 'Original Release Date: December 1988<br><br>\n\nIn this action-packed sequel to the popular Contra, players have little time to think. Experience run-and-gun gameplay at its best as you take control of Mad Dog or Scorpion and once again battle the forces of Red Falcon. Stages feature a combination of perspectives (side scrolling, top down, etc.) and intense battles against huge bosses. Use a variety of powerful weapons and tap into your killer instinct to survive the deadly waves of enemies. Because if your trigger finger lacks stamina, then Earth will lack a future!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/VfLowvS.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5766, '0004000000087500', 'CTR-N-JMNE', 'Crazy Chicken Pirates 3D', 'USA', 26618724, 'eshop', '50010000011387', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0997f83c0d95bf95c8c79ab2ddcbe4d0cc2d1ff8c392679f7043eaa0d180e675.jpg', 'The splendor and the beauty of the Chicken Island would make it an ideal vacation spot - if it weren''t for those pirates. A one-legged captain, a gunner, a cutlass-wielding chicken and a treasure hunter... the island is home to countless perils, hidden extras and mysteries. The lords of the island are by no means willing to surrender themselves and their treasure without a fight.\n<br><br>\nCrazy Chicken Pirates 3D is a point & shoot action game where you take aim at birds as they scurry through the island and plunge bravely into the waves for a desperate counterattack. You only have 90 seconds to complete your raid by slaying pirates and collecting all hidden treasures.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/KX4sDVQ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5767, '000480044b354945', 'TWL-N-K5IE', '5 in 1 Solitaire', 'USA', 5765940, 'dsiw', '50010000001001', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/79084f37f0c3d69c481273a084216f76e0ac8aed32d3fbd9b217a181437c80c5.jpg', 'Now you can take five of the most popular solitaire games with you on the go! 5 in 1 Solitaire features the always popular Klondike, Spider and FreeCell games as well as the unique Golf and Gaps versions of solitaire. Each of these versions has a unique gameplay style that is easy enough for any novice player to enjoy, but will also challenge the expert solitaire player. You’ll also be able to view tutorials for each game as well as track your scores and gaming stats to see your progress. See how fast you can win!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Vn5VAZa.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5768, '000400000007de00', 'CTR-N-RBPE', 'Castlevania: The Adventure', 'USA', 3312484, 'eshop', '50010000012206', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6d8ec5899aaf2f38197f8842a74ce5ea670c723857eca2f1a0bbdc2706f412a6.jpg', 'Original Release Date:  December 1989\n<br><br>\nAfter getting his wings clipped, the death-defying Count Dracula has risen again.  Desiring revenge even more than blood, he''ll descend upon you with fangs glistening by the light of the full moon. Play the role of another hero from the long lineage of vampire hunters, the Belmont clan. Battle your way through the Count''s maze of torture chambers and vampire crypts. Unlock the castle''s secrets by locating hearts, crystals and crosses. \n<br><br>\nYou must also possess the strength to master the Mystic Whip, which wards off unearthly evils, like the She Worm. So risk your neck and accept the challenge. If you fail to destroy Dracula now, he will rule the night forever.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/WfZv5Pg.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5769, '0004000000083100', 'CTR-N-RBVE', 'The Sword of Hope II', 'USA', 3722084, 'eshop', '50010000011008', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/315a09243f2863e5886dd161c86fd6db6e2a3512128c01a2b09ec5242299a8ed.jpg', 'The Sword of Hope II is a Role Playing Game released in 1996, for the handheld video game device Game Boy.\n<br><br>\nYou will take on the role of young Prince Theo of Riccar, going on an adventure to find out the truth of the mystery which is threatening the Kingdom. The key to solve the numerous puzzles and gimmicks are the commands like "look", "open" and "hit". You will find your way looking around and finding many places and items during the adventure, with some friends waiting for to lend their hands on the way.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/E2EVFpA.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5770, '0004000000094a00', 'CTR-N-TAYE', 'Gradius®', 'USA', 6187876, 'eshop', '50010000012201', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/75a1edde51a8a61af4c09fbcea6bebc6375e7a4aec8a625c47ec2402d225f34a.jpg', 'Across the galaxy, there exists a distant planet known as Gradius.  Gradius'' peaceful existence has been brought to an end by an intense space invasion by a race known as the Bacterion.  To save the planet, the hyperspace fighter Vic Viper has been deployed to fight the Bacterion invasion.  Players pilot the Vic Viper through seven stages, shooting and dodging through deadly obstacles, while using various power-ups, including missiles, lasers, options and shields.  The Vic Viper''s target is the enemy fortress, Xaerous.  The only way to end the war is to plunge deep through the enemy forces and destroy its very core.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/lytj0aP.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5771, '0004000000050d00', 'CTR-N-RA7E', 'Side Pocket', 'USA', 3591012, 'eshop', '50010000007616', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/952e46adfa45e1bcef3ebb90c21290941ab37bc10b20c2922c21ff22ab0a8d50.jpg', 'Chalk up, and get ready for some cool pool action! Stroke a mean cue, and you might just work your way to the big time in the Pocket Competition. Execute consecutive shots, sink by numerical order, and perform amazing trick shots such as massés and jumps for a chance to earn additional points or shots. If you manage to sink a ball in a pocket marked with a star, you''ll get a chance for bonuses!\n\nTest your billiard skills in two great modes! Pocket offers the traditional 16-ball game, and 9-Ball is a more contemporary version of the sport but still quite the challenge!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/b2cvnqD.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5772, '0004000000093800', 'CTR-N-RB7E', 'Mole Mania™', 'USA', 3967844, 'eshop', '50010000011386', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/43f60911cc7105412a32317c2de79451dbbf7e005ab5d7f98f599fcc96e1248a.jpg', 'Original Release Date:  February 1997\n<br><br>\nJoin Muddy Mole in a race to defeat the evil farmer, Jinbe. Work your way through each puzzle by pushing, pulling, or throwing black balls to defeat or trap enemies. Blast strategic exits and burrow into soft soil to tunnel your way through underground paths to the next action-packed level. Defeat the bosses and solve all of the puzzles in Jinbe Land to reunite Muddy Mole with his beloved wife and kids. You''ll dig the fast pace and challenging fun of Mole Mania!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/gSfFtwl.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5773, '000480044b493745', 'TWL-N-KI7E', 'Music on: Learning Piano Volume 2', 'USA', 4328244, 'dsiw', '50010000002013', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2c81903b84c9521b0a8ba05e83240c9de35c25e7bb3fb45e47116b9c4a17cabf.jpg', 'Bravissimo! The entire orchestra follows your performance of 15 great classics. By playing each day, your ability may increase. Earn the bronze, silver and gold medals for each song, completing all different levels. A simplified music score is shown on the upper screen and a full piano keyboard on the touch screen, guiding beginners note by note on their first steps.\n\nSongs included:\n*Air on the G string (J.S.Bach)\n*Frühlingslied Op. 62 (F.Mendelssohn)\n*Gymnopédie No.1 (E.Satie)\n*La Campanella (F.Liszt)\n*Gnossienne No.1 (E.Satie)\n*Pavane for a dead Princess (M.Ravel)\n*Rêverie (C.Debussy)\n*Piano Concerto No.1 (P.I.Tchaikovsky)\n*Etude Op 25 No.1 (F.Chopin)\n*Of foreign lands and peoples Op 15 (R.Schumann)\n*Impromptus Op 142 D. 935/2 (F.Schubert)\n*Impromptus Op 90 D. 899/3 (F.Schubert)\n*The Seasons Op 37 June (P.I.Tchaikovsky)\n*The Nutcracker: Waltz of the Flowers (P.I.Tchaikovsky)\n*The 4 Seasons: Winter 2. Largo (A.Vivaldi)', 'none', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/FHBF5Kh.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5774, '000400000008ac00', 'CTR-N-RBYE', 'Kirby''s Star Stacker™', 'USA', 3722084, 'eshop', '50010000013050', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1c36ea0347ed26cbd1631dbefb000aad623f42a049b34f65d98193d43acb2925.jpg', 'Original Release Date: April 1997\n<p>\nJoin Kirby as he stacks the falling stars with help from his friends, Rick the Hamster, Kine the Sunfish, and Coo the Owl. Watch out for King Dedede. He is out to stop you!  With a few quick moves and some well-timed strategy, you can quickly outwit him and move on to the next challenging level. \n\nKirby’s Star Stacker features pure puzzle fun for everyone. From above, blocks rain down constantly.  From below, whole lines appear with unrelenting clock-like regularity. Simply sandwich the stars between Kirby’s pals and you’ll soon be on your way to the high score.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ce0fOyY.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5775, '000400000007e400', 'CTR-N-RBRE', 'MYSTICAL NINJA starring GOEMON', 'USA', 3672932, 'eshop', '50010000011906', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2acbb64cf66f31aa0cf75523d043a2f32b1f14e1a31dfaa7f608eb66381ecf69.jpg', 'Original Release Date:  April 1998                                        A mysterious group of pirates called "The Black Ship Gang," appear in the Great Edo Harbor, and begin wreaking havoc across the land.  Join Goemon and his friends Ebisumaru and Sasuke as they battle to save ancient Japan from the clutches of the evil gang, and rescue their fellow ninja Yae from the gang''s clutches.  MYSTICAL NINJA starring GOEMON is an action role-playing game featuring three different characters to control, each with unique skills.  Fight your way from Karakuri Castle, through bustling villages, all the way to Skull Island.  Visit towns and question the inhabitants for clues, buy items to aid your quest, and solve brain-teasing puzzles to seek out Yae and defeat the pirates.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/bLqJqwo.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5776, '000400000007e100', 'CTR-N-RBQE', 'Quarth®', 'USA', 3308388, 'eshop', '50010000012032', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/43fe1c5a3ce46e9f4ac9824cc4ba539ab69a081ab2aac7b951998c5aaa3532ac.jpg', 'Original Release Date: December 1990\nQuarth is the blockbuster puzzle challenge guaranteed to knock your socks off at a maddening, mind-numbing pace.  With a rain of bionic block patterns descending upon you, you must race back and forth in your powerful Block-buster ship destroying the blocks before they blow you up.  Stay alive and rake in points for every block you wipe out.  If you chalk up enough points to qualify, you''ll charge into bonus games where it''s you against the clock and the unstoppable blocks of Quarth.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/U4cbsUt.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5777, '0004000000050a00', 'CTR-N-RA6E', 'Burger Time Deluxe™', 'USA', 3439460, 'eshop', '50010000007908', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/226d7ee6d581d3c8966208402c8abe8fcdc0791465c2dcb40bbcff5367aebe65.jpg', 'Give Chef Peter Pepper a helping hand in creating the ultimate hamburger! Each hamburger ingredient is located on a different platform, and the chef must climb through a series of ladders in order to reach them. Walk across the ingredient to drop it closer to the waiting plate down below. Once all of the burgers have been completed, you’ll be able to move on to the next level! But watch out! Renegade ingredients will stop at nothing to put an end to our chef’s cooking days!  Dodge them, stun them using pepper, or drop a hamburger ingredient on top of them to stop their chase! If you run out of pepper, collect bonus foods such as coffee, chocolate, or fries to recharge! It’s a non-stop food-fight in this classic arcade game!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/RUwuYNR.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5778, '0004000000058800', 'CTR-N-RBFE', 'Maru''s Mission', 'USA', 3390308, 'eshop', '50010000009139', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7b25fb9af81945a7796550b7c7218aeb8dcce3de69f7ddf4d79a5c30421b6e04.jpg', 'Play as the ninja Maru in this action-packed side-scrolling game that will take you on a journey across the world!\n\nWhile Maru is out for a walk with his girlfriend Cori, an evil samurai named Muramasa suddenly appears and kidnaps her! In Maru''s efforts to track down and rescue her, he must face a number of mythological monsters while gaining new and powerful weapons in order to defeat them. Using the hints that are left behind by his enemies, Maru will follow a trail that will lead him across six different locations--including the bug-infested forests of America and the scorching desert sands of Egypt. Help our hero on his mission as he fights to rescue Cori!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/UplPFvN.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5779, '00040000000e5b00', 'CTR-N-AAWE', 'Phineas and Ferb: Quest for Cool Stuff', 'USA', 275753828, 'eshop', '50010000015796', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0e0a0a34b74dcd41f1c97a3dda006d93cf4e7355e476a28c790905fc8c72beee.jpg', 'There’s a whole lot of stuff to do during the last week of summer vacation and Phineas and Ferb want to do it all! Join these charismatic brothers of invention as they create, travel and explore in their quest for treasures to add to the Museum of Cool.\n<br><br>\nPerry the pet platypus, aka Agent P, has their backs when bumbling villain Dr. Doofenshmirtz unleashes his latest obscure -inator devices designed to take over the entire Tri-State area! \n<br><br>\nPlay as Phineas, Ferb and Perry/Agent P as you interact with supporting characters from the show including Dr. Doofenshmirtz, Candace, Isabella, Buford and Baljeet.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/lFhPCOC.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5780, '000400000013ea00', 'CTR-N-KWSE', 'Comic Workshop', 'USA', 122768228, 'eshop', '50010000024155', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7e014a5900ff4c9f2cbe3643cf51f3145f69fae57e70498bbccead8b5d22ce95.jpg', 'No need to wait any more, here is the software you were looking for!\n<br><br>\nWith Comic Workshop, you will be able to easily create Comics and Manga, step by step, thanks to the various tools available.\n<br><br>\nFrom frame’s management to text entry, everything you need to make the best creations is gathered in this software.\n<br><br>\nSpeech Bubbles, Pattern Filling, Stickers or other Roller Stamps are not only useful but also fun to use! Many standard tools are also present like the Eraser, Straight Line tool, Color Picker, Selection tool, etc.\n<br><br>\nFeatures:\nIn-game detailed Lessons to learn about the interface and tool’s functions.<br>\nCustomize and make your own colors as well as your own Stickers and Roller Stamps!<br>\nProfessional interface with layers, Undo & Redo commands, import of photos/pictures, etc.<br>\nInterface fully controllable with the Stylus and a left-handed mode is also available!<br>\nSave your creations on your SD Card and print or share them!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/XH0naLw.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5781, '00040000000c9500', 'CTR-N-JMYJ', 'peakvox ミュウミュウトレイン', 'JPN', 19929956, 'eshop', '50010000013111', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bdc9885f2b60286429d6aea648afcd30d17dd0ab9ceb2860d486fae69c1871bd.jpg', 'ダッシュとジャンプだけの簡単操作でゴールを目指すアクションゲームです。\n<br>逃げまわるネコたちをつかまえればつかまえるほど、猛スピードでかけぬけて行くことができます。\n<br>\n<br>ゴールタイムのランクに応じて手に入るメダルを集めて、さまざまなアイテムをアンロック! ちょっとやそっとじゃ攻略できない全30ステージで、すべてのメダルを手に入れよう!\n<br>\n<br>ほかにも、Miiでプレイできるようになったり、すれちがい通信で他のプレイヤーとベストタイムやゴーストを交換できたり、いつの間に通信でpeakvoxからお知らせやゴーストが届いたりなど、やりこみ要素が盛りだくさんです。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/96fb5345dd4b0cce4924a7c371c10bf048a9806ed93bc1f3263c21cca29b550f.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/99waIx6.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/2TjEPmP.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5782, '0004000000126800', 'CTR-N-JCPJ', 'ハコボーイ!', 'JPN', 81468308, 'eshop', '50010000025215', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/94efc0669e86328b60d9a8e669973ba8f25310e4b79b31bfe09909883d201686.jpg', 'ハコを出すことができる主人公「キュービィ」を操作し、ハコを使って段差や穴、仕掛けなどのさまざまな障害を乗り越えて進んでいく、パズルアクションゲームです。まっすぐ積み上げたり、階段状に出したり、フックのように引っかけたり。ハコをどんな形で出して、どう使うかという、ひらめきが試される150以上のステージを収録しています。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/61661480aa1abe3c175580344f3e477db0b01823378814142745380f915e8f43.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/0mpA7kJ.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/fpyL4QP.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5783, '00040000000e9300', 'CTR-N-JD5J', '@SIMPLE DLシリーズ Vol.14 THE 脱出ゲーム ～裏切りの密室～', 'JPN', 111860580, 'eshop', '50010000015299', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/dfdad100c0bc16f9f2ad163715f051644c01d2040ea34a26887d62eaf9b4257d.jpg', '何者かによって閉じ込められた危険な密室から、生死を賭けて脱出を試みる『THE 脱出ゲーム』の第2弾。今作では友達のクルミやダイスケと協力して脱出するステージも用意。カラクリ忍者屋敷、2層式エレベーター、走行中の特急列車など、さまざまな密室を舞台に、命がけの「脱出ゲーム」が再びはじまる。\n<br>\n<br>■「今回もまた、私のゲームに付き合ってもらおう」 \n<br>危険な脱出ゲームの発端が数年前のある出来事ではないかと気づいたケンタロウ。真相を確かめようとするが、その途中エレベーターが突如停止し、スピーカーから聞き覚えのある声が流れ出す。……そして再び危険な「ゲーム」が始まった。 \n<br>\n<br>■仲間と協力して脱出せよ! \n<br>ケンタロウと一緒に閉じ込められたサークルの友達･クルミやダイスケと協力して脱出するステージも。彼らとの何気ない会話から、思わぬ脱出のヒントが得られるかも? \n<br>\n<br>■5ステージの危険な密室 \n<br>カラクリ忍者屋敷、2層式エレベーター、走行中の特急列車など、あらゆる日常が危険な非日常に。全5ステージ収録。 \n<br>\n<br>■ヒント機能&やりこみ要素 \n<br>「推理する」コマンドでいつでもヒントをきくことができ、初心者の方や謎解きが苦手な方でも安心してプレイOK。前作で好評だった「実績」システムも搭載し、より深く楽しむことができる。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/456d0cdda171561faecc0093b2a64a3ef802225d10f54eb3f181a3308678971f.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/062KaAu.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/cq3we3R.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47');
INSERT INTO `3dsgames` (`id`, `titleID`, `serial`, `name`, `region`, `size`, `type`, `contentID`, `iconURL`, `gdesc`, `thumb`, `scrcount`, `imgur_iconURL`, `imgur_thumb`, `count`, `time`) VALUES
(5784, '00040000000e9200', 'CTR-N-JD4J', '@SIMPLE DLシリーズ Vol.12 THE 脱出ゲーム 危険な5つの密室', 'JPN', 107875172, 'eshop', '50010000014070', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1eca6948e0c069677656215980fcb4ec4cdb2117a4829e6bbcf465ce22833f04.jpg', '『THE 密室からの脱出』シリーズのD3から新たな『脱出』が登場。\n<br>\n<br>主人公のケンタロウは何者かの手によって危険な脱出ゲームに参加させられてしまう。謎の部屋、トイレ、走行中のクルマなど、5つの密室から生きて脱出するため、密室をすみずみまで探索してアイテムや手がかりを入手し、数々の謎や罠を解き明かそう。\n<br>\n<br>■「ゲーム」の犯人は誰だ? 密室サスペンスストーリー\n<br>目が覚めると、そこは見知らぬ密室。窓はなく扉も開かない。そして響き渡る犯人の声。「君はその部屋に監禁されている。ルールは簡単。そこから脱出するだけだ」。そして死の脱出ゲームが始まった。\n<br>\n<br>■魅力的なキャラクターたち\n<br>主人公のケンタロウや、その彼女サクラをはじめ、「ゲーム」の全貌はとあるサークルのメンバーたちによって徐々に明らかになっていく。\n<br>\n<br>■多彩な密室が登場 日常が「ゲーム」の舞台に\n<br>窓ひとつない謎の密室、居酒屋のトイレ、走り続けなければ爆発するクルマなど、さまざまな日常が「ゲーム」の舞台となる。全5ステージ収録。\n<br>\n<br>■ヒント機能･やりこみ要素\n<br>謎解きに詰まったら好きなタイミングでヒントを聞くことができ、初心者の方でも安心してプレイOK。また特定の条件を満たすと獲得できる「実績」システムも搭載で、上級者も納得のやり応え。\n<br>\n<br>■D3×インテンス!\n<br>開発担当は、『THE 密室からの脱出』をはじめ、脱出ゲーム制作随一の実績を誇る株式会社インテンス!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4ecf8fa32af256a11704b3312d65d85f9a5a0572d819127fa9a487511c6c44ed.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/3oKk9J8.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/26cSoL3.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5785, '0004000000119f00', 'CTR-N-QBBJ', 'ポケモンカードGB', 'JPN', 4238180, 'eshop', '50010000020074', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/15c86475680771047390e6f9ce966fd80652b8a01fca1cf2d33d2a115eb86bcb.jpg', 'このソフトは、1998年に発売されたゲームボーイカラー用のカードゲームです。\nプレイヤーは伝説のポケモンカードを求めて、さまざまな強敵とカードで対戦します。勝利するともらえる「拡張パック」でカードを集めてデッキを強化し、8人の個性的なクラブマスターに挑みましょう。\n登場するカードは200種類以上。カードゲームを遊んだことがなくても、くわしいルール解説があり、ポケモンカードゲームの世界をたっぷり楽しめます。\n\n※現行の「ポケモンカードゲーム」とは、一部のルールが異なります。あらかじめご了承ください。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d97d1e99eaf0d2a757501ed283e4568dcdda570649f787657f85f8bc86c1d924.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/hv2YFaa.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/eVnBufT.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5786, '0004000000093e00', 'CTR-N-TATJ', 'スーパーマリオブラザーズ2', 'JPN', 5983076, 'eshop', '50010000011227', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c683db604c1f0a67fc112a440c901776b01199f70f077c51901c7b4e17bfbd5c.jpg', 'このソフトは、1986年に発売されたファミリーコンピュータ･ディスクシステム用のアクションゲームです。\nさらわれたピーチ姫を助け出し、キノコ王国を甦らせるために新たな冒険に出たマリオとルイージ。操作しやすい安定した動きのマリオと、高く跳べるけれどちょっと滑りやすいという個性をもつルイージ。特徴の異なる2人が、個性を活かしてゴールを目指します。取るとミスになる毒キノコが出現するなど、前作とは一味違った冒険が楽しめます。\n', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0de95329de63364b6115cc446b55559bcbe557620bb81936ee7e501e1c8c5249.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/HQRsOI0.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/vkHdZZI.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5787, '0004000200163601', 'CTR-T-KS3J', 'Simple DL Series Vol 36: The Misshitsu Kara no Dasshutsu: Tabi ha Michidure! Tetsudou-Hen', 'JPN', 37650432, 'demo', '50030000005908', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5788, '000400000010fd00', 'CTR-N-QA6J', 'ゲームボーイギャラリー3', 'JPN', 4189028, 'eshop', '50010000019613', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5f89b44fce0f030203c7bd320dff5d857e75d50888645b4f2e70460d68a07065.jpg', 'このソフトは、1999年に発売されたゲームボーイカラー用のアクションゲームです。\n1980年代に発売された携帯型液晶ゲーム機「ゲーム＆ウオッチ」のゲーム5作を遊ぶことができます。転がってくる食べ物をキャッチする「エッグ」、上下2つの部屋にある花を敵から守る「グリーンハウス」、動物の上に乗って荷物を運ぶ「タートルブリッジ」、マリオとルイージを操作してコンベアを流れる荷物をトラックまで運ぶ「マリオブラザーズ」、ジャンプやツタで敵をかわしながらカギを取ってドンキーコングを助ける「ドンキーコング JR.」を収録。「ゲーム＆ウオッチ」発売当時の内容をそのまま再現した「むかし」モードと、現代風にアレンジした「いま」モードが用意されています。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4203296217e59a55cd86fc3d2236583cda67ca2cd2aa8fe3942ca05c6b287f9e.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/MEgprTd.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/4WkIRQP.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5789, '000400000009e000', 'CTR-N-TBAJ', 'SUPER魂斗羅', 'JPN', 12053396, 'eshop', '50010000012028', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1b6f1b42a735b4ef0591980f81992c1316cee91d4135f66fb53bafea5c3270c5.jpg', 'このソフトは、1990年に発売されたファミリーコンピュータ用のアクションシューティングゲームです。\n「魂斗羅」と呼ばれるゲリラ戦のスペシャリストが、パワーアップアイテムで武器を強化しながら、襲いくるエイリアンを倒して進みます。横スクロール形式の「ノーマル画面」のエリアと、上から見下ろす形式の「TOP VIEW画面」のエリアがあり、それぞれ操作方法や使えるアクションが異なります。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/89ab1dc0bb3b45729dfcab7b07822ceddd5f02ad4224f2d870d4049d6b2c3411.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/8CZRna3.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/hslfx9y.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5790, '000400020017aa01', 'CTR-T-KS9J', '@SIMPLE DLシリーズ Vol.39 THE 密室からの脱出 体験版', 'JPN', 39350272, 'demo', '50030000006707', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5791, '00040000000df500', 'CTR-N-TDFJ', 'バトルシティー', 'JPN', 12237716, 'eshop', '50010000015353', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/075de0795e351a5fca18f94bfc04bbc8353d93a5fb414e5cc9eb17ff0677e8fb.jpg', 'このソフトは、1985年に発売されたファミリーコンピュータ用のシューティングゲームです。\nマイタンク（戦車）を操作し、司令部を守りながら決められた数の敵を倒すとステージクリアになります。赤く点滅した敵タンクを倒すと出現するスペシャルターゲットを取ると、マイタンクがパワーアップしたり、敵の動きが止まったりと、さまざまな効果があります。\n特徴の異なる数々のバトルフィールドを舞台に、前に出て敵を撃つか、守りを固めるか、戦略的なプレイが楽しめます。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b7569d5d1b5f5925b795e70ad11e6800de9145c043444e45db5b79b0bc0ca6c6.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/L30IUjy.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/tR1iT3A.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5792, '000400000f702f00', 'KTR-N-UARE', 'Donkey Kong Country 3: Dixie Kong''s Double Trouble™', 'ALL', 10005348, 'eshop', '50010000040455', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/a8879d029a233e18d96c57382c298a681af71811280465dd80800a7dbb56b013.jpg', 'Donkey Kong and Diddy Kong have gone missing! As Dixie Kong checks in with the rest of the family, she gets stuck with babysitting duties! But that won''t stop her from going on her next adventure!\n<br><br>\nPlay as Dixie Kong or Kiddy Kong solo, against a friend, or with a friend! Take advantage of each of their unique abilities as they throw each other into action in over 40 levels. There are plenty of collectibles—including Bear Coins, which grant access to the services of the Brothers Bear, and Banana Birds, which Wrinkly Kong has a deep fondness for.\n<br><br>\nYou can also call on Funky Kong to build some wild vehicles for you to try to get to places that seem far out of reach. Not to mention there are animal friends to fight at your side! The final showdown takes place in a cliff-top laboratory at the End of the World. Things could get seriously ugly, so you''d better be ready!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/1RhkkIM.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5793, '0004000e0016ee00', 'CTR-U-KASE', 'ASH Update Ver. 1.1', 'USA', 1215284, 'update', '50010000040535', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3a380be743e123c431f5e158c6baff40817327bd3d0d77b3601f650d831e457d.jpg', 'This is an update for ASH game. This download does not contain the full version of the title. In order to use this update, you must have the full version of ASH.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2b12fc4e23dbaf745dafe3f2be4111ba3d1f5ae094a5c6480f01cb61f34b763d.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/XmHyDr2.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/AGdU0Pq.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5794, '000400000009ee00', 'CTR-N-JN2J', '一騎当千!スマッシュヒーローズ', 'JPN', 31689572, 'eshop', '50010000010414', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2a72f1f5a37898bac279340d9c18b893ead5d22a9ce76b7bedddebf32ceed26a.jpg', '無数の敵を、斬って、斬って、ふっとばす、ふっとばしアクションゲームです。\n<br>ふっとばしで敵を連続撃破する爽快感は、まさに一騎当千!\n<br>Yボタン連打でつながるコンボ攻撃、Yボタン長押しで放たれるチャージ攻撃で敵をふっとばせ!\n<br>ゲームボリュームは、使用可能キャラクター6匹、総ステージ数80以上!\n<br>キャラクターごとに異なるアクション性、豊富なミッションに育成要素、さらにはコミカルなストーリー展開と、遊びごたえ十分です。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1f4b50148ec73e22dd6d13351d180893a667372e7f2e6ed18a9288c2ef4dd6a3.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/zC7x3jk.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/OgOJxYT.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5795, '00040000000bf900', 'CTR-N-JP4J', 'ぷよぷよ!!ミニバージョン', 'JPN', 54401892, 'eshop', '50010000012410', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7d693f1d4ac2f1dbed21539cf43e6625d136e52ef732ff155addb4afe1f95410.jpg', 'シリーズ20周年記念ソフト『ぷよぷよ!!』の中から、内容を厳選して収録したお買い得プライスのミニバージョン。\n<br>\n<br>アルル･アミティ･りんご･ラフィーナの4人のキャラクターから1人を選択し、『ぷよぷよ』『ぷよぷよ通』『ぷよぷよフィーバー』『ペアでぷよぷよ』の4つのルールでCOMと対戦して遊べる「フリーたいせん」、りんごを主人公とした「ストーリー」全8話を収録。まんざいデモとぷよ勝負が楽しめます。\n<br>さらに、ゲームを進めると、十字ボタンの上で「まきもどし」ができる練習モード「とことんれんしゅう」と、「フリーたいせん」で選ぶことができる「カーバンクル」も登場します。\n', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/800751791f4cfc793f58910793b5e5f0dfc376e32bfb5a089b9b75e0e80f51fd.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/CeHUa5f.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/unP2A0Q.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5796, '0004000000145300', 'CTR-N-KC2J', '魔神少女 -Chronicle 2D ACT-', 'JPN', 138206052, 'eshop', '50010000024496', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/353656fd719a1977610cc4e6db00aa7dc1afaf61e3d0df4ee2fca7c361b95dc7.jpg', '『魔神少女』は、様々な魔法を使って、敵を倒して進んでいく2Dアクションゲームです。\n<br>\n<br>ステージによって、いろんな敵や仕掛けがプレイヤーの目の前に登場します。\n<br>\n<br>敵やボスを倒すことで、キャラクターがどんどん成長していきます。\n<br>\n<br>好きなステージを選び、奥にいるボスキャラを倒していきましょう。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2a2fae47a06d3ea0d084bbf8fe79ce2f618708691774f118210229785517c3f8.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/EyxJBQc.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/tD4NfQb.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5797, '000400000017ad00', 'CTR-N-KRVJ', '第2次スーパーロボット大戦 ニンテンドー3DS移植版', 'JPN', 2157412, 'eshop', '50010000035975', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d3cdd27e7aea21ae0c8404354153242e5a83039dbafd7bd0f4acdd30fdaa0db6.jpg', 'ファミコンソフトとして発売された『第2次スーパーロボット大戦』が、ニンテンドー3DS移植版として遊べます。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/60cf2d9f3a0180b01133deeceb36e8c099b34d9eda86025d483649302d243f9b.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/FLhsIgg.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/7XXp6pN.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5798, '0004000000126700', 'CTR-N-JWTP', 'Another World - 20th Anniversary Edition', 'EUR', 74365796, 'eshop', '50010000022876', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/214b79a7cb92ca0609259d81e61718e40ae2249d3d8629a00474ffee8b9f7d99.jpg', 'Also known as Out Of This World™\nand released across more than a\ndozen platforms since its 1991 debut,\nAnother World™ has attained cult\nstatus among critics and sophisticated\ngamers alike for its cinematic effects\nin the graphics, sound and cut scenes.\n<br/><br/>\nAN IMMERSIVE ADVENTURE WITH\nUNIQUE STORYTELLING\n<br/><br/>\nAnother World™ chronicles the story\nof Lester Knight Chaykin a young\nscientist hurtled through space and\ntime by a nuclear experiment that\ngoes wrong. In an alien and\ninhospitable world, you will have to\ndodge, outwit, and overcome the host\nof alien monsters, while surviving an\nenvironment as deadly as your\nenemies. Only a perfect blend of logic\nand skill will get you past the deadly\nobstacles that lie in wait.\n<br/><br/>\n20TH ANNIVERSARY EDITION\nESPECIALLY DESIGNED FOR\nCONSOLE\n<br/><br/>\n* Remastered presentation: a joint\neffort between visionary\ngame-designer Eric Chahi and\ndeveloper Martial Hesse Dreville,\nAnother World is back in its 20th\nAnniversary Edition with High\nDefinition graphics faithful to the\noriginal design.\n<br/><br/>\n* 3 difficulty modes, Normal (easier\nthan original game), Difficult (Equal to\noriginal game) and Hardcore (more\ndifficult than original game).\n<br/><br/>\n* Choose between 100% remastered\nSounds/FX, Original Sound and\nOriginal CD in-game soundtrack.\n<br/><br/>\n* Switch between Original/HD\ngraphics.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/dbb75b9bbe1e2d0ab28e5e0346b151786f3595780adb57b8b0d6cf5e67dcaf98.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/5nvBgLG.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/uegoOMG.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5799, '0004000200186301', 'CTR-T-KMJP', 'The Legend of Dark Witch Episode 2(DEMO)', 'EUREUR', 107352064, 'demo', '50030000008266', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
