(5845, '000400000016f000', 'CTR-N-JTQE', 'Gotcha Racing™', 'USA', 113666916, 'eshop', '50010000036597', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4a6a50fc95d20b7b02a7966222301d0fd29ba705a67ffae8ec27b8eeb5cb540e.jpg', 'Enjoy the fast-paced action of a top-down racing game, but with a twist! All of the parts you use to make your car are dispensed by Capsule Machines! Therefore, when you start racing, you won''t have the greatest car, but as you progress and gain access to better Capsule Machines, your car will become the envy of the racing world! The game uses both screens together when you race, so the tracks will appear huge on your Nintendo 3DS™, and even more so on your Nintendo 3DS XL! And you''re free to customize your car any way you like! Try to make the ultimate, unbeatable car! Compete on 12 different tracks, race in Grand Prix races, and compete in 6 different racing grades! The game includes 6 grades of Capsule Machines, and even more special Capsule Machines you can unlock! You can even combine parts to raise their stats! In addition, you can use StreetPass to race against other players and receive new parts!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/p3D6CPJ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5846, '000480044b543845', 'TWL-N-KT8E', 'GO Series Tower of Deus', 'USA', 4212532, 'dsiw', '50010000003841', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bbe8106d7d1050fc51183a0021cbb58709398b74e73c1c8446d03ddafd4b1487.jpg', 'Overcome a deadly curse as you race to the top of the tower in this dark, atmospheric, 2D platform game. The only way to release the curse is to reach the top before the clock runs out. \n\nTower of Deus is modeled after an old-fashioned, 2D platform game from the 80’s. Take control of a cursed man and race upwards, higher and higher inside a tower, in a desperate race to break the curse. You''ll need to overcome hordes of ghastly creatures and demons that lay in wait obscuring the twisting path to the top. Run, jump and fly your way to the top, with time always against you. There are 40 eerie levels with 10 types of gothic-style graphics, not for the easily scared or faint-hearted.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Wdwh9EY.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5847, '000480044b514b45', 'TWL-N-KQKE', 'Ace Mathician', 'USA', 4541236, 'dsiw', '50010000010889', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/28090fc05de7596352d51e91e152b6341ff88d23f652dffea3c19a0943df45cf.jpg', 'Ever wondered why you needed to learn math in school? The answer is simple; to change the world! And that''s exactly what you get to do in this game!\n　\nYou play as a cute Koala named Ace who loves fruit! Unfortunately a few delicious pieces of fruit are just out of reach and you need to change the positions of the platforms to get to the fruit!\n　\nYou can change the positions of the platform by entering a math formula.\n　\nThere''s no right or wrong answer, every formula the player can come up with will have an effect on the world! Suddenly math becomes as fun as drawing!\n　\nThere are many possible ways to finish a level... be creative!\n　\nLater levels will feature enemies and traps keeping the game challenging. And while your at it, you can collect stars for a better score!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/V3KKVzW.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5848, '000480044b4b4e45', 'TWL-N-KKNE', 'Flipper 2 - Flush the Goldfish', 'USA', 8522548, 'dsiw', '50010000009025', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/1e0c59415140d1edf8c790b937d87655134a50c50f5417d6b6ab279a21b3d06f.jpg', 'The boy has been kidnapped by an evil monster and there is no time to waste! Flush has to act quickly in order to rescue his best friend and owner. Luckily, Flush has a super-secret robot suit...that will make things easier!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/cbEwBW7.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5849, '000480044b355545', 'TWL-N-K5UE', 'Crazy Train', 'USA', 4282164, 'dsiw', '50010000039335', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ce9c8bca81bc81a45c015c6cda55f2bc9faafbb35f1a99c999c921617f0d716c.jpg', 'Crazy Train is an easy to learn and hard to master puzzle game that''s a highly addictive. Put on your thinking cap because hopeless train director Lionel Steeltrack needs your help sending passenger and cargo trains to their correct stations! Don’t get "sidetracked"... as you need to make sure your trains don’t crash.\n<br><br>\nJust when you think you got the hang of it, the pace increases as the speed of trains and their frequency in which they enter the game field becomes fast and furious. All of a sudden... It''s railroad madness!\n<br><br>\nJump into story mode where there are four unqiue track layout to complete. Or take part in challenge mode where the difficulty and speed is ever increasing.\n<br><br>\nWith the proper concentration and practice you will become a master engineer!\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ElgSPKw.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5850, '000480044b584b45', 'TWL-N-KXKE', 'Goony', 'USA', 5279540, 'dsiw', '50010000013531', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e5e1b49ec651b834b8a3957cf698ce3f08ff86a560df053768d13bae01cfa92c.jpg', 'Goony is a one-button arcade game for casual and core gamers. You control Goony, a jelly-like creature, who is running down a road with hazardous obstacles. The goal of the game is to stay alive for as long as possible. Goony is constantly on the move. He goes either left or right.\n<br><br>\nSpecial blocks, which can help you, are scattered across the playfield. The playfield is infinitely long and lasts until you make a mistake. The number of steps you took is your final score.\n<br><br>\nFeatures:<br>\nRandom generated, infinitely long playfield<br>\nDraw your own blocks using the built-in Block editor<br>\nExchange user generated blocks locally or online via QR Codes<br>\nRace against a buddy on the same system in multiplayer mode', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ptFtWfe.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5851, '000480044b545954', 'TWL-N-KTYT', 'Snapdots™', 'USA', 3281716, 'dsiw', '50010000006402', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/47b476df31c26714b77eb9548d94d32c37a66cc2928f2dd4c75ed31650c55e34.jpg', 'Welcome to Snapdots! Complete dozens of puzzle pictures by rotating the puzzle to find the best angle and then shooting blocks from your UFO. If the placement isn’t quite right, use the UFO to grab blocks back to shoot them in different spots. Adding to the challenge, puzzles often contain several types of blocks and spots, each with its own characteristics, on the playing grid. Journey to multiple planets to tackle puzzles individually in Puzzle mode or try to clear as many puzzles as you can within the time limit in frenetic Time Attack mode. In either mode, the combination of strategy and action result in a classic puzzle game that definitely hits the right spot!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/RV94y1s.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5852, '0004000000048100', 'CTR-N-AMHJ', 'モンスターハンター3(トライ)G', 'JPN', 1835912036, 'eshop', '50010000007993', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/fa056ce1e03d3dc53cc5930d3dcb09db4dbfb3fe853567fa56be3039ee72267b.jpg', '雄大な自然の広がるモンスターハンターの世界では無数の巨大なモンスターが複雑な生態を持って生活している。プレイヤーはモンスターの狩猟を生業とする者・ハンターとなりゲームを進めていく。ニンテンドー3DSの特徴を活かした機能に加え通信協力プレイやダウンロードクエスト配信により、濃密な狩猟生活を体験できる。\n<br>\n<br>※本作は、拡張スライドパッドに対応しています。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/cf27e993ec0f56fa3cd18b1cb008bd9c75ac97ba33847f6263c3865b31d8bacd.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/MK8lBbW.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/4jUL98r.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5853, '00040000000a0b00', 'CTR-N-ANEJ', '大合奏!バンドブラザーズP', 'JPN', 579038052, 'eshop', '50010000017473', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b420b1183232e970a11860d4ac704e24f2476cd8b1c540e94183d021fe2b242a.jpg', '演奏、合奏、作曲と音楽をトコトン楽しめる『大合奏!バンドブラザーズ』シリーズ最新作。自分そっくりのボーカロイド™を操作するボーカルパートが追加され、さらに音楽の世界に没頭できるようになりました。インターネットに接続すれば、自分の好きな曲をダウンロードできたり、遠くの人とセッションすることもできます。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3b1d610dae50ff1d3375b8e97abf64fe1de8a4dc553560d44cefca7ea5138d53.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/mqdynWP.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/yCE0SOb.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5854, '0004000000072000', 'CTR-N-AFEJ', 'ファイアーエムブレム 覚醒', 'JPN', 1281649508, 'eshop', '50010000009786', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/86e58ac14e60b19f7a853e81ddb7b953bb474d85347567e69b59c57746644051.jpg', '壮大な物語と、戦略シミュレーションの醍醐味が楽しめる「ファイアーエムブレム」シリーズ5年ぶりの完全新作。。\n<br>プレイヤーであるあなたは、イーリス聖王国の王子クロムと出会い、彼が率いる自警団の軍師として、世界の存亡を賭けた戦いに身を投じることになります。\n<br>ローカルプレイで他のプレイヤーと協力して勝ち抜き戦に挑む「デュアルタッグ」や、すれちがい通信を使ったマイチームのやり取り、いつの間に通信での過去作キャラクターやアイテムの配信など、通信要素も充実。\n<br>さらに、本編シナリオとは関係のない追加マップとエピソードを有料の追加コンテンツとして配信します。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/43d3a5ea6f730b6a047d30d73c8439aad91051ad8ed0f186b6afce4deedcedfa.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/dmma4Lm.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/uECsBJ8.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5855, '0004000000132300', 'CTR-N-JVHP', 'VAN HELSING SNIPER ZX100', 'EUR', 55630692, 'eshop', '50010000023395', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/3ea703d37eb0dcb3b52cf4674236375d28f71a2c72047359d1ec53f8bc915879.jpg', 'If you like sniper arcade games and\nhunting vampires, there''s nothing\nbetter than reincarnating as the best\nVampire exterminator of all time: Van\nHelsing!!!\n<br/><br/>\nTake aim in the most natural way\nthere is with your Nintendo 3DS™.\nWith the motion sensor, turn your\nNintendo 3DS™ into a mortal\ncrossbow against the Vampires.\n<br/><br/>\nIf your hand trembles a bit, don''t\nworry: the option of slowing down\ntime will help you aim with greater\nprecision during difficult moments, as\nwell as finding hidden Vampires with a\nspecial filter.\n<br/><br/>\nSearch, aim and fire with resolve on\nall the blood-thirsty Vampires that are\nstalking humans in London, and face\nthe terrifying Bosses.\n<br/><br/>\nYou can also unlock a survival\nminigame if you earn the cursed score\nof 6 6 6 (pts).', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/I5IC9br.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5856, '00040000000c5c00', 'CTR-N-MBAP', 'The 3D Machine Series: Episode 3', 'EUR', 28797748, 'eshop', '50010000012621', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/76445145df11e7f312e5ee23a65860905876326bd45ab8ea88f2c8ac70fa7109.jpg', 'Our monster-hunting duo travels deep\ninto the jungle to find a terrifying\ntarantula! Unfortunately the hunter\nbecomes the prey and the professor\ngets caught in a web of horror! It''s up\nto Igor to save the day.\n<br/><br/>\nLength 2:30 min', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/bc1ce02521266806eab433f1e4e12ebe4d0ec659c5a30372b43ab34c85177b2c.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/0UZKZqp.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/cpaX296.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(5857, '0004000000062200', 'CTR-P-ASNP', 'Sonic Generations™', 'EUR', 686865252, 'eshop', '50010000007746', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/087d2ad692be0c936d5fa02a1708df8c52e7857f85e35200c40971c3f9609d83.jpg', 'Sonic’s universe is thrown into chaos\nwhen a mysterious new power sends\nSonic back in time. Whilst there,\nSonic runs into a younger version of\nhimself! Now they must team up to\ndefeat their enemies, save their\nfriends, and find out who is behind\nthis diabolical deed.<br>\n<br>\nSonic Generations allows players to\nplay as both Classic and Modern\nSonic - taking advantage of their\nunique abilities. Master Classic\nSonic’s spin dash, and grind and\nboost as Modern Sonic as you run\nthrough levels created exclusively for\nthe Nintendo 3DS console.<br>\n<br>\nThe Nintendo 3DS version also\nincludes additional bonus stages, as\nwell as the exclusive 2 player versus\nmode - beat your friends and win the\nultimate bragging rights! You can also\nuse Street Pass to collect new\ncontent and unlock bonus material\nthroughout the game!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/Yi5fCKS.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
