(6057, '0004000000117d00', 'CTR-N-JLQP', 'Rubik''s® Cube', 'EUR', 88329060, 'eshop', '50010000040624', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b77346f2aef4bd1c83c614b185aba20168829686952807075b6db0e5d10c0c50.jpg', 'The official Rubik’s Cube game is\nhere!\n<br/><br/>\nPlay anywhere, anytime on the most\nauthentic digital representation of the\nRubik’s Cube available. Rubik''s Cube\nis a 3-D combination puzzle invented\nin 1974 by Hungarian sculptor and\nprofessor of architecture Ernő Rubik.\n<br/><br/>\nGame Features:\n<br/>\n-Intuitive touch controls\n<br/>\n-Cube 2x2x2 and Cube 3x3x3\n<br/>\n-Solver\n<br/>\n-Camera Capture\n<br/>\n-Internet rankings\n<br/><br/>\nThe game is developed under the\nlicense of the Rubik''s Brand Ltd.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/366eYfi.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
