(6059, '0004000000182700', 'CTR-N-BZEP', 'Zero Escape: Zero Time Dilemma', 'EUR', 1254026084, 'eshop', '50010000040699', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/9f7a81eba540c877c47f049d18da35fab30edfa15fefa4c70eb728e9312a2d24.jpg', 'Zero Escape: Zero Time Dilemma features diabolic new puzzles and fully animated story sections that push the boundaries of interactive storytelling! Newcomers and familiar faces round out a robust cast of characters while English and Japanese voice over options flesh out the narrative. Multiple endings and non linear story mechanics will keep you coming back for more!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/VtnEjdx.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6060, '000400000018bc00', 'CTR-N-KNSE', 'The Battle Cats POP!', 'USA', 455867236, 'eshop', '50010000040735', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6f74ae56b061c310cab44e47671e6670a0fc72f5eb85bc696275134db9f2a50e.jpg', 'Rampage across the globe with weird ''n wild Cats in an exciting but straight-forward tower defense adventure!\n<br>\nCollect 100s of fightin'' Cats to power up your army, take down bizarre and hilarious enemies and win glorious treasure!\n<br>\n<br>Super Simple Battle System\n<br>Just tap on the Cat you want to join the fight! Oh, and maybe fire the Cat Cannon once or twice. Take down the enemy base before the baddies can destroy yours!\n<br>\n<br>Super Simple Levelling System\n<br>Use the XP you get from clearing stages to train your Cats! Once they hit level 10, it''s time to EVOLVE!\n<br>\n<br>Super Simple Fun!\n<br>Collect treasure sets to create powerful items and boost your powers! \n<br>Go to the Capsule Machine to collect rare and exotic Cats(?)!!\n<br>Battle your friends with the 3DS-exclusive Versus mode to unlock even more cool rewards!\n<br>\n<br>Perfect for Casual Play! Fun for all ages, anyone (and their cat too!) can enjoy the "Battle Cats"!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/xUO9npu.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6061, '000400000005b300', 'CTR-N-JE4J', '[E3出展映像 3D版] どうぶつの森（仮称）', 'JPN', 23558452, 'eshop', '50010000006880', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b71bc81c84bda1ac45b70bb662566e8c5cbc2add8b6d2d4d01e3c647103975d3.jpg', 'このソフトは米国時間2011年6月7日にロサンゼルスで開催された E3（Electronic Entertainment Expo)で公開した映像を3Dでご覧いただけるダウンロードソフトです。\n本ソフトの配信は2011年6月28日で終了します。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/66eb60837bbdb898c92a1b809d1cea7747444260e51dfd401e4eceac9790557b.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/QycBY4b.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/abG5xSg.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6062, '000400000f700000', 'KTR-N-CAFJ', 'Newニンテンドー3DS専用 Xenoblade ゼノブレイド', 'JPN', 3666156388, 'eshop', '50010000030235', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c3f87bf315b922837e077fdce0fd3d8e5eef003f6c8329dd9f827937360be80f.jpg', 'SFとファンタジーが融合するWiiのRPG『ゼノブレイド』を、Newニンテンドー3DS専用ソフトにリメイク。ストーリー、サウンド、フィールド探索、バトルシステム、やりこみ要素、全てが圧倒的なボリュームで制作されたRPGが、手軽にいつでもプレイできます。\n<br>\n<br>遥か彼方まで広がる巨神と機神のフィールドには様々な敵が存在し、遭遇するとシームレスにバトル開始。敵の背後や側面に自由に移動しながら“アーツ”と呼ばれる技を繰り出して戦います。\n<br>\n<br>立体視対応やCスティックでのスムーズなカメラ操作、下画面でのステータスやミニマップ表示などNewニンテンドー3DSに合わせた調整を行い、ゲーム内に登場する3Dモデル、サウンドが楽しめる「コレクション」モードも新たに追加されています。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/909c81827dc8732c564e478f3145c773e33b01fc9945d2e1c551a45ffaa4c17e.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/lFRGtq9.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/PrpGYXb.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6063, '00040000000f4a00', 'CTR-N-ASXE', 'Secret Mysteries in New York', 'USA', 92916580, 'eshop', '50010000017916', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c66f93a660e080c88b515af440809b68eba795fdd857e7b1a2bfb8f76b4a401a.jpg', '1920: When a politician is found murdered in a local park, the police make the unconventional decision to ask Oscar Gaebelein, a young forensic scientist, for help.\n<br><br>\nMotivated by his desire to prove his value to the investigating team, Oscar throws himself headfirst into the investigation. However, very soon he and his colleagues discover that this first murder is only the beginning of something much more sinister.\n<br><br>\nHelp Oscar to find the killer in this thrilling hidden object game.\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/fn4qDP2.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6064, '000400000016ee00', 'CTR-N-KASE', 'ASH', 'USA', 183901028, 'eshop', '50010000040222', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d401e908574e3dacb49937cdcbf68182fe3a7b2857d00331aea3409bf734aa6e.jpg', 'Ash is a classic turn-based RPG, featuring a massive, fully-realized world with lush visuals, and a wonderfully compelling story. \n<br><br>\nThese are strange days for Aghaus. By order of the Magistrate, the Royal Guard is to assemble for deployment in two days’ time. It has been years since I last left the capital, and further still that I can remember such a command being issued! But what need is there for a Royal Guard, when no King sits upon the throne? Though my oath binds me to his service, the Magistrate is not my liege. He rules in the absence of a rightful heir. \n<br><br>\nMy men await their orders; they too are uneasy. It is for their sake that I stay my tongue, and place my faith in the Almighty that my fears are unfounded. \n<br><br>\nTomorrow, we make for the East. ', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/yklxBwm.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6065, '0004000000124000', 'CTR-N-JWPE', 'The Keep', 'USA', 191740772, 'eshop', '50010000025696', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/642da07320cb57960fd6fb25526007a8e84d1ccf52a54298b4a7e15cc3e149c9.jpg', 'Enter the Keep as an unsung hero on a quest to destroy the nefarious wizard Watrys. Explore the subterranean depths in this first-person dungeon crawler featuring real-time combat, a unique rune magic system, exploration, and puzzle solving.\n<br><br>\nThis game will awaken memories of what made old-school RPG dungeons so much fun to play while you fight, hunt for hidden treasures, and avoid deadly traps. Get to know your enemies, find their weaknesses, and crush them. Experiment with magic to discover powerful spells.\n<br><br>\nOnly the strongest will survive.\n<br><br>\nTo defeat the seemingly undefeatable Watrys, you will need to level up your character and find powerful armor and weapons. The game controls were designed with a stylus in mind so mastering both sword and magic is a fun and intuitive experience.\n<br><br>\nDo you have what it takes to stand against such evil? Then don’t procrastinate and enter. The Keep awaits you ...', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/xot1VtJ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6066, '000400000018e800', 'CTR-N-KCAP', 'BOXBOXBOY!™', 'EUR', 95312740, 'eshop', '50010000040377', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d5fa280f4b8e52c04f90b202d7b3db8d7446999fc318add413da9d0b14f5b70d.jpg', 'It’s time to think outside the box once again. Our boxy hero, Qbby, has a new power that lets him create TWO sets of boxes. He’ll put every box to use to survive perilous traps across more than 120 puzzling levels. Learn new tricks and box formations to get past obstacles like switches, spikes and even lasers! If you’ve played the critically-acclaimed first game, BOXBOY!, every costume earned can be carried over into BOXBOXBOY!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/i11og6d.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6067, '00040000000c5900', 'CTR-N-JF4E', 'Fishdom H2O: Hidden Odyssey', 'USA', 89701220, 'eshop', '50010000015053', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/c13742f3ef8f4985a596de46a7683066a1a6e24e1772c1a1abdaac14a3857406.jpg', 'Help Jennifer, a young marine biologist, win the Best Aquarium Award. Dive to the bottom of the sea and find various hidden items in numerous eye-teasing locations. Get cash for them to buy cute sea creatures and beautiful ornaments to create three unique aquariums. Choose from tons of accessories and supplies to make the life of your exotic swimming pets fun and comfortable. Become a genuine aquarist, polish your design skills and win trophies in this dazzling hidden object spin-off of the original Fishdom™.\n<br><Br>\nUnderwater hidden object fun<Br>\nOver 1000 cool items to find<Br>\n3 themed aquariums in stereoscopic 3D<Br>\nInteractive and customizable environment<Br>\nTons of accessories and decorations<Br>', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/rP3iTsf.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6068, '00040000000c1100', 'CTR-N-AM8E', 'Murder on the Titanic', 'USA', 83516260, 'eshop', '50010000012608', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f84388d6b7daf3ca78293869579a16801c2aedc3b7ecf40ace079e38d6a7aa4b.jpg', 'It is 1912, and a fabulous voyage on the Titanic awaits you. As assistant to globetrotter Professor Jacob Larsson, you board that breathtaking ship to experience a wonderful passage to New York.\n<br><br>\nYet early in the evening of April 14th, Captain Smith unexpectedly requests Larsson''s help. Deep within the bowels of the mighty Titanic, the body of a stoker had been discovered. Now it is up to you to solve this murder.\n<br><br>\n50 faithfully depicted scenes on board the luxurious Titanic<br>\nLots of tricky mini-games for pondering and puzzling<br>\nA gripping story with numerous tasks and puzzles over six extensive chapters', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ObRv4Ft.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6069, '00040000000dde00', 'CTR-N-ADHE', 'Mystery Case Files Dire Grove', 'USA', 209132388, 'eshop', '50010000021514', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7af3c5a42a89955349209e5e09cd113a19b34b89cf411a3c0ca937f3174f4497.jpg', 'The Celtic legend of Dire Grove has been passed down from generation to generation for centuries.\n<br><br>\nConsidered a fairytale, its telling was common at campfires and as a bedtime story meant to frighten small children into staying in their beds through the night. However, a recently unearthed artifact in the United Kingdom corroborates the legend and so begins a journey of survival for a small band of graduate students in the secluded resort of Dire Grove.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/86mKuYJ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6070, '00040000000ddf00', 'CTR-N-AAQE', 'Mystery Case Files® Ravenhearst', 'USA', 112155492, 'eshop', '50010000021513', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/06a6f5f0773e66b6bd6e7fef8b64be8a35ba696591a2c86ed73e1a1558777df3.jpg', 'Rumors surrounding the history of stately Ravenhearst Manor have circulated for decades.\n<br><br>\nThe recently acquired diary of Emma Ravenhearst may hold the key to unraveling the tale behind this unsettling place, yet the pages are missing. Players assume the role of Master Detective to unlock secrets held within Ravenhearst™, scouring a myriad of enchanting rooms in the manor for cleverly hidden clues. Locating and assembling diary pages helps tell the story of the house and, ultimately, unlock the mystery.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/bmnz1a7.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6071, '00040000000c2100', 'CTR-N-JBGE', 'Witch’s Cat', 'USA', 50531172, 'eshop', '50010000013171', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/8dbe46f23ad1ef3572d2988ec1588885f29bf81ea73e5dcb4cf07cf2a77708e2.jpg', 'A spin-off from the Rabi Laby series, in the previous adventure, the Queen sent her precious minions, the Cheshire Cats, to capture Alice and Rabi. Shortly, after they were captured, a Cheshire Cat named Alicia, became curious of Alice and instinctually knew that Alice was a good person. Alicia, unknown to Alice and Rabi, helped them both escape from their imprisonment.\n<br><br>\nInspired by Alice, Alicia desired to become a human. The Queen learned of Alicia’s secret and banished her from her kingdom. \n<br><br>\nDubois a powerful witch with a questionable reputation and a foe of the Queen discovers Alicia and helped her escape. Dubois offers her assistance to transform Alicia to a human. Alicia, well aware that she is no longer welcomed in Wonderland, and with her deep desire to become a human, reluctantly accepted her proposal, despite Dubois’s reputation.\n<br><br>\nTogether Alicia and Dubois set out on an ambitious journey to escape Wonderland and travel to the human world. ', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ZLkOzJD.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6072, '000480044b50534a', 'TWL-N-KPSJ', 'ファンタシースターZERO Mini', 'JPN', 15733556, 'dsiw', '50010000005536', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/612a1c360e21acebe8778483257273d5493043f718da2754c3644b716835ae8f.jpg', 'ファンタシースターZERO MiniはニンテンドーDS用ソフト「ファンタシースターZERO」をアレンジした、いつでもどこでも遊べる本格派3Dアクションゲームです。敵を倒しながら渓谷を進み、再奥にいるドラゴン・レイバーン撃破までのスコアを競います。DSワイヤレス通信を使って、最大4人でビジュアルチャットを使用しながらの協力プレイも楽しめます。繰り返し冒険することで腕をみがき、みんなでスコアを競うことができます。\n\n複数人で遊ぶ場合には、人数分の本ソフトとDSi本体が必要です。\nまた、ニンテンドーDS用ソフト「ファンタシースターZERO」との通信はできません。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/dce77bbea2591be90b82e0fd8750fec8aa41c84b03ce3fbf0c089df2ba883a4a.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/U1IJEwc.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/ZKdSsdE.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6073, '0004000000148500', 'CTR-N-KC2P', 'The Legend of Dark Witch - Chronicle 2D ACT', 'EUR', 138009444, 'eshop', '50010000028195', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/0b730f6c8112b3b30f5105f8487f2ce3977280b4a12847a36daca40b20d9e1e4.jpg', 'Syega Crystals gave their powers to\nthe people of the world, but\nsomebody has stolen all of them.\n<br/><br/>\nAfter all the Syega crystals are\nmissing, the world plunges into\ndarkness. As the dark witch Zizou,\nyou must retrieve the missing Syega\nCrystals.\n<br/><br/>\nThe Legend of Dark Witch is a 2D\nplatform action game. Zizou can learn\nnew attacks by defeating bosses. She\nwill need every one of those attacks if\nshe is going to save the world.\n<br/><br/>\nOther Features:\n<br/>\nA magical world beautifully depicted\nthrough in-game graphics.\n<br/>\nZizou''s abilities can collect Tres in\nbattle, which she can later use to\nupgrade her abilities.\n<br/>\nDiverse levels that provide a fair\nchallenge.\n<br/>\nAdditional bonuses that reward those\nwho replay the game.\n<br/>\n3 difficulty modes.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/iVpUSrI.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6074, '0004000000186300', 'CTR-N-KMJP', 'The Legend of Dark Witch 2', 'EUR', 464882532, 'eshop', '50010000039418', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/cef514de36af651956a3827a15bd5ac59c3cac1e64bf455c245e2a1e905d1e46.jpg', 'Created by indie games company\nINSIDE SYSTEM in 2014, Legend of\nthe Dark Witch 2 is a 2D action story\nsequel to the "Legend of the Dark\nWitch for 3DS".\n<br/><br/>\nTrue to its predecessor, Legend of\nthe Dark Witch 2 retains its simple\ncontrols and enough challenges to\nsatisfy the completist.\n<br/><br/>\nGame system\n<br/><br/>\nPlayers have 8 stages to choose\nfrom and must use SHOTs to make\ntheir way through a variety of\nobstacles to reach the boss enemy.\n<br/><br/>\nWithin each stage there are hidden\n"Pura Syega" which are helpful to\npower up player characters.\n<br/><br/>\nNew Features\n<br/><br/>\n・Increased number of stages to\nchoose from\n<br/><br/>\n・Allows finer customization for player\nstats using "Tres"\n<br/><br/>\n・"Technical skills" can be customized\nnot only to increase power, but add\nabilities as well\n<br/><br/>\n・New "Forbidden" items added for a\nwider variety of game play', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/nqmlH6H.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6075, '000400000014f700', 'CTR-N-KDKP', 'Demon King Box', 'EUR', 156253028, 'eshop', '50010000025955', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/ddce28c88fb399ad4486b5914b2926d349c4719408adbf76b8fff086a1956b46.jpg', 'Demon King Box mixes real-time\nstrategy with classic RPG gameplay.\nGather demons and heroes to join aid\nyour quest. Multiple types of minions\ncan be gathered not only by\nconquering, but also by researching\nminions. The demon heroes can\nenhance the demon legion with their\nunique skills. Demons level up and get\nstronger not only by victory, but also\nby feeding them with their favourite\nfood.\n<br/><br/>\nOther features:\n<br/><br/>\n- Intense battles that can only be won\nthrough strength and skill\n<br/><br/>\n- Expansive demon world with diverse\nlocales to be explored\n<br/><br/>\n- Various demon heroes reveal their\npersonality through captivating\nvoice-over work\n<br/><br/>\n- A gripping storyline\n<br/><br/>\n- Gallery and achievements offer\nadditional content for the dedicated\ngamer\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/lhOjNm2.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6076, '000400000018f500', 'CTR-N-KNSP', 'The Battle Cats POP!', 'EUR', 455879524, 'eshop', '50010000040700', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e8404f84875549d65e77229afe39ccad7b0bf5c520f07ef99dac5b4f45a33830.jpg', 'The tower-defense hit Battle Cats has\nachieved over 23,000,000\ndownloads worldwide for smartphones\nand tablets, and is now bursting onto\na new handheld scene with a\nNintendo 3DS™ release! Why be\ncontent with conquering the planet\nwhen the galaxy is yours to\ndominate?!<br />\nPlus, The Battle Cats POP!\nintroduces the hotly anticipated VS\nMode feature. Battle your friends and\nfamily for cool rewards!\n<br/><br />\nSpecial Features for the 3DS<br />\n・3D Battle Sequences<br />\n・No additional in-app purchases<br />\n・Pick up Uber Rare units from\nCapsules\n', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/YItORDk.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6077, '0004000000117200', 'CTR-N-JPKJ', 'プチコン3号 SmileBASIC', 'JPN', 12450660, 'eshop', '50010000027755', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/2980c1f13a2cd252d3c62ad65b44d4c4829f12303a7693a1a0f277daf7a83c10.jpg', '『プチコン3号 SmileBASIC』は、プログラム言語「BASIC(ベーシック)」です。\n<br>BASICはプログラム学習用に開発された初心者向けの言語。\n<br>起動したらいきなりプログラムを入力! そのまま実行! と、難しいことを考えずにプログラム作りが楽しめます。\n<br>\n<br>■作りこめる命令が盛りだくさん\n<br>･飛び出す絵や文字!\n<br>･各種センサーからの情報を取得\n<br>･マイクからの録音と再生\n<br>･ローカル通信を使った対戦\n<br>･線や円や塗りつぶし等の描画命令\n<br>･MMLによる作曲\n<br>･漢字を含む日本語表示にも対応\n<br>\n<br>プログラム初心者向けの説明を強化。\n<br>熟練向けにインラインヘルプも搭載。\n<br>ゲームから実用アプリまで好みのプログラムが作れます。\n<br>\n<br>■便利なツール\n<br>･スマイルツール(SEやキャラ番号確認)\n<br>･ペイントツール(キャラや背景などを描く)\n<br>･アニメーションツール(パラパラアニメ登録)\n<br>･マップツール(タイルを並べてマップ作成)\n<br>･波形ツール(サンプリングと波形作成)\n<br>\n<br>■豊富なサンプル\n<br>･さまざまなシーンで使えるキャラや背景の画像\n<br>･100種類以上の効果音や40種類以上のBGM\n<br>･BASICを覚えるためのシンプルなプログラム\n<br>･命令ごとの実行結果を確かめられる技術サンプル\n<br>･高度な技術で作られたゲームサンプル\n<br>\n<br>他の人が作ったプログラムを見て改造することで、楽しみながら技術を手に入れることができます。', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f49410b4d2b6a6aad9af7fa35f52a6dd61a5afc8de12a863aeda8f49290ea81b.jpg', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/w5xBixt.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/RbSyuN7.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6078, '0004000e00186300', 'CTR-U-KMJP', 'The Legend of Dark Witch 2: Update', 'EUR', 15661876, 'update', '50010000040497', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/98d6b198e6ddbae5a15d069c56a5b94a1676bce0b250553a57b216e4a3b45a7e.jpg', 'Fixed a glitch that caused some\nbosses'' attack to have no effect.', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/5f13e3e4185b3ccfd27fddc5a9e4e7d63aa4eb651016bb86fffc8a6f1933a108.jpg', -1, 'http://i.imgur.com/hXrCtXj.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/US4oQsQ.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6079, '000480044b4d5245', 'TWL-N-KMRE', 'My Farm', 'USA', 5765940, 'dsiw', '50010000002942', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f1baba70837b227ef82e42734580d20e7778a11bc15f8646c14338cb690a87be.jpg', 'My Farm is a livestock farming simulation game!\n\nAt the beginning, all you own is an empty field, a few pennies and a single little hen... You need to feed the hen and take care of it! Then your hen will lay eggs which can be sold. And with this money, you can buy new animals at the Farmers’ Market and purchase equipment from the shopkeeper. Little by little as your farm builds up, you will unlock certain bonuses (wind turbine, rooster, guard dog, tractor, etc.). You will be able to exchange your animals with your friends who play My Farm or My Exotic Farm!\n\n• 6 kinds of animals to customize\n• Take care of your animals (food, clean, health, etc.)\n• Many farm improvements to buy and bonuses to collect\n• Exchange of animals and products with other players', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/WidxH23.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6080, '00040000000f2c00', 'CTR-N-JAJE', 'Brunch Panic', 'USA', 102542180, 'eshop', '50010000017073', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/d7c99debcaf3ea49d8e4983b72f7abedfabd3cd2681759a6e416f4c911a5eec0.jpg', 'Ever dreamed of running your own food truck? Or traveling to the places you''ve always dreamed about? \n<br><Br>\nHere''s the story of Bonnie, a young bright-eyed girl, with a talent for cooking and a love of travel and adventure. One fateful birthday, her grandfather presented her with a gift that combined her two passions. A brunch truck! And so began her dream adventure, traveling all over the world with one brunch spot at a time. \n<br><Br>\nWant to help Bonnie to cook her delicious brunch specials? Want to meet interesting people around the globe? Let''s jump in with Bonnie and start the brunch truck journey together! \n<br><Br>\nFeatures: <br>\nEasy to play food making dash game\n<Br><Br>\nFun filled chapters with 50 levels\n<Br><Br>\nFun and easy gameplay with storyline style tutorials\n<Br><Br>\nDiverse food creation and interesting levels challenging your speed and accuracy\n<Br><Br>\nMeet interesting people and travel to distant cities\n<Br><Br>\nAnd of course, cook up some brunch!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/oNpj5lm.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6081, '000400020018a401', 'CTR-T-BPJE', 'Rhythm Heaven Megamix Demo Version', 'USA', 66301952, 'demo', '50030000008406', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6082, '000480044b415145', 'TWL-N-KAQE', 'G.G Series NINJA KARAKURI DEN', 'USA', 2912052, 'dsiw', '50010000001025', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/7defebcdeb38507c0c2411cbb09c150e5a1d9fa72aa9e8c03a6c1520bb6d7e26.jpg', 'Jump and slash as a gravity-defying ninja in this acrobatic action game!\n\nControl a jumping ninja as he fights his way through a booby-trapped mansion. When your ninja touches a platform, it will automatically disappear and he will jump, making for pretty unstable footing! But where some see obstacles, a ninja sees opportunity. You will be forced to think on your feet, push your reflexes, and bend the very rules of physics to conquer your treacherous surroundings. Master the art of the dash, shuriken, and sword. Be a ninja.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/1dLoZ9p.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6083, '000480044b445845', 'TWL-N-KDXE', 'X-Scape™', 'USA', 16293684, 'dsiw', '50010000002082', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/6c99d2be6a71dcc3df52df117fe717ba6d1b94567696f44fc82787f99e5063e9.jpg', 'Your journey through the universe of X-Scape begins as you wake from 10 years of cryosleep, only to find yourself unexpectedly thrown into a fearsome battle against an evil empire bent on your destruction. You’ll travel to numerous planets in the Kiisa system and engage in a wide variety of challenges (including optional side quests) in your fight for answers…and survival.\nAt your command is VIXIV, an advanced battle tank able to deftly maneuver both on land and in the air and loaded with an array of formidable weapons. Also onboard, and ready to help with advice or upgrades to VIXIV’s abilities, is your highly capable support bot, VIX-529. To progress in your adventure, you’ll use the Touch Screen to pilot VIXIV in one of two modes: tunnel mode and free-movement mode. In tunnel mode, you navigate through narrow, dangerous tunnels that connect planets. Successful completion of tunnel mode opens free-movement mode, which allows you to freely roam the surface of planets and take up missions.\nPresented in 3-D with a stylishly retro graphic style, X-Scape combines continuous action with an epic story to create an experience sure to keep players on the edge of their seats!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/rT6sG81.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6084, '000480044b5a4f45', 'TWL-N-KZOE', 'GO Series Undead Storm', 'USA', 6231860, 'dsiw', '50010000009082', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/051c8022e156349f60732824d4a91e2039fe45794dddbef009be0a4e2cfc70bf.jpg', 'The explosive action is non-stop as you take the fight to the zombie hordes.\n\nSix months after a mysterious meteorite strike, the undead have awoken and are taking over the city. You’ll face wave after wave of killer zombies with only some serious firepower to protect you. Play solo or team up with your friends via DS Wireless Communications and take the fight to the shuffling hordes.\n\nSolo zombie slayers can find other survivors to join them as allies. In multiplayer mode, you can cooperate with up to three friends via DS Wireless Communications. They''ll have your back in the firefight against the undead, and can revive you if your health flatlines. Choose from four player characters and face down the zombie threat in a horrific hospital, a hazardous chemical plant, and the decimated downtown area. What lies behind this zombie epidemic? Only you can discover the truth...', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/4PU58rr.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6085, '000480044b4e5a45', 'TWL-N-KNZE', 'G.G Series Z•ONE', 'USA', 2583348, 'dsiw', '50010000003285', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e2a367ff34e55afded13e3101091baac9fab23345a14b2c5629faf941d3c9ffb.jpg', 'Breach enemy lines in this technical side-scrolling shooter!\n\nThe enemy has bolstered their defenses with a perilous fortress of blocks. Skillfully work your way around your surroundings and make use of pods that fire in eight directions to vanquish foes as you advance towards the heart of enemy territory. Each level features a unique landscape and varying difficulty, forcing you to adapt. Learn the art of quick evasion as some levels scroll faster than others, and master advanced shooting techniques such as shooting in the opposite direction.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/JCacWld.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6086, '000480044b424e45', 'TWL-N-KBNE', 'Galaxy Saver', 'USA', 4781876, 'dsiw', '50010000012862', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/14f42e9708d844652f97acdb30bf1695bc545523492ecd7c1751dd5cd939e1b1.jpg', 'Take on wave after wave of invading attacks as you protect the mothership from 360 degrees of enemy bombardment. Circle around the mothership to form a perimeter, blasting the incoming alien ships with guns and missiles as they swarm in from all directions. Blast everything in sight as the aliens attack with rush attacks, stealth attacks, swarms, and tracker beams, surrounding you from all directions.\n<br><br>Recruit partnership ships to help you fend off the invaders or team up with a friend using DS Wireless Communications. Hold off the hordes of aliens while your mothership recharges its warp drive in a series of steps that edge you closer to earth, where the final battle awaits.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/8OT0gQJ.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6087, '000480044b584745', 'TWL-N-KXGE', 'Abyss', 'USA', 4717364, 'dsiw', '50010000011526', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/82f2cc103a52eb64243951f157bddb113130eb642fc83fdf0845767397804472.jpg', 'Earth, 3024.\n\n Natural resources are scarce and the survival of the human race is in danger. Desperate to find new energy resources, the ASAN creates a biomechanical robot called Nep2no that is capable of withstanding extreme depths in the hope of finding new energy sources. After many years of exploration, a new energy source is found, code named "Gaia".\n\n Your mission will be to find the "Gaia" energy stones by exploring the depths. To do so, you must control Nep2no by counteracting gravity and the surrounding darkness with the aid of a Light that will go out little by little.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/9CbfdoN.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6088, '000480044b4e5945', 'TWL-N-KNYE', 'Moke Moke', 'USA', 3743540, 'dsiw', '50010000013293', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f631b348dde395d961bf0b2ab35b94e5945f119c85784c966746fdecc330b451.jpg', 'Take control of a Moke forest creature and compete in a series of frantic 4 player head-to-head games to see who can collect the most treasure scattered throughout the forest. \n<br><br>\nFlap around the forest picking up treasure and taking it to the goal as fast as you can. The Moke who retrieves the most treasure before the time runs out is the winner. Use your attack to fend off other rival Moke and to also steal their treasure.\n<br><Br>\nAll games are played with four Moke at once with the CPU taking the role of the other Moke in Single Player. In Multiplayer, up to 4 friends can go head-to-head via DS Wireless Communications. \n<br><Br>\nChoose from a host of different game rules, levels and settings to create dozens of different game variations. Players can also compete in Battle Cup competitions that contain various mixes of game rules for each round.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/6Owl7zx.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6089, '000480044b455745', 'TWL-N-KEWE', 'Earthworm Jim', 'USA', 12064564, 'dsiw', '50010000006947', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/b8c5c6b8951babc69e1a87759818d58c754ae65e59a5089d6c0a6bc100d65777.jpg', 'The all-time classic action platformer you used to play on Super NES is back in a remake that keeps the essence and core gameplay of the original, plus a never-before-seen feature, exclusively on the Nintendo DSi system.\n\nPlay as the grooviest earthworm in the galaxy. Run, gun, swing from hooks with your head, launch cows, bungee jump, rocket through speed levels and more, in a dozen crazy universes that offer huge gameplay possibilities. Earn bonuses with facial-expression-based challenges that track your face using the inner camera. Put on a smile, frown or make a variety of other faces to mimic Jim.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/25b7CaS.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6090, '000400000f702a00', 'KTR-N-UAPE', 'Super Ghouls''n Ghosts™', 'USA', 5585764, 'eshop', '50010000040737', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/574ddc81d35faae0329325ad2deab10a45145e0e38ae4f430d300ef618de519d.jpg', 'The third game in the legendary Ghosts ''n Goblins series of video games, Super Ghouls ''n Ghosts follows Arthur in another quest to rescue the princess, his fair maiden and damsel in distress at large. Players take control of Arthur and defeat the creatures of the night to save the day once more. Discover what glory awaits those brave enough to take on the armies of Super Ghouls ''n Ghosts.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/pkHW2qF.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6091, '000400000f702800', 'KTR-N-UANE', 'MEGA MAN™ 7', 'USA', 7076708, 'eshop', '50010000040676', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/180c9a77b91c5a1b43349f5f0a8b82e64094a5fa8a7bc3f7846ea6187ac993d7.jpg', 'Dr. Wily knew that one day his plans would fail him. But as the world cheered at his capture, the nefarious scientist stowed four robots in his lab, set to activate after six months of no communication from their master. Now the robots have started a rampage in the city, which serves as the perfect distraction for Dr. Wily to make his getaway. \n<br><br>\nBut Mega Man and his trusty sidekick, Rush, are hot on his trail...and so are Bass and Treble? Who are these mysterious companions? Jump, power up, and blast your way through robotic enemies, and send Dr. Wily back to prison where he belongs!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/GwD7oYh.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6092, '000400020016d601', 'CTR-T-KWHE', 'Witch & Hero 2 Demo', 'USA', 62058496, 'demo', '50030000008306', 'none', 'none', 'none', -1, 'none', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6093, '000400000018ee00', 'CTR-N-KCAE', 'BOXBOXBOY!™', 'USA', 94169956, 'eshop', '50010000040655', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/f0a662a5799ead57a259b74098be1f0089376be92b631de29a2c34134320f13d.jpg', 'Available for pre-purchase and pre-load. With the new pre-load feature, you will be ready to play after a small update when the game launches on 6/30 9 a.m. (PDT). \n<br><br>\nBy clicking ‘Purchase,’ you agree that you will be charged in advance for the full purchase price of the title (plus applicable taxes), and that you cannot play the title before the launch date. This purchase price is non-refundable except to the extent required by law. \n<br><br>\nAn internet connection is required to receive the small update.\n<br><br>\nIt’s time to think outside the box once again. Our boxy hero, Qbby, has a brand-new power that lets him duplicate his blocky bod into TWO sets of boxes. He’ll put every box to use to survive perilous traps across 11+ worlds of puzzling levels. Learn new tricks and box formations to get past obstacles, like switches, spikes, and even lazers!\n<br><br>\nOnce you learn the ropes—erm, boxes—take on the bonus challenge world to beat levels using the Bunny or Ninja outfit with a lower box count. Medals overflowing your pockets? Take them to the shop to purchase new costumes, like the Robo-Suit, read humourous comics, or listen to the tunes of BOXBOXBOY! If you’ve played the first title, BOXBOY!, you can unlock many of those costumes too because almost every one can be used in BOXBOXBOY!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/B3MiJrD.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6094, '000400000010bd00', 'CTR-N-JLQE', 'Rubik''s® Cube', 'USA', 88107876, 'eshop', '50010000040736', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/12c6793133d9c502994f6db745d30ea4ba733ae927f51409580b3dcf215ff7cd.jpg', 'Play anywhere, anytime on the most authentic digital representation of the Rubik’s Cube available. Rubik''s Cube is a 3-D combination puzzle invented in 1974 by Hungarian sculptor and professor of architecture Ernő Rubik.\n<br>\n<br>Game Features:\n<br>Intuitive touch controls\n<br>Cube 2x2x2 and Cube 3x3x3\n<br>Solver\n<br>Camera Capture\n<br>Internet rankings\n<br>\n<br>The game is developed under the license of the Rubik''s Brand Ltd.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/1i3L1nz.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6095, '000400000019b400', 'CTR-N-KGWE', 'Gunslugs', 'USA', 19372900, 'eshop', '50010000040675', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/02a28dad405c4fef73b8470be0fd3e15fc6e16569125833f0438abb85bf69516.jpg', 'Gunslugs is a fast paced run and jump game with procedurally generated levels and a rogue-like permadeath element. You get one life, and the only way you can extend that is by running into the Voodoo priest selling continue statues.\n<br>\n<br>Unlock the roster of Gunslugs heroes as you go, and use them to advance your way to the gates of Hell to defeat the final boss.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/lNVrtc0.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6096, '0004000000183500', 'CTR-N-KS4E', 'Sssnakes', 'USA', 15297380, 'eshop', '50010000040560', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/e06aa1dd660bc98de33b2f8d3f5d75ced79bc01bea5126cf0a3e1bdbbf2377e3.jpg', 'Sssnakes is a new twist on the classic snake video game. It is an upgrade for modern times without giving up its essence.\n<br>\n<br>Go through the jungle to the inside of the temple, avoid the traps, move through intricate mazes and face other snakes.\n<br>\n<br>But above all, you will need to keep away from your biggest enemy... gluttony!\n<br>\n<br>Features:\n<br>Easy to play, hard to master.\n<br>Many levels with different objectives and enemies.\n<br>8-bit mode.\n<br>The ability to shoot provides new opportunities and strategies to get out of tough situations.\n<br>Online scoreboard to compete for the top score.\n<br>Tricks and hidden secrets to get the top score or to make the game easier.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/l9oQBfW.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
