(6099, '000400000009cb00', 'CTR-N-JSUP', 'Football Up 3D', 'EUR', 26114964, 'eshop', '50010000014895', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/27905cd874d5053a959fb755c2d3efab682e328c7b29ecf46c094e6943057680.jpg', 'Football Up 3D is a funny soccer\ngame that allows you total control of\nany of your team''s player''s actions:\nControl the ball, dribble and shoot\nwith effect to confuse the goalkeeper\nand score a goal!\n<br/><br/>\nThe ball has inertia and will move\nfreely over the field. Show your ability\nto control it and make short and long\npasses. Choose the height, effect and\npower before shooting at the goal.\n<br/><br/>\nBecome a football master and make\nyour rival defenders tremble!\n<br/><br/>\nEach country has its national team.\nYou can create your own team with\nthe in-game editor: give it the name\nyou like,choose its equipment and,\nmost importantly, play with your Mii™\nsaved on the Mii Maker™ of your\nNintendo 3DS™.\n<br/><br/>\nFeatures:\n<br/><br/>\n*Supports "Download Play", allowing\ntwo players to share a single copy of\nFootball Up 3D.\n<br/><br/>\n* Create your own teams using your\nMii.\n<br/><br/>\n* Full stereoscopic 3D.\n<br/><br/>\n* Total control of height, direction\nand effect in each pass and shot you\nmake.\n<br/><br/>\n* Play the World Cup!', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/ECKF8AY.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6100, '000480044b415556', 'TWL-N-KAUV', 'Nintendo Countdown Calendar', 'EUR', 4586292, 'dsiw', '50010000001717', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/58209242d8df071a8b899d50777d4c12215b695c864ea6146307f8f5ebce4ea6.jpg', 'These days we all lead increasingly\nbusy lives. Nintendo Countdown\nCalendar is an easy, fun way to keep\ntrack of not only urgent appointments\nbut also to remind you about life''s\nsmall yet important tasks.<br>\n<br>\nYou can organise your day-to-day\n''Events'' by category, selecting from\neither School (such as trips,\nhomework deadlines), Work\n(meetings, projects) or Everyday\n(doctor''s appointments, holidays).\nYou can even add your own Custom\nEvents using handwritten notes via the\nTouch Screen. What''s more, each time\nyou start the calendar, a useful\nreminder tells you how many days are\nleft until your added event!<br>\n<br>\nThe software can be used until 2099,\nincluding important dates like public\nholidays (some countries only, not all\nholidays) and phases of the moon.\nYou can even leave yourself a quick\nwritten reminder which will appear the\nnext time you use the software. With\nNintendo Countdown Calendar, you\nwill have no excuse to forget another\nbirthday!', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/df720e07e30aec454532dfefec9c7df83de870db048c0bd7767e941970e18800.jpg', 2, 'http://i.imgur.com/42suj2o.jpg', 'http://i.imgur.com/FN4D7ZW.jpg', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47'),
(6101, '000480044b555345', 'TWL-N-KUSE', 'Paul''s Shooting Adventure 2', 'USA', 5383988, 'dsiw', '50010000010070', 'https://kanzashi-ctr.cdn.nintendo.net/i/4c13262d7a4922496e097e0aea0d7cd8ca236ce2f53fbfaceb8258a585fc0399.jpg', 'Paul and his twin brother join forces to smash the Insectians in this explosive sequel.\n\nThe player controls Paul and his brother, twins of a super hero family who was born with innate super powers. The two brothers have the ability to take flight and attack with powerful projectile energy. However, most importantly, they are both gifted with the ability to take the form and seize the weaponry from fallen enemies.\n\nThe Insectians have vowed revenge for their defeated ally – the Oceanians. Paul is once again summoned to fight an alien invasion force bent of retribution, but this time Paul is not alone. It’s up to Paul and his twin brother to use their combined powers and weapons obtained from the aliens to fight back and smash the Insectians.', 'none', 3, 'http://i.imgur.com/T5r1BQP.jpg', 'none', 0, '2016-07-11 20:08:47');
